(14, 'com.idanapps.myalbum', 'MyAlbum For Facebook', 'Idan Yael', 'NOTE TO ALL USERS: If you set the app visibility in Facebook to be lower than public it WILL effect the albums list the app can upload to. To ensure the app will be able to upload to any album, set the app visibility to public.<p>NEW! Pro version of MyAlbum is out. The pro version is ad-free and has the ability to Tag photos. <br>If you like the app, show your support and grab the paid version here: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://goo.gl/daa5H&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEHnzbKOUmGnFiwckCkCUqpPABilA" target="_blank">http://goo.gl/daa5H</a><p>Thank you all for making this app the #1 Android Market app for Downloading/Uploading Facebook photos !!!<p>Downloading and Uploading pictures from and to Facebook just got easier.<p>With MyAlbum you can:<p>1. Download a Facebook entire photo album with just one click.<br>2. Download all Facebook photos you were tagged in.<br>3. Share multiple photos to Facebook. Upload any number of photos to an existing or new album.<br>4. PRO version ONLY - Tag uploaded photos<p>What you CANNOT do:<p>1. Download your friends albums - Not allowed by policy (It&#39;s not yours!)<br>2. Choose specific photos to download inside a Facebook album (it&#39;s all or nothing).<br>3. You cannot upload files that are not located on your device. meaning, picasa photos that are synced and if you have any other app the syncs your pictures by view and not by the actual files, it will not work. To upload the files should be on your phone storage. (Like this app does...)<p>Instructions for downloading:<p>1. Open the app and login to your Facebook account. When asked for permissions click [allow]. (you have to allow the permission so the app can access your Facebook account and stored media).<br>2. In the album list, use the check box to choose the Facebook albums you would like to download.<br>3. Touching [download] will start the process. When finished you can see the downloaded photos by accessing your image gallery.<p>Instructions for uploading:<p>1. Open your image gallery or any other image/files browser of your choice.<br>2. Check the images you would like to upload (one or many).<br>3. Use the [share] option from the menu to choose MyAlbum as your sharing app.<br>4. Choose the Facebook album you would like to upload the photos to or create a new one.<br>5. The upload begins. You can use the [hide] button to continue the upload at the background, a notification will pop once the upload completed.<p><br>If there are features you would like to see in the app that are currently missing, send me an email.<br>I&#39;m always interested in upgrading the app and adding more cool stuff. <p>Please note, I cannot answer your comments here in the market.<br>Leaving comments about bugs and/or complaints about the features will only downrate the app. Instead, send me an email with your issue and i&#39;ll do my best to help.<p>Don&#39;t forget, If you like it - rate it.<p>This app is not developed, sponsored or related to/by Facebook corporation in any way.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.idanapps.myalbum', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/9je9CVF0m8Y-Qgg0xEpsmpf3gP1Ay8Xg-wcajXeVw4YQiiXgdh_gJije6AmAAdlT5Dru', 4.31, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '1,000,000+', ''),
(15, 'com.wapmx.telephony.banter', 'Seen: Video calls for Facebook', 'OpenMarket', 'Want to video call your Facebook friends? The OpenMarket Seen application lets you make high quality video and voice calls over Wi-Fi or 3G to your Facebook friends and groups. Better yet, these calls are FREE worldwide (mobile operator permitting and data rates may apply).<br> <br>By downloading, you agree to the Seen End User License Agreement - please see <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://jointheseen.com/eula&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGdCuZgboWdb89F_vL1dDOAtRWzNg" target="_blank">http://jointheseen.com/eula</a> for details.<br> <br>N.B. Seen on Android is currently in PUBLIC BETA.  Please help us improve the app by reporting any bugs: press your phone&#39;s menu button whilst on the main app screen and selecting &#39;Submit Bug Report&#39;, clearly explaining what went wrong.  Thanks!<p>Seen lets you: <br>* Make video or HD Audio voice calls without using cellular voice minutes <br>* Call any Facebook friends or groups worldwide <br>* Share your visual experiences with your friends <p>Making a call is simple — just log in to Seen with your Facebook account and tap on a friend&#39;s profile picture to place a call. If they don&#39;t have Seen, you can invite them to use it through the app. <p>Seen also includes privacy settings so that you can choose who can call you. <p>See friends from the past and share your experiences with them! It&#39;s a great way to connect and talk! <p>All you need is a Facebook account and an Android phone, iPhone 3GS or iPhone 4. Grab the app, tell your friends, and join the Seen!<p>Download now and enjoy! <p>--- <p>Seen is built using the OpenMarket Softphone Toolkit. Please visit <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://jointheseen.com/sdk&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEjpq4nWCk2B8N3dGzEQDrwwCASyg" target="_blank">http://jointheseen.com/sdk</a> if you&#39;d like to add Seen video/voice calling to your own app!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.wapmx.telephony.banter', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/3vUI6tUyVT9pkHSC3jWSk5RXqcIT7L2WudaLPv8KiI3ahMXWkjTxZRABSovMfARUwU4', 4.17, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'android.permission.CAMERA, android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO, android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS, android.permission.READ_LOGS, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, com.wapmx.telephony.banter.permission.C2D_MESSAGE'),
(16, 'air.com.fbvideochat.fbvideochat', 'TK Video chat for Facebook', 'Tk', 'TK Video chat for Facebook is not a copy of Facebook functions, but it&#39;s an extending with new possibilities which does not exist in an official version:<br>- free video chat with boys and girls from your friends list and also with other hot Facebook members<br>- watching profiles, photos, time lines, likes and friends lists of any Facebook member<br>- removing of language barriers by an auto translation function built-in group chat<br>So, those functions allow you to communicate with your existing friends and also meet and dating with many interesting strangers.<p>Spending time in group chat you can easily find many new friends. Have you ever thought how great it would be to have a cam to cam talk with people from different countries and discuss things you love or hate? And every time such meeting or dating didn&#39;t held because you speak only your native language? Your problem is solved! In live chat you can talk with strangers speaking any language without any limits. Messages in group chat are translated, so this time your meeting will be hot, successful and pleasant. <p>Why is TK Video chat for Facebook the best choice?<br>- Millions of girls and boys are using devices: Android, iPhone, BlackBerry, PC, MAC<br>- Thousands of people are available in messenger (IM)<br>- Hundreds of people are waiting for you in random chat<br>- A large number of hot functions allow you to have a fun with friends and strangers.<br>Have you already tested some free video chats like Skype, but were limited to talk only with people you know? Our cam to cam APP is different; it gives you freedom to talk with people you know and also find a new partner in the chat room full of people like you. You will fall in love with this APP!<p>Interaction with your Facebook profile:<br>- Creating of your personal profile on the basis of publicly available data<br>- Creating of photo galleries using your publicly available Facebook photos<br>- Facebook friends list<br>- Free live chat with Facebook friends<p>Interacting with other Facebook accounts:<br>- Profile Information<br>- Photos<br>- Likes<br>- Friends list<br>- Time line<br>- Video chat room<p>Additionally APP includes:<br>- Random video chat with all available users<br>- Video chat room for meetings just with friends.<br>- Private chat like Skype<br>- Creating photos and videos<br>- Searching for boys and girls by multiple criteria<br>- Friends list<br>- Instant messenger (IM)<p>Function of TK Video chat for Facebook:<br>- Broadcast of your webcam stream<br>- Partners webcam stream<br>- Public video chat<br>- Private video chat like Skype<br>- Friends only live chat<br>- Text messages<br>- Auto translation from 50 languages<br>- Messenger (IM)<br>- List of who is in chat<br>- People search<br>- Connecting with a random person<br>- Partners profile<br>- Photo sharing<p>Protection of chatters:<br>- Personal ban<br>- Report to administrators<br>- Matrix webcam monitoring<br>- Bad words filter (remove all adult erotic words)<br>- Personal filters: whose messages you can read, filtering level, groups of people, and filter by user sex<br>- Spam filters<p>In public chat is strongly prohibited:<br>- Showing erotic or nudity (naked parts of body)<br>- Sex conversations<br>- Going around bad words filter<br>- Spam<br>- Show contact information<br>Violation of those rules will kick you out from the cam to cam chat and remove your account. So, do not download this APP if you are planning to show nudity or looking just for erotic, love and sex. Administrators follow the chat and have zero tolerance for nudists and rules violators.<p>- You must be adult, at least 18 years old, for participating and dating in TK Video chat for Facebook APP. Read why here - <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.videochatforfacebook.com/parental_control&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGpbbxDUuRJ_vszfK6y-YdJ2RT5_A" target="_blank">http://www.videochatforfacebook.com/parental_control</a><p>Name &quot;TK Video chat for Facebook &quot; was approved by Facebook legal department. APP use Facebook API for developers and is able to access only public information which API allows (Age, Sex, Description and your public photos). APP cannot get access to your private details, password or any other personal information, because Facebook API for developers does not allow it!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.fbvideochat.fbvideochat', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/TLihAE_qRrRoBrs92p-QoMVoDb9Th9KJm3dj6BbYnnQIpaUkHltsoecNVgYyHtmhjZ2J', 3.83, 'COMMUNICATION', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'android.permission.CAMERA, android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO'),
(17, 'com.rockyou.horoscopes', 'Horoscopes for Facebook', 'horoscope.com', 'Written by the best and most experienced astrologers: <br>- Number 1 Horoscope on Facebook <br>- Over 4 million users monthly <br>- Over 14 million installs <p>Check daily your horoscope for today and tomorrow, your compatibility, your lucky number and your tarot card. <br>Receive a notification every day to remember to check out your horoscope. <p>Discover Horoscopes as they are meant to be.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.rockyou.horoscopes', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/UXulo8mTJG-1xdUIKUbZ0-z3pT6O65NnM2c52SsyyUYEMMUrYUaXN6OU2OwgMVoZaRE', 3.86, 'LIFESTYLE', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION'),
(18, 'com.adictiz.spacedogplus', 'Space Dog + | Facebook Game', 'Adictiz', 'Facebook players’ favorite dog got a facelift! Discover, or rediscover Space Dog, his new wacky items, his new missions system, and lots of new features which make the game even more fun to play! Shoot Space Dog as far as you can and travel through three exclusive worlds: the park, the beach, and the winter world!<br><br><br>PLAY TO SPACE DOG’S BEACH WORLD!<br>Unlock up to 60 new ultra-fun items:<br>- The ‘surf hat’ will help you to go through surf boards<br>- The water pistol fires Space Dog with breakneck speed  <br>- The sun cream gives you a crazy acceleration<br>- Unveil dozens of new accessories 100% made in Space Dog!<br><br><br>FACEBOOK CONNECT FOR EVEN MORE FUN!<br>Have fun with new exclusive tactile items and shoot Space Dog as far as as you can. <br>Invite and challenge your Facebook friends to upgrade your items even faster!<br>Exclusive: Connect with Facebook, challenge your mates, and win as many bouncy balloons as you have friends playing Space Dog +. Space Dog bounces on these balloons which stand for your friends’ scores, which help you to go even further and explode your score!<br><br><br>SHOW YOUR FACEBOOK FRIENDS WHO IS THE KING OF THE BEACH!<br>“Space Dog’s beach world is so much fun, I can’t stop playing!” – Christina<br>“I love Space Dog’s Facebook page! There are advice and tips to help me improve my shooting technique!” – Max<br>“Beating your friends at Space Dog is a real challenge! Every week I do a shoot or two so I don’t lose the vibe!” – Lee<br>“The beach world is my favorite! My tip: Challenge loads of friends and share your score on Facebook = more balloons = a better score!” – Tom<br><br><br>FUNCTIONS OF THE GAME<br>- A new, entirely free game<br>- New graphics<br>- 3 exclusive worlds: beach, park and winter<br>- Even more fun with 60 new items<br>- Challenge your friends and share your scores on Facebook<br><br><br>TIPS<br>- Combine items to increase your score!<br>- Become a fan of Space Dog on Facebook for even more tips:<br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.facebook.com/SpaceDog.Game&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGeAVrnRT04cqi-2jHiFh_GTZtxBw" target="_blank">https://www.facebook.com/SpaceDog.Game</a><br>- Follow Space Dog on Twitter for 140-char. exclusive tips:<br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://twitter.com/spacedoggame&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFEZOoYmHki1tF2Oxa5XaFKZWCO0g" target="_blank">http://twitter.com/spacedoggame</a><br>- Do you like Adictiz games touch? Follow us on Twitter @Adictiz or on Facebook.com/Adictiz<br>- Feeling like sharing a comment or reporting a bug? Contact the support and we’ll do our best to sort the problem quickly.<br>- Space Dog + is a registered trademark of Adictiz.<br><br><br>Space Dog comes back in a brand new game: Space Dog Run! <br>Download it here: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.adictiz.com/games/spacedogrun&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNE5qT0DwfieG5sk6TAAHB4e9B9a1g" target="_blank">http://www.adictiz.com/games/spacedogrun</a><br><br><br>ATTENTION<br>When installing Space Dog, you’ll be asked to authorise the app to receive and send text messages. This authorisation will only be used if you use the in-game payment system.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.adictiz.spacedogplus', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/58tLkV38KUzjiBO1WB7aUHSSZX3EB8D9wm5lSD7yfQARdbjtkbD7Vo33Rh0GhedIzQ', 4.42, 'ARCADE', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'android.permission.INTERNET, android.permission.WAKE_LOCK, android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE, android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE, android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, com.adictiz.spacedogplus.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.VIBRATE, com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.RECEIVE_SMS, android.permission.SEND_SMS, com.adictiz.lib.fortumo.PAYMENT_BROADCAST_PERMISSION, android.permissio