(19, 'com.jmt.application.facebookthemes.activity', 'Color Themes for Facebook', 'JMT Apps', '? ONE OF THE 2012 TOP APPS<br>? TOP 100 SOCIAL APPS WORLDWIDE<p>Create your own Facebook! Customize Facebook with themes and skins!<p>Facebook Color Themes for Android provides awesome themes to have a unique Facebook experience! Make your own Facebook fancy and fun!<p>One of the most addictive apps on Android!<p>Want to customize your Facebook? Want to enjoy Facebook with your own colors? Rasta, Red Wine, Brazil, Aurora Borealis, Color Chic, Clean Modern, Pink Girl, Dark Light, Tropical...Never get the dull white &amp; blue Facebook colors again! You can also have your own country theme: Brazil, UK, US, France, India, Israel,...!<p>We now support the latest Facebook web app. With Facebook Themes, you can customize Facebook Touch with your own colors. Go pink, black and white, rainbow or any other of our most popular themes, or just go by the standard Facebook colors. <p>REVIEWS<br>? ? ? ? ? <br>&quot;So much better than the Facebook app!&quot; - Justin<p>&quot;I love to have my own Facebook experience!&quot; - Mandy<p>&quot;The best personalization app!&quot; - Nicole<p>Download and enjoy :)<p>??? If you do not want ads in your app, just download the Ad Free version here: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://bit.ly/XH4H0s&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFh9CHMchNXDvN6pVBebH4fXeEBAg" target="_blank">http://bit.ly/XH4H0s</a> ???<p>??? Issue with our app? Suggestions for a new theme? - Please send us an email: <a href="mailto:support@jmtapps.com">support@jmtapps.com</a> ???<p>Tags: facebook, themes, customize facebook, fb, skin, facebook wallpaper, wallpaper, wallpapers, black, red, yellow, custom facebook, custom facebook, personal facebook, create own facebook, social network, fb skin, fb wallpaper, background, facebook background, entertainement facebook, have your own facebook, color, colors, color themes, layout, layouts, socialize, social<p>Note: We are not affiliated or