(33, 'com.amazon.mp3', 'Amazon MP3 – play and download', 'Amazon Mobile LLC', 'Amazon makes it easy to play your music, everywhere.<br> <br>With the free Amazon MP3 app, you can play music from your Android phone or tablet, shop for music at Amazon, or stream your music stored in Amazon Cloud Player - even download your music from the cloud and listen offline.<br> <br>Amazon has over 20 million songs at low prices - see new music, bestsellers, and free music from rising artists.  Save your MP3 purchases directly to Cloud Player for free and play them instantly on your phone or tablet, plus play or download them anytime from your computer or other devices.<br> <br>To listen to your music, visit amazon.com/cloudplayer and quickly import your library from iTunes or your MP3 music folders.  Then use the app to stream your music from Cloud Player, or download it to play offline or reduce data plan usage.  You can also play your music from Cloud Player on your computer, iPhone or iPad, or other devices.  Or, if you prefer, sideload the music to your Android phone or tablet and start listening instantly.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.amazon.mp3', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/y_rbHJIOBexASJA5Yzr0ZkhFYtE01eH2ULBk5H9nI0k7Xq0L0vr3J6j4LHASZlZnjA', 3.46, 'MUSIC_AND_AUDIO', 'Free', '10,000,000+', 'android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE, android.permission.BROADCAST_STICKY, android.permission.READ_LOGS, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS, android.permission.BLUETOOTH, android.permission.BLUETOOTH_ADMIN, com.amazon.dcp.sso.permission.account.changed, android.permission.AUTHENTICATE_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.MANAGE_ACCOUNTS, com.amazon.dcp.metrics.permission.METRICS_PERMISSION, com.amazon.permission.SET_FLAG_NOSOFTKEYS, com.amazon.CONTENT_PROVIDER_ACCESS, com.amazon.CONTENT_NOTIFICATION_ACCESS, com.amazon.mp3.CLEAR_CACHE_PERMISSION'),
