(39, 'deezer.android.app', 'Deezer', 'Deezer Mobile', 'All your music, all the time. Plus hand-picked recommendations to fall in love with.<p>Deezer is a revolutionary global music service, available in 182 countries. Download the app now to begin 15 days of Premium+ for free.<p>Key features:<p>- Listen without limits to over 30 million tracks.<br>- Sync your music to your device for offline listening.<br>- Give music the attention it deserves. No ads, no interruptions.<br>- Receive hand-picked recommendations from the Deezer Editors on Hear This, your personal music feed.<br>- Listen to your own MP3s that you upload to Deezer.<br>- Access your music on your computer, mobile, and tablet. <br>- Explore thousands of themed and artist radio channels.<br>- Control playback from your home screen.<br>- Access great apps built around Deezer in the App Studio.<p><br>Build your ultimate music library with your favourite artists, albums, and playlists.<p>Nominated for Best Music Service Provider at the 2013 ME Awards.<p>Follow Deezer!<br>Facebook: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.facebook.com/deezer&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFvywhBhkcB4Nr5I5TG2mbtAuuc5Q" target="_blank">http://www.facebook.com/deezer</a><br>Twitter: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.twitter.com/DeezerUK&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHn4Va3xyek2zqh-8NS6W9jYr2kZg" target="_blank">http://www.twitter.com/DeezerUK</a><p><br>Keywords : music, mp3, streaming, download, Deezer Lite, unlimited, song, track, radio, webradio, smartradio, playlist, artist, album, media, online.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=deezer.android.app', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/dt3ZQjS2oKkUA8948-vmMI3w_azueh_vjzSvZyqodIjimBaKTVDh16ZxPD0i2WXFEWo', 3.86, 'MUSIC_AND_AUDIO', 'Free', '10,000,000+', 'android.permission.DISABLE_KEYGUARD, android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS, android.permission.READ_LOGS, com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS, com.sonymobile.media.permission.TILES_ACCESS, deezer.android.app.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, deezer.android.app.permission.YNP_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE'),
(40, 'com.shazam.encore.android', 'Shazam Encore', 'Shazam Entertainment Limited', 'Shazam recognizes music and media playing around you. Tap the Shazam button to instantly match, and then explore, buy and share. Shazam Encore offers a Shazam experience without the banner ads. You can Shazam as much as you want! <p>Once you’ve Shazamed something, you can:<p>? Buy tracks on Amazon MP3<br>? Watch the videos on YouTube<br>? See what your friends have Shazamed<br>? Use LyricPlay to sing along to streamed lyrics<br>? Listen to the music you Shazam in Rdio or Spotify<br>? Check out the artist’s bio and discography<p>You can also<p>? Preview and save your favourites<br>? Share what you Shazam on Twitter, Facebook &amp; Google+<br>? Shazam even when you don’t have any coverage; Shazam will match when you have a connection and get back to you with the result<br>? Shazam from your phone’s home screen with the Shazam Widget<p>Upgrade to Shazam Encore for the Shazam experience without the banner ads. <p>Notes: <br>* Previews available: US, UK, DE, FR, CH, AT <br>* Lyrics and LyricPlay available: US, CA, UK, FR, IT, DE, ES, AU, NZ.<br>* Spotify available: AD, AT, AU, BE, CH, DE, DK, EE, ES, FI, FR, HK, IE, IS, IT, LI, LT, LU, LV, MX, MY, MC, NL, NO, NZ, PL, PT, SG, SE, UK, US<br>* Shazam supports devices with cellular connection<p>MIPS devices are not supported<p>Tags: ID song, search music, recognize song, song identification, what’s that song, track lyrics, tag radio, tag tv, tag television, TV Ad, Android Beam', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.shazam.encore.android', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/BQQBfQEpacqI_IWge9lYp7IGhvbM-11GkcH6sSW2u4vl8aPMDn-rD0kFyQ2aTzzJfIY', 4.45, 'MUSIC_AND_AUDIO', '$5.59', '500,000+', 'com.shazam.encore.android.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO, android.permission.BROADCAST_STICKY, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.AUTHENTICATE_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.READ_SYNC_SETTINGS, android.permission.WRITE_SYNC_SETTINGS, com.google.android.providers.gsf.permission.READ_GSERVICES, android.permission.NFC, com.shazam.android.preloadinfo.provider.ACCESS_DATA, android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS, com.android.vending.CHECK_LICENSE'),
(41, 'com.mixzing.basic', 'MixZing Music Player', 'MixZing', 'MixZing is simply the most advanced media player around!<p>? Internet Radio brings you thousands of great stations to listen to: browse by genre or let us recommend ones that match your taste<p>? Music ID identifies your songs, even those without valid tags, and lets you clean up their tags and album art<p>? Displays lyrics for millions of songs<p>? Mood Player creates custom listening sessions--like Pandora for your music!<p>? Graphic equalizer for MP3, AAC/M4A and OGG files<p>? Automatically saves playlists and lets you restore deleted ones<p>? Folder browser lets you access your media collection by storage folders<p>? Tag editor for most file types<p>? Discover new music with spot-on recommendations<p>? Lock-screen widget to control player while phone is locked<p>? Sleep timer<p>? Automatically downloads missing album art<p>? Home-screen widgets with album art<p>? Batch playlist editing<p>? Genre and video browsing', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mixzing.basic', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/tuPZGLMVSxxVb_PKm3NnsrRTFjOvz1yircffrU9AejlqWqXGiT63SexdsQr6HLtkfg', 4.40, 'MUSIC_AND_AUDIO', 'Free', '5,000,000+', 'android.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.SET_WALLPAPER, android.permission.GET_TASKS, android.permission.DISABLE_KEYGUARD, android.permission.KILL_BACKGROUND_PROCESSES, android.permission.RESTART_PACKAGES, android.permission.READ_LOGS'),
(42, 'com.mojang.minecraftpe', 'Minecraft - Pocket Edition', 'Mojang', 'Minecraft is about placing blocks to build things and going on adventures!<p>Pocket Edition includes randomly generated worlds, multiplayer over a local Wi-Fi network, and Survival and Creative modes. You can craft and create with your friends anywhere in the world so long as you have hands spare and battery to burn. <p>Our most recent update added the iconic Creepers. They’re big, green, mean and explody. But it’s just one of many. Since Minecraft — Pocket Edition first appeared, we’re continuing to add loads of new features, including...<p>- Food! Now you can cook and go hungry<br>- Swords! Bows! TNT!<br>- Chests<br>- Skeletons<br>- Spiders<br>- Beds<br>- Paintings<br>- Lots more!<p>But enough sales talk! Download it already! And have fun!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mojang.minecraftpe', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/wnJIWJ7KlHhOR2rnu3BhZMZ90YdulOLNiNg6DEXlBQPgf7S9ddJ5-E97HGsXapMapvI', 4.51, 'ARCADE', '$6.99', '1,000,000+', 'android.permission.INTERNET, android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, android.permission.VIBRATE, android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE'),
(43, 'com.makru.minecraftbook', 'CleverBook - A Minecraft Guide', 'Marius Krusen', 'CleverBook - A Minecraft Guide (previously known as Minecraft Book) is a must have for all minecraft fans.<br>It offers quick access to every ID and every recipe of the popular indie game &quot;Minecraft&quot; by Notch/Mojang, as well as of the mobile version &quot;Minecraft - Pocket Edition&quot;. CleverBook - A Minecraft Guide is your first-choice app if you need help.<p>Features: <br>• Information about every single item/block<br>• List of all achievements, biomes, structures, mobs, potions, cheats<br>• ID list with search functionality<br>• Server list to check your favorite minecraft servers<br>• Twitter feeds of Minecraft developers<br>• latest minecraft information and news<br>• Redstone Circuits/Logic Gates<br>• English &amp; German<br>• App2SD<p>&quot;Minecraft&quot; is a registered trade mark of Mojang AB.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.makru.minecraftbook', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/tSGll0gXL-6BKGi0XATsuUXU_uW4XyhUVEB9OgCzQKNGfDo3jzR9i5tAk_0MB3f2vg', 4.76, 'BOOKS_AND_REFERENCE', 'Free', '1,000,000+', ''),
(44, 'com.ninjacoders.mcanary', 'MineCanary Minecraft Guide', 'David León', '&quot;MineCanary is your one-stop quick reference app for all things Minecraft to help you along your way.&quot; - DroidGamers<p>&quot;I do believe this is the best Minecraft application out there&quot; - The Ace&#39;s Place<p>&quot;This app is invaluable&quot; - Pocket-lint<p>- Quick access to every recipe.<br>- Useful info about: Tips, Food, Circuits, Traps, Mobs, The Nether, Block IDs, Server Commands.. and much more!<br>- Dawn/Dusk Timer: You&#39;ll never wonder what time is it outside again!<br>- Quick useful links list, from Notch&#39;s Blog to the Minecraft subreddit.<p>** MineCanary is an unofficial guide for Minecraft. MineCanary is not affiliated in any way with Mojang AB. The Minecraft Name, the Minecraft Brand and the Minecraft Assets are all property of Mojang AB or they respectful owner. All rights reserved. Copyright MineCanary **', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ninjacoders.mcanary', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/xo0ISU9S3Ym4ETZJdsctTBduVIOPvXbqg66DtjsCeSQ9mKgF1SPFzV9H1IS0_7rLWY-T', 4.47, 'BOOKS_AND_REFERENCE', 'Free', '1,000,000+', ''),
(45, 'com.sitrusy.minecraftWiki', 'Unofficial Wiki For Minecraft', 'Braydon B', '**This app is not created by Mojang, nor is it affiliated, or supported by them at all.**<br>(Mojang is the company who created Minecraft.)<p>The Wiki for Minecraft for your mobile device is here! It serves as a directory to all of the most popular Wiki for Minecraft content and allows you to easily access any guides for Minecraft, tips, item details and more directly from your mobile device! If you&#39;ve been waiting for a true mobile Wiki for Minecraft, here it is!<p>- Over 300 of the most popular Wiki articles for Minecraft.<br>- Item descriptions, tutorials, and more - everything you&#39;d expect from the Wiki for Minecraft app!<br>- Constantly updated content for our Wiki for Minecraft app!<br>- A MUST HAVE for any Minecraft fanatics that like to have a complete reference by their sides at all times while playing one of the greatest games of all time!<p>DISCLAIMER: This app is in no way affiliated with minecraftwiki.net and does not claim ownership of any of the content this app provides from minecraftwiki.net all applicable content rights regarding ownership are given to the owners of minecraftwiki.net. This app simply serves as a directory to minecraftwiki.net for easier navigation on mobile devices.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sitrusy.minecraftWiki', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/8c7MUJ_GqIrIUjAN3eNcY184_kb9jTQ4jsBl5bSxrBdGLMIWzLpFae2aL4Y6J7YTO2c', 2.99, 'BOOKS_AND_REFERENCE', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, com.android.browser.permission.WRITE_HISTORY_BOOKMARKS, com.android.browser.permission.READ_HISTORY_BOOKMARKS, com.android.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, com.motorola.dlauncher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, com.motorola.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, com.lge.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, com.android.launcher.permission.UNINSTALL_SHORTCUT, com.android.launcher.permission.READ_SETTINGS, com.htc.launcher.permission.READ_SETTINGS, com.motorola.launcher.permission.READ_SETTINGS, com.motorola.dlauncher.permission.READ_SETTINGS, com.fede.launcher.permission.READ_SETTINGS, com.lge.launcher.permission.READ_SETTINGS, org.adw.launcher.permission.READ_SETTINGS, com.teslacoilsw.launcher.permission.READ_SETTINGS, com.anddoes.launcher.permission.READ_SETTINGS, com.android.launcher.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, com.htc.launcher.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, com.motorola.launcher.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, com.motorola.dlauncher.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, com.lge.launcher.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, com.fede.launcher.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, org.adw.launcher.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, com.teslacoilsw.launcher.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, com.anddoes.launcher.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW, android.permission.GET_TASKS'),
(46, 'com.poyo.minecraftcraftingguide', 'Crafting Table Minecraft Guide', 'poyopoyo91', 'Formerly known as Minecraft Crafting Guide, this app is a guide to every crafting recipe in the game and more vital lists of information about Minecraft.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.poyo.minecraftcraftingguide', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/pQVIM_2jsSrsVHgIvHZc7bFqjdIW50V1nHP_3E3ix6ErKA18lyjtXjPiZcQRWCWq9w', 4.40, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '1,000,000+', ''),
(47, 'com.pxstudios.minecraftpro', 'MinerGuide - For Minecraft', 'MinerGuide Inc', 'MinerGuide is a guide to the popular indie game &#39;Minecraft&#39;. This app has Info on crafting, mobs, achievements, redstone and more!<p>*Updated for version 1.4.6 of Minecraft.*<p>Base Features:<br>- Item info<br>- Redstone circuit info<br>- Mob info<br>- Clickable crafting squares<p>Unlockable Features:<br>- Search for any piece of information in the app<br>- Achievement info<br>- Biome info<br>- Structure info<br>- Gameplay info<p>This app is a must have for all miners whether you&#39;re a beginner or pro!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.pxstudios.minecraftpro', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/-I6V25HRb6aMuilXESVRgY0O2-I5mYSuMI9_fjMzLT-zvcnLY_tNtw8FWG_uXRyZOno', 4.34, 'BOOKS_AND_REFERENCE', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'com.android.vending.BILLING'),
(48, 'com.GavvaGames.ShareLand', 'ShareLand Online MineCraft', 'GavvaGames', 'Build land with your friends. Online App. ?ommunicate: game ?hat. Be creative: &gt; 40 bloks. Do not lose: save or load your land.<p>Please: rate 5 stars.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.GavvaGames.ShareLand', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/OE4eflppavoATsuLex4P9dW71ulpeTvAjLDgAyDJRtpi7DQnXmYZ-JqE300XeFIHOlSZ', 3.61, 'CASUAL', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO, android.permission.INTERNET, android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE'),
(49, 'com.saranomy.skinstealer', 'Skin Stealer for Minecraft', 'Saranomy', 'Steal Minecraft skin and apply it to your skin. This app lets you steal Minecraft skin using username and save it into your gallery. You can also apply it to your skin on Minecraft for PC, MCPE or MCPE demo.<p>Changing skin on devices that use Android 4.1+ will no longer work because new version of MCPE cannot be modified anymore. Sorry about that.<p>==========<br>Ask me about this app at<br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://developer.saranomy.com&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNH5EZVEo4yauAw_6KcERO1EQAv9vA" target="_blank">http://developer.saranomy.com</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.saranomy.skinstealer', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/xGXBt401RZzYqvMeU-QnQ2VM4mciJ2Axv_JFO5O-sWAgUZe5wVEI5zMx65Vt3pD_6g', 3.88, 'TOOLS', 'Free', '1,000,000+', ''),
(50, 'com.misiunas.mcs', 'MineCraft Sweeper', 'K.Misiunas', 'Game of mine sweeper with mathematical and logical elements set in a  theme and modes that resemble MineCraft.<p>MineCraft Sweeper is fan made mine-sweeper game with an exciting  Minecraft theme and refreshing new game mode to explore! <p>The game was featured on Kotaku: <br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://kotaku.com/minecraft-sweeper/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFWTS7-HBgYcdH-7DjlUt_W3HC-_A" target="_blank">http://kotaku.com/minecraft-sweeper/</a><p>You like MineCraft? So do we! This is a game for those who can&#39;t wait to play MineCraft again. It features 2D mine where you aim to gather as many resources as possible. But on your way you stumble upon zombies and creepers. Will you succeed to explore the mine and stay alive?<p>This is a minesweeper game. It is a logical puzzle game with elements of mathematics to it. The interface is custom designed for smartphone users - you can play for long periods or for brief moments while waiting for a friend. This game is also unique  among other minesweeper games:  there are multiple lives, hidden treasures and absurdly large maps. We hope you like it!<p>Features:<br>+ 3 game modes: Adventure, With Food, Classic<br>+ extremely large maps (if you like)<br>+ multiple lives (finally saved from accidental clicks)<br>+ online score system<br>+ zoom in/out<p>Compatibility: <br>The game was tested on Nexus like devices. So phones with 800x480+ resolutions and with at least 1GHz processors should be able to play the game without any problems. The game will run on other devices but please let us know if you encounter any problems (via email please).<p>Authors:<br>K.Misiunas and T.Misiunas (brothers)', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.misiunas.mcs', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/USvrAX7aHHDEmK_qQhS867MNJsgQezSIvOz_IQObDoTJuH3hNLQpb8_ZBGwcayIfhl8I', 4.01, 'BRAIN', 'Free', '500,000+', 'android.permission.INTERNET, android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.VIBRATE, android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE'),
(51, 'cn.wodong.minecraftGuideHouses', 'House Guide + Minecraft Cheats', 'Solano Apps MC', '? Ready to build an amazing home in Minecraft? Want ideas for the most impressive homes with step-by-step instructions? ?<p>From beginner to the most advanced Minecraft player, this is the home building and design idea app for you! This app also includes a complete beginner&#39;s guide to Minecraft!<p>Some amazing Minecraft home designs included: <p>House Designs with step-by-step tutorials:<br>? Fancy Home<br>? Treehouse<br>? Japanese House<br>? Beginner House<br>? Houseboat<br>? Cottage<br>? Brick House<br>? and many more!<p>Unique Creations<br>? Bomb Shelter<br>? Underwater observation deck<br>? Watch Tower<br>? and many more creations and structures!<p>Search &quot;Solano Apps&quot; on Google Play for more FREE Minecraft apps!<p>Enjoy!<p>Disclaimer: <br>1- In creating this unofficial guide we assert its rights under the &quot;Fair Use&quot; doctrine pursuant to United States copyright law and the equivalent in other jurisdictions. If you believe that there has been a contravention of your proprietary rights, please email details to <a href="mailto:malibumicrocap@gmail.com">malibumicrocap@gmail.com</a>. This application is the sole creation and responsibility of Solano Apps. This application is not endorsed by or affiliated with the creator of this game or its licensors. All characters, their names, places, and other aspects of the game described within this application are trademarked and owned by their respective owners. This application is intended for educational purposes only. <br>2- Creating an app takes time and money, In order to keep creating great (and free!) apps, we are using a new search service to monetize our apps. With this service we are able to create more great apps for you guys. This option bundles a few search points (icon, bookmark and homepage) for you to use. You can erase these easily and with no effect to our app. Thanks!<p>Please support Mojang and purchase Minecraft at www.Minecraft.net', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=cn.wodong.minecraftGuideHouses', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/k4OxYMKaZuigrgDKGxOK9PmkPpu9FNIqHA0EU1pTlf2bQASKjS9llaATreSKMplrAw', 3.93, 'BOOKS_AND_REFERENCE', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'com.android.browser.permission.WRITE_HISTORY_BOOKMARKS, com.android.browser.permission.READ_HISTORY_BOOKMARKS, com.android.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, com.motorola.dlauncher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, com.motorola.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, com.lge.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, com.android.launcher.permission.UNINSTALL_SHORTCUT, com.android.launcher.permission.READ_SETTINGS, com.htc.launcher.permission.READ_SETTINGS, com.motorola.launcher.permission.READ_SETTINGS, com.motorola.dlauncher.permission.READ_SETTINGS, com.fede.launcher.permission.READ_SETTINGS, com.lge.launcher.permission.READ_SETTINGS, org.adw.launcher.permission.READ_SETTINGS, com.teslacoilsw.launcher.permission.READ_SETTINGS, com.anddoes.launcher.permission.READ_SETTINGS, com.android.launcher.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, com.htc.launcher.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, com.motorola.launcher.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, com.motorola.dlauncher.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, com.lge.launcher.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, com.fede.launcher.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, org.adw.launcher.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, com.teslacoilsw.launcher.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, com.anddoes.launcher.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW, android.permission.GET_TASKS, android.permission.PROCESS_OUTGOING_CALLS, android.permission.READ_CONTACTS, android.permission.DISABLE_KEYGUARD'),
(52, 'com.andrejbroncek.minecraft.booth', 'Photo Booth for Minecraft', 'Andrej Bron?ek', 'Raise your pickaxe!<p>This app shows the GUI from Minecraft (items/blocks, hotbar, healtbar, hungerbar) over Camera view. It also allows you to take stunning photos with famous Minecraft items/blocks and GUI :)<p>Got any suggestions for changes? Let me know! Use the &quot;Email Developer&quot; button below. <p>Please use the same button to report any bugs or crashes. Negative reviews don&#39;t give enough details, and no way for me to get in touch with you. If I can&#39;t get in touch, I can&#39;t get any more details, and I can&#39;t fix it. Thank you :)<p>Needed permissions:<p>CAMERA - Needed to access the camera to take pictures.<br>EXTERNAL_STORAGE - Needed for storing photos.<br>INTERNET - Needed for ads.<br>NETWORK STATE - Needed for ads.<br>READ_PHONE_STATE - Needed for ads.<p>Your photos are stored in your default galery folder ;)<p>** &quot;Minecraft&quot; is a registered trade mark of Mojang AB. **<p>Tags: minecraft, photo, booth, diamond, tnt, block, pickaxe, torch, grass, infiminer, miner, biome, free, graphics', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.andrejbroncek.minecraft.booth', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/Yic5u2faHMBZ8eT3m5oPDp62QetX6EMaCGxiU9bZhJkDKqbTgHDnODHmothAd89aq7sE', 4.04, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '500,000+', 'android.permission.CAMERA'),
(53, 'appinventor.ai_colson72098.Pro_Craft', 'Pro Craft-A Minecraft Guide', 'Cold Flash Labs', 'This is the must-have app for any minecraft gamer. If you are new to minecraft or are an advanced player you will find a use for this app. You can check crafting recipes, see how to build a redstone circuit,see what use an item has, listen to the soundboard with over 30 minecraft sounds, or just find out a block id number.<p>Pro Minecraft Guide is not affiliated with Minecraft or Mojang.<br>&quot;Minecraft&quot; is a trademark of Mojang', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=appinventor.ai_colson72098.Pro_Craft', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/Rw1OngBj1_Somv5lVn5Oi-Eh6Su1HMBRb630cNFss9OSM3raiOUyvqRn6H8w_ktGOmnA', 4.20, 'BOOKS_AND_REFERENCE', 'Free', '100,000+', ''),
(54, 'com.ruuhkis.skintoolkit', 'Skin Toolkit for Minecraft', 'Lowhill Apps', 'Create, share and download!<p>With Skin Toolkit for Minecraft you can create Minecraft skins, share your best creations and download skins created by community!<p>Features:<br>* Create skins from scratch<br>* Import skins from Minecraft<br>* Export skins to Minecraft<br>* Share your creations with whole world<br>* Load skins from your phone to view<br>* Save skins to your storage<br>* Import pictures as part of the skin<br>* Skin packs<br>* Use skins on MCPE<br>* Use texturepacks on MCPE<p>This application is not created by Mojang AB, nor is it affiliated, or supported by them at all.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ruuhkis.skintoolkit', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/mCU02F4GhfXCI1leotL2dUQl_GlcsN39LZoIELoZHox1EKpX4cFzX1O_wypiGaXjJTE', 3.87, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '100,000+', 'com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS'),
(55, 'com.stellar.minecrafto', 'Craft O for Minecraft', 'StellarWave', 'Tired of interrupting your game of Minecraft to look up information about the game on your browser? Need information about the game on the go? Try Craft O.<p>New players can read tutorials on how to play, learn how to craft the items, and get acquainted with the various creatures in the game.<p>Experienced players can store coordinates for their favorite places, generate seeds for new maps, look up vital enchantment and potion brewing information, search the Minecraft wiki, and more!<p>Server owners can quickly grab data values, color codes, and server commands to save a lot of time and frustration.<p>And to top it all off, the entire app is searchable!<p>(If you are looking for Minecraft the game, look elsewhere. This is player&#39;s guide for the game! Minecraft is a registered trademark of Mojang AB, and I am in no way affiliated with them.)', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.stellar.minecrafto', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/fAoUviTnOOBGh_gpY0Wf_zCgq2EOBvl1bAsw_6g8YJWXACYhXV55WyfNaMXcXyDD9MI', 4.33, 'BOOKS_AND_REFERENCE', 'Free', '500,000+', ''),
(56, 'studio.coldstream.minecraftlwp', 'Craft Your Live Wallpaper', 'Coldstream Solutions', 'We sincerely love Minecraft and would like to give something back to the community by providing a customizable dynamic live wallpaper with a proper Minecraft creative mode theme. Please Google search for how to install and set it properly on your handset (e.g. HTC Wildfire requires &#39;LauncherPro&#39; app in order to pick Live Wallpapers). No special permissions are required (That means we are honest and sincerely respect our users privacy).<p>Wanna support us? <br>Bitcoin Donations Accepted: 1KeMc81v2HnhBfu6YiPL3aDpqfnjiBXXpH<br>Please check out our new super customizable Lemon Live Wallpaper: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://tiny.cc/s5drfw&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHksczhRYbZDXEpnfqcoQARTGbNRg" target="_blank">http://tiny.cc/s5drfw</a><p>Additional notes:<br>Installation is commonly done by pressing a few seconds on an empty space (no widgets or icons) on the homescreen. Then select live wallpaper. With reservation that some devices might do it differently, e.g. through the Android settings application.  <p>The settings are not yet fully implemented (still in beta). Please email bug-reports and we will try do our best to fix them!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=studio.coldstream.minecraftlwp', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/bAUJ5B8EHDsmO2iX_DpFEZeyGgdSAP-FLpEJfkfXIZRFpa2TZgsD5XlxvDlOy42H2A', 4.65, 'PERSONALIZATION', 'Free', '1,000,000+', ''),
(57, 'com.minecraft.fr', 'News Minecraft.fr', 'Clément Reynaud', 'Please note that the application is in French.<p>This application allows you to follow the news of Minecraft via the RSS feed Minecraft.fr anywhere.<p>The application was creates in the purpose of enabling you a simple and quick access to latest news. The fact the interface is uncluttered and the articles load very quickly by consuming very little of your bandwidth.<p>You have the possibility to set the application for a notification either displayed when a new article is available.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.minecraft.fr', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/F1cN9ZMR4Yi6epbsTbYNF9cFmRMr_UIBwTDswuQzzsLLwj6eS4ccVwzU9xqWtg853Lw', 3.90, 'NEWS_AND_MAGAZINES', 'Free', '50,000+', 'android.permission.FLASHLIGHT, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED'),
(58, 'net.kaltner.MinecraftMobileAdminFree', 'Mobile Admin for Minecraft (F)', 'Kaltner.net', 'Mobile Admin for Minecraft allows to you manage your Minecraft server, plugins and user right from your phone!<p>For more information and to download the MobileAdmin plugin, please visit <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.kaltner.net&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGBCYAdv4c3IPKjd0pjg18mrMEXFA" target="_blank">http://www.kaltner.net</a><p>IMPORTANT: this application requires you to run your own Minecraft server using Bukkit.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.kaltner.MinecraftMobileAdminFree', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/8ysoanmLfP19CIh_9dQk1DtcowY6eu53aelp2Zj6YScl1uxQ8ifSFhVC6tnmP0JptEgO', 3.79, 'TOOLS', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION'),
(59, 'com.alban.deubeda.MinecraftSoundBoard', 'Minecraft Soundboard', 'alban de ubeda', 'Listen sounds and music from the famous games Minecraft.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.alban.deubeda.MinecraftSoundBoard', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/vnHWgLQt9pAcy4dsqi91g-TLMEPspGEzD4yNnQK-CtS87_oLV3AnMH4_KGn83UFV5mU', 4.33, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS'),
(60, 'com.rabross.android.minecraftskinwidget', 'Skin Widget for Minecraft', 'Rab Ross', 'A simple widget allowing you to display your favorite Minecraft character skins.<br>Developed this app for myself and thought I would share.<p><br>Any feature requests/bug reports please contact me.<p>YOU NEED TO ENTER THE PLAYER NAME OF A PAID MINECRAFT (PC) ACCOUNT<p>Adding widgets to your home screen may differ on devices from various manufacturers.<p>Want to help make it better? <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://groups.google.com/forum/?fromgroups%23!forum/skin-widget-for-minecraft-beta&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFhzSFg2snX-i2OUHNQYlHAaRs9Jw" target="_blank">https://groups.google.com/forum/?fromgroups#!forum/skin-widget-for-minecraft-beta</a><p>Skin Widget for Minecraft is not affiliated with Mojang AB.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.rabross.android.minecraftskinwidget', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/65mhp5bsHkY0BzUzahs-VCtQOUlTnEClYCsltQOmY6N9BSJmCc39wlgw4oVN2HR4g8c', 3.84, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '100,000+', ''),
(61, 'is.theapp.best.minecraft.soundboard', 'Best Minecraft Soundboard', 'Jón Arnar', 'Over 150 selected sounds from all the mobs in Minecraft (Version 1.5.1)<br>+ all the songs from the original Minecraft<p>Next version will make it possible to use sounds as alerts and songs as ringtones<p>If you have any ideas on how to improve this app email me ;o)', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=is.theapp.best.minecraft.soundboard', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/UV2Qvwd4Bsxi1eoGZ_uNiT4PDOBl1GZPuGmpTb7bYT22uSceKibHF0tBJE-DSFXd4A', 4.25, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '100,000+', ''),
(62, 'com.twitter.android', 'Twitter', 'Twitter, Inc.', 'Twitter is the best way to connect, express yourself and discover what’s happening. <p>• Connect with people and your interests to get unfiltered access and unique behind-the-scenes perspectives. <p>• Express yourself with photos, videos and comments. <p>• Discover what&#39;s happening. Get real-time stories, pictures, videos, conversations, ideas, and inspiration all in your timeline.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.twitter.android', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/RAUnR7oW6F45t-OqR-afDC4tosuTYAx0vQEeE4yGgkL52TOE9WGY6KbtGLaHIExgzVQ', 3.97, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '100,000,000+', 'com.twitter.android.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.twitter.android.permission.RESTRICTED, com.twitter.android.permission.AUTH_APP, android.permission.READ_PROFILE, android.permission.READ_CONTACTS, android.permission.RECEIVE_SMS, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.MANAGE_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.AUTHENTICATE_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.READ_SYNC_SETTINGS, android.permission.WRITE_SYNC_SETTINGS, android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS, com.twitter.android.permission.READ_DATA, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, com.google.android.providers.gsf.permission.READ_GSERVICES, com.twitter.android.permission.MAPS_RECEIVE, com.android.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, com.sonyericsson.home.permission.BROADCAST_BADGE, com.sec.android.provider.badge.permission.READ, com.sec.android.provider.badge.permission.WRITE'),
(63, 'com.handmark.tweetcaster', 'TweetCaster for Twitter', 'OneLouder Apps', 'TweetCaster has a gorgeous look with an intuitive interface that makes it super easy to use while packing in tons of features. Optimized for both phones and tablets, TweetCaster has been highly praised by users and reviewers.<p>Features:<br>* Multiple Twitter Accounts – Manage and easily post to multiple Twitter accounts<br>* Facebook – Simultaneously post to Twitter and Facebook<br>* Notifications – Get notified of new tweets, mentions, messages, or by specific user. Notifications are expandable and actionable on Android 4.1+<br>* Photo Effects – Add cool filters, effects and captions to photos, as you upload them<br>* Zip It – Zip annoying tweeters or keywords from your timeline without unfollowing<br>* Widgets – multiple widgets, including one that is scrollable and sizeable (Android 3.0+)!<br>* Themes – Twelve vibrant, colorful themes<br>* Sync between devices – Keep your place in the timeline across multiple devices and web using TweetCaster.com<br>* Smart Filter – Filter your timeline to look only at tweets with photos, links, videos, or hide retweets or replies<br>* Search Party – How Twitter search was meant to be! Lets you search just your own timeline, someone else’s, or all of Twitter.<br>* Smart Lists – The best way to use Twitter Lists, including robust list management and viewing tools<br>* My Stats – Up-to-the-minute tally of stats includes Most Retweeted, Most Mentioned, Most Favorited, &amp; many more<br>* Photo previews – View previews and open photos from most image services, including  Instagram<br>* Speak Tweets – Tap microphone on New Tweet screen to speak instead of typing<br>* Schedule Tweets – Compose a tweet and send later or send to Buffer<br>* Read Later – Save links to read/view later using Pocket, Instapaper, or Readability<br>* Streaming – Tweets are streaming in real-time when connect via WiFi<br>* Readability – View links in Readability mode for a mobile-optimized view<br>* Color Code Tweets –Color code your Tweets and mentions<br>* Long Tweets – Use Twitlonger to tweet over 140 characters<br>* Who to Follow – Suggests people to follow<p>What People are Saying:<br>“Nicely designed… Colorful but clean.” – CNET<br>“Contender for best Twitter app. 5/5 bars.” – Appolicious<br>“Excellent Twitter client.” – TUAW<br>“This is the best Twitter app I&#39;ve found. Very easy to use and very beautiful.” – Che, TweetCaster User (v6.8)', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.handmark.tweetcaster', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/M-JpsVYoUomXVg8eZBUJw2Z-l3pHosacEavX9vLV3dPqUEicfEdYsY8MhfHqoDF_0K8', 4.38, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '5,000,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.READ_LOGS, com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED'),
(64, 'com.twidroid', 'UberSocial for Twitter', 'UberMedia Inc.', 'UberSocial: With so many easy-to-use features, it’ll make you feel like an octopus with 8 swiss army knives.<p>“A must have for any Twitter user” – BuildMobile <br>“An incredibly savvy Twitter management app that’s packed with features” – Mobilewalla <br>&quot;Check out Ubersocial – we’re convinced once you start using it you won’t go back to the Twitter client you were using before&quot; - Nightmaircreative.com <br>&quot;King of the mobile Twitter Apps&quot; - Berryfix <p>Key Features:<br>?	Inner Circle: Don’t miss Tweets from your BFFs <br>        --  Create a &quot;favorite users&quot; list and save yourself hassle searching for their Tweets in your timeline. <p>?	Mute  <br>        --  Tired of hearing about a certain topic? Mute hashtags or users for a period of time. Like, forever.<p>?	Menu Customization <br>        --  For quick &amp; easy access, add your most-used features to the UberMenu.<p>?	Facebook and Gchat status Cross Posting<br>        --  Connect your app to post Tweets to Facebook or edit your status on Gchat. One simple step.<p>?	Multiple Accounts <br>        --  Have a split personality? So do we. Seamlessly manage multiple social accounts all in one place.<p>?	Conversation View<br>        --  Stay atop the conversation better by seeing the previous Tweets and replies for a given chat; really know who&#39;s said what so far.<p>?	LivePreviewTM<br>        --  View rich media in real-time. Check out links, videos and images in your main timeline without having to leave the app.<p>?	Pull &amp; Shake-to-Refresh<br>        --  We recognize the international gesture for “I want the latest and best NOW!” In other words, all you have to do to refresh your feed is pull on it or shake it.<p>?	Themes<br>        --  UberSocial comes with color themes to enhance your Tweeting experience.<p>?	Extra Services<br>        --  Choose from the best services to upload photos, videos, shorten links, or send Tweets over 140 characters with TMI.me.<p>?	The fun don’t stop<br>        --  We offer even more great features, like customized notifications, location services, advanced search, edit profile, and of course the full Twitter functionality set (Tweet, ReTweet, Direct Message, @Mention, lists) and more!<p>UberSocial supports inline viewing of photos and videos from the following services: twitpic, mypict.me, yfrog, pic.gd, tweetphoto.com, lockerz, flickr, mobypicture, twitvid, twitgoo, twitsnap, imgur, instagram<p>UberSocial was previously known as Twidroyd.<p>For more info about UberSocial, check out <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.ubersocial.com&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGvqYwcloZ3VU-KuuOn_1p0SzUjHw" target="_blank">http://www.ubersocial.com</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.twidroid', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/dL4kLzt_EoD-3B6uDmKW_6q7GkYY75CzrFh-bt8T25kLkOlD0ddPAjMIDo97Bui8LhI', 4.07, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '5,000,000+', 'android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE, com.android.vending.CHECK_LICENSE, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.READ_SYNC_SETTINGS, android.permission.READ_SYNC_STATS, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, com.android.vending.BILLING, com.android.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, com.ubersocial.PERMISSIONS.READ_TWEETS, com.ubersocial.PERMISSIONS.READ_MENTIONS, com.ubersocial.PERMISSIONS.DIRECT_MESSAGES, com.ubersocial.PERMISSIONS.UNREAD_STATUS'),
(65, 'com.echofon', 'Echofon for Twitter', 'UberMedia Inc.', 'Echofon is the easy-to-use, super fast Twitter app that smartly syncs across all your devices. <p>Wrapped in a beautiful, clean interface, Echofon for Android packs a punch, featuring gorgeous desktop widget, instant notifications, light and dark color themes and more – all the Twitter features you need to bring order to your busy social media life. <p>Key Features:<br>* Full-featured dashboard widgets<br>* Sync between all your Echofon apps on Android or iOS devices so you never read a Tweet, @Mention or Direct Message twice <br>* Mute Users<br>* Background notifications alert you of new Direct Messages and @Mentions<br>* Easily manage multiple Twitter accounts<br>* Choose from light or battery-saving dark color themes<br>* View threaded conversations all in one place to easily keep track of who said what<br>* Full set of Twitter functionality: Tweet, Retweet, Direct Message, @Mention, lists<br>* Offers photo previews right in your Twitter timeline<p><br>Coming soon<br>* Gap detection<br>* In-app browser/in-app picture viewer', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.echofon', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/QCn-N60h2C4HieW8XvgvW5rNC0Rgcb7VuaNIkwW8t9csDoVGCkTADNgNsb3-D0LTMw', 3.70, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.READ_SYNC_STATS, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE, com.android.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, com.android.vending.CHECK_LICENSE, com.echofon.PERMISSIONS.READ_TWEETS, com.echofon.PERMISSIONS.READ_MENTIONS, com.echofon.PERMISSIONS.DIRECT_MESSAGES, com.echofon.PERMISSIONS.UNREAD_STATUS, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, com.echofon.permission.C2D_MESSAGE'),
(66, 'com.levelup.touiteur', 'Plume for Twitter', 'LevelUp Studio', 'Plume is a beautiful and completely customizable Twitter app that will revolutionize the way you use Twitter! Brought to you by the authors of the popular Beautiful Widgets, Plume is one of the best Twitter clients for Android! (Plume was formerly known as Touiteur)<p>- Colorize your timeline/friends from Twitter<br>- Multiple twitter accounts support<br>- Scrollable widgets to display your twitter timeline on your home<br>- Lockscreen widget (Android 4.2+)<br>- Mute twitter users, word or applications<br>- Facebook timeline &amp; posting<br>- Live Streaming in app<br>- Picture preview in timeline, large view of images with pinch to zoom<br>- Twitter geotagging<br>- Swipe scrolling<br>- Very customizable<br>- Internal browser<br>- Autocomplete twitter hashtags and username<br>- Share photo with Twitter, Twitpic, YFrog, Mobypicture, MyPict.me<br>- Bit.ly support for your URLs<br>- Inline twitter conversation<br>- Display replies to a tweet<br>- Display twitter profiles<br>- Pull to refresh<br>- a lot more!<br> <br>Plume is a beautiful, highly customizable Twitter client, which will change the way you feel about Twitter!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.levelup.touiteur', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/uADrrF0FMReNrt7ap_cI-057Zmsl6awZWhpjA0Eupe-HGou1-FFb1ECeta3ED4N1Mos', 4.15, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.FLASHLIGHT, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS, android.permission.NFC'),
(67, 'com.justunfollow.android', 'JustUnfollow Twitter,Instagram', 'Codigami Inc.', 'Find your Twitter and Instagram unfollowers. You don&#39;t need to wonder &quot;who unfollowed me?&quot; any longer. The JustUnfollow app, featured on TechCrunch, The Next Web, MakeUseOf and other leading social media websites, is the best friend management app. <p>JustUnfollow is the ultimate Twitter and Instagram unfollow and follow tracker. We help you find those who unfollow you on twitter and Instagram, unfollow them back, see your new followers and follow them. <p>This app quickly finds and displays all your Twitter and Instagram unfollowers. Whether you have 100 users who unfollowed you or 10,000, we will catch them and show them to you. <p>It&#39;s absolutely free to get started and find unfollowers. <p>JustUnfollow aims to be the best and simplest application to manage twitter accounts and to help you find users who unfollowed you. <p>Key Features (Twitter &amp; Instagram have separate features): <p>- Notifications: New followers and unfollowers will be tracked automatically and you will receive notifications(once in every 24 hrs) <br>- Send automatic welcome DMs to new followers <br>- Activate automatic tracking and tweeting of your stats <br>- Non-Followers: Find and unfollow tweeps you follow who do not follow you back <br>- Fans: Find and follow tweeps who follow you but you are not following them back <br>- Who Unfollowed Me: Find tweeps who stopped following you <br>- Who Followed Me: Find tweeps who started following you <br>- Inactive Following: Find tweeps who haven&#39;t tweeted in the last 1,3 or 6 months <br>- All Following: Shows and allows you to unfollow everyone you currently follow. Use this when you want to start twitter all over again! <br>- Friend Check: Check your relationship with a particular twitter user <br>- Whitelist: View all the users you have whitelisted. We make sure you do not end up unfollowing whitelisted users. Whitelist your favorite celebs <br>- Blacklist: View all the users you have blacklisted. We make sure you do not follow blacklisted users <br>- Copy Followers: Follow the followers of any other twitter account. Admire a twitter account’s followers? You can follow them using this feature <br>- Multiple Accounts: Add multiple twitter accounts and manage them from a single place <br>- Settings: Upgrade accounts (for Premium users) and all other app settings can be found here <p>- Non-Followers for Instagram: Find and unfollow Instagram users you follow who do not follow you back <br>- Fans for Instagram: Find and follow Instagram users who follow you but you are not following them back <br>- Copy Followers for Instagram: Follow the followers of any other Instagram account. Admire an Instagram account’s followers? You can follow them using this feature. This is one of the best ways to gain more followers on Instagram <p>This free version grants you access to all our features and lets you unfollow and follow users in the fastest way possible. You get to follow/unfollow up to 50 users per day for free on twitter and 60 users per hour for free on Instagram. In order to remove these limits or to add multiple twitter accounts to the same account, you can unlock these features within the app by clicking the &#39;Upgrade&#39; option. You cannot remove the Instagram unfollow limits as that limit is set by Instagram but you can upgrade to be able to add multiple Instagram accounts. <p>We&#39;re the best app for tracking Twitter and Instagram unfollowers and followers! <p>Contact us: <a href="mailto:info@justunfollow.com">info@justunfollow.com</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.justunfollow.android', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/TWUocrG04zqhtDJQ-5N4nLx58Br-n2oe9XaH93zpRF1sJ78IPna0PDtNN9ueiGMruZ0', 4.40, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'com.justunfollow.android.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.android.vending.BILLING, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS'),
(68, 'com.handmark.tweetcaster.premium', 'TweetCaster Pro for Twitter', 'OneLouder Apps', 'TweetCaster has a gorgeous look with an intuitive interface that makes it super easy to use while packing in tons of features. Optimized for both phones and tablets, TweetCaster has been highly praised by users and reviewers.<p>Features:<br>* Multiple Twitter Accounts – Manage and easily post to multiple Twitter accounts<br>* Facebook – Simultaneously post to Twitter and Facebook<br>* Notifications – Get notified of new tweets, mentions, messages, or by specific user. Notifications are expandable and actionable on Android 4.1+<br>* Photo Effects – Add cool filters, effects and captions to photos, as you upload them<br>* Zip It – Zip annoying tweeters or keywords from your timeline without unfollowing<br>* Widgets – multiple widgets, including one that is scrollable and sizeable (Android 3.0+)!<br>* Themes – Twelve vibrant, colorful themes<br>* Sync between devices – Keep your place in the timeline across multiple devices and web using TweetCaster.com<br>* Smart Filter – Filter your timeline to look only at tweets with photos, links, videos, or hide retweets or replies<br>* Search Party – How Twitter search was meant to be! Lets you search just your own timeline, someone else’s, or all of Twitter.<br>* Smart Lists – The best way to use Twitter Lists, including robust list management and viewing tools<br>* My Stats – Up-to-the-minute tally of stats includes Most Retweeted, Most Mentioned, Most Favorited, &amp; many more<br>* Photo previews – View previews and open photos from most image services, including  Instagram<br>* Speak Tweets – Tap microphone on New Tweet screen to speak instead of typing<br>* Schedule Tweets – Compose a tweet and send later or send to Buffer<br>* Read Later – Save links to read/view later using Pocket, Instapaper, or Readability<br>* Streaming – Tweets are streaming in real-time when connect via WiFi<br>* Readability – View links in Readability mode for a mobile-optimized view<br>* Color Code Tweets –Color code your Tweets and mentions<br>* Long Tweets – Use Twitlonger to tweet over 140 characters<br>* Who to Follow – Suggests people to follow<p>What People are Saying:<br>“Nicely designed… Colorful but clean.” – CNET<br>“Contender for best Twitter app. 5/5 bars.” – Appolicious<br>“Excellent Twitter client.” – TUAW<br>“This is the best Twitter app I&#39;ve found. Very easy to use and very beautiful.” – Che, TweetCaster User (v6.8)', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.handmark.tweetcaster.premium', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/gsOh8Dl-gAJvi4IJT6pTLpE_UIEPFcMWcqxolFWiR0CSN4YMc4DzMTj-uWmDDj3zZg', 4.44, 'SOCIAL', '$4.99', '50,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.READ_LOGS, com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED');
