(115, 'com.revunote.client', 'Revunote for Evernote', 'Revunote.com', 'Revunote works with Evernote to help you learn things off by heart using &#39;spaced repetition&#39;. Some things are more useful in your head than they are in the cloud.<p><br>&quot;If I don&#39;t review I might as well not have spent the time learning in the first place. My problem has always been keeping track of what to review and when. Thankfully Revunote with Evernote makes it really easy.&quot;<p>Easy to use:<br>Step 1: Tag the notes (in Evernote) you want to review<br>Step 2. Synchronise Revunote<br>Step 3: Review and swipe the notes<p>&quot;Revunote lets me review at my convenience - whilst I am commuting or anytime I have five minutes to spare.&quot;<p>Benefits of Revunote:<br>? Implements spaced repetition for you (1, 3, 7, 14, 30, 60 days)<br>? Review your notes anywhere. No need to be at your computer or connected to the internet.<br>? Helps you review actively (by recalling) rather than just passively (by re-reading)<br>? Take advantage of spare moments to review your notes.<br>? No messing about with tags; simply swipe and sync.<br>? No messing about with reports. A single list of all notes due for review.<br>? No need to remember what or when to review... Revunote tells you!<br>? Easy to setup.<br>? Picks out the few notes you need to review from among the 1000s you have.<p>&quot;We are bombarded with information all the time and its so easy to access that we can fall prey to an &#39;in one ear, out the other&#39; mindset - even toward things we want or need to remember. Revunote helps me to consciously make choices about what I learn.&quot;<p>Benefits of reviewing:<br>? Valuable knowledge is at your beck and call<br>? Contribute effectively in collaborative situations<br>? Stand out as knowledgable in your chosen field(s)<br>? Spend less time cramming<br>? Study more efficiently<p>&quot;I did a training course earlier this year. I used Evernote to create some high quality notes and I used Revunote to help that information stick. As a result, my ability to apply what we covered is much improved over what it would have been.&quot;<p>Use it to:<br>? Keep current with professional developments<br>? Review lectures, presentations, training courses<br>? Pick up new skills like football, dance or martial arts<br>? Learn lyrics, poems, quotes or jokes<br>? Acquire languages<p>For students at school, college or university. For professionals engaged in continuous professional development. For people just interested in developing their hobby. Revunote with Evernote is an essential combination.<p>Features:<br>- Drives a review cycle at 1, 3, 7, 14, 30, 60 days<br>- Displays all your notes for review in one place<br>- Touch to open notes in Evernote<br>- Swipe to indicate review done<br>- Synchronises with your Evernote account<br>- Retains review history in the cloud<br>- Creates a review tag in your evernote account or synchronises with them if they already exist<br>- Widget to remind you from your home screen <p>Note: Revunote is a Free to Trial app (30 days). Thereafter it requires the purchase of an inexpensive key. It has no distracting app-vertising.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.revunote.client', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/hoKp0bLnooUOzgvUkIYLGacJJ9HSl4SHzMcQ5SbI4DxkE3-IXCLs600QO4VaZKvC194', 4.36, 'EDUCATION', 'Free', '5,000+', 'android.permission.DUMP, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED'),
(116, 'com.access_company.android.nflifescreen', 'NetFront Life Screen', 'ACCESS CO., LTD.', 'Download NetfrontTM Life Screen - A great Homescreen replacement with a cool user interface, a great app launcher and automatic updates from your social networks and phone apps.<p>Features:<br>- Sleek user interface with 3-D effects<br>- 3-D App launcher for all apps installed on your device<br>- Customizable app carousel with instant access to your favorite apps and services, and the latest updates<br>- Evernote® integration – one-touch access to the latest updates to your Evernote® account<br>- Instant viewing of updated from your social networks - Facebook, Twitter, Mixi<br>- Add your choice of widgets to the home screen display<br>- Customize background with your choice of wallpaper <p>NetFrontTM Life Screen is a home screen (homescreen) replacement app with an intuitive interface that delivers previews of social network updates as well as phone services data. Use the app launcher cube to quickly find any installed app and launch it. New in version 2, see and access your latest Evernote® account updates. NetFront Life Screen replaces your built-in homescreen and gives you one-touch access to the information you would currently need to launch several apps to see. <p>NetFrontTM Life Screen uses an advanced 3-D UI engine. It lets you interact with your Android phone with 2 main UI elements.<br>• The rotating 3-D app cube lets you quickly find and launch any app that is installed on your phone. <br>• The app carousel shows apps that you use most often. You can customize it by adding apps into the carousel or removing  them. Screen lets you access and launch apps by rotating the carousel. It has a “hot spot” position  - move any app in the carousel to the hot spot, and instantly see recent actions and updates for that app. Examples: <br>- Evernote Integration. Rotate the ring to Evernote and see the latest updates to your Evernote account. Not using Evernote? Get a free account at <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.evernote.com/about/referrer?code%3Daccess-screen&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEiAVg6E6mp4Sm34LMFazz1F1YNPA" target="_blank">http://www.evernote.com/about/referrer?code=access-screen</a><br>- Twitter , Facebook and Mixi . Tap on either of these services to see the latest updates from your Facebook and Mixi friends and the people that you follow on Twitter. <br>- Browser. See your browser bookmarks by rotating or tapping the browser icon. Go to any of your bookmarked pages quickly by tapping on an entry. <br>- Contacts. Scroll through your favorite and recent contacts and access them with the contacts service icon. <br>- Call History. Missed a call from someone? Call them back easily with a tap on an entry in the list that displays when you choose the call history service icon. <p>Background:  Pick a wallpaper picture of your choice for the home screen background. <p>Widgets: Add your choice of widgets to the default home screen display so that anytime you press the home button, your chosen widgets, up to three (space permitting) will be displayed with the ring of services', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.access_company.android.nflifescreen', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/lwh8klToaYAHQdDsk4SFJE1G9nvadmgOa_RQy1qkSX7hWbJVX_mbCR1-1YDviwA1xuU', 3.61, 'TOOLS', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.READ_CONTACTS, android.permission.READ_SMS, android.permission.READ_CALENDAR, com.android.browser.permission.READ_HISTORY_BOOKMARKS, android.permission.CALL_PHONE, android.permission.BIND_APPWIDGET, android.permission.SET_PREFERRED_APPLICATIONS, android.permission.CHANGE_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.BLUETOOTH, android.permission.BLUETOOTH_ADMIN, android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE, android.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, android.permission.WRITE_SECURE_SETTINGS, android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, com.google.android.gm.permission.READ_GMAIL, com.google.android.providers.gmail.permission.READ_GMAIL, com.access_company.android.nflifebrowser.permission.db, android.permission.READ_CALL_LOG'),
(117, 'com.penser.note', 'Evernote InkNote', 'penser', 'inknote is a powerful handwirting calligraphy note, focusing on digital ink rendering, storage, compression technology. it also including photo,voice,handwriting,text,etc. You can not only using as a notepad, but also writing something in a calligraphy style and draw something.<br>    inknote is not for profit, only designed to give you a good handwriting experience.<p>Main features:<br>    1 Handwriting calligraphy rendering, built-in variety of calligraphy styles<br>    2.Handwriting calligraphy and edit system, including handwriting calligraphy generation module and editing module.<br>    3. Digital ink compression technology is used to save ink handwriting dynamic information, you can replay the process of handwriting<br>    4 handwriting, text, voice, images, notes and other commonly used functions of note<p>why designing inknote?<br>    With the widespread use of touch screen, many new technologies of human-computer interaction are invented, Undoubtedly handwriting interaction is one of the most convenient technologies. There are some researches on the digital handwriting calligraphy generation, but the effect is far from satisfied. How to take advantage of the limited information to restore the diversity of calligraphy is a very challenging research topic.<p>System Requirements: <br>    Android4.0 or later<p>I am sorry for my poor English, if there is any error, please let me know, thank you very much!<br>    <br>For inknote, any suggestions?  <a href="mailto:inknote.penser@gmail.com">inknote.penser@gmail.com</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.penser.note', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/D-eZZ4C4W3vOxw28NJyYfVno-atdwe1NdVyUDKR4WDAi5GgSo-WiMt1-Q1wOqETJ9zD-', 4.92, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '1,000+', 'android.permission.RESTART_PACKAGES, com.android.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.PERMISSION_NAME, android.permission.READ_LOGS, android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE, android.permission.MOUNT_UNMOUNT_FILESYSTEMS'),
(118, 'com.access_company.android.nflifedocuments', 'NetFront Life Documents', 'ACCESS CO., LTD.', 'Download NetfrontTM Life Documents – A Document Viewer for Microsoft Office® Documents (Word, Excel, PowerPoint and Text Files)<p>Features:<br>-View Microsoft Office® (Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and Text) files on the go<br>-Does what you want to do on the go: Lets you view Documents, and does it right!<br>-The Document Reader with the best rendering of all the complicated details in Word, Excel, and PowerPoint files<br>-Full support for Office 2007 file formats (.docx, .xlsx, and .pptx plus .doc, .xls, .ppt, and .txt files.)<br>-Evernote Integration – Access documents in the cloud<br>-Interactive Document Viewing with Pinch to Zoom support<br>-Supports Portrait and Landscape Mode<br>-Search Text in documents, or Copy to Clipboard to use in another application<br>-Easy file browsing with helpful filters<br>-Many options for file access and storage: SD Card support, open docs attached to emails, web downloads, and more!<p>Stay Productive On the Go<br>NetfrontTM Life Documents lets you view Microsoft Office® files on your Android phone or tablet. It’s a quick and easy way to review your documents - no need to fire up the laptop! <p>Easy File Browsing <br>The included file organizer shows you all documents on the device and let you filter them by category (e.g. Excel documents only). You can also search for files and open them from the list view – or delete them. <p>Interactive Document Viewing<br>Open and view MS Word, Excel® and PowerPoint® files. Documents can be opened from the file organizer or straight from your email inbox. You can view them in portrait or landscape mode and zoom in and out as you need it. You can also search for specific text inside the documents, or copy text to the clipboard for use in another application. <p>Evernote Integration<br>NetfrontTM Life Documents can access your Evernote® account to download and view any Microsoft Office® files you have stored. Likewise you can upload any documents from your device to your Evernote account for later access on any device or computer. Don’t have an Evernote account yet? Sign up for free here <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.evernote.com/about/referrer?code%3Daccess-docs&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFXHZSFiVpUuDGo2tswYCiHj-zzDA" target="_blank">http://www.evernote.com/about/referrer?code=access-docs</a>!<p>Many Options for File Access and Storage<br>Files can be stored and accessed on the device (memory or SD-Card) or in your Evernote® account. Other ways of getting to your files are to open them from the email inbox, copying files to the Android device while it’s connected to your computer or saving them from the web using the browser.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.access_company.android.nflifedocuments', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/f_MocVeuUILolrd0otUhpaJsDjUBVcjrat28YGJJKH-bARVKqwrmxpeOjcyEP0o-8A', 4.08, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '100,000+', 'com.android.email.permission.READ_ATTACHMENT, com.android.email.permission.ACCESS_PROVIDER, com.google.android.gm.permission.READ_GMAIL, com.google.android.providers.gmail.permission.READ_GMAIL'),
(119, 'jp.co.omronsoft.BizcaroidLite', 'Bizcaroid Lite', 'OMRON Software Co.,Ltd.', '&quot;Bizcaroid Lite&quot; is the application to read the contents of Business Card by handset camera.<p>?Features?<br>?Business card reader<br>?- Read the following items from the card and display the results. (editable)<br>???Name<br>???Company<br>???Division<br>???Job Title<br>???Zip code<br>???Address<br>???Tel<br>???Fax<br>???E-mail<br>???Web<br>?Save contact<br>?- Read the contact details on Business card and save them to Address book.<br>?Multilingual settings (Japanese, English, German, French, Italian, Spanish, Chinese (Simplified))<br>?- Display language switching corresponding to the &quot;System Locale&quot;.<br>?- Language switching of card reader by the user settings.(Japanese, English)<br>?Design settings<br>?- Switch screen design.<br>?Evernote cooperation<br>?- Directly launch &quot;Evernote for Android&quot;.<br>??(If you have not installed the application, Evernote home page will be displayed.)<br>?- Upload the captured images of Business cards to Evernote (User&#39;s note) .<br>??(For uploading images, &quot;business card&quot; are tagged.)<p>?Requirements?<br> ? An Android 2.1 smartphone or higher with camera attached.<br>    * An auto-focus capable camera is required<br>    * A 2 megapixel camera or higher is recommended<p>* Evernote and the Evernote logo are registered trademarks of U.S. Evernote Corporation.<br>* Bizcaroid is a registered trademark of the OMRON Corporation.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.omronsoft.BizcaroidLite', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/mO8bhe7xOqrY6eXguRbDYSyyHgPg5J38JbRMuu4kVkkXB-BWIIq7rUd_I64eisDoNNKL', 3.59, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.CAMERA, android.permission.READ_CONTACTS, android.permission.WRITE_CONTACTS, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.READ_CALL_LOG, android.permission.WRITE_CALL_LOG'),
(120, 'de.innovationz.snapcapture.noroot', 'SnapCapture for Snapchat', 'innovationZ', 'SnapCapture is the most popular solution for easy snapchat saving.<br>It just takes one click to save all the unopened snapchats in your inbox permanently on your device.<br><br><br>FEATURES:<p> * Save unopened snapchat pictures<br> * Save unopened snapchat videos<br> * Enjoy your saved snapchat pictures and videos in a beautiful gallery<br> * No time limit<br> * The sender of the snapchats won&#39;t get notified<br> * No root access required<br> * Ad-free<p>SnapCapture saves the first 20 snapchats for free, try it now!<br>Full version for unlimited saving can be unlocked in-app.<p>If you have root access, switch to &quot;SnapCapture [ROOT]&quot; for additional features!<p>[Q&amp;A]<br>1. It says &quot;Unknown Error&quot;, what&#39;s wrong?<br>Please send a email to <a href="mailto:innovationz.de@gmail.com">innovationz.de@gmail.com</a> describing your problem.<p>2. I can&#39;t download a specific snap, but it works with others.<br>Please go into Snapchat settings and clear the feed to avoid this problem in the future.<p>3. Where do I sign up?<br>If you don&#39;t have a Snapchat account yet, download Snapchat to sign up.<p>4. I can&#39;t find the download icon.<br>Press the menu button of your device and select &quot;Capture snapchats&quot;<p>Feel free to contact <a href="mailto:innovationz.de@gmail.com">innovationz.de@gmail.com</a> for further questions.<p>This software is provided &quot;as is&quot; and may not offer its advertised functionality in future as it is depends on the further development of the Snapchat application.<br>The &#39;Snapchat&#39; application as a whole and all rights, titles, and interests in and to the application are owned by the Snapchat, Inc.<br>This application is not affiliated or related with Snapchat, Inc. in any way.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=de.innovationz.snapcapture.noroot', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/F-KmIsooWc4OvshEXm2WIuW0ix0MhcyhR46ceTPXX-_I2JzfMIt-u0drteP6eqNFlw8', 4.21, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '500,000+', 'com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS'),
(121, 'com.zwunk.snapsave', 'Snapsave for Snapchat', 'Zwunk Mobile', 'ROOTED PHONE NOT REQUIRED<p>Snapsave for Snapchat is the ultimate Snapchat replacement app. We tried to recreate the Snapchat experience with the added feature of being able to view snaps as many times as you want without letting the sender know! You can also save the snap to your gallery. And you can still let the sender know that you viewed if you want to use Snapchat the normal way.<p>This version lets you view 25 snaps before it asks for a one-off in-app-purchase of $1. <p>NEW VERSION DECEMBER 2013 FINALLY LETS YOU SAVE VIDEOS AS WELL AS IMAGES!<p>FEATURES:<p>* Save unopened snapchat pictures<br>* Save unopened snapchat videos<br>* Enjoy your saved snapchat pictures with no timer running down<br>* Save snapchats to your phone gallery<br>* Usually the sender doesn&#39;t get notified you&#39;ve viewed, unless you want them to by clicking the TrollFace icon<br>* No root access needed', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.zwunk.snapsave', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/v2HLA48lgQLhJAhSe1YrM06hEPnlx6yGG57I4ul7dxJcvsGgyMIEkWIuX5a9LKYnMLs', 3.64, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '100,000+', 'com.zwunk.snapsave.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.READ_CONTACTS, android.permission.FLASHLIGHT, android.permission.CAMERA, android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO, android.permission.SEND_SMS, com.android.vending.BILLING'),
(122, 'com.snapkeep', 'SnapKeep for SnapChat', 'GhostApps', '*** No Root Required ***<br>*** Saves BOTH pictures and videos ***<br>*** Sign into ANY SnapChat account ***<br>*** Works on tablets like the Nexus 7 ***<p>SnapKeep is designed to save those SnapChats from friends that you think you might need in the future.<p>Simply login with your SnapChat details and the application will check to see if there are any SnapChats waiting for you.<p>If there are, SnapKeep will let you download them to your phone while leaving them in your SnapChat account!<p>The sender gets no indication this has happened and you can still open the SnapChat in the normal way.<p>This can all be done without the complicated rooting process that other SnapChat saving apps require.<p>This is my first app so if you have issues or find any bugs please contact me before leaving a review so I can fix it.<p>PLEASE NOTE, THIS APPLICATION CANNOT RETRIEVE SNAPCHATS THAT HAVE ALREADY BEEN OPENED.<p>This software is provided &quot;as is&quot; and may not always offer its advertised functionality in future as it is dependent on the Snapchat application operates as it does when this application was developed.<p>The &#39;Snapchat&#39; application as a whole and all rights, titles, and interests in and to the application are owned by the Snapchat, Inc. This application is in no way affiliated with the Snapchat, Inc.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.snapkeep', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/nQAY80aaTkg4_oTqIHOx1pC-YLnbbMf1ee32n8OEu5PDkmsplyU2x34bwiV0-0tjSK4', 3.23, 'COMMUNICATION', '$0.99', '10,000+', ''),
(123, 'com.appztastic.snapchatsavepics', 'SnapChat Save Pics', 'Appztastic', 'SnapChat Save Pics is a SnapChat client that lets you view snaps without the sender knowing! You can also save all your snaps to the gallery. And you can let the sender know you&#39;ve viewed like normal by clicking one button. It&#39;s 100% FREE and does NOT REQUIRE ROOT.<p>FEATURES:<p>* Save unopened snapchat pics<br>* View your snapchat pictures anytime in the client<br>* The sender of the snaps doesnt&#39;t get notified<br>* No time limit countdown on snap viewing<br>* No root access required<p>Unfortunately, video is not supported at this time. And it can&#39;t magically view snaps that have already been viewed in the official app!<p>SnapCapture saves the first 20 snapchats for free, try it now!<br>Full version for unlimited saving can be unlocked in-app.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.appztastic.snapchatsavepics', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/RaVjPxUmFmy9mJnWAMeLf2khizIDv-XRlUAvmr17Uav8DyaZffRQm2c4DlyxgbkJSgY', 4.03, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '100,000+', 'com.appztastic.snapchatsavepics.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.READ_CONTACTS, android.permission.FLASHLIGHT, android.permission.CAMERA, android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO, android.permission.SEND_SMS, com.android.vending.BILLING'),
(124, 'com.cfg.supersnap', 'SuperSnap for Snapchat', 'cfg apps', 'Send Snapchat snaps from gallery and automatically save snaps to your phone, and more!<br>Use your existing Snapchat username and password to get started right away.<p>***Note: Turn off &quot;Save snaps I send&quot; (default is off), causes text to not show up for some users, patch coming soon!<p>Features:<br>-No ROOT required<br>-No limit on text length, no limit on video duration (1mb max)<br>-Snapchat saver ability will automatically capture and saves all snaps that haven&#39;t been opened in Snapchat, no time limits<br>-Don&#39;t need to keep logging back into Snapchat because SuperSnap can completely replace your Snapchat app<br>-Better camera options available than Snapchat&#39;s by using phone&#39;s camera app<br>-Use fun camera apps to draw on your snaps, add stickers, and more! (ex. &quot;LINE camera&quot; app)<br>-Send and receive longer videos (turn your video app quality down for longer videos, 1mb max = ~50sec @ low quality)<br>-Send Snapchat photos and videos from your gallery, even animated gifs (receiver must also have SuperSnap for animated gifs, regular Snapchat users won&#39;t be animated, 1mb max on all snaps)<p>Bugs being looked into (please send me an email with as much detail as possible if you have these problems):<br>-Text not showing up for some users<br>-iPhone users receiving all black screen snaps<p>FAQ:<br>Q: How do you send from gallery?<br>A: Open your gallery app and select the picture you want, then hit the share button. It will ask what you want to share with, pick SuperSnap.<br>Q: How do I fix &quot;Message size limit reached&quot; when I try to record video?<br>A: Go into your video recorder app and lower the quality. You are trying to send HD video, so it reaches the 1mb max too fast.<br>Q: I accidentally deleted a snap, can I re-download it?<br>A: If it&#39;s still unopened in Snapchat, clear SuperSnap data in your app manager to re-download all unopened snaps.<p>Logo artwork by Rachelle L Miller.<br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.sweet-tactics.net/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGm0vA1GHE9kdlUoR7GYhTjWTr_xQ" target="_blank">http://www.sweet-tactics.net/</a><p>Super Snap is not affiliated with Snapchat.<br>Super Snap is provided &quot;as-is&quot; and is dependent on the future development of Snapchat.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.cfg.supersnap', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/0F8slKL8xxXcvwP1_eCtb5721VBftA01W0D5eyS0vqcSFyMqvxjf43Q_3RBBkCZUTYw', 3.70, 'SOCIAL', '$0.99', '5,000+', 'android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED'),
(125, 'com.apparitionhq.instasnap', 'InstaSnap - Not Like Snapchat!', 'InstaSnap Social Photo Sharing', '&quot;Snap Life for an Instant&quot; <p><br>Share your dorky, funny, goofy, sexy, embarrassing, sexting, hilarious, &amp; wild photos with the best Free photo-messaging app! Your photos are safe, can’t be saved and disappear from your friends phone forever.  Add awesome captions to your photos, draw funny stuff on them, then share them with your friends!<p><br>Follow us @InstaSnapApp (<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.twitter.com/InstaSnapApp&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFj_YArYDzjfVqqH_gdNewZo7WpRg" target="_blank">http://www.twitter.com/InstaSnapApp</a>) for cool updates!<p><br>“Its amazing Its the best app i have on my phone. Its so easy to use and instead of it charging you to send pictures ln a text you can send them on here and it wont coat a thing. All in all this app it simply amazing. Xx” - Abby Clarke <p>“Amazeballs This is seriously amazing, so much better than snapchat, especially for HTC Cha Cha, actually works, I love it :D” - Clarey Elliott  <p>“Asome I. Totally recomend this to others Brilliant no words for how cool it is” - Clodagh West <p>&quot;Cool I think its cool follow me on instagram @hey_its_chloe246 Ok&quot; - Chloe Rogers <p><br>Share your photos with your friends, family, boyfriend or girlfriend with the safety and security of knowing that no screenshot can be saved.  Plus pictures can’t be saved in the receiver’s app.  After the pic is viewed, it’s gone forever!  <p><br>Fun, private picture texting (SMS) has never been easier!<p><br>--- Keep your private picture-text-messages secret, safe and secure with the coolest photo messaging app.  Have fun and be safe sexting and sharing your ‘secret’ photo messages ---<p><br>Features:<br>• Easy to use!<br>• MAKE THE APP YOURS! Use the in-app Feedback and Survey feature to let us know what you want in future versions.  <br>• Draw on your private photo messages! Add dorky drawings and cool mustaches! :)<br>• Best private photo sharing app.<br>• Works like a texting (SMS) app except with photos and is more fun.  Once you get a photo, you can send one right back easily!<br>• Add captions to your photos with the Free text editor!<br>• No cost to send your pictures internationally!  Great for couples in separate countries or cities in long-distance relationships, sexting made easy and free.<br>• Did we mention it’s Free so send your pic “texts”!<br>• More fun than Snapchat, Clipchat or other so-called &quot;sexting&quot; apps.<br>• Send pictures already on your phone or take new ones from the camera.<br>• Great Free alternative to SMS apps.<br>• Send and receive unlimited photos for free quickly and securely - no restrictions now!<br>• Choose from three awesome free ringtones to change the notification sound<p><br>Safety &amp; Security (aka, just a few reasons InstaSnap is balla’):<br>• Photo’s only stay on the server until the other person has viewed them (this is so people who are offline can see their pix later), then they’re deleted forever.<br>• Your photos are safe via 128-bit encryption and can only be decrypted by the person you send them to.<br>• Photos cannot be saved on your friend’s phone!  <br>• Your friends can’t take a screenshot when using the awesomest texting messaging app :)<p><br>We liked Snapchat (and Facebook has jumped on the bandwagon with Facebook Poke) but both allowed the receiver to take a screenshot.  So really, your photos weren&#39;t safe from unwanted eyes seeing them, or if the phone was ever stolen.  Not cool!<p><br>We solved that problem by not allowing a user to take a screenshot while using InstaSnap.  Photos also will “self-destruct” (which means they’re not saved on the server or your friends phone) after they have been viewed.  So there’s no way for your personal, goofy or sexy private-photo-messages to be saved by anyone else!<p><br>A few techy things…<p>• InstaSnap only works on devices that have a phone number and NOT TABLETS - yet.<br>• INSTASNAP ONLY WORKS WITH INSTASNAP and not other photo sharing apps, like Snapchat, Facebook Poke, Clipchat, Instagram, Wink or Squak!<p><br>We love to hear from our InstaSnapa’s!  Write us at <a href="mailto:FANS@INSTASNAPAPP.COM">FANS@INSTASNAPAPP.COM</a> or use the Feedback feature in the app.  <p><br>Download InstaSnap today for FREE and have fun InstaSnap’n!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.apparitionhq.instasnap', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/LPHlgNJEU6iYipTAt7BWxDpKu8iuL5ZRqp7qFJ2v4OqTUajCqZyJKM8O7TbJSyWaSA', 3.94, 'LIFESTYLE', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.WRITE_INTERNAL_STORAGE, android.permission.KILL_BACKGROUND_PROCESSES, android.permission.RESTART_PACKAGES, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, android.permission.READ_CONTACTS, android.permission.SEND_SMS, android.permission.RECEIVE_SMS, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.READ_LOGS, android.permission.GET_TASKS, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, com.apparitionhq.instasnap.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION'),
(126, 'com.projectggk.snapsave', 'Snap Saver for Snapchat', 'Harima Kenji', '<b>***ROOT REQUIRED! ***</b><br>IMPORTANT: This app requires your device to be rooted for it to work. If you don&#39;t know what that means, then your device probably isn&#39;t rooted and this app will not work as a result.<p>Formerly known as &quot;SnapChat Save&quot; which was taken down due to alleged trademark infringement, now reuploaded with a new name and icon. It&#39;s the same great app as before. <p>This app will allow you to save incoming Snapchat pictures and videos! Does not notify the sender!<p><br>The app now has a built-in gallery for quickly opening and viewing up saved Snapchats. <p><b>Paid users get:</b><br>- No Ads<br>- Auto Save (pictures and videos automatically saved whenever Snapchat is opened)<br>- Option to choose which individual Snapchat pictures to save<br>- Refresh Saved Snapchat folder in Gallery<br>- Duplicate search and delete of Saved Snapchats (duplicates sometimes occur when the Snapchat app refreshes its caches)<br>- (coming soon) Ability to hide specific pictures from the Android gallery<p><p>If you have any problems, feel free to e-mail me.<p><br>This app is not in any way affiliated with Snapchat Inc. &quot;Snapchat&quot; is a wordmark of Snapchat Inc, and the use of the word is not meant to infringe on their trademark.<p><p>If you experience any bugs or problems, please e-mail me!<p><br><u><b>Changelog: </b></u><p><b>1.8 beta</b><br>- Re-did implementation. Should be easier to find bugs and expand features.<br>- Bug fixes<p><b>1.7 beta</b><br>- Fixed compatibility with newest Snapchat beta.<p><b>1.6 beta</b><br>- New auto-save implementation. Should be working fine now for both pictures and videos. It will automatically check and save pics/vids when Snapchat is opened. (Paid only)<br>- Minor bug fixes.<p><b>1.5</b><br>- Minor bug fixes. <br>- Added basic auto-save picture option for paid users. <br>Let me know if you run into any problems with this. Contact-specific actions and auto-saving videos will come in the near future.<p><br><b>1.4</b><br>- Improved interaction with Android&#39;s gallery. <br>- Fixed video saving problems occurring on Android 4.0 and below. (Thanks to Thomas for being a patient tester). <br>- Other minor fixes and optimizations. <p><br><b>1.3</b><br>- Fixes and optimizations.<p><br><b>1.2</b><br>- In-app gallery should be more stable now.<br>- In the preview/choose-files part (for paid users), clicking on the thumbnail will now open the picture in Gallery for better preview.<br>- Fixed a couple of silly bugs happening on older devices.<br>- For paid users, there&#39;s a(n experimental) new option when pressing the menu button: &quot;Delete Duplicates&quot;. It will search for duplicate files in the Saved Snapchats folder and automatically delete all but the newest/oldest one. Duplicates sometimes occur when the Snapchat app refreshes its cache.<p><p><b>1.1</b><br>- Bug fixes and optimizations.<br>- Added a simple in-app gallery for saved snapchats.<br>- Paid users can now also preview and choose specifically which pictures to save.<p>I wanted to get an update out quick to fix some weird bugs but its not yet completely polished. The kinks (especially with the in-app gallery) should be straightened out with coming updates.<p><p><p><p><b>Info on rooting:</b><p>Be aware that rooting your phone might void your warranty. Of course there are methods to restore it so that they don’t know it was ever rooted, but you might not feel comfortable with that.<br>Also, I recommend backing up your phone before trying to root.<br> <br>Here’s a nice guide if you want to familiarize yourself with what rooting is, its benefits, etc: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.talkandroid.com/guides/beginner/newbies-guide-to-rooting/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGUJssOfTj9Mrh61Xe3ZlYsDmAs2g" target="_blank">http://www.talkandroid.com/guides/beginner/newbies-guide-to-rooting/</a><br> <br>Now the exact steps to root a phone depends on the phone’s model, but here are some useful resources: <br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.androidcentral.com/root&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHmIxmTYEjgGws-Mpx-v1x0s5gSPw" target="_blank">http://www.androidcentral.com/root</a><br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://lifehacker.com/5789397/the-always-up%2Bto%2Bdate-guide-to-rooting-any-android-phone&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEsUf_UeM4bnnAX5yrFsVlYzg-KMw" target="_blank">http://lifehacker.com/5789397/the-always-up+to+date-guide-to-rooting-any-android-phone</a><br>Or just Google “ root”', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.projectggk.snapsave', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/Qjv1p7EhVfBWURLZfKRV3bVwEo72dS5djMDRF_grm-j-smp5Yaq0ze6w-apg-o0tJUw', 3.88, 'TOOLS', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_SUPERUSER, com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.READ_LOGS, com.android.vending.CHECK_LICENSE'),
(127, 'uk.co.appcheatz.a00snappedcheat', 'Snapchat Cheats', 'AllAppz', 'Snapchat Cheats gives you all the latest tips and tricks for snapchat. Currently not many but sure more will be implemented in time. <p>This application is not affiliated or partnered with Snapchat.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=uk.co.appcheatz.a00snappedcheat', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/KrIVJf7-GXIWIh4VE9tL_Ap1BRUM7dksn9fxv8dNK7G9fuvfQtTsCi611sj93uCh_hA', 2.50, 'PHOTOGRAPHY', 'Free', '100,000+', ''),
