(133, 'com.eth10.snappeeker', 'Peek-a-Snapchat', 'Dev10 Productions', '****ROOT IS REQUIRED FOR THIS APP TO WORK PROPERLY****<br>If you&#39;re phone is NOT rooted then you may only be able to save videos, or nothing at all.<p>Save unopened snapchats without notifying the sender. Unlike some other apps, Peek-a-Snap does not require you to log in and override the original Snapchat application. <p>If enabled in Settings &gt; Accessibility, this application will monitor incoming Snapchat notifications to automatically save new Snapchat pictures without any further action. <br>If your device is running Android 4.3 or above, enable the Notification Listener in Settings &gt; Security &gt; Notification Access instead of the accessibility service to automatically save new Snapchats.<p>Features:<br>- Save Snapchat pictures<br>- Save Snapchat videos<br>- Easily view and delete pictures and videos in a gallery<br>- Move or copy saved snapchats to a different folder<br>- Accessibility or Notification Listener service to automatically save snapchat pictures<p>Snapchats are saved in &quot;sdcard/Pictures/Snaps&quot; by default.<p>If you would like to support development of this application, you can now DONATE and remove ads (accessed from the menu).<p>If you experience any bugs or have any suggestions, feel free to send me an e-mail. If you are reporting an issue please INCLUDE A LOG that records when the issue happens, otherwise I will not be able to help you if you just tell me what is happening, thank you!<br>e-mail address: <br>eth10 DOT developer AT gmail DOT com<p>This app is not in any way affiliated with Snapchat Inc. &quot;Snapchat&quot; is a wordmark of Snapchat Inc, and the use of the word is not meant to infringe on their trademark.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.eth10.snappeeker', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/001FK7gthUZktwL8yO4F2tIk13l8lBnAuPt0eeNVMS5Ch72Kesm1JuQr_uX9oQQEtOfl', 3.71, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '5,000+', 'android.permission.GET_TASKS, com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.ACCESS_SUPERUSER'),
(134, 'com.chatforsnapchat', 'Chat Room for SnapChat', 'Cupids Chat Rooms', 'Chat with other Snap Chat users using our CupidsChat - chat rooms. Find new SnapChat users that share your similar interest. You can even and add them to your friends list, so you can chat with them later.  Use the chat rooms to exchange Snap Chat usernames. Best of all, chatting is free and live. So what are you waiting for ? Time to find new friends today. <p>Benefits:<br>•	Real SnapChat Users<br>•	Snap Chat users from worldwide, not just the  US<br>•	Live instant chat, no delay ( Fast US Servers)<br>•	Multiple chat rooms for different interests, not only for finding SnapChat Users<br>•	Create your own profile, and view others<br>•	Safe - ability to report users &amp; active moderation<br>•	spamming &amp; bad word filters enabled<br>•	Colorful emoticons<p>Reviews:<br>&quot;Lots of people to talk to. It&#39;s really cool.  I made friends and found many SnapChat users!&quot; - Lilian<p>&quot; Cool App. Fun and easy to meet people.&quot; - Hailey <p>&quot;I wish I found this app sooner. Now I have a lot more fun when I&#39;m bored, and I found a ton of new Snap Chat friends!&quot; - Lucy<p>For best performance please connect to WI-Fi. <p>Chatrooms for SnapChat  are for users 18 years and older only. Even though this is a mature chat, do not upload adult or offensive content. If caught violating our terms, your account will be blocked permanently.<p>Disclaimer: These chat rooms are maintained by CupidsChat.com, and are in no way affiliated with SnapChat. SnapChat is a trademark of SnapChat Inc.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.chatforsnapchat', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/Xsqm6WlG5mfe_xfcGEsDSe0cxHmN3f8zp5GcKa0Tbe3_szLULSCmiSsPiCO7iLGEMxI', 3.88, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '1,000+', 'android.permission.RESTART_PACKAGES, android.permission.CAMERA, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, com.android.vending.BILLING'),
(135, 'com.scratch.pic', 'ScratchPic - like snapchat', 'Double G', 'Take a pic and send it... Scratch it and guess it! <p>Scratch Pic - What&#39;s your itch? <p>Take a picture from either your camera, your gallery or even right from your Facebook albums. You can also draw your own pictures. Assign a word to the picture, and send it to a friend. Then, when they get it, that&#39;s called an Itch, and it needs to be scratched. So, start scratching! As soon as you know what the image is, try and guess the word. But if you&#39;re not quick about it, your opponent is gonna win that round and steel all the coins.<p>&quot;Scratch Pic is a game for the whole family. So much fun to play!&quot;<p>&quot;Scratch Pic is like Snapchat and Draw Something combined!&quot;<p>&quot;It&#39;s fun and let&#39;s you be very creative!&quot;<p>&quot;This will be my new obsession! It&#39;s like Snapchat, but a game&quot;<p>&quot;I love it! It takes a concept like snapchat and turned it into a guessing game.&quot;<p>&quot;So much fun! So addicting!&quot;', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.scratch.pic', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/-b67V9IN0m1VfeqPW1bvgy69zuZbMTNZlgK-ZQhpJZ8V_q9uCGyCJd1JAwPEEfvTXO8w', 4.00, 'BRAIN', 'Free', '1,000+', 'com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.INTERNET, android.permission.CAMERA, android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.WAKE_LOCK, com.scratch.pic.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE'),
(136, 'com.dainiax.gcm2', 'SkyDater - Snapchat for Dating', 'Lot Invest', 'Browse profiles of daters nearby.<p>Every member has 1 hidden secret photo. Answer 3 questions and see it. Photo disappears after 10 seconds.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dainiax.gcm2', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/4rqqDczC-3Bk5-oyewpC8Y8pBAE5fFDYKFdsLg3lRD90VqN0swPwQr-_TQAseP7d_g', 4.67, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '1,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, com.dainiax.gcm2.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, android.permission.READ_CONTACTS'),
(137, 'com.cosmicexploration.snapdownloader_root', 'SnapDownload For Snapchat Root', 'Cosmic Exploration', '**Rooted / Jailbroken Phone or Tablet Required**<br>**Rooted / Jailbroken Phone or Tablet Required**<p>Compatible with new Snapchat update.<p>Quick and easy way to save your Snapchat photos forever.  No longer will you be stuck with no way to save your Snapchat photos, you&#39;ll now be able to save them before Snapchat deletes them.  <p>You can view your Snaps here or copy to your Gallery.  Enable automatic scanning and images will automatically be imported to the app.<p><br>So easy to use:<br>(1) On a ROOTED device, grant root access.<br>(2) Choose &quot;Refresh&quot; to load up your Snapchat photos.<br>(3) Keep or move them to gallery.<p><br>Not affiliated with Snapchat in any way.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.cosmicexploration.snapdownloader_root', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/qHlpBqsB60bC02cfEtTIkNya885A57H-SUPcuYWEJ47pXr4HA-g6JZotNwYSC4GFesA', 2.78, 'SOCIAL', '$0.99', '100+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_SUPERUSER'),
(138, 'com.im.fantastic.snapchatforum', 'Snapchat Forum', 'InfiniteMonkeys.mobi Apps', 'If you are looking for snapchat usernames you&#39;ve come to the right place. Snapchatforum have developed an app to give you the ease of finding snapchat usernames by live chat or community talk.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.im.fantastic.snapchatforum', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/L4veMTdyf0qhUxRF02Ic23IEYceJjijUFpCZvZ1VGMuH597awb34IgK4jSbzse0oDQ', 3.00, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '1,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.CAMERA'),
(139, 'com.cbs.sportsapp.android.ole', 'Ole Miss Sports', 'CBS Sports.com College Network', 'This is the OFFICIAL application of Ole Miss created by the CBSSports.com College Network, in partnership with the University. This exclusive sports application offers LIVE STREAMED games:<p>************************************************************<br>LIVE VIDEO* &amp; AUDIO*<br>- Upgrade in the application to stream select games<br>************************************************************<p>* Audio and video are only available on certain compatible Android devices running OS2.2 or later. This device has not been tested for video compatibility. In order to access the audio or video please install the Sports Media Player in Google Play and re-launch this application.<p>Annual Subscription $9.99<p>ADDITIONAL APPLICATION FEATURES<p>-	Live Scoring<br>-	Play-by-Play<br>-	Complete Sport Schedules<br>-	Exclusive breaking sports news<br>-	Video on demand<br>-	Alerts (game start and final scores)<br>-	Team and Coaches Rosters &amp; Bios<br>-	 Much more…<p>COVERS ALL SCHOOL SPORTS!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.cbs.sportsapp.android.ole', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/DviCMQ7y2dwYacNPw3_vfJlJXX9zQVXk56yDJGBdbFqRZe0oPk47Ai-00wdLMOUziLjQ', 4.67, 'SPORTS', 'Free', '5,000+', 'android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, com.cbs.sportsapp.android.ole.permission.C2D_MESSAGE');
