(140, 'com.mobilerush.olemissfootballrush', 'Ole Miss Football *FREE*', 'Mobile Rush LLC.', 'Do you love Ole Miss Football? The Ole Miss Football Rush is now available to you for FREE but for a *Limited Time*! Now you can catch the Ole Miss Football game!<p>Features of this app include:<p>* Ole Miss Football News<br>* Ole Miss Football Videos<br>* Ole Miss Football Photos<br>* Fan Wall<br>* Ole Miss Rebels Shop<br>* Talk Smack Against Other Teams<br>* Connect Easily With Mobile Rush<br>* NCAA Scores<br>* NCAA Standings<br>* Ole Miss Rebels Schedule<br>* Ole Miss Rebels Roster<br>* and MORE!<p>DISCLAIMER: Mobile Rush is not affiliated with Ole Miss Football. But a 3rd party company that&#39;s dedicated to connecting Ole Miss Football fans with their team as best as possible. With wallpaper, live wallpapers, background and theme.  77777<p>The history of Ole Miss Football from Wikipedia.<p>The Ole Miss Rebels football team represents the University of Mississippi, also known as Ole Miss, in the sport of American football. The Rebels compete in the Football Bowl Subdivision (FBS) of the National Collegiate Athletics Association (NCAA) and the Western Division of the Southeastern Conference (SEC). The football history of Ole Miss includes the formation of the first football team in the state and the 26th team on the list of college football&#39;s all-time winning programs. The Ole Miss Rebels posted their 600th win on September 27, 2008 when they defeated the (then ranked No. 4 and future 2008 BCS National Champ) Florida Gators 31–30 at Ben Hill Griffin Stadium in Gainesville, Florida.<p>Throughout the 115-year history of Ole Miss football, the Rebels have won six Southeastern Conference titles (1947, 1954, 1955, 1960, 1962, and 1963); they also have a claim to three national championships (1959, 1960, 1962).<p>In 1890, Dr. A.L. Bondurant, later the dean of the Ole Miss Graduate School, rallied Ole Miss students to help form an athletic department to encompass the sports of football, baseball and tennis. The students brought this initiative to reality and in 1893, with Bondurant as the coach, a football team came to fruition. The first team won four of five games during that inaugural football season. One of those wins was the very first football game ever played by an Ole Miss team, a 56–0 victory over Southwest Baptist University of Jackson, Tennessee (now known as Union University). This was on November 11, 1893.<p>The next year, 1894, Bondurant passed on his coaching duties. Ole Miss Football, a book published in 1980 by Sports Yearbook Company of Oxford, MS, says J.W.S. Rhea was the first coach at Ole Miss having been hired part-time by Bondurant and having led the 1894 team to a 6–1 record. The annual Ole Miss media guide lists C.D. Clark as the coach of the 1894 team and further says about him, &quot;Although it has never been documented, it is thought that C.D. Clark of Tufts was the first paid football coach at Ole Miss. His name appears as manager of the team as shown in the Ole Miss Magazine dated November 1894.&quot; The College Football Data Warehouse also lists Clark as the coach for the 1894 team.<p>Twice in its history, Ole Miss did not field a football team. In 1897, a yellow fever epidemic cancelled the football season. In 1943, football was abolished at all Mississippi state-supported institutions by the state college Board of Trustees due to World War II.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mobilerush.olemissfootballrush', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/XAoX8c1b7y3UfMsuPzfSsjTL_7RRLXMXd09FaHVzY4k0G7-1lZ-Vav7CiqHPnng7Rryj', 4.60, 'SPORTS', 'Free', '1,000+', 'android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, com.mobilerush.olemissfootballrush.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE'),
(141, 'smartPhones.rotatingWallpaper.college.mississippi_AND', 'Ole Miss Revolving Wallpaper', 'Smartphones Technologies, Inc.', 'Officially licensed Ole Miss Rebels Revolving Wallpaper app, with the background image automatically rotating between 10 different Ole Miss wallpapers. <p>Tap the logo on the top left of the Home Screen to access the settings menu, where you can select which images to display, customize transitions and change the timing. This revolving wallpaper also works with the Ole Miss Clock Widget &amp; Schedule Widget (sold separately). <p>Instructions: (1) After downloading, go to Menu &gt; Notifications to install; (2) Go to Menu &gt; Wallpaper &gt; Live Wallpaper to customize settings and set it as your wallpaper.<p>Tags: Ole Miss, Rebels, Mississippi, SEC, NCAA, college, football, basketball, March Madness, bowl games, Smartphones Technologies, Inc.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=smartPhones.rotatingWallpaper.college.mississippi_AND', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/34en5WJKYj3BGxhiw5_GTx1O2fm8KXlGkeihW3sHrI_0oKFynVAGtAjE6GMNz17uI1Go', 5.00, 'PERSONALIZATION', '$1.99', '100+', 'com.android.vending.CHECK_LICENSE, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION'),
(142, 'smartPhones.liveWallpaperV3.mississippi', 'Ole Miss Rebels Live Wallpaper', 'Smartphones Technologies, Inc.', 'Officially licensed Ole Miss Rebels Live Wallpaper, with animated 3D logo. Background animation alternates between &quot;Ole Miss&quot; and &quot;Rebels&quot;.<p>The Settings button lets you customize your live wallpaper with several options, including: where the logo should be on the page, on which pages the logo should appear, and how fast the logo animates. This live wallpaper also works with the Ole Miss Rebels Clock Widget (sold separately).<p>Instructions: (1)Download; (2)go to Menu&gt;Notifications to install; (3)go to Menu &gt; Wallpaper &gt; Live Wallpaper. Tap “Settings” to customize the look and performance of the wallpaper.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=smartPhones.liveWallpaperV3.mississippi', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/Td1pzDxzG0Xxq9ef_sJQCIoKe3WgzNf_pL3kOd6yyrJ9zbViTp3KQ96tW6pa6pnq', 4.27, 'SPORTS', '$1.99', '100+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, com.android.vending.CHECK_LICENSE'),
(143, 'com.smartPhones.clockwidget.ncaa.live.oleMiss_AND', 'Ole Miss Rebels Live Clock', 'Smartphones Technologies, Inc.', '**7 Day Free Trial!** Ole Miss Rebels Live Clock, with football and basketball scores below the clock when games are on. This widget lets you replace the standard clock in your phone with a custom Ole Miss clock, with instant access to schedules, news and scores by conference. <p>*2013-2014 schedules and scores are in the clock. If you don&#39;t see them, please update your app!<p>Subscription: This is an officially licensed product with royalties paid to the university. The $2.99 annual subscription is good for 12 months from date of purchase (after the free trial ends). If you don&#39;t like it, just cancel your subscription within 7 days and you won&#39;t be billed. To manage subscriptions, launch the Google Play Store app, then tap Menu &gt; My Apps &gt; Subscriptions.<p>- Includes 3 layouts: Flip Clock, Scoreboard &amp; Analog. (Scoreboard does not appear on the clock face with Analog, but you can still tap for scores).<br>- Tap the widget to see detailed scoreboard, schedule and news by conference<br>- With the widget open, tap the conference name to view other conference schedules, or tap the week number to view schedules for different weeks.<br>- Scoreboard will appear below the clock when games are on. In landscape mode, scores appear beside the clock.<br>- We don’t have room to show every game below the clock. To see more games, just tap the clock and select the Scores tab.<br>- To see other apps &amp; widgets for other teams, visit: www.SmartApps.com/College<p>INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS: This clock is a widget, not an app. To add the clock to your home screen, follow the installation instructions below:<br>OS 3.0 versions: After downloading: (1) go to Menu &gt; Notifications to install; (2) tap and hold on your home screen and select Widgets to add it to your phone. Tap the widget to see the latest conference schedule, news or scores, or to change user options.<br>OS 4.0 and above: On your Home Screen, go to Apps &gt; Widgets, then swipe over until you see your clock widget. Then tap and hold to drag it to the selected location on your home screen. If it doesn&#39;t work, make sure you have enough available space (you may need to move other icons). The space required is 4 wide x 2 high.<p>Time Zones: Schedule times are displayed based on the time zone set on your phone. When you change time zones, the scheduled times displayed in the widget will automatically adjust. <p>A Note on Live Scores: The scores on your clock will always be slightly behind the actual game time. Unfortunately, we can’t change the laws of physics. It takes a few seconds to enter the scores into the computer, go out to the server, come back to our server, and finally out to your phone. If you’re already watching the game live, just enjoy the game! <p>Warning: If you’re using a task killer, make sure you add the schedule widget to the exceptions list or it will kill the schedule updates.<p>Tags: Ole Miss, Rebels, SEC, Mississippi, sports, scores, scoreboard, NCAA, college, football, basketball, March Madness, bowl games, Smartphones Technologies, Inc., clock, widget', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.smartPhones.clockwidget.ncaa.live.oleMiss_AND', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/zy53ePycOyeImDwx6CrQJl2zdr_9lb-NlFBVV3gic2_nKPgYCKxCECiQPsKtVSoo2g', 4.71, 'SPORTS', 'Free', '500+', 'com.android.vending.CHECK_LICENSE, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS'),
(144, 'olemissitalia.ccfc', 'Ole Miss Italia', 'Russell Christensen', 'Looking for an easy way to share the Gospel with your Italian friends? Ole Miss Crusade has put together several tools to help you.<p>Included in the app are:<br>1) Would You Like to Know God Personally? (One of the most effective and widely used tools of all time in English and Italian.)<br>2) Four Masterpieces (Four masterpieces and four key points of the Knowing God Personally booklet in English/Italian.)<br>3) The book of Romans/Romani (The Apostle Paul’s letter to the Romans in Italian.)<br>4) Sex and the City Uncovered ( In the book, Sex and the City Uncovered, Marian Jordan writes, “A painful existence of ‘looking for love in all the wrong places’ is hidden behind images of couture fashion, witty dialogue, and beautiful people. I know this to be true because I’ve lived it.” A former party girl with her own personal stories of hookups, hangovers, and heartbreaks, Marian now speaks to women nationwide about the unfailing love that she has found in Jesus. This first chapter of her book will help struggling women everywhere fill their hearts with this same joy in English/Italian.) Note: you can purchase the book in English at www.redeemedgirl.org)<br>5.) Video (There are youtube links to several videos of students sharing how God has changed their lives in English and Italian.)<p><br>Best of all, once downloaded to your Android device, “Ole Miss Italia” can be used anywhere, even without requiring internet access. This is especially helpful when using “Ole Miss Italia” on your iPhone or iPod Touch in Italy! If you have any comments or suggestions, please write us at <a href="mailto:olemisscrusade@gmail.com">olemisscrusade@gmail.com</a>.<p>Vorresti condividere il Vangelo con facilita’ con I tuoi amici Italiani? Ole Miss Crusade ha preparato questi strumenti per aiutarti:<br>1) Vorresti conoscere Dio personalmente? (Uno degli opuscoli piu’ efficaci e popolari, in inglese ed italiano)<br>2) Quattro capolavori (quattro opere d’arte con i quattro punti principali del libretto “conoscere Dio personalmente”, in inglese ed italiano)<br>3) Lettera ai romani (la lettera dell’apostolo Paolo ai romani, in italiano).<br>4) La verita’ dietro “Sex and the City” scoperto (nel libro “La verita’ dietro Sex and the City”, Marian Jordan scrive: “dietro alle immagini di alta moda, dialoghi spiritosi, e persone bellissime e’ nascosta una vita dolorosa di ricerca dell’amore nei posti sbagliati. Lo so perche’ l’ho vissuta.” Marian e’ un’ex ‘party girl’ con le proprie storie di avventure sessuali, sbronze, e cuori infranti, che parla a donne di tutta l’America dell’amore vero e sicuro che ha trovato in Gesu’. Il primo capitolo del suo libro aiutera’ donne in difficolta’ a riempire il loro cuore con la sua stessa gioia. In inglese ed italiano). NB: puoi comprare il libro in ingelse a www.redeemedgirl.org)<br>5)Video(ci sono link riguardanti vari video su youtube di studenti che testimoniano,in inglese e in italiano,come Dio ha cambiato le loro vite.)<p><br>Una volta scaricato sul tuo Android, “Ole Miss Agape” puo’ essere usato dovunque, anche senza accesso a internet. Questo e’ particolarmente utile quando usi “Ole Miss Agape” in Italia. Per commenti o suggerimenti, scrivere a <a href="mailto:olemisscrusade@gmail.com">olemisscrusade@gmail.com</a>.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=olemissitalia.ccfc', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/3WZmZVmfA20NxSOPhIrxt7vnIAZROTsr8pCxYFKrwDaXlpiqaWQiCsaqcrIy3C_bMQ', 4.27, 'BOOKS_AND_REFERENCE', 'Free', '1,000+', ''),
(145, 'com.noticesoftware.OleMissBlog', 'Ole Miss Blog', 'Bloguin', 'Don&#39;t get left behind on the web, get the Ole Miss Blog app and be ahead of the rest.<p>- Instant alerts of news.<br>- Be part of the action by sending in your photos, videos, and stories.<br>- Email your friends the Rebels news you find interesting.<p>Get your Ole Miss Rebels news delivered to your phone.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.noticesoftware.OleMissBlog', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/0qpG5HRWYYkQm41fBurcXgd0NG0QXJYrWE1kO5DD07a8v_BVZRPuz3WKhbQbPsmFIJDA', 3.90, 'SPORTS', 'Free', '1,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.ACCESS_LOCATION_EXTRA_COMMANDS, android.permission.CAMERA, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, com.noticesoftware.OleMissBlog.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE'),
(146, 'com.a2146462082521a629bdf3ad3a.a11810972a', 'Ole Miss Football', 'Sports News Apps', 'Get all your Ole Miss Football News in one place with our top rated FREE app!<p>Are you a big Rebels football fan?  Get all your Ole Miss college football news, videos, and more.  With this University of Mississippi football app you can easily keep up with everything related to the Rebels!<p>You’ll get:<br>* Ole Miss football schedule<br>* The latest Ole Miss Rebels Football news<br>* Official Facebook page<br>* The latest highlight videos from YouTube<br>* And more!<p>Download this FREE Rebels football app now and never miss another Rebels Football news story again!<p>Not affiliated with the University of Mississippi. Images and articles on this app are used under the fair use provision of the Copyright Act for purposes of reporting.  Information shown in this app is gathered from the various internet sources.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.a2146462082521a629bdf3ad3a.a11810972a', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/IfwxRX55f-l_x7kU6WZeZ4NO-KRk_WVxqrFJNQivaoT9m5uqRUxc8kGG66l9MHCVpAo', 4.67, 'SPORTS', 'Free', '100+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.ACCESS_LOCATION_EXTRA_COMMANDS, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, com.a2146462082521a629bdf3ad3a.a11810972a.permission.C2D_MESSAGE'),
(147, 'twothumbs.livewallpaper.create_mississippi', 'Ole Miss Live Wallpaper Suite', '2Thumbz, Inc', 'This application allows you to display the Officially Licensed University of Mississippi logo as a Live Wallpaper on your phone.  You can choose to either display the Live Wallpaper as a 3-D animated flag on your phone with the University of Mississippi logo, or as a picture frame for your personal images with the University of Mississippi logo.<p>Users can set the following options to personalize their phone with the University of Mississippi Live Wallpaper:<p>1. Select a variety of different modes including the animated flag mode or as a picture frame for images from your Facebook account, your FlickR account, or from your phone.<p>2. Select from a variety of different picture frame templates, including: 1) a Chalk board, 2) Cork Board, 3) Football Field, 3) Wild West Template, 4) Fire Template or 5) Metal Template<p>3. Select a variety of settings for different templates such as how fast the images change, how the images rotate, random picture shuffling and automatic image resizing.<p>Installation Instructions<br>-----------------<br>1. After downloading, go to Applications and Select &#39;University of Mississippi Live Wallpaper&#39;<p>2. When the initial screen opens, tap the &quot;Select Wallpaper/Change Settings&quot; button<p>3. Select the &quot;University of Mississippi Live Wallpaper&quot; application from the list of Live Wallpaper applications<p>4. Tap the &quot;Settings&quot; button to configure the application<p>5. Tap &quot;Photo Source&quot; to select either &quot;Animated Flag&quot; mode or picture frame mode for personal images from your phone, Facebook or FlickR.<p>Instructions for setting up Picture Frame SlideShow<br>---------------------------------------<br>1. Go to ‘University of Mississippi Live Wallpaper’ and select ‘Settings’<p>2. Select &#39;Photo Source&#39; and choose either Facebook, FlickR or Phone Images<p>3. If you chose Facebook, go to &#39;Log In&#39; and enter your Facebook account information.  The University of Mississippi Live Wallpaper application will log into your Facebook account.<p>4. You can select to show images from your Facebook Albums, as well as photos you have been tagged in.  You can also select to show images from your news feed<p>5. After you have setup your Facebook settings, you can choose which University of Mississippi Live Wallpaper Picture Frame Template you would like to use from the &quot;Select Template&quot; settings.<p>6. If you chose FlickR, you can choose a particular FlickR feed to show by either searching on a specific search term or user.<p>7. After you have chosen either Facebook, FlickR or your own phone images, you should &quot;Clear Images&quot; and &quot;Force Update&quot; which will reset your images', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=twothumbs.livewallpaper.create_mississippi', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/jHDY9-jdSfmt3ixSXRNdBRJvP7uJJvrD88J0Yt6kgBHrcMbUcYkMotTBrO5GIIpDAg', 0.00, 'PERSONALIZATION', '$0.99', '50+', 'com.android.vending.CHECK_LICENSE'),
