(158, 'com.conduit.app_4535da7188654e98862d6889d0005d03.app', 'DM mobile', 'The Daily Mississippian', 'The Daily Mississippian app is a mobile hub for Ole Miss students and alumni  providing the content that our fans want to know.  Get the latest Oxford &amp; Ole Miss news via Daily Mississippian, entertainment on the square, video reporting, local drink specials, sports, internships, opportunities, etc.   Our mission is too keep you informed and to keep you entertained what our app user&#39;s want to keep up to date on in Oxford, MS.<p>Visit us on our website www.thedmonline.com to view our Print version online!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.conduit.app_4535da7188654e98862d6889d0005d03.app', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/ZMseeP-ZrqmPkIeKGpZ7RHYetNo5XacYxzptWPB-zzULNKcQ8ynKlkJnqoChh4BZSWQ', 4.33, 'NEWS_AND_MAGAZINES', 'Free', '500+', 'android.permission.CAMERA, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.ACCESS_LOCATION_EXTRA_COMMANDS, com.conduit.app_4535da7188654e98862d6889d0005d03.app.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE'),
(159, 'com.mk.iNeedToDo', 'todo.txt', 'K Soft', 'iNeedToDo is ToDo (do/task) manager list application syncs your iNeediNeedToDo.txt file to Dropbox.<br>To use this app, you must have a Dropbox account (<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://dropbox.com&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEE3dZSyzQkOBslwStD3I5YIfWRQQ" target="_blank">http://dropbox.com</a>).<br>This trial version. Need to purchase license once trial expired.<br>Most apps and sites store your to-do list in their own proprietary database and file format. But you can open a iNeediNeedToDo.txt file with every text editor under the sun. iNeediNeedToDo.txt for Android manages your iNeediNeedToDo.txt list on the go and automatically syncs the file to all your computers and devices via Dropbox.<p>This application program has provided the following features though a basic function is similar to a general ToDo list (addition/edit/deletion of the task).<br>? beautifully designed, simple to use and user friendly.<br>? Keep your todo list in a documented, human-readable, plain text format.<br>? Save your iNeedToDo.txt file in Dropbox for access from all your devices.<br>? Enter multiple tasks in a single input box.<br>? Always there when you need it - iNeediNeedToDo syncs seamlessly with Dropbox so you can stay on top of just about anything across all your devices.<br>? Perform batch updates (complete, prioritize, delete) to multiple selected tasks at once.<br>? Quickly filter and group tasks by project or context.<br>? Search your list by keyword.<br>? Sort your list by priority or line number.<br>? See how long a task has been on your list.<br>? Archive completed tasks to a done.txt file.<br>? Dial a phone number or send an email directly from a task with a phone number or email address in it.<br>? Keep your list on your homescreen with a resizable, scrollable widget.<br>? Set up optional background sync at an interval you choose.<br>? Share selected tasks or the whole list via Android&#39;s Share menu.<br>? Send text from any other app on your phone, like email, into a new task via Android&#39;s Share menu.<br>? Enter tasks using Android&#39;s &quot;Note to self&quot; Voice Action.<br>? Adjust the app&#39;s text size via Android&#39;s system font size setting.<p>Key benefits: <br>? Seamless cloud sync<br>? Alerts<br>? Snooze tasks <br>? Prioritize tasks<br>? Amazing Widgets<br>? Gesture support &amp; much more!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mk.iNeedToDo', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/mG0KC0hDWKmQypto43mRIscVW_OuCEGSt4e_B4hF_SzNpqdmJtx4Gn9R76DvwTTduss', 3.55, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '100+', 'android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS'),
(160, 'com.mk.iNeedToDoLicence', 'todo.txt License', 'K Soft', 'This is license for iNeedToDo<p>iNeedToDo is ToDo (do/task) manager list application syncs your iNeediNeedToDo.txt file to Dropbox.<br>To use this app, you must have a Dropbox account (<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://dropbox.com&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEE3dZSyzQkOBslwStD3I5YIfWRQQ" target="_blank">http://dropbox.com</a>).<br>This trial version. Need to purchase license once trial expired.<br>Most apps and sites store your to-do list in their own proprietary database and file format. But you can open a iNeediNeedToDo.txt file with every text editor under the sun. iNeediNeedToDo.txt for Android manages your iNeediNeedToDo.txt list on the go and automatically syncs the file to all your computers and devices via Dropbox.<p>This application program has provided the following features though a basic function is similar to a general ToDo list (addition/edit/deletion of the task).<br>? beautifully designed, simple to use and user friendly.<br>? Keep your todo list in a documented, human-readable, plain text format.<br>? Save your iNeedToDo.txt file in Dropbox for access from all your devices.<br>? Enter multiple tasks in a single input box.<br>? Always there when you need it - iNeediNeedToDo syncs seamlessly with Dropbox so you can stay on top of just about anything across all your devices.<br>? Perform batch updates (complete, prioritize, delete) to multiple selected tasks at once.<br>? Quickly filter and group tasks by project or context.<br>? Search your list by keyword.<br>? Sort your list by priority or line number.<br>? See how long a task has been on your list.<br>? Archive completed tasks to a done.txt file.<br>? Dial a phone number or send an email directly from a task with a phone number or email address in it.<br>? Keep your list on your homescreen with a resizable, scrollable widget.<br>? Set up optional background sync at an interval you choose.<br>? Share selected tasks or the whole list via Android&#39;s Share menu.<br>? Send text from any other app on your phone, like email, into a new task via Android&#39;s Share menu.<br>? Enter tasks using Android&#39;s &quot;Note to self&quot; Voice Action.<br>? Adjust the app&#39;s text size via Android&#39;s system font size setting.<p>Key benefits: <br>? Seamless cloud sync<br>? Alerts<br>? Snooze tasks <br>? Prioritize tasks<br>? Amazing Widgets<br>? Gesture support &amp; much more!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mk.iNeedToDoLicence', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/dLJzWysHKfRH7NRQsRdq-H6vuFr6UhnvSm-TbAzWS1BU2lp1qn7hWPl30qRWoGAp1to', 0.00, 'PRODUCTIVITY', '$0.99', '1+', ''),
(161, 'com.pomodorotxt', 'Pomodoro.txt', 'iDevotion', 'Based on the Pomodoro Technique is a time management method developed by Francesco Cirillo in the late 1980s. The technique uses a timer to break down periods of work into 25-minute intervals called &quot;pomodori&quot; (from the Italian word pomodoro for &quot;tomato&quot;).<p>There are five basic steps to implementing the technique:<br>- decide on the task to be done on the TODO tab<br>- select the task and start a pomodoro.<br>- work on the task until the timer rings; application will record it for you.<br>- take a short break (3-5 minutes)<br>- every four &quot;pomodori&quot; take a longer break (15–30 minutes)<p>Based on the simple GTD task organization, this application is using the todo.txt file format sync with Dropbox.<p>Public link on Trello to vote next features : <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://trello.com/b/UAKt0Y8A/pomodoro&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEam8JcV-cchqnHdoEo4D5ThdNeNw" target="_blank">https://trello.com/b/UAKt0Y8A/pomodoro</a><p>Send me a mail if you want to contribute with new idea.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.pomodorotxt', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/ybqCiw-wy5uLNldxAr0NyoyJ0f8Up1iyDUopoqmc7o_MSjn4HF-V6u3lY0KdFTIFGA', 4.33, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '100+', ''),
(162, 'net.phlam.android.clockworktomato', 'Clockwork Tomato', 'phlam', 'Clockwork Tomato is a time management application, based on the Pomodoro technique, a method that boosts productivity by breaking down work periods into 25-minute slices, separated by short breaks.<p>This application is both a timer and a desktop clock, with simple and complete features:<br>• Original display of all the informations: a light and smart-looking clock showing the start time, end time and progress of the current timer, and the next timer to come.<br>• Timers can auto-chain<br>• Enhanced manual mode featuring &#39;extended timers&#39;<br>• Optional continuous ticking sound during Pomodoro timers<br>• Optional flashing screen at the end of a timer, and during extended timers<br>• Home screen clock widget.<br>• Lock screen clock widget (Android 4.2+)<br>• Persistent statistics on achieved pomodoros with history sharing capabilities.<br>• Fully configurable (timers length, colors, elements display)<br>• Ability to call Tasker tasks for more customizations.<br>• Optimized for both small and large displays, including tablets<br>• Resource-friendly<br>• No fancy permission required: READ_PHONE_STATE permission, to detect phone calls and pause the ticking sound playback accordingly.<br>• No Ads<p>Russian translation by ??????? ???????.<br>Simplified Chinese translation by ??.<br>German translation by Marcus Hoja and Hans Nix.<br>Spanish translation by Miguel Pagola.<br>Korean translation by ??.<p>Please do not hesitate to share with us any suggestion on the features and upcoming translations', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.phlam.android.clockworktomato', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/BBqp-JvG_tam53pgtxIDh-_Kv4p6zifE4yp-SWnLL75k2sy0riwBYyCPtjplc37PfZg9', 4.83, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '50,000+', 'android.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, net.dinglisch.android.tasker.PERMISSION_RUN_TASKS');
INSERT INTO `apps` (`id`, `packageName`, `title`, `author`, `description`, `url`, `icon`, `playRating`, `category`, `cost`, `numDownloads`, `permissions`) VALUES
(163, 'com.tatkovlab.pomodorolite', 'Pomodoro Timer Lite', 'Tatkov Lab', 'This simple and beautiful Pomodoro™ Timer will help you do more in less time and regain your lost concentration. <p>Some of the Pomodoro Timer Lite features:<br>* No ads<br>* Beautiful design<br>* Simplicity<p>The Pomodoro Technique® is a popular time management method developed in the late 80&#39;s. It&#39;s really simple. You break down your work into 25 minutes intervals separated by short breaks.<p>Here&#39;s how it works:<br>1.) Pick a task you need to accomplish.<br>2.) Set a timer for 25 minutes and start working<br>3.) When the time rings, take a 3-5 minute break<br>4.) Every fourth break should be long 15-25 minutes<p>*******************************************************************If you want to support development team and enjoy more features such as tasks history, please consider getting the Pomodoro Timer Pro version.<br>*******************************************************************<p>Pomodoro™ and Pomodoro Technique® are registered trademarks of Francesco Cirillo. This app is not affiliated with Francesco Cirillo.<p>Feel free to email me with any ideas and comments that can help to improve this app.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tatkovlab.pomodorolite', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/lvzhOnGwhocUQ-eGWpJZvVskxKByATRGU2tkSXhjjq_5YItUL-Z_oCjmHJUJsMJqQEw', 4.56, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '10,000+', ''),
(164, 'net.artifix.pomodroido.free', 'Pomodroido: A Pomodoro Timer', 'Flying Signals', 'This very simple Pomodoro™ Timer will help you concentrate and be productive. You can customize the pomodori and break times to fit your work style.<p>Pomodroido was the first Pomodoro Timer on the Android platform, hundreds of thousands of people have used this app to make the most of their time. Read the reviews to see how our users have stayed productive with the Pomodoro Technique® and Pomodroido app.<p>The Pomodoro Technique® is a popular time management method developed in the late 80&#39;s. You break down your work into 25 minutes intervals separated by short breaks.<p>This timeboxing technique can help you concentrate, avoid procrastination, and get work done.<p>If you like it and use it often, please consider buying the Donate/Pro version, which offers some additional features such as Tasker integration.<p>It does not have a todo or tasking system (yet), but I have added a few game mechanics, starting with a leveling system. Attain higher ranks by getting your work done. And brag about it!<br> <br>What&#39;s coming in the next versions? (our priority depends on your interests; so please e-mail me with feedback!)<p>• Analytics<br>• Achievements<br>• A todo/task system<p>I highly appreciate emails with comments or suggestions. I&#39;d like to know what would make this more valuable to you!<p>Pomodoro™ and Pomodoro Technique® are registered trademarks of Francesco Cirillo. This app is not affiliated with Francesco Cirillo.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.artifix.pomodroido.free', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/ntKS7jyJV7j3HNycIRiXPrFcW9GQWEWoDE0TLsCCu0D3Av0x76xmjm0Si2XG7Cox7Ks1', 4.51, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '100,000+', ''),
(165, 'com.dacer.simplepomodoro', 'Simple Pomodoro', 'tossking', 'A simple pomodoro timer.<p><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://dacer.github.io/myapps/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHXDM3za7glNZxk7lHmLteRgf4Z6Q" target="_blank">http://dacer.github.io/myapps/</a><p><a href="mailto:dacerfeedback@gmail.com">dacerfeedback@gmail.com</a><p><br>Features:<p>• Beautiful &amp; Simple - SimplePomodoro is beautifully designed, simple to use and user friendly.<br>• Full function - White/Black theme, lights on, weekly statistics, vibrations, alert, etc.<br>• FAST MODE - Auto lock/unlock screen and you can forget your lockscreen button, just focus on your work!<br>• Google task - Sync your tasks between your device and Google.<p>Please DO NOT report bugs in reviews. For some reasons, I CAN NOT see every reviews. You can report them to my email(linked blow)  directly. Thanks.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dacer.simplepomodoro', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/i8vMgfNar9F8gcGr51cVFODXbZ-DQtNNQjkgyua7JERJdWzDtQ06gINQ8zvuuiUEbBo', 4.58, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '1,000+', 'android.permission.GET_TASKS, android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW, android.permission.DISABLE_KEYGUARD, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS, android.permission.MANAGE_ACCOUNTS, com.google.android.providers.gsf.permission.READ_GSERVICES'),
(166, 'com.tatkovlab.pomodoro', 'Pomodoro Timer Pro', 'Tatkov Lab', 'Pomodoro Timer is a great tool that can help you boost your productivity and quality of your work. The Pomodoro Technique® was found in the 80&#39;s and it continues to be one of the most popular time management techniques being used today.<p>And it&#39;s really simple:<br>1.) Create a list of things to accomplish<br>2.) Pick one task to work on<br>3.) Pomodoro will start 25 minute timer<br>4.) Work on your task until timer runs out<br>5.) Take a short 3-5 minute break, relax your body and mind<br>6.) Every 4 Pomodoros take a longer break (10-30 minutes)<p>One Pomodoro™ lasts only 25 minutes and you should avoid all interruptions during it. Yes, your mails, phone calls and all the other things can wait few more minutes. Taking frequent breaks allow the brain to keep fresh and stay focused. This makes the Pomodoro Technique® a simple and effective method of finishing a task as quickly as possible.<p>The Pomodoro Timer Pro is the ultimate weapon in your battle with time. You can add multiple tasks, their estimates, see the history and much more. You can always clearly see how much time you have left. The style of this app was inspired by the original pomodoro &quot;kitchen&quot; timer.<p>Pomodoro™ and Pomodoro Technique® are registered trademarks of Francesco Cirillo. This app is not affiliated with Francesco Cirillo.<p>This app can be also used for TimeBoxing techniques or as a Productivity Timer.<p>************************************************************************************************<p>If you have any ideas and comments that can help improve this app, feel free to email me.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tatkovlab.pomodoro', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/eaKKhSXDW7JHsMhJnW4UOxl6V_AifpnPTgHjtW6LmJGC5edHW4jPfJBuujzknTCoQA', 4.54, 'PRODUCTIVITY', '$1.99', '1,000+', ''),
(167, 'net.avantic.pomodoroTools.activity', 'Pomodoro Soup Timer Free', 'Avantic', 'Become the most efficient at work and at study with Pomodoro Soup Timer. It helps you to apply the Pomodoro Technique®.<p>Pomodoro Soup Timer Free is not an official application of the Pomodoro Technique®.<p>Pomodoro Soup Timer includes:<br>- Control of working and resting time<br>- Notification and information while minimized<br>- Advanced settings<br>- Task List<br>- Mark interruptions<br>- Notice of 5 minutes to complete<br>- Spanish language<br>- Deutsch language<br>- Disable locking screen option<p>Keywords: pomodoro, timer, pomodoro technique, productivity, work, study, efficiency<p>This application is not affiliated with, associated with nor<br>endorsed by the Pomodoro Technique® or Francesco Cirillo.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.avantic.pomodoroTools.activity', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/pQRzvZsUGtefV1g-dFfP44C5cJ8OUbilVGY-EwGesghQMa_7GVDjpnu4y5aj-OrA3w', 4.23, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '10,000+', 'android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS'),
(168, 'com.kpz.pomodorotasks.activity', 'Pomodoro Tasks', 'Kavan Puranik AppLabs', 'A simple app to manage your daily tasks using a time management method called Pomodoro Technique. <p>*New* Version 1.4 - Now you can change notification settings and break duration in the Options menu.<br>- New Help page<br>- Now the timer will ring even  when the phone goes to sleep<br>- UI improvements based on user feedback', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kpz.pomodorotasks.activity', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/CJq20-fIHVYBGGhml0UZegV_9mWSauDm6E2VMBNAqHSayDWONalcDAFBNND9bEcQJA', 3.23, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '10,000+', ''),
(169, 'net.artifix.pomodroido', 'Pomodroido Pro: Pomodoro Timer', 'Flying Signals', 'This is the donation/pro version of Pomodroido. It will import the Pomodoros™ you have done from the free version. <p>Additional features compared to Free:<br>- Skip main screen<br>- Integration with Tasker (Instructions below)<p>????????????<br>This very simple Pomodoro™ Timer will help you concentrate and be productive. You can customize the pomodori and break times to fit your work style.<p>Pomodroido was the first Pomodoro Timer on the Android platform, hundreds of thousands of people have used this app to make the most of their time. Read the reviews to see how our users have stayed productive with the Pomodoro Technique® and Pomodroido app.<p>The Pomodoro Technique® is a popular time management method developed in the late 80&#39;s. You break down your work into 25 minutes intervals separated by short breaks.<p>This timeboxing technique can help you concentrate, avoid procrastination, and get work done.<p>If you like it and use it often, please consider buying the Donate/Pro version, which offers some additional features such as Tasker integration.<p>It does not have a todo or tasking system (yet), but I have added a few game mechanics, starting with a leveling system. Attain higher ranks by getting your work done. And brag about it!<br> <br>What&#39;s coming in the next versions? (our priority depends on your interests; so please e-mail me with feedback!)<p>• Analytics<br>• Achievements<br>• A todo/task system<p>I highly appreciate emails with comments or suggestions. I&#39;d like to know what would make this more valuable to you!<p>------- Tasker Instructions --------<br>* In Profiles tab click on &#39;+&#39; and select &#39;Event&#39;<br>* In the Event list, select &#39;3rd Party&#39;, and &#39;Pomodroido&#39; from there.<br>* You will have two event options, &#39;Started&#39;, and &#39;Stopped&#39; which will be triggered at the beginning and end of every Pomodoro™ respectively.<br>* Select &#39;Started&#39; or &#39;Stopped&#39; and click on back button to go back.<br>* You&#39;ll now be prompted to add &#39;New Task&#39; or select from existing tasks to this event.<p>Pomodoro™ and Pomodoro Technique® are registered trademarks of Francesco Cirillo. This app is not affiliated with Francesco Cirillo.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.artifix.pomodroido', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/ha6rXTnu_QqB22P76YUyPhvEWv6omx3XLtl4WlJjL_PAj6Vqmp2lM1YTxjJ-7Q1R5EE', 4.42, 'PRODUCTIVITY', '$2.99', '1,000+', ''),
(170, 'amqo.pomodomore', 'Pomodoro Calendar', 'AMQO', 'Pomodoro Calendar, do more, faster: Pomodoro Technique™ together with Google Calendar<p>NEW: Graphical statistics and internal/external interrupts management!<p>? Check out your Pomodoros and daily tasks through an intuitive calendar<br>? Create new tasks or import from your Google Calendar tasks<br>? Synchronize your Pomodoros with Google Calendar, creating a detailed tracking of your, or your team&#39;s activities<br>? Fully customizable<br>? Interface adapted to each type of device, mobile or tablet<br>? Agile methodologies, increases your productivity<p>If you like the app, please take a second to evaualte it in Google Play<br>Please, feel free to send any comments, suggestions or requests to <a href="mailto:alberto.mqo@gmail.com">alberto.mqo@gmail.com</a><p>You may also want to give support by getting the Donate - no Ads version, &quot;Pomodoro Calendar Donate&quot;<p>If you still don&#39;t know the Pomodoro Technique™, or you want to learn more about it, please visit <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.pomodorotechnique.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHI6dg9DeOBCj1tDKgaoRX3bV-0Dw" target="_blank">http://www.pomodorotechnique.com/</a><p>Important: You must have installed and synchronized Google Calendar application on your device to enable this functionality.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=amqo.pomodomore', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/qSvfsZvaxcuxw2oOOKAOX2cf3lEyn6BzpzxHj0yRQNxfPA_WAYUw9aBKRQfzvkn63yQ', 4.50, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '1,000+', 'android.permission.READ_CALENDAR, android.permission.WRITE_CALENDAR, android.permission.CHANGE_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE'),
(171, 'com.fsp.pomodoro_master', 'Pomodoro Master', 'FESEPO', 'Pomodoro Master is a little tool that will help you on your productivity time. It is based on Pomodoro Technique (See <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.pomodorotechnique.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHI6dg9DeOBCj1tDKgaoRX3bV-0Dw" target="_blank">http://www.pomodorotechnique.com/</a> )<br>It has a total counter (pomodoros + time) and a last x counter (also pomodoros + time) where x is a number of days.<br>The application will calculate your productivity grade based on the partial counter and a 7 hours work day. The productivity grade is easier to get at lower values.<br>You can also set a number of pomodoros as a personal goal.<br>Long press on the clock to get acces to Quick Times Profiles.<br>Gesture down-up enable/disable a quick mute.\\n&quot;;<br>Gesture up-down launch the free app lockScreen (I recommend you to download it from the market).<br>Hope you find useful the application.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fsp.pomodoro_master', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/cogbig3OkiytMu3hkXQynYvxs2wHIzkA7q-3TzMXUHGwjW1X3jWPUVyz9X6cTnlJcqxP', 3.75, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '5,000+', 'android.permission.GET_TASKS'),
(172, 'its.pomodoro.time', 'It''s Pomodoro Time!', 'Baris Sarer', 'It’s Focus Time! is a Pomodoro timer that will help you boost your focus and manage your time more effectively. It is based on Pomodoro Technique. With its sleek design and simplicity of use, this is the most effective Pomodoro timer in the market. <p>It&#39;s Focus Time! features:<p>- Ticking/Alarm sound preferences<p>- Ability to set your sessions and break and long break durations<p>- Break indicator that tells you where you are in the cycle<p>- Counter to keep track of your daily accomplishments<p>To learn more about our Pomodoro Timer, please visit <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.pomodorotime.org&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGmoNH7skV3G5KZuPtwMtQ2BroubQ" target="_blank">http://www.pomodorotime.org</a> <p>Our free online timer is available at <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.pomodorotime.org/timer&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFKFArnsTyFywMxIA274IIz5BboMA" target="_blank">http://www.pomodorotime.org/timer</a><p>It&#39;s Focus Time! for IOS is also now available. <p>POMODORO TECHNIQUE and POMODORO are the trademarks of Francesco Cirillo. This application is not affiliated or associated with or endorsed by the Pomodoro Technique® or Francesco Cirillo', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=its.pomodoro.time', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/B-xjd0IsGf9iNvSrHFEyGepIU4q0LXjPSjZQSfeWlYk7BBZ04rfu5Sphc_ofDpimSA', 3.21, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '1,000+', ''),
(173, 'com.alperhadev.pomodorotimer', 'Pomodoro Timer', 'Alper HACIO?LU', 'Pomodoro Timer is designed for maximum productivity. A round is divided into three parts with golden ratio, while color is green be as fast as you can, on yellow color start to slow down, when color is red finish your current task and take a break on blue color. Using Pomodoro Timer makes life easier and feel better, That&#39;s why so many people use it.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.alperhadev.pomodorotimer', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/dUJX81bezur4-mHVuwqc5TySX_mp35vc_SRfgAilTEzLPL32MV5ac8LqHLaaxtxe3Q', 4.68, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '1,000+', ''),
(174, 'ua.a5.pomodoro.handset.free', 'The Pomodoro Technique H. Free', 'a5.ua', 'Free version of our Pomodoro Technique for Handsets: 1 pomodoro only.<p>Custom implementation of timer used for Pomodoro Technique time management approach invented by Francesco Cirillo. This application is recommended for usage on smartphones and has a tween-brother named “The Pomodoro Technique Tablets” for tablet-size devices.<br>Please notice: when you click &quot;Yes!&quot; after session end application will go to background (close) and restart after long pause (can be set in settings). This is not a bug, this is how it suppose to be!<br>The application is easy to use, supplied with nice graphic and sound elements.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=ua.a5.pomodoro.handset.free', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/BFSc3vH7zmK4YOyF4g9e-E1ZfDEClWQV6CpHh3fWDTU9MyR_nMRIWEp8Bodd37Wd9FZd', 4.17, 'BUSINESS', 'Free', '1,000+', 'android.permission.DISABLE_KEYGUARD'),
(175, 'ua.a5.pomodoro.tablet.free', 'The Pomodoro Technique T. Free', 'a5.ua', 'Free version of our &quot;The Pomodoro Technique Tablets&quot;: one pomodoro only.<p>Custom implementation of timer used for Pomodoro Technique time management approach invented by Francesco Cirillo. This application is recommended for usage on smartphones and has a tween-brother named “The Pomodoro Technique Tablets” for tablet-size devices.<br>Please notice: when you click &quot;Yes!&quot; after session end application will go to background (close) and restart after long pause (can be set in settings). This is not a bug, this is how it suppose to be!<br>The application is easy to use, supplied with nice graphic and sound elements.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=ua.a5.pomodoro.tablet.free', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/bz3EYLn20g1IZUdFGIoBEteXqToev7Bf9Vamcw7tuuY3W5GyiBLpd4A4FVUQ-T2Av2w', 3.78, 'BUSINESS', 'Free', '500+', 'android.permission.DISABLE_KEYGUARD'),
(176, 'com.hlidskialf.android.pomodoro', 'Pomodoro - Productivity Timer', 'Hlidskialf', 'A tomato timer for using the Pomodoro technique.<p>The pomodoro technique is a personal time management method:<br> 1. Choose a task.<br> 2. Work uninterrupted for 25 minutes.<br> 3. Walk away and break for 5 minutes.<br> 4. After 4 tomatos, take a longer break.<p>Source code available<br>Free downloads on website', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.hlidskialf.android.pomodoro', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/EeA-3COZ53rQALN8MVK3iQlLp9bUHM01VreRMEaRrOYfMALN3a3Hb0dxvV_dcen0Tg', 3.57, 'TOOLS', '$0.99', '100+', 'android.permission.DISABLE_KEYGUARD'),
(177, 'com.swavdev.apps.pomodoro', 'Android Pomodoro Timer', 'Swav Kulinski', 'Android Pomodoro Timer is a simple time management tool. It has two settings for normal and extended break.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.swavdev.apps.pomodoro', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/XDMHJDwr0TLJHhCNqhqzQswcQE-0d6cPMoWrjDlDogWKKsEuv7KUo9mWG5TpwxSBkPE', 4.17, 'TOOLS', 'Free', '1,000+', ''),
(178, 'com.fsp.pomodoro_master_unlocker', 'Pomodoro Master Pro', 'FESEPO', 'Pomodoro Master is a little tool that will help you on your productivity time. It is based on Pomodoro Technique (See <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.pomodorotechnique.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHI6dg9DeOBCj1tDKgaoRX3bV-0Dw" target="_blank">http://www.pomodorotechnique.com/</a> )<br>This app is a unlock application that will give to free version all features open.<br>Pomodoro Master has a total counter (pomodoros + time) and a last x counter (also pomodoros + time) where x is a number of days.<br>The application will calculate your productivity grade based on the partial counter and a 7 hours work day. The productivity grade is easier to get at lower values.<br>You can also set a number of pomodoros as a personal goal.<br>Long press on the clock to get acces to Quick Times Profiles.<br>Gesture down-up enable/disable a quick mute.\\n&quot;;<br>Gesture up-down launch the free app lockScreen (I recommend you to download it from the market).<br>Hope you find useful the application.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fsp.pomodoro_master_unlocker', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/pT6twUM3hpScXd2ewuDp_NQlUxY3VX5I1Bo6KnaD8itgGhWW8M_t_Vyi027HoxxgcgA', 4.71, 'PRODUCTIVITY', '$2.25', '100+', ''),
(179, 'com.codaver.pomodoroagent', 'Pomodoro Agent', 'Codaver', 'Pomodoro Agent is a simple, yet powerful, timer which helps you keep track of your daily Pomodoro blocks.<p>During the course of the day, Pomodoro Agent will continuously inform you when it is time to take a break and when you should continue with your work.<br>Information about each finished block is added to an easy-to-navigate log.<p>Getting started is easy and only takes up a few seconds of your time. Start Pomodoro Agent and tap the play key - that&#39;s it!<p><br>Features:<p>  - No pre-customization needed. Just launch and go!<br>  - Audio notifications make sure you never miss your breaks. (Can be disabled)<br>  - 24h reset which guarantees that you only see your daily Pomodoro blocks<br>  - Mini stats let you keep track of the amount of finished blocks and breaks respectively<br>  - Statistics sharing - let your friends on social networks know about your progress!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.codaver.pomodoroagent', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/tsYpNcYZXiTTEtRHTGpwP1WZAJlk-dlo4OY9Yd-VM_Nc8sjYDnnrTabWmJ_gkHcO0A', 3.80, 'TOOLS', 'Free', '100+', ''),
(180, 'org.gingerproject.pomodorogtd', 'Simple Pomodoro', 'Gingerprojects', 'This is a simple Pomodoro Technique timer that we use for work. Start the timer, press the home button and perform that task - The app works in the background and notifies you (vibration/sound/message) when its time to take a break. Suddenly interrupted? No worries - You can pause the timer at any time.<p>We highly value your comments, wishes and feedback! So feel free to send us an email.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.gingerproject.pomodorogtd', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/8G9Dy_BnK-4SqnHzht2IwJHp5q12JGvvGnh5Xo_3Bf8YMqtXywTce4Lo_ICgS2j4XA', 4.10, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '5,000+', ''),
(181, 'com.amazon.mShop.android', 'Amazon', 'Amazon Mobile LLC', 'The Amazon App allows Android users to browse and “Shop by Department”, quickly search, compare prices, read reviews, share products with friends, access Gold Box Deals, and make purchases on Amazon.com. To make on-the-go shopping and price comparison even easier, the Amazon App includes helpful shopping features that allow users to scan a barcode, snap a photo, or type a search, to quickly compare prices and check availability. Customers can sign up to receive a daily notification for Lightning Deals and also stay up to date on status of their orders.<p>Shoppers are able to access any of Amazon&#39;s sites around the world from a single app by simply selecting their desired Amazon country store. Amazon customers have full access to their existing cart, wish lists, payment and Amazon Prime member shipping options, order history, 1-Click settings and can also take advantage of Amazon.com&#39; Subscribe &amp; Save. All purchases made on the Amazon App are routed through Amazon&#39;s secure servers just as they are on the web.<p>** Requires Android OS 2.1 &amp; up and rear facing camera.<br>*** The Amazon App for Tablets is available on Google Play. Search for &quot;Amazon Tablet&quot; to install the app and begin shopping.<br> <br>Important note regarding permissions. The Amazon App requires access to the following services to operate properly:<br> <br>Location: due to the fact that this is now a world wide app, location permissions are required to support a delivery service feature offered by Amazon in France and Japan. Only in those stores is the location data required or used. In those locations you are able to request delivery to a convenience store closest to your current location. That service is not available in other Amazon countries.<br> <br>Phone calls: within the app you are able to place a call to Amazon Customer Service. Tap Menu -&gt; More -&gt; Help -&gt; Call Customer Service, and we will place the proper number in the phone app and dial it.<br> <br>Take pictures: bar code scanning and image search require access to the camera function if you choose to start the bar code scanner from the app.<br> <br>Account Permissions: This permission is used by the Amazon app suite for account authentication on select handsets.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.amazon.mShop.android', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/6HhRii8cRFwUegWHpYpvWUGuM5l3RAcsUYc-_NKXFHw7dy6x24AZudb4zyjT6B4sow', 4.53, 'SHOPPING', 'Free', '10,000,000+', 'com.amazon.mShop.android.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, android.permission.CAMERA, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, com.amazon.dcp.metrics.permission.METRICS_PERMISSION, com.amazon.dcp.config.permission.DYN_CONFIG_VALUES_UPDATED, com.amazon.dcp.settings.permission.READ_SETTINGS, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS, android.permission.MANAGE_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.AUTHENTICATE_ACCOUNTS, com.amazon.identity.auth.device.perm.AUTH_SDK, com.amazon.identity.permission.GENERIC_IPC, com.amazon.dcp.sso.permission.USE_DEVICE_CREDENTIALS, com.amazon.dcp.sso.permission.EXPIRE_ACCESS_TOKEN, com.amazon.dcp.sso.permission.account.changed, com.amazon.dcp.sso.permission.MANAGE_COR_PFM, com.amazon.dcp.sso.permission.CUSTOMER_ATTRIBUTE_SERVICE, com.amazon.identity.permission.CAN_CALL_MAP_INFORMATION_PROVIDER, amazon.permission.COLLECT_METRICS'),
(182, 'com.amazon.ember.android', 'Amazon Local', 'Amazon Mobile LLC', 'Amazon Local offers customers awesome deals so they can enjoy deep discounts not only from local businesses, but also from national chains and online merchants. We deliver savings of up to 75% on restaurants, spas, events, travel getaways, hotels and more so you can enjoy familiar favorites and new experiences in your city.<p>Download the Amazon Local Android app to:<br>• View and buy deals within seconds on your Android smartphone<br>• Use deals directly without printing vouchers<br>• Set preferences to get deals tailored for you <p>With our nifty app you can:<br>• Quickly mark deals as used and see your unused deals<br>• Receive notifications for deals<br>• Decide whether you’d like to receive emails or push notifications or both for your cities<br>• Lock the app with a passcode for added security<br>• Share deals with your friends and family <p>Terms of Use: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://local.amazon.com/terms&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNG_tiUrmh7B-VxRIu-QlC1BB7TSbw" target="_blank">http://local.amazon.com/terms</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.amazon.ember.android', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/JcZnymVX_JvQDCXCXLAeONnfTOtJOutphePFdJakjl2HZsJzMc0ej7tzWYqZbahRy_C6', 4.61, 'SHOPPING', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'com.amazon.android.push.NOTIFICATION, android.permission.CALL_PHONE, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS, android.permission.MANAGE_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.AUTHENTICATE_ACCOUNTS, com.amazon.dcp.sso.permission.account.changed, com.amazon.dcp.sso.permission.AMAZON_ACCOUNT_PROPERTY, com.amazon.dcp.sso.permission.AmazonAccountPropertyService.property.changed, com.amazon.dcp.sso.permission.USE_DEVICE_CREDENTIALS, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, com.amazon.identity.auth.device.perm.AUTH_SDK, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, com.amazon.ember.android.permission.C2D_MESSAGE'),
(183, 'com.amazon.pricecheck', 'Price Check by Amazon', 'Amazon Mobile LLC', 'Use Price Check to scan a barcode, snap a picture, or type or say an item name to check prices instantly on millions of Amazon products and buy it directly from the app. And to make in-store price comparison even better, we’re introducing a new price sharing feature that helps ensure our prices remain competitive for our customers. <p>Search for products using four easy methods: <br>• Scan a barcode: Amazon’s barcode scanner will match your item and provide Amazon and merchant product pricing in seconds.<br>• Snap a picture: This app uses Amazon’s photo matching algorithm to instantly match your picture to books, DVDs, CDs, video games, and more. <br>• Say the product name: Speak your search queries and use voice search to return accurate product matches and Amazon’s pricing.<br>• Type your search: Type the product name to retrieve instant matches.<br>• Buy directly from the app: Buy with confidence and complete a secure purchase directly from the app.<br>Price Check provides access to Amazon.com product descriptions and customer reviews to guide you in making informed purchase decisions. When you find a low price while using the Price Check app, simply log into your Amazon account to complete a secure purchase. Price Check also supports add to Wish List; sharing via Twitter, Facebook, text message or e-mail link; immediate purchasing using 1-Click ordering and Amazon Prime. <br>All products are from the US catalog; all prices are in US dollars. Price Check is compatible with Android devices with auto-focus cameras and Android 2.1 or greater.<br>The categories available within Price Check include: Books, Textbooks, Movies, Music, Video Games, CDs, Electronics, Home &amp; Garden, Automotive, Baby, Beauty, Camera &amp; Photo, Cell Phone &amp; Services, Clothing, Computers, Grocery, Health &amp; Personal Care, Home Improvement, Industrial &amp; Scientific, Jewelry, Kindle, Kitchen &amp; Dining, Magazines, Music Instruments, Office Products, Patio &amp; Garden, Shoes, Software, Sports &amp; Outdoors, Video, &amp; Watches.<p>* Copyright: © 2011 Amazon.com and its affiliates.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.amazon.pricecheck', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/E41zzezf6vIhZ-i5hc_JacF79p7bbn1Hme043gkMV8QeZqgCy8gPN3c9qzMl0VNHHKpz', 4.29, 'SHOPPING', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'android.permission.CAMERA, android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION'),
(184, 'com.amazon.student.android', 'Amazon Student', 'Amazon Mobile LLC', 'College Students, keep Amazon.com in your back pocket. The Amazon Student App allows instant price-checks on textbooks and more. Simply scan a barcode to check a price, or use one-click access to scan items you want to buy or sell back. Amazon’s convenient trade-in program can turn your books, games, movies, and electronics into Amazon Gift Cards. Plus, join Amazon Student to get FREE Two-Day Shipping for six months with Amazon Prime shipping benefits!<p>Included in the Amazon Student App:<p>- Instant Price Checks: Scan a barcode—check a price: It’s that easy. Shop smarter and compare prices on textbooks and everything else you buy, no matter where you are. Access Amazon.com’s low prices and vast selection to buy books, music, DVDs, electronics, apparel, and just about anything else from your phone.<p>- Sell Your Stuff: Turn your used stuff into Amazon.com Gift Cards. Just scan a textbook, game, movie, or gadget you no longer need and see the trade-in value for any eligible item. Ship it for free and get an Amazon.com Gift Card to spend on millions of items on Amazon.com.<p>- FREE Two-Day Shipping: The Amazon Student program offers college students FREE Two-Day Shipping for six months with Amazon Prime shipping benefits.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.amazon.student.android', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/1zMHB_-pSaiB47VwS0KFJpyeTFfg7VtwRqmOt64TtduPMKB3FWWEBlCt5KRMXbEMJIo', 4.28, 'SHOPPING', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.CAMERA'),
(185, 'com.bigfishgames.google.heafree', 'Amazon: Hidden Expedition', 'Big Fish Games', 'Big Fish Games takes you on an adventure into the stunning world of the Amazon with the Hidden Expedition team in search of a missing professor. A tattered map referencing the legendary Beetle Temple is your only clue as you begin your adventure deep into the Amazon Rainforest. Explore cities, temples, and ruins while unlocking the secrets of an ancient yet advanced civilization. This adventure is the largest yet for the Hidden Expedition team, and the discovery of the Beetle Temple is just the beginning.<p>TRY IT FREE, THEN UNLOCK THE FULL ADVENTURE FROM WITHIN THE GAME! <p>????? Features ????? <p>? 50 hidden object scenes <br>? 14 unique mini games <br>? Replay chapters to gain higher rankings <p>??? Discover more from Big Fish Games! ??? <p>We’re big believers that everyone is a gamer at heart and that games are a great source of joy and relaxation. Founded in 2002, Big Fish Games is a developer, publisher and distributor of casual games. We offer a virtually endless selection of interactive games that you can enjoy anytime, anywhere — on your PC, Mac, mobile phone, or tablet. Renowned for offering A New Game Every Day!® on www.bigfishgames.com, Big Fish Games distributes more than two million games per day worldwide.<p>We have many other great Google Play games including:? <p>? Empress of the Deep: The Darkest Secret<br>? Empress of the Deep: Song of the Blue Whale<br>? Nightmare Adventures: The Witch&#39;s Prison<br>? Big City Adventure: San Francisco<br>? Atlantis Sky Patrol<br>? The Serpent of Isis<br>? Adventure Chronicles<br>? Azada<p>And coming soon:<br>? Secrets of the Dragon Wheel<br>? Mahjong Towers Touch<br>? Azada: Ancient Magic<br>? Fairway Solitaire<br>? Uncharted: Hidden Expedition<br>? Lifequest<p>Visit www.bigfishgames.com from your Android device to see the whole list!<p>Follow us on Twitter: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://bigfi.sh/BigFishTwitt