(197, 'com.havok.amazon.freeapp.widget', 'Free App Widget 4 Amazon', 'Havok_Apps', '? How to use Free App Widget 4 Amazon ?<br>To use this widget you must &quot;long press&quot; on an empty space on your home screen and then from the &quot;widget menu&quot; select &quot;Free App Widget for Amazon&quot;<p>? What is Free App Widget 4 Amazon ?<br>Amazon gives away a paid app each and every day. The purpose of this home screen widget is to give you a visual reminder each and every time you see it on the screen so you don&#39;t forget to check the app store.  If you love and use this app please help support it by leaving comments or contacting me!  Those who leave star ratings without comments are not helping to improve the project.<p>? Note ?<br>It is set to update automatically every 60 minutes and can also be updated manually.  Will allow you to automatically load and download the current app of the day just by clicking the widget.  No more missing out because you forgot to load up Amazon&#39;s AppStore that day.<p>? Features of Free App Widget 4 Amazon ?<br>  ? Shows Free App of The Day Name <br>  ? Shows Free App of The Day Developer<br>  ? Shows Original Price <br>  ? Shows App Icon<br>  ? Shows App Star Rating<p>  ? Auto Launch Amazon App Store from pop-up window <br>   (just tap the widget)<br>  ? Manual Refresh (supports manual refresh)<br>  ? Share Today&#39;s App link<br>  ? Direct Download Link for Amazon App Store <br>   (provided for you if you don&#39;t currently have it installed.  After download select the file from your notifications or storage in order to be prompted for installation.)<p>  ? In App Email support (please email me any suggestions, feedback, or bug reports.  If the app loads and you wish to report a bug or a problem please use the in-app form in order to submit device information automatically to me for troubleshooting. Also I cannot directly reply to comments left here so please email me if you need support.)<p>  ? Direct link to rate this application.<p>?? Compatibility Android 1.5 or Greater ??<p>? Uses Permissions ?<br>  ? android.permission.INTERNET (necessary to download information from Amazon.com)<br>  ? android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE (to check for connectivity)<p>? Disclaimer ?<br>I am in no way affiliated with Amazon or the Amazon Appstore. I do not take credit for any content or apps published on the Amazon AppStore. You&#39;re paying for the Convenience of the daily reminder.<p>? Tags ? <br>Amazon, Amazon&#39;s, Free apps, Download, Free app of the day, Free app a day, Havok Apps, Havok apps, notify, notification, free, free app, free app of the day, Amazon free app widget, amazon notifier, Free App Widget 4 Amazon<p>? Recent Changes ?<br>v2.01 - Graphic changes and App Name Change to comply with Amazon trademarks.<br>v1.95 - minor bug fixes and code optimizations.<br>v1.85 - Landscape support<br>v1.80 - Added &quot;Share Today&#39;s App&quot; option.<br>------- Improved error handling.<br>v1.75 - Repaired issue with Email Developer option.<br>v1.70 - Complete UI redesign including menu.<br>------- Minor bug fixes.<br>v1.50 - Optimized AppStore Detection &amp; Limited Entries.<br>------- Rate App added to menu.<br>v1.30 - Added Additional Error Handling.<br>------- Added Check Network State.<br>------- No longer tries to reload if data hasn&#39;t changed.<br>------- No longer tries to reload if there is no connection.<br>------- Minor UI adjustments.<br>------- Minor Bug Fixes.<br>v1.00 - Release Version.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.havok.amazon.freeapp.widget', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/yghdcyueQwvPS3gwz-VA97HrXbmOiat4FtD3GJWBIAbaBHWVfLBovFkmFi1TgSwiRw', 3.85, 'TOOLS', '$0.99', '1,000+', ''),
