(199, 'com.weberbooks.freeapp', 'Free App of the Day for Amazon', 'Weber Books', 'Each morning you&#39;ll see the new &quot;Free App of the Day&quot; from Amazon&#39;s app store for Android and Kindle users.<p>The Amazon Appstore, available in the U.S. only, includes a &quot;free app a day&quot; feature. Each morning, an application, frequently a game, is offered for free. The first-ever feature was the game Angry Birds Rio.<p>The appstore&#39;s &quot;Test Drive&quot; feature allows users to try an application in their web browser by launching a virtual copy of Android in the Amazon EC2 cloud for half an hour.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.weberbooks.freeapp', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/8X8Z867yxcZ-l90JyE9dud0os0qgzGKsClUxg7FNiDHYRkKRd49XSydfh1S8EMTHHw', 3.28, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '10,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION'),
