(205, 'com.jsondata.www.generic', 'Netflix Top Rated Movies', 'WebsiteInstantly.com', 'Tired wasting time scouting for an instant movie on Netflix? <p>No worries, this app will list 100&#39;s of the best rated films (3+ stars) on Netflix that you can play / watch instantly!<p>Note: this app is not a streaming player. It is a search engine with the best movies of Netflix!<p>Enjoy :)<p>Keywords: movie, film, search, top, best, rank, ranked, ranking, favorites, top 10, top 100, must see, watch now, instant, play, netflix, sort, group, classic, action, api, data, stream, watch, play', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jsondata.www.generic', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/ln3tTm0B7BoT_GdexLo4kMSfansud8korD3FS1smg7ZwDdaG5qd60J93_C7Vp-9wuQ', 3.07, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '100,000+', ''),
(206, 'com.sporadicsoftware.NetQ', 'NetQ - A Netflix Queue Manager', 'SporadicSoftware', 'The most complete Netflix queue manager on Android. Please email with any problems or suggestions or contact us on Twitter @SporadicSoftwre<p>NOTE: NetQ cannot be moved to your SD card IF you use the widget<p>If you are being force to re-authenticate every time, please try the &#39;Clear Tokens&#39; option in Preferences or re-installing the app (uninstall/install).<p>INFO: Netflix is removing access to all rental history access (as of 9/15/12) (At Home, Shipped, Returned, &amp; Watched). This will also disable the &quot;Remove Watched Instant&quot; feature and the &quot;Check if already...&quot; options<p>INFO: Netflix&#39;s new Profiles are not available to 3rd-party apps at this time<p>If the app is stuck at downloading, please go to checkout.google.com and verify your credit card details<p>Features:<p>-STREAMING! If NetQ determines that the Netflix app is installed you will see a play icon overlaying the box art in the movie details screen (if the movie is available to watch instantly). Touching the box art will now launch the Netflix app and start playing the movie. If the title is a Series or Season, you will first be shown a list of episodes to watch. Selecting one will launch the Netflix app and start playing the episode.<br>-Rotten Tomatoes scores and reviews<br>-Add movies currently in theaters to your disc queue<br>-Search YouTube for movie trailer<br>-Set/change format (DVD/Blu-ray)<br>-drag-&amp;-drop queues (using box art or drag icon)<br>-barcode search (requires the free ZXing Barcode Scanner app)<br>-search IMDb (either through the Browser or the IMDb Android app)<br>-add NYTimes reviewed movies to your queue<br>-search from Quick Search Box (Google Search widget)<br>-configurable widget<br>-share ratings and movies w/Facebook<br>-browse by genre and filter results<br>-search titles,people,instant titles,queues<br>-remove entries from disc queue when found in instant queue<br>-remove entries from Instant Queue that you have already watched<br>-move titles from Disc to Instant queue (if available)<br>-add future Instant titles to local queue. Setting available to automatically check if movies are available and add them to your Instant queue<br>-separate wifi/3G/edge settings<br>-long press a movie title in a list for available options<br>-in a movie&#39;s details screen you can press the box art to open the Netflix webpage for the movie<br>-view cast list of a movie and view other titles featuring a given cast member<br>-view similar titles<br>-view Netfix&#39;s Recommendations for you<br>-Instant Only Mode<p>NOTE: NetQ cannot be moved to your SD card IF you use the widget<p>STREAMING (If the Netflix app is installed and supports your device see: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://goo.gl/NvzCJ&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHFHfeMAM3qvH5UPMyWkXaz12EJgw" target="_blank">http://goo.gl/NvzCJ</a>)<p>KNOWN ISSUES:<br>-Future Watch Instantly feed is sparsely populated. Netflix is not properly reporting future Instant release titles in their API. They are aware of the problem.<br>-TV series/seasons/discs cannot be added to your Disc queue<br>-Netflix log-in page is missing the log-in image. Pressing the ? icon will still log you in<br>-Shortcut in home screen does not work after update. Simply remove the shortcut and re-add it', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sporadicsoftware.NetQ', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/78jU7H-57FpN23FOGDZDpJ8SB-VIc0p4tJtDFWXbHYaxG6ee1JgEWGuy6ZYXJA-xP8WY', 4.12, 'ENTERTAINMENT', '$0.99', '10,000+', ''),
(207, 'com.ashwin.netflixsearch', 'Catalog Search For Netflix', 'Ashwin.2610', 'UPDATE: This app is currently being updated with the latest Netflix API. Until then, the app might not function as expected. Thank you.<p>&#39;Catalog Search For Netflix&#39; enables you to search the Netflix catalog for movies, TV Shows, documentaries, etc. The app also tells you all the different formats(instant, DVD, Blu-Ray) the titles are available in at that moment. The app also enables you to customize your search results by genres and title ratings. At this time the search results are limited to a maximum of 50.<p>This application is only to help search the Netflix catalog.<br>You cannot add DVDs to queue or watch instantly using this application.<p>Please Note: This application allows the users to search the Netflix catalog without requiring the users to log in using their Netflix credentials. This however limits the number of searches in a day to 5000. Any feedback regarding errors is welcome. Thanks!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ashwin.netflixsearch', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/-wADbBebfN42GQo4LTnAMrh3--tJVumn5JzxuAVFFMIcqGJUHf0dv7CyscxhW0pJ4MkJ', 3.09, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '100,000+', ''),
(208, 'com.jetap.android.iwguide', 'IWGuide for Netflix', 'jeTap Inc', 'IWGuide for Netflix is your personal movie listing for discovering what&#39;s new on Netflix Instant Watch service in the USA. Once a week, if not more often, IWGuide for Netflix content will be updated and you will be able to discover quickly:<br>+ what has been released recently on Instant Watch,<br>+ what new titles are coming soon on Instant Watch,<br>+ what are the best recent titles currently on Instant Watch,<p>If you are interested by a particular movie or TV series, simply tap on it to view more detailed information about it.<br>Learn more and watch a video demo at <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://iwguide.com&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGdHQ_BnSIdRB_Jx7Z3EjJ7xnr1aw" target="_blank">http://iwguide.com</a> and subscribe to IWGuide mailing list.<p>Unfortunately the category &quot;Going Away&quot; had to be removed from the app due to Netflix changing their API: Netflix decided to remove the information related to movies going away from their catalog and the direct effect of that decision is the &quot;Going Away&quot; category from IWGuide had to be removed.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jetap.android.iwguide', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/1UYTCuI9RVDA37iEMajw_BBwbHUMRZRsHMdTGAqW0n0VgttOtygE9fEt1TxzlVdBJw', 4.00, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '10,000+', 'android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED'),
(209, 'dk.zoon.unblocknetflix', 'Unblock Netflix', 'Zoon Software', '* This app. does NOT provide free movies, or the ability to watch them from the app. Please read the ENTIRE app. description *<p>Depending on where you are located on the globe - Netflix™ will show you a version approved for that region/part of the world. Usually it means more local movies/series, but it might also be TV-series not available in other parts of the world.<p>Unblock Netflix allows you to switch between different versions of Netflix. The app does *NOT* provide that service in itself!<p>This program is only a quick interface to the Unblock-US(<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://bit.ly/10hnDHl&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGfg2ZDBlluUzr0hCisOkVYEZfbPA" target="_blank">http://bit.ly/10hnDHl</a>) or Overplay(<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://bit.ly/1ecE2jl&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEV39ZA9W3Y3-OHMa6E9d8Dgpq2jg" target="_blank">http://bit.ly/1ecE2jl</a>) site - where you can also change you Netflix™ country settings through a browser.<p>But instead of opening a browser, and navigating the site, this app allows super-easy access to all the countries that Unblock-US/Netflix supports!<p>With a tab of your finger, you can easily switch country. All you then have to do, is reboot your Netflix™ device (BD player, Set Top Box, TV...), and you should be good to go!<p>Features<br>* Search the entire Netflix streaming catalog (Denmark, Sweden, Norway, Finland, Ireland, Mexico, Brazil, United Kingdom, United States, Canada and the Netherlands)<br>* Activate your current IP address! Bring Netflix to your friends house :)<br>* Get catalog info for all countries (how many titles are available for each country!)<br>* Search within a year-range or to/from a specific year<br>* Search for actor and director<br>* Search for movies in a specific region, or with specific subtitles, or a specific keyword!<br>* See the seasons available for each Netflix country, so you can find the seasons you are missing!<br>* Add movies to your favorites - find them easily again (long-click on movie in your search results)<br>* Browse the Netflix™ genres<br>* Browse all the latest releases<br>* Subscribe to notifications on your favorite series<br>* Get cast/director/release-year information<br>* Request support/report bugs directly from within the app<br>* Designed for both tablets and phone - all in the same app!<br>* Unblock-US can be used from all over the globe :)<p>* Sign-up to Unblock-US here: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://bit.ly/10hnDHl&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGfg2ZDBlluUzr0hCisOkVYEZfbPA" target="_blank">http://bit.ly/10hnDHl</a>  if not already a member/user!<p>Follow us on Facebook: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.facebook.com/ZoonSoftware&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGia-Zyc9uaX7JAz3s3Od1S-es3Ng" target="_blank">https://www.facebook.com/ZoonSoftware</a><br>Follow us on Twitter: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://twitter.com/UBNFApp&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEEmAAsd1Hkw6WBaF9q86drm4Yjwg" target="_blank">https://twitter.com/UBNFApp</a><p>The Youtube video is currently outdated! It will be updated soon!<p>** THE UNBLOCK-US/OVERPLAY SERVICE DOES NOT WORK OVER 3G/4G CONNECTIONS **<p>**   THIS APP REQUIRES A PAID SUBSCRIPTION TO EITHER UNBLOCK-US OR OVERPLAY IF YOU WISH TO SWITCH NETFLIX REGION. SUCH AN ACCOUNT IS NOT PROVIDED WITH THE APP **', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=dk.zoon.unblocknetflix', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/mc3Bh6KIYbS69YZcUoPh3_UpYH6FbvwleEFsKCJc7BqP-LWoaiG7EYIHhoehTl8XQEs', 3.10, 'ENTERTAINMENT', '$2.73', '1,000+', 'android.permission.READ_LOGS, android.permission.GET_TASKS, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, dk.zoon.unblocknetflix.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE'),
(210, 'com.thehopemachine.netflix', 'nQueue for Netflix', 'The Hope Machine', 'Tired of only finding 10 movies at a time when you search on a Roku? Don&#39;t like the search results that keep showing the same movies? nQueue for Netflix will find more movies and TV shows and let you add them to your Netflix instant queue. <p>It makes it really easy to find the right show for viewing through your XBox, Wii, Roku, et al, or just getting the DVD. nQueue is also designed to let you share your love of movies by letting you email a synopsis to a friend.<p>Now lets you search for movie stars and read their bio!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.thehopemachine.netflix', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/q3_YFNtySUsOIwNX04Z2QdnAZ5Z79jXs45cXqi7FWgFztSxfwnEgkzfA2OkYaIPESJ0', 2.93, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '10,000+', ''),
(211, 'com.nexapps.myq', 'MyQ For Netflix', 'nexapps.net', 'Note: reordering items in the instant queue is currently broken on Netflix&#39;s side.<p>Can&#39;t find anything to watch on Netflix?  Then MyQ For Netflix is for you!<p>View the latest new releases, browse by genres, view personalized recommendations, manage your queues or search all from one app.  Now has an tablet optimized user interface for tablets 7 inches and larger.<p>While MyQ does not require linking a Netflix account, certain features will either be unavailable (recommendations, user ratings, managing queues) or imprecise (search).<p>Please note that there is also no way to view discs at home due to a limitation set by Netflix.<p>App is supported by ads (Google Admob), a paid version that removes ads is available as MyQ For Netflix Pro.<p>Future plans:<br>  * Better user interface for really large screens (Nexus 10) to reduce unused space<br>  * Better TV series support<br>  * Recommendations sorting<br>  * Whatever users ask for!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nexapps.myq', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/VdpFWhVWO6nkt4tuBquy6qE5yMo2qcQql5M1jPyfIyPK2UKw6hgEktnIXAhsT7ITGWc', 3.93, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '10,000+', ''),
(212, 'com.bk.helloandroid', 'Critics Pix For Netflix', 'BeeKay', 'Application that lets you add New York Times Critics Picks, latest movies on DVD and in theatres to your Netflix queue. Also search for movies by name and add to Netflix.<p>Release 1.1.1<br>- Fixed login issues.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bk.helloandroid', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/aEeClF9MuPV75g2gGGJ5nCb6IjoJGZarvofCWO9rIJF_pUmfZPTMlA2p3DzQasSxtbw', 3.25, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '10,000+', ''),
(213, 'air.whatsonnetflix', 'What''s on Netflix', 'Posterity Information Technology LTD', 'Fans of Netflix will love this application as it offers direct access to What&#39;s On Netflix&#39;s what&#39;s new section with the latest Netflix content for the United States Netflix and United Kingdom Netflix. <p>With regular updates to extend the experience you can download this app completely ad free today.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.whatsonnetflix', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/l6aLhNg1oDsqIFiE0EOOAV8g6XERham0mtgx3stPbRFmW5RWqUn8cOjer9gfu4VrCKo', 3.64, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '1,000+', ''),
(214, 'com.andromo.dev27897.app104457', 'ANFA - A NetFlix App', 'Malone Enterprise', 'Just an easy to navigate app that displays the Top Netflix movies by genre, Top 100, and new Watch Instantly arrivals. Sometimes, simpler is best!<p>The ads displayed help support my effort, so please visit the advertisers. Please contact developer if you are interested in an ad-free version!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.andromo.dev27897.app104457', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/J1aYztXWR-ka8MWJyeQA5my0YlXWSwMVRiYXtCqqNNZZhJlDkNe9Hj0evQ44YVzpwD0', 2.05, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '5,000+', ''),
(215, 'com.ktighe.mynetflixq_d', 'My Netflix Q Donate', 'Kevin Tighe', 'A simple app to manage your Netflix queues (donation version).<p>Features:<br>-Ability to manage disc and instant queues<br>-Search for titles<br>-View Netflix recommendations<br>-Browse titles by category<br>-Rate titles<br>-No ads<p>This app is identical to the free &quot;My Netflix Q&quot; app, except that I get a small donation from this one :).  Thank you!!<p>NOTE:  Currently Netflix is not returning information for some account types.  Unfortunately Netflix has discontinued support for 3rd party apps, so this may or may not get resolved.  Sorry!<p>Email me with problems / suggestions!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ktighe.mynetflixq_d', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/4ox1cqlPym5AiwljHQE5CSkNlato2PZAWk1-NoCbS32QIIKuKtbxBAW1WQDlLfOiG5o', 4.38, 'ENTERTAINMENT', '$1.50', '500+', ''),
(216, 'dk.zoon.ubnfsearch', 'Netflix Global Search', 'Zoon Software', 'Search the entire Netflix catalog - all the countries that Netflix is available in - NOT just the U.S! <p>Search Denmark, Sweden, Norway, Finland, Ireland, Mexico, Brazil, United Kingdom, United States, Canada and the Netherlands<p>** If you already bought the Unblock Netflix app. you already have this search functionality - and more :-)  No need to buy both of them **<p>Enter you search term, and the app. will show you program-info, and in which countries the program is available - including which subtitles are available!<p>If you do a subtitle search, it will only show you the countries where that subtitle is available!<p>Works fantastics on tablets! <p>* Includes catalog-info (see screenshot)<br>* Extended movieinfo<br>* Save movies as favorites for later<br>* Search for actor, director, production year, title<br>* Search in a specific Netflix region<br>* Search for specific subtitles<br>* Browse Netflix genres<br>* Superfast search!<br>* Save favorites<br>* Subscribe to notification when new seasons are available for your favorite show<br>* and much more!<p>Use the settings to configure your search parameters!<p>Follow us on Facebook: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.facebook.com/ZoonSoftware&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGia-Zyc9uaX7JAz3s3Od1S-es3Ng" target="_blank">https://www.facebook.com/ZoonSoftware</a><br>Follow us on Twitter: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://twitter.com/UBNFApp&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEEmAAsd1Hkw6WBaF9q86drm4Yjwg" target="_blank">https://twitter.com/UBNFApp</a><p>New updates will provide more features!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=dk.zoon.ubnfsearch', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/Cr9cR6UqgmwRvY6ow2ZdYbdjRO1lNF0TgTQmNDcZMeGzsxrwP6DPel9-u7FghMJ_Jrtr', 4.06, 'ENTERTAINMENT', '$2.14', '500+', 'android.permission.READ_LOGS, android.permission.GET_TASKS, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, dk.zoon.ubnfsearch.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE'),
(217, 'com.vdowall.getnetflixfree', 'How To Get Free Netflix', 'appsongkhla', 'How To Get Free Netflix Videos App for Android!<p>- Free How To Get Free Netflix Videos from YouTube<p>For Copyright Holders : All the movies are youtube videos. For any copyright report contact by mail. we will remove links.<p>Disclaimer: All the movies hosted on YouTube we dont host anything. And you cant download video DUE TO THEIR TERMS OF SERVICE!. We always respect your creation. If any copyright issue please report to youtube and us.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.vdowall.getnetflixfree', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/qCyIP0ah1-GUJSQ3_XAIug7ej0Bb8xHHJ5KU4Ko8I7zYBEp0GntmAdDF5dP9j8xduQ', 3.83, 'MEDIA_AND_VIDEO', 'Free', '1,000+', ''),
(218, 'com.nexapps.myqpro', 'MyQ For Netflix Pro', 'nexapps.net', 'This is the ad free version of MyQ For Netflix.  Please make sure to try out the free version on your device first.<p>Can&#39;t find anything to watch on Netflix?  Then MyQ For Netflix is for you!<p>View the latest new releases, browse by genres, view personalized recommendations, manage your queues or search all from one app.  Now has an tablet optimized user interface for tablets 7 inch and larger.<p>While MyQ does not require linking a Netflix account, certain features will either be unavailable (recommendations, user ratings, managing queues) or imprecise (search).<p>Please note that there is also no way to view discs at home due to a limitation set by Netflix.<p>Future plans:<br>  * Better TV series support<br>  * Whatever users ask for!<br>  * Subgenre browsing', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nexapps.myqpro', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/Nh3svMO38ByZZlFxjdGkkYfUMsismZyZrGeyCnPVE0-gcUrcvddUjTPg_XHmAv9omV0', 4.43, 'ENTERTAINMENT', '$0.99', '100+', ''),
(219, 'sm.dev.flixdroidAS', 'FlixDroid (Ad Supported)', 'Sam Matthews', '- ATTENTION - NEXFLIX HAS DISCONTINUED THE DATA FEED THAT FLIXDROID DEPENDED ON TO PROVIDE SEARCH.  THE SEARCH FACILITY WILL NO LONGER FUNCTION.<p>I have already unpublished the &#39;pay&#39; version of Flixdroid.  This app will soon be discontinued as well.<p>Sorry for any inconveniences.  <p>Sam Matthews - Developer<p>PS.. Netflix sucks<p>---------------------------------------------------<br>FlixDroid is a high power search engine for the Netflix movie catalog.  It will help you find all the movies you&#39;ve been looking for on Netflix.  You can search by Title, Synopsis, MPAA Ratings, Genres, Actors, Languages, Format, Release Year, User Ratings, and more.  Once you have a search you like, you can save it to use over and over.  Flixdroid is also a full featured Queue manager.  Once you find the title you&#39;ve been looking for add it to your queue.  <p>*Note - NOT FOR INSTANT VIEWING!  Currently there is one ONE app on Android that can view Netflix &#39;Watch it Now&#39;, and that is the official NETFLIX app, so please don&#39;t download this if your are looking for that feature!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=sm.dev.flixdroidAS', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/0y1v_xifi5Vkzucp-qYFsi6ETeav8jTlQkYfbLZbrYy2AhE6lhFBt2pauxWJZZOFJ98', 3.47, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '50,000+', ''),
(220, 'com.in2flick', 'In2Flick (Lite version)', 'DMT Inc.', 'In2Flick (Lite version) - Netflix Queue Manager for Android<p>Netflix Queue Manager. Manage your movie queues, Search movies by keyword, Browse all 20 categories, Rate your movies.<p>Add, remove, rearrange movies on your Netflix queue.<br>View and Browse ALL 20 movie categories.<br>Search for movies by keyword and retrieve detailed movie descriptions and graphics.<br>Rate movies you have watched(1 to 5 stars).<br>View your movie history (Items Shipped, Items Watched, Items Returned).<br>Display your Netflix movie recommendations.<br>Multi-language support: English, Spanish, French.<br>The most fun Android Netflix queue manager!<p>**Note: this version is not designed for OS 4.x(ICS)', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.in2flick', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/pB3K6BsH5kJMzRHPoxbeM3bkpdXAjDsae7ei00h-7YEEuG30av3f3SUr5Wd1t0eikY-I', 3.29, 'MEDIA_AND_VIDEO', 'Free', '10,000+', '');
INSERT INTO `apps` (`id`, `packageName`, `title`, `author`, `description`, `url`, `icon`, `playRating`, `category`, `cost`, `numDownloads`, `permissions`) VALUES
(221, 'com.instagram.android', 'Instagram', 'Instagram', 'Over 150 million users love Instagram!<br>It&#39;s a simple way to capture and share the world&#39;s moments on your Android.<p>Customize your photos and videos with one of several gorgeous and custom built filter effects. Transform everyday moments into works of art you&#39;ll want to share with friends and family.<p>Share your photos and video in a simple photo stream with friends to see - and follow your friends&#39; photos with the click of a single button. Every day you open up Instagram, you&#39;ll see new photos from your closest friends, and creative people from around the world.<p>Features<p>• 100% free custom designed filters: XPro-II, Earlybird, Rise, Amaro, Hudson, Lo-fi, Sutro, Toaster, Brannan, Inkwell, Walden, Hefe, Nashville, 1977, and others.<br>• Linear and Radial Tilt-Shift blur effects for extra depth of field.<br>• Instant sharing to Facebook, Twitter, Flickr, Tumblr and Foursquare<br>• Unlimited uploads<br>• Interact with friends through giving &amp; receiving likes and comments<br>• Works with Android versions 2.2 and above that support OpenGL ES 2<br>• And much much more…', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.instagram.android', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/vFpQP39LB60dli3n-rJnVvTM07dsvIzxrCL5xMiy1V4GV4unC1ifXkUExQ4N-DBCKwI', 4.60, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '100,000,000+', 'android.permission.CAMERA, android.permission.READ_CONTACTS, android.permission.GET_TASKS, android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.READ_PROFILE, android.permission.READ_FRAME_BUFFER, android.permission.SET_ORIENTATION, android.permission.BATTERY_STATS, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, com.instagram.android.permission.C2D_MESSAGE'),
(222, 'com.innovatty.instafollow', 'InstaFollow for Instagram', 'INNOVATTY, LLC', 'Discover who unfollowed you on Instagram and who is not following you back, track new followers, find mutual friends, view fans and more ...<p><br>Use InstaFollow app so that you can guard your Instagram account and get so much insight. It&#39;s fast, accurate and extremely intuitive. Tracking your followers on Instagram is almost instantaneous. This app will not only detect unfollowers, it will also make them think twice before unfollowing you. Just let them know that you&#39;re using InstaFollow Instagram followers checker.<p><br>Features:<br>- Login using Instagram account<br>- Retrieve lists of followers and following<br>- Detect new followers + unfollowers<br>- Detect non-followers<br>- Detect mutual friends and fans<br>- Follow/unfollow users<br>- Show user profiles<br>- Support accounts up to 10,000 followers<br>- Support multiple accounts<p>Engagement Package (Optional):<br>- Show top likers<br>- Show top commenters<br>- Show best followers<br>- Show worst/ghost followers<br>- Show secret admirers<p><br>So next time you asked yourself &#39;Who unfollowed me on Instagram?&#39;, just use InstaFollow. It will answer this question plus more. You&#39;ll like it instantly.<p><br>If you get featured on InstFollow, you can gain more followers on Instagram very quickly.<p><br>Find out who your best friends on Instagram are using our InstaBestFriends app. You can also generate &#39;My Best Friends&#39; cards for sharing on Instagram.<p>You need an Instagram account to use this app!<p>Follow us on Instagram @InsTrack to get latest news', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.innovatty.instafollow', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/JHKVLP_A1WGOKafwFfdxmo0tvBNieji91KTGUUY7CF8AH-UzdfZquNa2liafeuKZFrU', 4.44, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '5,000,000+', 'com.android.vending.BILLING'),
(223, 'com.tinypiece.android.ipf', 'InstaPicFrame for Instagram', 'Tiny Piece Co., Ltd', 'This app has powerful functions and it is very easy to use. You can use this app to merge lots of photos into one photo through a very simple operation.<br>and you can post the photo to instagram.<p>Features<br>1.You could customize the style or use templates to merge photos.<br>2 Shake your iPhone/iPod touch to change the photo template.<br>3 Provides a lot of beautiful frames and background templates to make the result photo much more beautiful.<br>4. You could share your photos to instagram, Facebook, Twitter, Tumblr and Flickr.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tinypiece.android.ipf', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/CJwYT10FH8du3zHCt78nCJgKDnOh40d0-vgZVbr7q8UgIGUOQ6EUD_pckk86MWB6idXN', 4.17, 'PHOTOGRAPHY', 'Free', '10,000,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_LOCATION_EXTRA_COMMANDS, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, com.android.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, android.permission.CAMERA, com.android.vending.BILLING'),
(224, 'codeadore.textgram', 'Textgram (for BBM & Instagram)', 'Codeadore', 'Create beautiful pictures out of any text and share them with your friends on Facebook, Instagram, Whatsapp, etc.. or save them in your gallery.<p>USER REVIEWS<br>????? – “Simple: great, great, great.”<br>????? – “Awesome app. Very creative and fun. Easy to use also!!”<br>????? – “I love this app. It helps me get things out on instagram”<br>????? – &quot;I have fun with the designs and frames. U need to take time and play with it.” <p>AWARDS<br>? App of the day 28 May 2012<br>? Featured in Android Magazin (Dutch Edition) May 2012<p>TOP FEATURES<br>? Custom backgrounds<br>? Emojis<br>? Custom stickers<br>? Variety of fonts<br>? Many cool text effects (reflection, shadow, rotation &amp; more...)<br>? Filters<br>? Frames<p>You can save them in your gallery, or share them with your friends on Facebook, Instagram, Twitpic, Pinerest,Whatsapp, Streamzoo, Picstitch, Instacollage ,Instaframe (or Pic stitch), BBM (BlackBerry Messenger), etc.<p>You may use it with Picstitch, Instacollage, Instaframe, Twitpic, ebuddy, line, viber, pinterest, and many other other apps.<p>It comes with many cute and beautiful backgrounds, frames, filters, fonts, effects &amp; more...<p>Textgram can be used along with other photo editing applications like: brannan, sutro, hefe, photogrid, picsart, grid, walden, inkwell, drawcam, fontself, amaro, collages, collage, piccollage, earlybird, yakitori, nashville, studio, hudson, toaster.<p>ABOUT PERMISSIONS:<p>INTERNET ACCESS - Used for Textgram Store, where extra templates, backgrounds, stickers &amp; frames are available to download for free.<p>STORAGE - Used to save the textgrams you create, and to save the items downloaded from Textgram Store.<p>GET_ACCOUNTS - This is used by Pocket Change to identify users across multiple devices. This way, rewards earned through Pocket Change, will still be available if you change your phone and reinstall the app on a new device.', 'https: