(225, 'com.csms.activities', 'TextCutie-Instagram & Whatsapp', 'Leko Studio', 'Best picture editor to add beautiful text to your photo and share with the world on Instagram, Whatsapp, Facebook, Pinterest, tumblr, twitter, BBM etc.<p>Cute pictures combined with your favorite text make a popular message. You will get more likes on Instagram, make your Whatsapp friends smile:)<p>Thanksgiving card theme package is released! Send Thanksgiving greetings.<p>?USER REVIEWS?<br>????? – “Text Cutie Instagram It is so cute! It puts a smile on everyones face receive my Thanksgiving card.”<br>????? –Wow! Thanks! Because of this, I got my 70 likes on instagram.<br>????? – “So easy to use and really good at making nice text photos :) Galaxy Note3”<br>????? – “Awesome	I love this app , it has gotten me more followers and it is just great to be creative with the designs they have . I love this app go and download it”<br>????? – &quot;It is cute :D	Over 1000 adorable backgrounds, fonts, stickers and emojis, quick and easy to use, lots of options. Would recommend!”<p>TOP FEATURES<br>? Random templates<br>? Custom backgrounds<br>? Variety of fonts, themes, stickers<br>? Emojis<br>? Custom stickers<p>  Thanksgiving card theme package is released! we also have a varirty of holiday themes ,birthday themes ,movie themes.<p>***WHAT’LL YOU DO WITH IT<p>? Choose a suitable template for your text<br>? You also can load a picture from your gallery<br>? Position the text in the way you want<br>? Change the text size, font, color, rotate.Show your creativeness!<br>? Add stickers,shapes,emojis to your picture.<br>?Share the text-picture to Instagram, Whatsapp, Facebook, Twitter or save to your picture gallery!<p>You can save them in your gallery, or share them with your friends on Facebook, Instagram, Pinterest, Whatsapp, Streamzoo, Picstitch, Instacollage ,Instaframe (or Pic stitch), Airdrop (IOS7 feature), Line, Go SMS etc.<p>You may use it with Picstitch, Textgram, Instacollage, Instaframe, Twit