(281, 'com.subsplash.thechurchapp.graysharborfoursquarechurch', 'Grays Harbor Foursquare Church', 'Subsplash Consulting', 'Welcome to the official Grays Harbor Foursquare Church Application for Android.<p>Our church family application connects you to what’s going on weekly at Grays Harbor Foursquare Church. Catch up on all of Pastor Steve Purdue’s recent messages by watching the video or listening to the audio, and easily share links via Twitter or Email. You also have access to our live streaming so you can watch the entire service LIVE on the go.<p>Our Event section allows you to keep up with the latest happenings in our church. Plus, you can stay connected to the community through our Connect section.<p>For more information about Grays Harbor Foursquare Church, please visit: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.ghfoursquare.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHkGnpshF_M1OdNg8zsVP6qdX5GtA" target="_blank">http://www.ghfoursquare.com/</a><p>The Grays Harbor Foursquare Church app was developed with the Subsplash App Platform.<p>App: © 2013 The Church App, Content: © 2013 Grays Harbor Foursquare Church. All rights reserved.<p>Keywords: Jesus, God, Bible, Christ, Subsplash, Church App, Church, Grays Harbor Foursquare Church, Grays Harbor', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.subsplash.thechurchapp.graysharborfoursquarechurch', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/metHHFrrTfPogCEbUYOZvrxpoYRIo7axM3spv8_GwXeycuIiExiedXZ7oFOvkYkeoJo', 5.00, 'EDUCATION', 'Free', '100+', 'com.subsplash.thechurchapp.graysharborfoursquarechurch.permission.MAPS_RECEIVE, com.google.android.providers.gsf.permission.READ_GSERVICES, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, com.subsplash.thechurchapp.graysharborfoursquarechurch.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS'),
