(283, 'com.apps.foursquare14', 'Foursquare Connection 13', 'Oodles Apps, LLC', 'Download the Foursquare Connection 2013 App to find maps, schedule info and more for the annual Foursquare family gathering, held May 28-30, 2013 in Lake Buena Vista, Fla.  You can also find fellow Foursquare friends attending the event, and see what&#39;s trending on Twitter.  Download this free app today!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.apps.foursquare14', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/fcIiVfBFp6TRAA-XA7gN7NIc8_L2JRcNGNwsMQULO0__XbT7rd59g_MRq4YmdnBZjbw', 2.00, 'BUSINESS', 'Free', '100+', 'android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.WRITE_CONTACTS, android.permission.CALL_PHONE, android.permission.CAMERA, android.hardware.camera, android.hardware.camera.autofocus, android.permission.READ_CONTACTS, com.apps.foursquare14.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, android.permission.WRITE_CALENDAR, android.permission.READ_CALENDAR, android.permission.READ_CALL_LOG, android.permission.WRITE_CALL_LOG'),
(284, 'foursqwifi.aithanasakis', 'VenueSpot - Wifi pass finder', 'thanasakis', 'BEST-UNIQUE FEATURE! SAVES THE RESULTS FOR LATER OFFLINE USE!<p>Get Internet access anywhere around the world, using wifi networks from cafe, restaurants, bars, finding their passwords from the tips left on foursquare !<p>NO FOURSQUARE ACCOUNT REQUIRED<p>Features:<br>-Find wifi access on the road, anywhere!<br>-Radar your results to easily locate them!<br>-No internet required! Save and search previous finds!<br>-Use GPS for better results<p>Browse venues from your home, around any place on earth you choose from an interactive map inside the app, automaticaly store them, so when you visit that place, you will have all the wifi passwords with you, no internet access required! 100% offline use! Ideal for places with low mobile signal, trips abroad, or when you just can&#39;t afford to pay for mobile data!<p>With just a few clicks, you can discover wifi networks around you, and find their passwords from the tips on foursquare! You can even use it offline! It&#39;s really easy!<p><br>IMPORTANT NOTE!: The app shows results in metres not in miles! 1m.=3feet<p><br>The app CONTAINS ADS to help for its development, but in the future there will be a low costing paid app without the ads, so please don&#39;t negative rate them.<p>Permissions analysis:<br>1)android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION<br>2)android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION<p>The app needs to know your location, to show the venues around you.<p>3)android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE<p>The app stores it&#39;s database to your sd card, or if you don&#39;t have one, to the internal storage<p>4)android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE<p>The app needs to know whether you are online or not to show you the right options for online or offline use<p>5)android.permission.INTERNET<p>Obviously the app needs internet access sometimes, to get the wifi passoword from foursquare and display the maps of the venues locations<p>keywords: wifi, password, venues, wi-fi, passwords, foursquarewifi, foursqaure wifi. 4sqwifi ,4sqwifi.com ,<p>Changes Log:<p>v.1.1.0<br>-New offline option! Find places around me, automaticaly searches for saved venues around your current location<br>-Minor bug fixes<br>V.1.0.8<br>-New option to find location by name, not only on map<br>-Easier to select from map<br>-New feature! &quot;Radar&quot; any venue, to locate it easily when you are on the road. <p>V.1.0.7<br>-better location identify<br>-bug fixes<p>v.1.0.6<br>-UI Improvements<br>-Bug fixes<p>v.1.0.5<br>-option to open location settings if can&#39;t find location', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=foursqwifi.aithanasakis', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/UkeW2-pp-CqvsLjqvaWibvkmrVWzf7eBjYMX_oBiCe7dVpRrgvq4169oZLKrYXWlyA', 4.16, 'COMMUNICATION', 'Free', '50,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION'),
(285, 'com.thunsaker.soup.pro', 'Soup Pro (for Foursquare)', 'Thomas Hunsaker', 'This app is just a license key for Soup (for Foursquare). You must download and install the free version of Soup.<p>**Pro Version Features**<br>Remove ads<br>View Foursquare Check-in History<p>**Soup Features**<br>Soup is a superuser app for foursquare superusers! Use this app to edit venues, flag them as mislocated/closed/etc. and try to make foursquare a better place for everyone.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.thunsaker.soup.pro', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/aKchxZheQG5DsgAgwZrETF0POu2cVTIOsO5RHnKi2Zm5feF4n2VbnlAShi0gj7y9-h0', 5.00, 'TOOLS', '$2.99', '50+', ''),
(286, 'com.footfeed', 'Footfeed', 'Footfeed', 'Footfeed is the first Android app that makes it easy to checkin to Facebook Places, Foursquare, Gowalla, Google Latitude and post to Twitter simultaneously. Built from the ground up as a multi checkin network, Footfeed makes it possible to checkin to many networks without the need to open multiple apps. No more wasting time checking in with multiple apps. No more checkin fatigue.??<p>Using Footfeed to check in is easy. Simply create an account and link up your network accounts. When you want to check in, select your location and press checkin. You will continue to earn your points, badges, mayorships, rewards and rankings from each of the checkin networks.??<p>Key Features?<br>* Multi Checkin Capable: check in once to multiple networks simultaneously including Facebook Places, Foursquare, Gowalla, Google Latitude, Facebook and Twitter??<p>* Nearby Check-in Deals &amp; Rewards: find all of the deals and rewards available from local businesses just for checking in. Includes over 15,000 Foursquare deals and hundreds of Geotoko check-in deals<p>* Tips &amp; To Dos: we aggregate all of the tips and recommendations shared by users across all the check-in networks so you can easily get ideas on where to go and what to do ?<p>* Single Check in Feed: view all your friends checkins from Foursquare and Gowalla in a single feed??* Stats: view all your stats across the checkin networks in a single view including, points, badges, mayorships, friends, stamps and more<p>??* Friends: view all your friends on your checkin networks including their stats and recent checkin history??* Favorite Locations: mark your favorite locations for quick checkin??<p>Footfeed is recommended for fans of Facebook, Foursquare, Gowalla, Latitude, Loopt, Whrrl, Buzzd and other checkin networks<p>Follow us on Twitter: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.twitter.com/footfeedapp&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNH8JGM4MA_uJO1gfRpzVgu9cPQoYw" target="_blank">http://www.twitter.com/footfeedapp</a>?<br>Friend us on Facebook: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://bit.ly/footfeed&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNE6V5FjUCpJR9HEWaii8Tv5qa3Smw" target="_blank">http://bit.ly/footfeed</a><p>And make sure to login to Footfeed.com where you get complete access to your account.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.footfeed', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/nwTmtxB6fHdHnuLEeciJT2KUjhs71h5ydoYjD2Yg2-vCEHSO-YYDEG5meAgN5O_Ang', 2.65, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '10,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION'),
(287, 'com.appcastnet.checkinhistory', 'Check-in History', 'AppCastNet', 'It is used for checking the history of check-in in Facebook, Foursquare, Gowalla.<p>Keyword: Map, Checkin, Check-in history, Facebook places, Foursquare, Gowalla, World map, information, check-in details, location point, country name, one click, all records, listing result, map presentation, places information content box, Android, multiple account, social network, keep record', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.appcastnet.checkinhistory', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/feFUGieOqe3TJlqXjNNXwjY46osM_JDD74kzWcUPaq2D7MWZMRQYGJhmhW1-X9HQkjI', 3.92, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '10,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION'),
(288, 'com.yasoom.lite', 'yasoom (Facebook,Twitter,4sq)', '5C-Basic Distribution', 'Never miss another post! See what your friends do in just one app and don’t waste any more time keeping up to date with Twitter, Facebook and foursquare individually.<p>yasoom for Android even goes beyond aggregating the information from the different social communities. Update your status, share photos, check-in to locations, comment and re-tweet - do everything from one place.<p><br>With its unique alerts system and its innovative bookmark feature, yasoom makes it easier for you to separate essential information from less important entries, and allows you to keep up to date with your social networks more quickly and easily.<p>??? Selected Features ???<br>?	A combined stream of messages for Twitter, Facebook, foursquare<br>?	Post everywhere: Type once and post across multiple social networks<br>?	Unique notification system based on your personal preferences.<br>?	Maintain different profiles from the same network using multiple accounts.<br>?	Innovative bookmarking function.<br>?	Facebook, Twitter &amp; foursquare integration.<br>?	Data caching: works fast and even when you are offline <p>??? Feedback &amp; Support ???<p>If you like yasoom please support us by giving a 5 star rating. If you do not like yasoom or happen to have a problem please let us know! <p><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://getsatisfaction.com/yasoom&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHk-X3wyF4xkXyFzTWyO3nuz9kSWA" target="_blank">http://getsatisfaction.com/yasoom</a><br>Twitter: #yasoomNews<p>NOTE: yasoom posts to Fourquare, Facebook and Twitter. We will add Google+, but currently they do not have a public API.<p>Keywords: cross-post, social network, Facebook, Twitter, Foursquare, 4sq, photo, easy to use, fast, comment, status update, share, alternative', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.yasoom.lite', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/MEW7ztgpZpXFEUVo66mbdKI-KSE-mhD0v6XiMTmvKxgXgvWyCm2RRzWABu9JmW4D_MM', 3.84, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '10,000+', 'android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, android.permission.GET_TASKS'),
(289, 'th.beng.foodsquare', 'foodSquare', 'Nuttakit K.yoo', 'Don&#39;t know where to have your lunch? <br>FoodSquare, can help you find food shops near you. Along with a number of people check-ins on FourSquare,so you can know how popular that place is!!.<p>If you still can&#39;t choose, just shake the phone, We will random a place for you.<p>Feature:<br>- find food shops, restaurants near you with number of people who been checked-in.<br>- sort by distance or checkin count<br>- type in place name to find restaurant somewhere else.<br>- shake to randomly pick a place.<br>- checkins to FourSquare.<br>- Upload picture to fourSquare Venue<br>- view place details, map, tips, images<br>- now you can use foodSquare without having to login to FourSquare first, unless you need to checkins.<br>- support multi-language included Thai.<p>TODO:<br>- submit tips.<br>- Show tip, picture list.<br>- Show detail of place in-app.<br>- etc.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=th.beng.foodsquare', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/aNYqMHJPxZkBvs6rRIXoDWu3JoCTDEe27tt-esOOptrb3E8uoRYHSsDeenBhAHDFycFr', 4.17, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '10,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.CAMERA'),
(290, 'com.speaktoit.assistant', 'Assistant', 'Speaktoit', 'Speaktoit Assistant is a virtual assistant for Android devices. Your very own customizable Assistant awaits your commands – answering your questions, performing tasks, notifying you about important events, and making your daily routine easier (and, often, more fun along the way).<p>The Speaktoit Assistant has been named:<p>????? New York Times: Top 10 Android App of the Year<br>????? Forbes: Top 10 Mobile App for Productivity<br>????? Red Herring Top 100 Global Winner<br>????? PC World: Best free Android apps of 2011<p>Your Speaktoit Assistant uses natural language technology to answer questions, find information, launch apps, and connect you with various web services (like Google, Wikipedia, Twitter, Facebook, Foursquare, Evernote, Yelp, and others).<p>What else can your Assistant do?<p>It Remembers - As the Assistant learns about your favorite places, services, and preferences, it takes into account your current environment and schedule in order to provide the best suggestions and Assistant functions customized to you.<p>It Understands - There&#39;s no need to memorize any commands or learn any special tricks to make the Assistant work for you - just speak naturally, the Assistant will understand you.<p>It Cares - Your Assistant offers proactive assistance when it thinks you might need it - your best interests are always in mind.<p>It Speaks Your Language - The multilingual Assistant is available in English, Spanish, Russian, German, Chinese and Portuguese - and it&#39;s currently being trained in many other languages that will launch soon.<p>It&#39;s Always at Your Service - Your Assistant is cross-platform: use the same Assistant on your smartphone, tablet, or laptop.<p>It Learns - Want your Assistant to respond or react in a specific way? Teach it to further improve its efficiency!<p>The list of the Assistant’s skills is too large to fit here, you can find them in the application under the little light bulb next to the microphone. Some of them are: talk, call numbers and contacts, send and receive texts messages and email, set alarms, search websites, get answers from encyclopedias, find places, read news, get weather forecasts, do basic math, updates Facebook statuses, tweet, organize calendar, tasks and notes, play music and videos, open sites and applications, translate, navigate, check in on Foursquare, remind, learn from you new commands and much more.<p>Currently, the Assistant work with the following services: Google, Twitter, Facebook, Foursquare, Evernote, Yelp, TripAdvisor, Wikipedia, Chacha, IMDB, Eventful, News360, Amazon, Gmail, Google Images, Google Calendar, Google Maps, Google Navigation, Waze and it’s being connected to more.<p>Compare it to other voice assistants like Apple Siri, Nuance Dragon Go, Vlingo, Evi, Voice Actions, Voice Search, Wolfram Alpha, Iris, IBM Watson, Maluuba, Skyvi, Jeannie, AIVC, EVA Intern,  and other voice control applications.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.speaktoit.assistant', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/stQiyI9vFIZEGpZmXMQXJIr7L8_1miuYTr_3j7fpuqjcmGpQuT2Svgz9BkIsQ1x4Rro', 4.67, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '5,000,000+', 'android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE, android.permission.BLUETOOTH_ADMIN, android.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, android.permission.WRITE_SYNC_SETTINGS, android.permission.BLUETOOTH, android.permission.READ_SYNC_SETTINGS, android.permission.READ_SMS, android.permission.WRITE_SMS, android.permission.CALL_PHONE, android.permission.READ_CONTACTS, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, com.android.alarm.permission.SET_ALARM, android.permission.SEND_SMS, android.permission.RECEIVE_SMS, android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS, android.permission.BROADCAST_STICKY, com.android.vending.BILLING, com.speaktoit.assistant.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS, android.permission.READ_LOGS, android.permission.GET_TASKS'),
(291, 'com.tumblr', 'Tumblr', 'Tumblr', '• Post anything, from anywhere.<br>• Share photos, gifs, video, music, quotes, chats, links, and text. Find and follow the things you love, and get all your latest news from your dashboard.<br>• Bonus: Add a &#39;create a post&#39; widget to your home screen.<br>• Advanced controls: Save drafts, queue posts, customize tweets, and more!<br>• Messages: View and reply to messages.<br>• Multiple blogs: Seamlessly manage all of your blogs.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tumblr', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/qL8WP8bO7qViEkxwTXYGzroI-U1JPkRwRv3YylZM8mvmrAdnKaAdgaNW2SFvZEfH1ic', 4.35, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '10,000,000+', 'android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.MANAGE_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.AUTHENTICATE_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.READ_SYNC_SETTINGS, android.permission.WRITE_SYNC_SETTINGS, android.permission.READ_CONTACTS, android.permission.NFC, android.permission.CAMERA, com.android.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, com.tumblr.SERVICE_PERMISSION, com.tumblr.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE'),
(292, 'com.hostj2me.stumblr.mobile', 'Stumbler: Tumblr Image Search', 'Brilliance Mobility', 'Stumbler is an easy way to search Tumblr for photos. You can bookmark your favorite blog discoveries and download or share photos. You can even post your own photos and apply filters. In addition, Stumbler can search seamlessly across Imgur, the web, Instagram, 500px, and Danbooru style image boards.<p>Features<p>? Search for blogs<br>? Save images<br>? Share images<br>? Reblog images<br>? Like images<br>? View Tumblr dashboard<br>? View Tumblr followers<br>? View Tumblr following<br>? Follow/Unfollow blogs<br>? Backup/Sync browsing history<br>? GIF Support<br>? Post images to Tumblr<br>? Live Wallpaper (Beta, not recommended for tablets)<p>Like us on Facebook<p><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.facebook.com/stumblr&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHQfSjLm957bxhRNasxIF1rB4k1IA" target="_blank">https://www.facebook.com/stumblr</a><p>*Stumbler is powered by the Tumblr API.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.hostj2me.stumblr.mobile', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/XqxUdMwmNGeP1YBQ_nQgGZH-OB4iAxKk7XA8L3Mu9xNj8oJFZIxTqFE18Q0DRbsJY-k', 4.15, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '100,000+', ''),
(293, 'com.luckydroid.tumblelog', 'ShortBlogger for Tumblr', 'LuckyDroid', '“If you haven’t already chosen your choice Tumblr app, we strongly suggest you give ShortBlogger a go. It’s quick, efficient, and looks great on the Android platform.”<br>www.androidappsreview.com<p>“A fantastic Tumblr client, one that advanced users would do well to check out for themselves”<br>www.androidrundown.com<p>ShortBlogger is powerful Tumblr client for Android.<p>Features:<br>* Post to Tumblr. Send a Text, Photo, Quote, Link, Chat, Audio or Video post.<br>* View your dashboard, posts, queue and drafts.<br>* View your liked posts.<br>* Animated GIFs.<br>* Following/followers list;<br>* Tracking by tags;<br>* Blogs cache. You can view blogs when you&#39;re offline.<br>* Edit or delete your own posts.<br>* Supports multiple blogs.<br>* Quick Reblog and Like.<br>* Follow or unfollow.<br>* Messages: View and reply to messages.<br>* View notes.<br>* Spotlight/Featured Tags.<br>* Powerful post editor with rich text styles.<br>* Save images to SD card.<br>* And much much more!<p>Follow luckydroid.tumblr.com', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.luckydroid.tumblelog', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/vUDeaLYMW1Qnq8VQncrIHwbL4qTrZXCv042EmRDu0sSufy0Nomn8KAV64Xeqpv07-3cn', 3.91, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.MOUNT_UNMOUNT_FILESYSTEMS, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION'),
(294, 'com.luckydroid.tumblelogpro', 'ShortBlogger Pro for Tumblr', 'LuckyDroid', 'ShortBlogger is Tumblr Client for Android.<br>This is the ADS-FREE version!<p>Features:<br>* Post to Tumblr. Send a Text, Photo, Quote, Link, Chat, Audio or Video post.<br>* View your dashboard, posts and drafts.<br>* View your liked posts.<br>* Following/followers list;<br>* Tracking by tags;<br>* Blogs cache. You can view blogs when you&#39;re offline.<br>* Edit or delete your own posts.<br>* Supports multiple blogs.<br>* Quick Reblog and Like.<br>* Follow or unfollow.<br>* Messages: View and reply to messages.<br>* View notes.<br>* Spotlight;<br>* Animated GIFs.<br>* Save images to SD card.<br>* And much much more!<p>Follow luckydroid.tumblr.com<p>ShortBlogger was formerly known as Tumblelog. (Tumblr requested that we change the name)', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.luckydroid.tumblelogpro', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/3MwBKvo-9XMFkTd4IfAT5iTiKTjnnnL3x3RrLpsppjxbYL0vb9X-Lxv5Qx55eVTzg9k', 3.78, 'SOCIAL', '$3.99', '1,000+', 'android.permission.MOUNT_UNMOUNT_FILESYSTEMS, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION'),
(295, 'jp.yujideveloper.twiblr', 'Tumblr plugin for twicca', 'yuji.developer', '*** Notification ***<br>Support Tumblr API v2!<br>required re-auth.<br>*** Notification ***<p><br>This is Tumblr plug-in for twicca.<p>Features:<br>1. Quote post the tweet to Tumblr.<br>2. Photo post to Tumblr.<br>2. Video post to Tumblr.<p>* This plug-in author is yuji.developer. If you have any questions, contact via E-mail or twitter (@yuji_developer)<p>This application needs &quot;twicca&quot; 0.8.7 or above.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.yujideveloper.twiblr', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/jzd3Ig1GzJiXVxUpG41bZQ2nJNKmQ-I59pn9lo9GtHBJvRlGqIG012RXRrqw4kJ-64Fq', 3.48, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '10,000+', ''),
(296, 'com.jkrolling.trlbumlite', 'Tumblr Viewer: tRlbum Lite', 'YoungJ', 'Fantastic, Easiest, Simplest app to view your &quot;tumblr&quot; dashboard in &quot;FULLSCREEN&quot; mode.<p>View your &quot;tumblr&quot; Dashboard photo in &quot;FULLSCREEN&quot; mode.<br>* Support GIF animation picture<br>* Simply to use<br>* Full screen photo<br>* Save &quot;tumblr&quot; photo to SD card<br>* Like/Unlike &quot;tumblr&quot; post<br>* Support landscape<br>* tRlbum Lite is powered by the &quot;tumblr&quot; API.<p>Try our FULL version of tRlbum for Reblog, NFC share, Liked list... features!<br>http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jkrolling.trlbum', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jkrolling.trlbumlite', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/YysqqmepdwTLHPIFsNZ63fSCj19vCTSs8w3pU0sb7rSBZ0QUTPC-j5mXoXKf6Rj03Jod', 3.24, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '5,000+', ''),
(297, 'com.appmakr.app560614', 'Famous Tumblr Blog', 'Luís Paulo', 'Best tumblr app for one of the most famous tumblr blog.<br> check it out, and follow on tumblr.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.appmakr.app560614', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/OBIAZ_EFupcvZsuxOTRrp7xem6o7fThTGqkGDUYy0Jyq8ILsSfu7IQ3XBN8kB22rJeE', 2.57, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '5,000+', 'android.permission.CAMERA, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.READ_LOGS'),
(298, 'com.kitasoft.soline', 'Social Line (Tumblr/Instag)', 'Kitasoft Co., Ltd.', 'The Social Client. Supports for Twitter/Tumblr/Instagram/YouTube.<br>- Connect to the social network using plugins.<br>- Categorize and management for contents and accounts by side menu.<br>- Switch by one-tap for connection destinations and accounts.<br>- Update display by pulling edge of the contents view.<p>--------------------<br>Plugins<br>--------------------<p><font color="#009900">This app connect to the social network using plugins. Please install together plugins that have features for your use.</font><p>Currently, has published the following plugins.<br>- <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kitasoft.soline.twitter">for Twitter</a><br>- <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kitasoft.soline.tumblr">for Tumblr</a><br>- <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kitasoft.soline.instagram">for Instagram</a><br>- <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kitasoft.soline.youtube">for YouTube</a><p>--------------------<br>Interactions<br>--------------------<p>Plugin features will interact.<p>For example<br>- Playback for YouTube URL on Twitter timeline.<br>- Open for Instagram URL on Twitter timeline.<br>- Tweet for the search results on YouTube.<br>- Tweet for the posts of Tumblr.<p>--------------------<br>FAQs<br>--------------------<p>Q. Why did adopt the plugin system ?<p>We want to support the new social network by adding plugin. Work adding the plugin is easy more than building the new app.<p>--------------------<br>Twitter<br>--------------------<p>@kitasoft_com', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kitasoft.soline', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/hw4gD6A-X55QbpVta4C0KvzosNbKYDG_sJlVJ4IU5DLshGDV59UXF4fMAchyLWk5ka8', 4.67, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '1,000+', ''),
(299, 'com.appmk.magazine.AOUEJCITXVQCRQME', 'Tumblr Nail Design', 'ArtDesign9', 'Get Free Tumblr Nail Design', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.appmk.magazine.AOUEJCITXVQCRQME', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/WY6pQhZzzwwYOSVkI_d-F39BqVEA2N4AHvn9hXXI9u0xP-iDQoJv6_3dNc8-rBOy447Y', 3.08, 'LIFESTYLE', 'Free', '1,000+', 'android.permission.CHANGE_CONFIGURATION, READ_PHONE_STATE, com.android.browser.permission.READ_HISTORY_BOOKMARKS, com.android.browser.permission.WRITE_HISTORY_BOOKMARKS, android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW');
