(300, 'com.popular.funny.picture.tumblr', 'Popular Funny Picture Tumblr', 'More Share Corp', 'POPULAR FUNNY PICTURE TUMBLR is a app with tons collection of memes,funny gifs,relatable and super hilarious post. Only The Funniest are featured in this apps. Hundreds of funny images. Get the newest and freshest funny pictures on market for free. Most hilarious funny pictures of animals, children, funny girls and boys, very funny faces, human caricatures, humorous comics, pictures of cats, dogs and birds, cool pictures and crazy pictures of funny situations, funny people, jokes photo and other fun stuff. Contains photo categories Reddit, absolutely awesome cute pictures, Fails, digg, Epic Fail Pics, Cute Pics, Funny Memes, cool pictures, cute dogs and cats, funny pets, rage comics, or anything other type of funny pictures, we think you will LOVE LOL Pics! Get it now while it&#39;s free, and UPDATED real time!<p>? FEATURES:<br>* Clear style and simple<br>* View image offline (after sync)<br>* Custom notification<br>* Automatic notification<br>* Custom Share content<br>* Easy bookmark/favorite/stars content for later reading<br>* Fast Data Transfers For low-bandwidth<br>* Auto/Manual sync<br>* Custom interval update sync<br>* Optional light or Dark theme<br>* And Many More features<p>? Popular RSS Tumblr Available (credited to owner)<br>* Advice-animal<br>* Epic-Fun<br>* FunnyFix<br>* FunSubstance<br>* ItsDamnFunny<br>* Laugh-Addict<br>* LaughingStation<br>* LOLFactory<br>* OMG-Humor<br>* RageComics4You<br>* WhatShouldWeCallMe<br>* (Contact me please if you want adding RSS to this app)<p>Official developer project: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.ms-room.com&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEI8BMzdoarm02R2Su-0LopTAgpAQ" target="_blank">http://www.ms-room.com</a><br>Twitter: @moreshare<p>??????????<br>GOOD RATE, GOOD COMMENT<br>WILL BE IMPROVE THIS PROJECT :)<br>??????????<p>??????????<br>? DISCLAIMER!<br>??????????<br>All the pictures, images, animate and videos contained on our apps were collected from Tumblrs RSS. All media featured in this apps belong to their respective owners. We don’t claim ownership to any of these photos.<br>??????????', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.popular.funny.picture.tumblr', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/RdwW_AJU7c1jOF-j7KEkW73-97L_5B9WSpsK6kfaRhKR7CPJOdRSgZ-i0iROHPPfigw', 4.25, 'COMICS', 'Free', '1,000+', 'android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, android.permission.FLASHLIGHT'),
(301, 'com.kullect.fixie', 'Fixie GIF Camera', 'Kullect Inc.', 'Create and share short animated GIFs in an instant.  <p>It&#39;s simple - capture a short GIF using our built in camera. Add cool fonts, doodles, and borders.  Share them easily to Facebook, Twitter, Google Plus, and Tumblr. <p>Features<p>? Create animated GIFs that you can share to anywhere from your camera.<br>? Each GIF is about 1.5 seconds.  Just enough time to capture the moment perfectly.<br>? Add funky borders, funny doodles, and styled text to make the GIFs pop!<br>? Instantly share with Facebook, Twitter, Google Plus, and Tumblr.  <br>? Send messages with GIFs to LINE, KakaoTalk, WhatsApp, WeChat, or KIK.  <p>Join our community!<p>? Add the tag #FixieGIF when you post to your favorite social networks to be featured in the app.<br>? Get inspired with our &quot;best of&quot; gallery by following our blog on Tumblr - <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://fixiegif.tumblr.com&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNG_Gixr8S9HTBFW7sPHza_60dpzZA" target="_blank">http://fixiegif.tumblr.com</a>.<br>? Follow us on Twitter (@FixieGIF) to see awesome GIFs created by users like you.<br>? Share your GIFs to Google Plus and we will share it on Fixie GIF page.<p>What our users are saying!<p>? &quot;Addicted already it&#39;s fast, simple and really fun, 10 stars.&quot;<br>? &quot;Easy to use, fun, and perfect!&quot;<br>? &quot;This is the most fantastic app I&#39;ve ever used!&quot;<p>What can Fixie GIF Camera be used for?<p>- To text the perfect reaction GIF!<br>- To make fun memes like &quot;Deal With It&quot;.<br>- To record your cat (or dog) doing funny things.<br>- For anything with motion - jumping, walking, running.<p>With Fixie GIF you can make your photos move.  This free photo app lets you have fun by creating short GIFs and decorating them with cute and creative designs.  You&#39;ll never want to go back to taking a still photo again.<p>Thank you for using FixieGIF!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kullect.fixie', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/u6_KYjJLb-dxqgy_0wcln_rL34SUeHPSkjfOj7mmbFk80kjvvvqOTsS8va7Rd4p3', 4.42, 'PHOTOGRAPHY', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.CAMERA, com.android.vending.BILLING, com.kullect.fixie.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.BROADCAST_STICKY'),
(302, 'com.pixcellant.Momentum', 'Momentum - Tumblr Photo Viewer', 'Pixcellant', 'Momentum is a photo browser for tumblr (www.tumblr.com).<p>It support full screen browsing of photo blogs from tumblr. It comes pre-configured with a set of blogs for starting up but these can be changed by the user. The user also has an option to set the current picture as a wallpaper.<p>More features coming soon:<p>GIF support<br>Lock code to protect innocent eyes<p>Please mail feature requests to <a href="mailto:support@pixcellant.com">support@pixcellant.com</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.pixcellant.Momentum', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/WxlexQtPNi3rKVsF8Xt5aAimrjFzJ0ayOjmhvf55jC6aArWVvhIgm8Jpe-xkuQXXVg', 2.25, 'MEDIA_AND_VIDEO', 'Free', '1,000+', 'android.permission.SET_WALLPAPER'),
(303, 'tumblr.easy.reader', 'Tumblr Easy Reader', 'Jojo Mobo', 'Tumblr is a blogging platform that allows users to post text, images, videos, links, quotes and audio to their tumblelog, and there are hundreds of thousands of blogs.  So how to find the right one?  This handy app collects some of the most popular topics, such as Love, One-Direction, Exo, Funny, and Quotes into one handy and easy way to read.  Note this app is not optimized for Android.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=tumblr.easy.reader', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/07ZFxpbnCaJv1z3Ob07mcMOTUEHYubc0oLoKbHa0S8yzZ9tiLSjWBUADQ8FnzRmFOBY', 2.67, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '1,000+', 'tumblr.easy.reader.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, com.android.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS'),
(304, 'com.kitasoft.soline.tumblr', 'Social Line for Tumblr/Tumbler', 'Kitasoft Co., Ltd.', 'Tumblr client for Android. If you using Tumblr, please try !<br>- Support for multiple accounts. / Switch by one-tap.<br>- Large pictures and fast scrolling for posts.<br>- Play animated GIFs on posts.<br>- Vertical and horizontal scroll for posts.<br>--- (Choose by tap-hold of side menu item or title bar)<br>- Categorize and management the users and posts by side menu.<br>- Bookmark the current posts by tap-hold on the title bar.<p>--------------------<br>Launch app<br>--------------------<p><font color="#009900">This app is plugin, therefore does not work alone. Please install together main app and launch it.</font><p>- <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kitasoft.soline">Social Line</a> (Main app)<p>--------------------<br>Get started<br>--------------------<p>Please follow the guide of app.<p>Will be roughly following.<br>- Enter the username of Tumblr.<br>- Login to Tumblr and allow this app.<br>- Tap the added items to the side menu.<p>*** When multiple accounts ***<br>This app to authenticate on external web browser. It keeping the login state also after authentication. Please working for next account after logout from prev account. You can move to page where can logout from link of &quot;What is this page?&quot; at bottom on authentication page.<p>--------------------<br>Limit of features<br>--------------------<p>This app has specialized in viewing. Can not use all features of Tumblr.<p>- Can not new post. (Can reblog and like)<br>- When the post of video and audio, will display only the link.<br>- Not support display of notes.<br>- Can not setting for account.<br>- Can not adding and editing for blog.<br>- Image of animated GIF is low quality.<br>- Playback of big-size animated GIF will end halfway.<p>If you want to use the full feature, We recommend using the official app or official site.<p>--------------------<br>Authentication<br>--------------------<p>Do user authentication on the official webpage of Tumblr. This app does not handle your password.<p>--------------------<br>Attribution<br>--------------------<p>Powered by Tumblr<p>This application uses the Tumblr application programming interface but is not endorsed or certified by Tumblr, Inc.<br>All of the Tumblr logos and trademarks displayed on this application are the property of Tumblr, Inc.<p>--------------------<br>Twitter<br>--------------------<p>@kitasoft_com', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kitasoft.soline.tumblr', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/iUaRukedHKxluR19FZnLsxYh1-PQwqvKAWI9m8bffUNZ5dnVAZaaydFENl_Z9NQW1vE', 3.00, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '500+', ''),
(305, 'com.biu.pic_tumblr', 'Colorful Tumblr', 'Liang Zhang', 'Tumblr client. <p>Only focus on photo posts. <p>Read it later supported.<p>Provides two browsing mode, grid or list view.<p>Easy to like/unlike or search posts by tags.<p>Full screen slide also provided.<p>Multi accounts supported.<p>Restrictions:<br>Ads banner included.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.biu.pic_tumblr', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/0j765yf64MLf618x9jtlES6s4DbomO2XE62kmIs8f6jSGwtjhUDlR_vNd9iT9qRH6mw', 1.56, 'TOOLS', 'Free', '1,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION'),
(306, 'com.fmroid.tmbreader', 'TmbReader for Tumblr', 'fmroid', 'It is an application to view the dashboard of Tumblr.<br>You can move the page by swipe or buttons.<br>It is the interface that is easy to operate with one hand.<p>Function<br>- Move the page by swipe or buttons.<br>- Reblog and Like.<br>- Pin Function.<br>- Page zoom.<br>- Advanced post option.(Add to queue, etc.)<br>- Save Photo.<br>- The maximum of reading is 260 posts.<br>- Play GIF Animation<br>- Support Photoset.<p><font color="red">* Please correct the date and time of your Android correctly to login.</font>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fmroid.tmbreader', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/P2WTRVXFuzK_nA9e6EaKD7ouE4N1zy_sJeb8hUBwM3iV8MorukGmaUaBOJLeJBg2OYDX', 4.09, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '1,000+', ''),
(307, 'com.jkrolling.trlbum', 'Tumblr Viewer: tRlbum', 'YoungJ', '????????????????????????????????????<br>Thanksgiving Sale!!<br>Extra 50% off!! Now it&#39;s only $0.99 to get tRlbum!<br>????????????????????????????????????<p>Fantastic, Easiest, Simplest app to view your &quot;tumblr&quot; dashboard in &quot;FULLSCREEN&quot; mode, is now on sale for $1.99, 60% off its regular price of $4.99.<p>View your &quot;tumblr&quot; Dashboard photo in &quot;FULLSCREEN&quot; mode.<br>* Share your favorite picture<br>* Support GIF animation picture<br>* Reblog to &quot;tumblr&quot; dashboard<br>* NFC share/follow through AndroidBeam(from ICS+ with NFC)<br>* Simply to use<br>* Full screen photo<br>* Save &quot;tumblr&quot; photo to SD card<br>* Like/Unlike &quot;tumblr&quot; post<br>* Switch to Liked list<br>* Support landscape<br>* tRlbum is powered by the &quot;tumblr&quot; API.<p>Try our LITE version of tRlbum for FREE!<br>http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jkrolling.trlbumlite', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jkrolling.trlbum', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/84q9HTz6-H1CY0JIWbPv-QdwPgF0AllxpgoEP9LekGtS3TLpHX8IEQ64P5nV-NKzg5U', 4.00, 'SOCIAL', '$0.99', '100+', 'android.permission.NFC'),
(308, 'com.hostj2me.stumblr.prime', 'Stumbler Prime', 'Brilliance Mobility', 'Browse and discover great images using this stunning Tumblr photo viewer. You can bookmark your favorite blog discoveries and download or share individual photos.<p>? No Ads<br>? Reblog pictures<br>? Like pictures<br>? Save pictures<br>? Bookmark blogs<br>? Backup your browsing history and bookmarks<br>? Post images to Tumblr<br>? GIF support<br>? Fullscreen, pinch zoom, and actual size image modes<br>? View Tumblr dashboard<br>? Live wallpaper (Beta, not ready for tablets)<p>*Stumbler is powered by the Tumblr API.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.hostj2me.stumblr.prime', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/z7-Ha0amIUfsykL8XGr-stUnWIyUmZLJeS4uyRT1pfXgZz611qYY6kgcYbMCCXmtoAE', 4.24, 'SOCIAL', '$2.99', '1,000+', ''),
