(312, 'jp.android.yas_mnkornym.SmartWatchK9MailNotifier', 'K9Mail Notifier for SmartWatch', 'YMSoft', 'This app notifies the Mail Receiving to K-9 Mail to SmartWatch MN2(SonyEricsson).<p>*Please try below, lite-version of this app first.<br> And make sure that it fully works in your device.<br>https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.android.yas_mnkornym.SmartWatchK9NotifierLite<p><br>*This app shows you these informations on SmartWatch.<br>1. Subject<br>2. Sender(Name if registered. or else, Mail Address)<br>3. Mail body(preview)<p>This app has these functions.<br>- Account Filtering(k-9 mail account)<p>*Screenshot is taken on the device which is set language Japanese but this app has English assets.<p>*Only mails which are in &quot;Unified Inbox(Integrated Inbox)&quot; to be shown.<br> If your e-mail receiving is not notified, go your account&#39;s Inbox and Open &quot;Folder settings&quot;, then check &quot;unify&quot;.<p>*When I tested, this app could display about 500 characters(in EM-size) of mail body text.<br>*This app doesn&#39;t need Internet, WriteExternalStorage Permissions.<p>*I tested this application in below environment.<br>1.K-9 Mail: ver 4.009<br>2.Android Device: NEC CASIO Mobile N-04D(docomo MEDIUS LTE)<p><br>LiveWare™ extension for SmartWatch<br>LiveWare™ extension for Smart Wireless Headset pro', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.android.yas_mnkornym.SmartWatchK9MailNotifier', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/ueRFcAh9nuUUMMpPwl2diGhGn3_Aw3CBbaWFmfMQst8vWpkZpCGng9N_1ejC5LdGUunj', 2.93, 'PRODUCTIVITY', '$2.50', '500+', 'com.fsck.k9.permission.READ_MESSAGES, com.sonyericsson.extras.liveware.aef.EXTENSION_PERMISSION'),
