ll for your comments, feedback, suggestions and constructive criticism that have greatly helped shape and polish this game over time. Thank you to all the reviewers that have posted spontaneous reviews on various websites.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kb.Carrom3DFull', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/guSxH8_CsJ5F0Qj6Tqk5p1qKeHQmzRCTHWwpLlHDBWAG9f1vXthk-jvaRtGIV1K7pC0', 4.55, 'SPORTS_GAMES', '$1.99', '100,000+', 'android.permission.INTERNET, android.permission.WAKE_LOCK, android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE'),
(352, 'com.backflipstudios.android.ninjumpdeluxe', 'NinJump Deluxe', 'Backflip Studios, Inc.', 'Get the all-new Deluxe version of the wildly popular NinJump ninja game. Download NinJump Deluxe today - it&#39;s free! <p>????? PRESS REVIEWS ?????<p>&quot;It&#39;s a fast-paced game with great graphics and that all-important &#39;just one more time&#39; factor.&quot; ~ 148Apps.com<p>&quot;This is a retro treat that once started will prove pretty tricky to put down.&quot; ~ Pocket Arcade<p>&quot;It is a casual, quick, pick-up-and-play title.&quot; AppModo.com<p>????? DESCRIPTION ?????<p>The classic NinJump game has been downloaded over 50 million times by fans around the world. NinJump Deluxe includes the same addictive ninja climbing fun in entirely new, heart-pounding settings. Jump your way past sea monsters, witch doctors, tropical snakes, monkeys, fire-breathing dragons and enemy ninjas. Collect shields and amazing new power-ups along the way. Your ninja&#39;s goal is to jump its way to the top of your screen while avoiding increasingly treacherous obstacles and enemies. How far can your ninja get? <p>NinJump Deluxe comes fully-loaded with:<p>? New Pirate, Jungle &amp; Castle levels<br>? Simple, fun single-tap gameplay<br>? Sea Monsters, Ogres, Dragons &amp; more<br>? Awesome power-ups &amp; shields<br>? Leader boards &amp; score sharing<br>? Amazing graphics &amp; characters<p>Install NinJump Deluxe today<p><br>_____________________________________<p>NinJump Deluxe is brought to you by Backflip Studios, makers of absurdly fun mobile games like Paper Toss, DragonVale, Strike Knight, Shape Shift, Army of Darkness Defense, Ragdoll Blaster and Graffiti Ball. Search the Android Google Play store and Apple App Store for &quot;Backflip Studios&quot; to see all our apps.<p>Follow @BackflipStudios on Twitter for free game announcements and other updates. <p>Thanks for playing!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.backflipstudios.android.ninjumpdeluxe', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/WON4vhfB9On8KaiqTtAOU6vNKpl_CTRgrAbeKDHutz1DR2CpTgG3zOYpxgq0IJvRQQ', 4.56, 'ARCADE', 'Free', '5,000,000+', 'com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.INTERNET, android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE, android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE, android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE'),
(353, 'com.backflipstudios.android.dragonvale', 'DragonVale', 'Backflip Studios, Inc.', '&quot;Best New Online Game&quot; ~ GDC Awards Nominee<p>&quot;Just between you and me, dragon parks are pretty rad.&quot; ~ TouchArcade.com <p>Hatched a dragon lately? Play DragonVale and raise, feed and breed your own lovable dragons. <p>PLEASE NOTE! DragonVale is completely free to play, but some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you don&#39;t want to use this feature, please disable in-app purchases. DragonVale requires an internet connection to play (3G or WiFi). <p>ALSO NOTE! By playing DragonVale you may find yourself hopelessly addicted to hatching and caring for adorable dragons. You may find yourself feeding them treats, watching them grow, building and decorating their habitats, and inviting others in to view them in their floating island home. You may even find yourself choosing pairs for breeding, or racing dragons to compete for awesome prizes. <p>DragonVale is an enticing social experience from Backflip Studios that is sure to keep you entertained. You get: <p>? Dozens of adorable dragons to raise <br>? A magical island you build in the sky <br>? Custom habitats where dragons graze <br>? Dragon races where you win great prizes <br>? Paths and decorations to delight your visitors <br>? Farms to grow dragon treats <br>? Full-color visuals and sparkling animations <br>? An original Renaissance music soundtrack <br>? Support for Facebook to visit other parks and trade gifts <p>Don&#39;t just take our word for it. Here&#39;s what the press has to say about DragonVale: <p>&quot;This new title has a depth and higher quality of art that’s reminiscent of the work that went into early console games.&quot; ~ VentureBeat.com <p>&quot;Jurassic Park was cool, but really it doesn&#39;t have anything on DragonVale.&quot; ~ Gamezebo.com <p>&quot;It builds up nicely, the art is colorful and fun.&quot; ~ TUAW.com <p>And to think it all started with an egg. <p>? Inst