(354, 'com.juicemaster.diet2', 'Juice Master 7lbs in 7 Days', 'Juice Master', '** PLEASE NOTE - We are getting reports of problems on Samsung devices. We are investigating and hope to have a fix soon **<p>Now on Android - The Best-Selling Juice Programme in the World - Jason Vale&#39;s (aka The Juice Master) 7lbs in 7days Super Juice Diet. <p>We are aware that a number of people have been having problems with the stability of the app and also the in-app purchase of the 14 day plan. We apologise for these problems and are working on a fix ASAP.<p>&quot;The No. 1 Celebrity Juice Diet&quot; - completed by celebs such as Katie Price (Jordan) and Beverly Knight and reported fans Sarah Jessica Parker, Drew Barrymore and Jennifer Anniston. <p>Featuring: <p>* All the recipes from the programme <br>* The Shopping List <br>* &quot;Why Juice&quot; video <br>* &quot;The Mental Juice&quot; video <br>* Motivational audio clips to support you <br>* Video Testimonials <br>* Photos of what the juices/smoothies should look like <p>What is the 7lbs in 7 days programme? <p>Lose up to 7lbs in 7 days with Jason Vale&#39;s ultra-fast 1-week super juice cleanse. The man who helped Jordan to get her post-baby body back has designed a healthy and effective diet and exercise programme to reshape your body in just one week, but with lasting results, and all from the UK&#39;s leading health coach and seminar leader Jason Vale. <p>Jason has designed a highly motivational and hard-hitting programme for effective speedy weight loss. The &quot;7lbs in 7 days Super Juice Diet&quot; can help you get in shape super-fast to give you a beach-perfect body or help you look sensational in that little black dress. With his simple diet and exercise programme and inspirational message, you will not only lose weight, but also have higher energy levels, clearer skin and be set free from the dieting trap forever.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.juicemaster.diet2', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/5cs1X