(362, 'com.hzwp.bridge', 'Wood Bridges', 'jackycrown', 'Build a bridge to let the train safely cross the valley.<br>This is a HD wallpaper of the beautiful  Bridge  City with rippling reflecting water and shining lights. <br>Bridge Night HD Wallpaper Free fully supports portrait and landscape display depends on your devices.<p>Tags:Light,Photography,Timelapse,Bridge,Wallpaper,Live Wallpaper,City Night,physics, bridge, construction, puzzle, game, simulation, crossing, building', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.hzwp.bridge', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/Z33CAkz8h7vPea0WI_1X8ehIJTC7dMpk3CnH1lnxhnvTgIsqZndZb2Dl-VkaBJYr4g', 3.02, 'BRAIN', 'Free', '50,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.INTERNET, android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, android.permission.SET_WALLPAPER, android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE'),
