(376, 'com.dolphin.battery.saver', 'Dolphin Battery Saver', 'Dolphin Add-ons', '????? “Not only saves battery, but also makes the browsing faster and protects browsing security!&quot;<p>Optimize your Dolphin Browser by easily saving battery, browsing faster all while protect browsing security. <p>Key Features:<br>-  Battery saver: Save power and extend your smartphone’s battery life with “ONE CLICK OPTIMIZE”<br>-  Browse faster: Improve your browsing speed by ending unnecessary background apps.<br>-  Security manager: Protect your browsing security, by getting a warning when on a website with untrusted WOT ratings. Also shows you the security info (WOT ratings) of each page.<p> <br>Dolphin Battery Saver is an exclusive Add-on for Dolphin Browser?Formerly Dolphin Browser HD?. Just search “Dolphin Browser ” in Android Market or download here: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://bit.ly/D-Android&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGBWH-xDzc7tiBNJuDsBRK2bFvNRw" target="_blank">http://bit.ly/D-Android</a><p>What is an Add-on?<br>Beef up your Dolphin Browser?Formerly Dolphin Browser HD? by installing your favorite Add-ons. Similar to a desktop Plug-in, each Add-on will provides additional functionality on mobile device. Forgot password? Password Manager can help. Want a new look for your Dolphin? Download Shiny Shake to change colors. Want to read a webpage in French? Get Dolphin Translate. Click here to learn more: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://bit.ly/AndroidAdd-onList&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHgq5tOdbxfSRMFsew_Szmb0nmEEQ" target="_blank">http://bit.ly/AndroidAdd-onList</a><p>The fine print: Dolphin Battery Saver is only compatible with Dolphin Browser HD v7.2 and higher.<p>Other popular Dolphin Add-ons:<br>• Bookmark to SD<br>• Dolphin YouTube Search<br>• Web to PDF<br>• Dolphin Google Services<br>• Google Reader Notifier<br>Join the Dolphin community!<br>Facebook: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.facebook.com/DolphinFans&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNE4Fzogban6uL_jJ0XrYVakeRJMWQ" target="_blank">http://www.facebook.com/DolphinFans</a> <br>Twitter: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://twitter.com/DolphinBrowser&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFm6z7DU7Ua5TZdidxxcnA7mkpJtw" target="_blank">https://twitter.com/DolphinBrowser</a><br>Any further suggestions, please contact at <a href="mailto:support@dolphin-browser.com">support@dolphin-browser.com</a>.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dolphin.battery.saver', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/yCkFwu6IIhJAdSnndhZZTSIPoSYo7RfHOcpV_CtbrZYMrSRYyjAc2oxzeDvExzV971o', 4.66, 'LIFESTYLE', 'Free', '500,000+', 'android.permission.KILL_BACKGROUND_PROCESSES, android.permission.WRITE_SYNC_SETTINGS, android.permission.BLUETOOTH_ADMIN, android.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, android.permission.CHANGE_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.WRITE_SECURE_SETTINGS, android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE, android.permission.BLUETOOTH, android.permission.READ_SYNC_SETTINGS, android.permission.DEVICE_POWER, android.permission.WRITE_APN_SETTINGS, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, android.permission.RESTART_PACKAGES, android.permission.GET_TASKS, android.permission.UPDATE_DEVICE_STATS, com.dolphin.browser.permission.MANAGE_TABS, com.dolphin.browser.permission.TITLE_BAR_ACTION, com.dolphin.browser.permission.ADDON_BAR_BADGE, com.dolphin.browser.permission.ACCESS_WEB_PAGES'),
(377, 'mobi.megeek.DesktopToggles', 'Dolphin Desktop Toggle', 'Dolphin Add-ons', '????? “I used to hate it when a site would force me to use their mobile version site. Now the choice is mine! Thx dev!”<p>Switch quickly between two browsing views: Mobile view and Desktop view. With Dolphin Desktop Toggles, you can:<br>- Load web pages as either traditional Android mode (mobile view) or Desktop mode (Desktop view)<br>- Have more flexibility in accessing the an easy to view mobile webpage or webpage’s full content and flash<p>Dolphin Desktop Toggles is an exclusive Add-on for Dolphin Browser?Formerly Dolphin Browser HD?. Just search “Dolphin Browser ” in Android Market or download here: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://bit.ly/D-Android&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGBWH-xDzc7tiBNJuDsBRK2bFvNRw" target="_blank">http://bit.ly/D-Android</a><p>What is an Add-on?<br>Beef up your Dolphin Browser?Formerly Dolphin Browser HD? by installing your favorite Add-ons. Similar to a desktop Plug-in, each Add-on will provides additional functionality on mobile device. Forgot password? Password Manager can help. Want a new look for your Dolphin? Download Shiny Shake to change colors. Want to read a webpage in French? Get Dolphin Translate. Click here to learn more: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://bit.ly/AndroidAdd-onList&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHgq5tOdbxfSRMFsew_Szmb0nmEEQ" target="_blank">http://bit.ly/AndroidAdd-onList</a><p>Other popular Dolphin Add-ons:<br>• Bookmark to SD<br>• PDF Viewer for Dolphin<br>• Web to PDF<br>• Dolphin Google Services<br>• Dolphin Screen Cut<p><br>Join the Dolphin community!<br>Facebook: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.facebook.com/DolphinFans&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNE4Fzogban6uL_jJ0XrYVakeRJMWQ" target="_blank">http://www.facebook.com/DolphinFans</a> <br>Twitter: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://twitter.com/DolphinBrowser&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFm6z7DU7Ua5TZdidxxcnA7mkpJtw" target="_blank">https://twitter.com/DolphinBrowser</a><br>Any further suggestions, please contact at <a href="mailto:support@dolphin-browser.com">support@dolphin-browser.com</a>.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=mobi.megeek.DesktopToggles', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/QaoSmnpU0Hai-5bMa0x60TR-tzqtmWA13qSuwOx-SbrneCIdVZ4QU5r5heGe-vEBd8A', 4.51, 'COMMUNICATION', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'tunnybrowser.permission.Extension'),
(378, 'mobi.mgeek.browserfaster', 'Browse Faster for Dolphin', 'Dolphin Add-ons', '????? “Works great. I can definitely browse faster on Dolphin than using stock browser. I have found my new Internet browser. A+ Milestone”<p>Speed up your browsing experience by killing all other working applications on your phone with just one click. With Browse Faster for Dolphin, you can save battery life and enable faster browsing.<p>Dolphin Browse Faster is an exclusive Add-on for Dolphin Browser?Formerly Dolphin Browser HD?. Just search “Dolphin Browser ” in Android Market or download here: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://bit.ly/D-Android&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGBWH-xDzc7tiBNJuDsBRK2bFvNRw" target="_blank">http://bit.ly/D-Android</a><p>What is an Add-on?<br>Beef up your Dolphin Browser?Formerly Dolphin Browser HD? by installing your favorite Add-ons. Similar to a desktop Plug-in, each Add-on will provides additional functionality on mobile device. Forgot password? Password Manager can help. Want a new look for your Dolphin? Download Shiny Shake to change colors. Want to read a webpage in French? Get Dolphin Translate. Click here to learn more: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://bit.ly/AndroidAdd-onList&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHgq5tOdbxfSRMFsew_Szmb0nmEEQ" target="_blank">http://bit.ly/AndroidAdd-onList</a><br>Other popular Dolphin Add-ons:<br>• Bookmark to SD<br>• Dolphin YouTube Search<br>• Web to PDF<br>• Dolphin Google Services<br>• Dolphin Screen Cut<p>Join the Dolphin community!<br>Facebook: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.facebook.com/DolphinFans&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNE4Fzogban6uL_jJ0XrYVakeRJMWQ" target="_blank">http://www.facebook.com/DolphinFans</a> <br>Twitter: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://twitter.com/DolphinBrowser&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFm6z7DU7Ua5TZdidxxcnA7mkpJtw" target="_blank">https://twitter.com/DolphinBrowser</a><br>Any further suggestions, please contact at <a href="mailto:support@dolphin-browser.com">support@dolphin-browser.com</a>.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=mobi.mgeek.browserfaster', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/0GB3W9AAHlBvGxmlsVxmGqgRAz14T7mNMTCNstYCY2pAdxNM8vOXGVfT536aiLh87T8', 4.46, 'COMMUNICATION', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'com.dolphin.browser.permission.Addon, android.permission.RESTART_PACKAGES'),
(379, 'mobi.mgeek.YoutubeSearch', 'Dolphin Youtube Search', 'Dolphin Add-ons', '**Dolphin Browser Add-on**<p>Search YouTube video without visiting youtube.com, saving you time and the hassle of traffic.<p>V1.1<br>*&quot;App to SD&quot;<br>*Fix bugs', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=mobi.mgeek.YoutubeSearch', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/ah8UWP-EWHLXXVm6RX_ZuqDeYBF-K8ojsD3eAq98-P8b9SmfvHMEJSqzWgYSBFGgQ08', 4.19, 'COMMUNICATION', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'com.dolphin.browser.permission.MANAGE_TABS'),
(380, 'mobi.mgeek.DolphinTranslate', 'Dolphin Translate', 'Dolphin Add-ons', '????? “THIS...is why Dolphin is the best Android Browser EVA!! :-) Works Perfectly with any website.”<p>Translate a webpage or even desired sentence into any language. With Dolphin Translate, you can:<br>-	Translate website/webpage<br>-	Translate desired sentence or section of a webpage<br>-	Translate without leaving Dolphin Browser <p>Languages supported:<br>Afrikaans, Albanian, Arabic, Armenian, Azerbaijani, Basque, Belarusian, Bengali, Bulgarian, Catalan, Chinese (Simplified), Chinese (Traditional), Croatian, Czech, Danish, Dutch, English, Estonian, Filipino, Finnish, French, Galician, Georgian, German, Greek, Gujarati, Haitian Creole, Hebrew, Hindi, Hungarian, Icelandic, Indonesian, Irish, Italian, Japanese, Kannada, Korean, Latin, Latvian, Lithuanian, Macedonian, Malay, Maltese, Norwegian, Persian, Polish, Portuguese, Romanian, Russian, Serbian, Slovak, Slovenian, Spanish, Swahili, Swedish, Tamil, Telugu, Thai, Turkish, Ukrainian, Urdu, Vietnamese, Welsh, Yiddish<p>Note: Dolphin Translate uses Google’s translation service to translate in up to 58 languages<br>Dolphin Translate is an exclusive Add-on for Dolphin Browser ?Formerly Dolphin Browser HD?. Just search “Dolphin Browser” in Android Market or download here: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://bit.ly/D-Android&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGBWH-xDzc7tiBNJuDsBRK2bFvNRw" target="_blank">http://bit.ly/D-Android</a><p>What is an Add-on?<br>Beef up your Dolphin Browser?Formerly Dolphin Browser HD? by installing your favorite Add-ons. Similar to a desktop Plug-in, each Add-on will provides additional functionality on mobile device. Forgot password? Password Manager can help. Want a new look for your Dolphin? Download Shiny Shake to change colors. Want to read a webpage in French? Get Dolphin Translate. Click here to learn more: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://bit.ly/AndroidAdd-onList&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHgq5tOdbxfSRM