(433, 'com.jiubang.goscreenlock.theme.right', 'GO Locker Simple RightTheme', 'GO Launcher EX', 'GO Locker Simple Right Theme, design to GO Launcher EX, is available now!<br>Notice:V1.02 Support alarm clock information. Update at once!<p><br>====&gt;Tips:<br>1. Make sure GO Launcher EX V2.58 or above and GO Locker v1.0 have been installed;<br>2. Click “MENU—-&gt;Preferences—-&gt;Theme Settings—-&gt;GO Locker----&gt;My locker” to choose the theme;<p>Please let me know if you meet any bugs or want any improvement!<br>E-mail: <a href="mailto:golauncher@goforandroid.com">golauncher@goforandroid.com</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jiubang.goscreenlock.theme.right', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/gTnnHbQit3ol5ZXlgOx6rcfM9biuoCJqKiIEX7Zl7AOxiIQqWTWRC4YBUkNDSaKVCw', 4.50, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '1,000,000+', ''),
