(470, 'air.nurdturd.games.ninjablitzfree', 'Ninja Blitz LITE', 'Nurd Turd Productions', 'Suggestions are welcome!!<p>A platformer-esque game where you play a ninja on the run! Avoid falling for as long as possible, but be warned your ninja continues to run faster and faster! Ninja Pandas will try to stop you. Cranes will try to stop you. But push through and make your way onto the leaderboard! <p>This free version only allows 60 seconds of gameplay at a time and does not allow the posting of scores. For full gameplay, high scores posting, and updates purchase the full game!<p>This game requires Adobe AIR', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.nurdturd.games.ninjablitzfree', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/AoJ3knvk9Qfh8yL_MxwSNlYHBcBUoM9I14q5zWYGIMHK9_qqTMHycb0foSemWJJI_24', 3.60, 'CASUAL', 'Free', '1,000+', 'android.permission.INTERNET'),
(471, 'com.starbucks.mobilecard', 'Starbucks', 'Starbucks Coffee Company', 'A Starbucks Card is the fastest, most convenient way to pay at Starbucks. And Starbucks for Android™ is the perfect companion to your card. Your Android™ phone will display a barcode that you use just like your card to make purchases at Starbucks. <p>With Starbucks for Android, you can check your balance, reload your card with any major credit card, view your transactions and conveniently track your Stars in the My Starbucks Rewards program.<p>Features<br>• Use a widget to pay, check balance, track your My Starbucks Rewards Stars, or find a location <br>• Check your Starbucks Card balance<br>• Reload your Starbucks Card with a major credit card or PayPal<br>• Transfer balances between Cards<br>• View your transaction history<br>• Pay with your Android™ phone at participating stores<br>• Locate a Starbucks near you<br>• Track your Stars in the My Starbucks Rewards program<p><br>Known Technical Limitations<br>• This application supports US, UK, &amp; Canada Starbucks Cards only, including Gold cards<br>• Starbucks Store Credit Cards or Duetto Cards are not supported<br>• Starbucks for Android  supports your personal Starbucks Cards. Cards may only be loaded onto one device at a time. If you wish to reload a friend or family members’ Starbucks Card, please visit Starbucks.com/card.<p><p>For more information, please visit <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.starbucks.com/coffeehouse/mobile-apps/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEjZ9hEXt1DI_iYtoNCSGB3h4k9oQ" target="_blank">http://www.starbucks.com/coffeehouse/mobile-apps/</a><br>If you are experiencing login or other technical issues, please email Info@Starbucks.com', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.starbucks.mobilecard', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/iABZrZd8HdfvP-U-v0Rk0F_sJVSiIM9nrlctGrwSCyhYMfgqPxEwEycC9I4g_9zCNig', 3.62, 'LIFESTYLE', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'android.permission.CALL_PHONE, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.BIND_ACCESSIBILITY_SERVICE'),
(472, 'com.starbucks.hk', 'Starbucks Hong Kong', 'Starbucks Coffee Company', 'The official Android application from Starbucks! In addition to paying from Starbucks Card in app and earn Stars in My Starbucks Rewards™ Program, you can also send your loved ones a Starbucks eGift.<p>With Starbucks Hong Kong Android app, you can make scan-and-go Starbucks Card payment, view your Starbucks Card balance, reload your card, transfer balance within your account, view transaction history. <p>and there&#39;s more! Send a Starbucks Card eGift - the fastest, easiest way to gift a friend or treat someone. and the new Messages function also connected you more closely to Starbucks with speical offers and intimate services.<p>Remarks: This app is only for use within Hong Kong and Macau. <p><br>More exciting features coming soon. Start earning Stars today and stay tuned. <br>Remarks: This app is only for use within Hong Kong and Macau.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.starbucks.hk', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/kOA2S7Y58I26gMv3vAJW_p_OChoScOg8DvIk3ZUwfplrY98SAxgxBR0f-gLBXHaqgE-v', 3.76, 'LIFESTYLE', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.CHANGE_CONFIGURATION, android.permission.GET_TASKS, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.MOUNT_UNMOUNT_FILESYSTEMS, android.permission.CALL_PHONE, android.permission.ACCESS_GPS, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, com.google.android.providers.gsf.permission.READ_GSERVICES, com.starbucks.hk.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, android.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, android.permission.READ_CONTACTS, android.permission.READ_CALL_LOG'),
(473, 'org.crocodile.sbautologin', 'Starbucks WiFi Auto Login', 'Codeminders', 'This program helps you to use free WiFi at Starbucks cafes and McDonalds restaurants using AT&amp;T WiFi newtwork. It automates the tedious task of starting your browser and clicking on &quot;Accept Terms&quot; button each time you walk in.<p>You still need to agree with terms of use. The program just automates this step for you so you do not have to do it over and over again.<p>The program works in background completely transparently from user. No configuration is required. Once connection to Starbucks WiFi network is detected and checks if terms need to be accepted and if so accepts them for you.<p>Now you can just walk into Starbucks, open your mail client and check your email without having to start web browser first.<p>This program is open source. You are encouraged to visit:<p><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://code.google.com/p/sbautologin/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHPRaTnd7ASqY62zSw_WlETXu7ckA" target="_blank">http://code.google.com/p/sbautologin/</a><p>and contribute your bug reports, suggestions and patches to make it better.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.crocodile.sbautologin', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/BW1ss243O2fsT61PzpSeq5BEfG_JDuWAwhqUAPx3DuRaIKkn2q6QMW_-sWv0wpqoRg', 4.01, 'COMMUNICATION', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.BROADCAST_STICKY'),
(474, 'com.uludaglabs.android.projects', 'My Starbucks Calorie', 'Can ULUDA?', 'It&#39;s an application where you can easily find the calories of your favourite Starbucks drinks and foods. Just make yoor choice and see how much calorie you will get when you drink or eat it. Also it has some extra informations about these foods and drinks. This app will be good guide for you when you enter a Starbucks Coffee.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.uludaglabs.android.projects', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/xqI2v3b204REBXkhdbSvZNqVaeMaOHiTtEXRKLQzlU0G0PuQ0II3s0myDyudFIEDE68E', 3.18, 'LIFESTYLE', 'Free', '50,000+', ''),
(475, 'com.CompleteStarbucksSecretMenu', 'Complete Starbucks Secret Menu', 'Blackmon Software', 'Delicious Starbucks drinks that you never knew existed! This collection of drinks, frappuccinos, and teas have been created by Starbucks Baristas and connoisseurs from all over the world! Not all Baristas will be familiar with these drinks, so be sure to include the recipe when ordering.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.CompleteStarbucksSecretMenu', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/ETPyCSmdJCZLk6so2C-Qfj8p2Yn8FI-fUYVuh3sCbs1TNTL3ekW0R2CWtDgUEwtyng', 4.05, 'SHOPPING', 'Free', '10,000+', 'android.webkit.permission.PLUGIN, com.CompleteStarbucksSecretMenu.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE'),
(476, 'com.couponsqueen.couponclub027', 'Starbucks Coupons Savings', 'CouponParty', 'Starbucks Coupons is an amazing little app that allows you to save on Starbucks claiming Starbucks Coupons has never been easier just create your social profile and get access to amazing daily coupons from your favorite Starbucks. Starbucks Coupons has been downloaded more than 4000 times on its first day become a part of our growing frugal living community.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.couponsqueen.couponclub027', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/9Iyk3oG3ZdjHeWCyNtZOVvMTdoWnaNaPaPAcg7lwfY9h3INyqKtZb3Yo3fcqjsw936E', 4.33, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '5,000+', 'com.android.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT'),
(477, 'com.birbeck.starbuckscard', 'My Coffee Card', 'birbeck', 'No more hunting through the purse or wallet. Now you can leave the card and cash at home and pay for your purchases at Starbucks with My Coffee Card for Android.<p>My Coffee Card is an advanced Starbucks Card manager that supports all of the features of the official Starbucks Card Mobile application such as:<p>• Mobile payments at all 6800 company owned stores in the U.S. and nearly 1,000 Target and Safeway licensed stores<br>• Quickly check your card balance and track rewards program status<br>• Reload your card on the go without leaving the app<br>• Search nearby stores with filters for what&#39;s open now or where accepts mobile payments and more<p> In addition, My Coffee Card has the following exclusive features:<p>• Homescreen widget to see your balance and reward stars at a glance with one-click access to mobile payment barcode and store locator<br>• Low balance notifications alert you when your balance is low with simple one-click to reload<br>• Prevent un-authorized access to your payment barcode with security PIN lock<br>• Share the same cards and rewards account on multiple devices<br>• Order notepad assists you with making an office coffee run or ordering your clients favorite drinks<br>• Share your rewards on Twitter or Facebook<br>• Check-in to foursquare<br>• Fast, intuitive user interface<br>• Very small install size and battery saving optimizations<br>• Supports Android 1.6 and higher<br>• Completely free. No ads, no nags.<p>Register your card on Starbucks.com to save money and receive rewards each time you use your card or mobile barcode.<p>Download My Coffee Card free and discover what makes the original Starbucks mobile payment solution for Android truly the fastest and easiest way to pay and manage your card.<p>Notes:<br>• Free version supports a single card, upgrade to My Coffee Card Pro for unlimited card support<br>• Requires a Starbucks Card gift card or Starbucks Gold Card<br>• Duetto VISA and MasterCard are not compatible. This is a Starbucks restriction for your privacy and security<br>• Mobile payments are only accepted at company owned retail stores in the U.S. and Target and Safeway stores. Mobile payments are not accepted at drive-thrus<br>• Partner cards must be activated before use<br>• Reward stars are only updated by Starbucks once per day. It may take up to 24 hours for stars to appear after a drink purchase<br>• If your stars are not updating, open My Coffee Card, press Settings icon, press Starbucks account, then press Logout. Login again and stars will work as normal. This can happen when receiving a system software update to Android 2.3 Gingerbread.<p>This application does not support apps2sd due to an Android limitation. You cannot use widgets when an application is moved to sd card. The application is 10% the size of Starbucks official app and requires less than 1MB of phone storage. Even after moving official app to the sd card, it uses over 3MB of phone storage.<p>My Coffee Card is an independently developed third-party application. It is not affiliated with or endorsed by Starbucks corporation. Starbucks, Starbucks Card and the siren logo are registered trademarks of Starbucks Corporation. Please visit the website for full privacy and security policies.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.birbeck.starbuckscard', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/xhG624HCGutS6pR5KSb13wYuii3YYgNfoWdubUh0leNf2YFWL9AEJl7VVhB-1265PA', 4.55, 'LIFESTYLE', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION'),
(478, 'appinventor.ai_gianlombard.freddycoffee', 'Talking monkey at Starbucks', 'Greenway', 'Freddy the talking monkey part 5.  A very funny video episode!  Freddy tries to order a cup of coffee at Starbucks without success because he can&#39;t understand the fancy talking server talking about grand medio capa capa... Freddy also about everybody making fun of his high school picture...  A very funny FREE video  featuring the famous Freddy the talking monkey! A FREE app that is great for all ages.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=appinventor.ai_gianlombard.freddycoffee', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/PNXRgXP-jZPoYgKoRknR0RgveKkd9qJgqsjvPzMj5_0eO4bu0-lDuE_ArYahS6slGQ', 4.57, 'COMICS', 'Free', '5,000+', ''),
(479, 'com.coupon.monsters56', 'Starbucks Coupons - 50% OFF', 'Digital Coupons Central', 'Starbucks Coupons -  Get 50% from your favorite brands. Register and generate coupons for your favorite brands and stores its easy to save with Starbucks Coupons. Enjoy this unique application and save money.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.coupon.monsters56', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/VEdQBXHEArFv0EaSWBApKji1R8QIExcMeBZc5BTehofVt57KsBev9YChigJVwT-l2LU', 4.83, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '1,000+', ''),
(480, 'vtop.starbucks.storelocator', 'Starbucks Store Locator', 'Avi Cohen-Shabat', 'There&#39;s probably a Starbucks coffeehouse near you. Let&#39;s help you find it.<br>If you love Starbucks coffee then this is the Starbucks Store Locator app for you. It’s real easy to use and will help you find a Starbucks store that is close to your current location. Find and connect to over 20,000 Starbucks stores worldwide.<p>On the main screen you can filter your search based on stores with certain features such as drive-through,Wi-Fi,Starbucks Evenings,Mobile Payment,Digital Rewards and more.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=vtop.starbucks.storelocator', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/a2AKV_Cf5bZrEed3k6Zzf_Gv3Lpq-tmSy-rhws4APnN4R4R_EUUekKQ_xIKhnrZojw', 2.67, 'TRAVEL_AND_LOCAL', 'Free', '100+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_GPS, android.permission.ACCESS_ASSISTED_GPS, android.permission.ACCESS_LOCATION, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.ACCESS_LOCATION_EXTRA_COMMANDS'),
(481, 'air.com.vyperlogix.android.FreeStarbucks', 'Free Starbucks', 'Vyper Logix Corp.', 'Free Starbucks gives away one Free (No Cost) loaded Starbucks Card to one lucky winner via every random drawing.  Check-In once for each drawing to qualify to win.  See the in-app Rules for the details. No purchase required to win. Donations and Sponsors are gratefully accepted to support this App.  Requires the Adobe AIR Runtime and Android 2.2+. Works with Honeycomb and Xoom as well as other tablets via Adobe Air 2.6.<p>This App works the same as every other giveaway, like the ones that ask you for a business card dropped into a fishbowl, all you need to do is Register then Check-In at No-Cost using your Internet EMail Address and when your EMail Address is pulled from the fishbowl you win a loaded Starbucks Card with No Cost or obligation other than to share your EMail Address.<p>Those who wish to make a generous Donation can do so, this is how the development of this App is possible, by generous Donations.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.vyperlogix.android.FreeStarbucks', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/bP7__5CB-Ibi301cvvtwob0CREs8_C4rvrQ9DAmFOhS9jA-z2ukrIo_WGNYDnBKTRvg', 3.00, 'LIFESTYLE', 'Free', '500+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.CAMERA, android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO');
