(513, 'cz.jhg.musiccontrolwidget', 'Phantom Music Control', 'Jan Gruncl', '** If you have problems with Winamp support, open Winamp settings and check &quot;Control Headset&quot; option. It will work as charm. **<p>** Music player setting is only available after you place the widget, not if you run it from launcher. **<p>Universal music control widget capable of hiding itself while there is no track playing. It is designed to be used with WidgetLocker Lockscreen, however it is possible to use it on your homescreen as well.<p>Supported players:<br>- Stock and modded Android Music (2.3+ with Pro)<br>- Google Music (Pro only)<br>- HTC Music<br>- MusicMOD<br>- PlayerPro<br>- PowerAMP<br>- UberMusic (Fede&#39;s Music App; Pro only)<br>- BeyondPod (Pro only)<br>- Experimentally Samsung TouchWiz (Pro only)<br>- Almost any other player (such as doubleTwist, Winamp, Meridian, ³/Cubed, MortPlayer, MIUI, Zimly, Songbird, Pocket Casts, Sony Walkman, n7 Player etc.) in compatibility mode (Pro only)<p>Features:<br>- Auto-hide with various hide/reveal settings<br>- WidgetLocker events integration<br>- Possibility to show/remove some elements such as volume control and current track info<br>- Nine graphical (H7C is just like Sense, Metro like WP7, Aero like Windows 7&#39;s Media Player, MIUI style, Xperia style and Carbon are self-explainatory) and two chromeless themes (minimalistic text inspired by Clockr and Calendr)<br>- Battery saving mode with almost zero energy consumption<br>- Localised to 19 languages (some fully, some partially)<br>- DashClock Widget Extension<p>- Support for 3rd party apps to utilize Phantom&#39;s wide range of controllable players (more info for developers at: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://goo.gl/ifyvL&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNF-FpQCEcnM_z2dJ7zUI6QLiq8M6g" target="_blank">http://goo.gl/ifyvL</a>)<p>Warning:<br>Do not forget, that not all players are supported, and that you need to hold your finger on your home screen in order to place a widget. Please do not try to find it in application drawer.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=cz.jhg.musiccontrolwidget', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/nOqHpgeJ_02iV5RZ9i5UnmJXQ3CeNtJPEleq6--FdbbF3qaMef0nfO_BRauu9NcdVA', 3.90, 'MUSIC_AND_AUDIO', 'Free', '500,000+', 'android.permission.INJECT_EVENTS'),
(514, 'com.aocate.presto', 'Presto Sound Library Open Beta', 'Aocate Inc.', 'Background service to add support for variable speed or pitch for playback of MP3 and Ogg Vorbis files.  AAC is not supported due to existing patents.<p>If you sent me an e-mail from Google Checkout, e-mail responses are bouncing as undeliverable.  Please e-mail me directly at <a href="mailto:aocate@gmail.com">aocate@gmail.com</a><p>I have been informed that the following apps have added support for Presto:<br>- BeyondPod<br>- DoggCatcher<br>- PodTrapper<br>- Pocket Casts<p>The Presto developer is a different developer from those applications.  Those developers are not responsible for Presto&#39;s implementation, bugs, or cost.<p>Presto is still in beta.  Bugs are listed at the end of this description.  Please e-mail me if you find new bugs.  I apologize for the lack of updates; I bit off way more than I can chew this semester.  Work is ongoing, but I can only spare a few hours at a time on some Mondays.  Please be patient.<p>Apps using Presto must be restarted after upgrading Presto.<p>Download problems are a problem with the Android Market, not with Presto.  See these pages for potential solutions:<br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.doggcatcher.com/node/843&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEuIsN3KVNaZktyHr8rCovw0CuCCQ" target="_blank">http://www.doggcatcher.com/node/843</a><br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.google.com/support/forum/p/Android%2BMarket/thread?tid%3D57b5e3efa7477b50&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFcfItnvttfTxavkv9G3m0KUxLxuw" target="_blank">http://www.google.com/support/forum/p/Android+Market/thread?tid=57b5e3efa7477b50</a><br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://code.google.com/p/android/issues/detail?id%3D1996%23makechanges&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNG16P7Btmtrhn7Nq9J2yhoxCJuE9Q" target="_blank">http://code.google.com/p/android/issues/detail?id=1996#makechanges</a><p>For developers:  See the home page for nearly drop-in code that replaces android.media.MediaPlayer, using Presto when available, or gracefully degrading to use the default Android MediaPlayer when not.<p>Known bugs (please e-mail me if you find any new ones or any of these impact you too severely; I have no means to  respond to Market comments).  Asterisks (*) indicate bugs that have not been observed in a while; please e-mail me if you encounter them so I can confirm they are not fixed.<p>#18 - ANR In BeyondPod<br>#36* - Self-Combined Files With Chapters Don&#39;t Work<br>#45 - Potential Infinite Recursion When Erroring<br>#48 - Only Signed 16 MP3s Work<br>#49 - Blogtalk radio media files duration calculated as twice as long as it actually is<br>#51 - PodTrapper Only Reaches 99% Progress<br>#62 - Very Large (&gt; 100 MB) Files May Not Play at Variant Speeds<br>#71 - Crash When Bluetooth Connected/Disconnected<br>#73 - UnsatisfiedLinkError causes force close<p>Remember that sending an e-mail is a lot more likely to get a problem fixed than anything else (such as posting a comment).<p>Internet access is necessary to play files from the Internet; before ICS, this was inherited from the calling app, but ICS changed this.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.aocate.presto', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/TReg8z0-MsUK6dCKVODGmLVThBQ4-Wyx0UjB3UgbSEl84tubUYAX3hPp491ZjhltJlKU', 3.95, 'LIBRARIES_AND_DEMO', '$4.99', '10,000+', 'com.android.vending.CHECK_LICENSE'),
(515, 'uk.co.chrisdadswell.bbcbc', 'BrowseCast BBC Podcast Browser', 'Christian Dadswell', 'UPDATE: BrowseCast HD now available for Android 4+ devices! <p>NOTE: This app is NOT an Podcast player!<p>BBC Radio Podcasts Browser with Listen Live (not all Android handsets are compatible). Also includes Radio Schedules for the entire range of BBC Radio stations (where mobile pages are available).<p>Easily search or browse (by Station or Genre) all available BBC Radio Podcasts. There are hundreds to choose from!<p>This application works alongside all the major podcasting subscribers and players, including; Pocket Casts, Google Listen (soon to be retired), BeyondPod, DoggCatcher and many others.<p>Why not follow @bbcbrowsecast on Twitter for updates and other news/information.<p>INSTRUCTIONS FOR USE:<p>-Launch BrowseCast (new podcast information is downloaded daily)<br>-Browse or search for a podcast<br>-View the podcast information and then send the Podcast subscription to your podcasting application of your choice<p>NOTE: If you attempt to add a podcast to Google Listen that you have already subscribed too, this application will force close. This is the fault of Google Listen and not this application! Please don&#39;t leave negative comments if this is what is happening to you. I have logged this issue with the Google Listen team.<p>Full information about BrowseCast can be found here;<p><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://tinyurl.com/29aljoq&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNE4MNVueUmaT5OqQG2FOguWz6YuLQ" target="_blank">http://tinyurl.com/29aljoq</a><p>CAVEATS:<p>Podcasts, Listen live and overseas use:<br>Listeners outside the UK may not be able to listen to BBC podcasts due to BBC licensing. This is down to how the BBC controls content and not this application.<p>Listen Live Stations:<br>Not all BBC stations are available for mobile devices. Namely;<p>- Radio 4 LW<br>- World Service<p>Listen Live will soon be depreciated as it no longer works on a large number of devices. For the best mobile Radio experience I&#39;d recommend TuneIn Radio on Google Play.<p>This application is not affiliated with the BBC. The developer is not an employee of the BBC.<p>*Information downloaded to this application is direct from the BBC website and is publicly available.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=uk.co.chrisdadswell.bbcbc', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/WcNP28F2hGuK5q9LTxilTUOomnCC6tvvm4bvMTh-sbqdj3zhQJISFYHjPwezDZ_3GQ', 3.76, 'MEDIA_AND_VIDEO', 'Free', '100,000+', ''),
(516, 'hc.silasmarner', 'Silas Marner', 'Mobile Fun', 'The novel is set in the early years of the 19th century. Silas Marner, a weaver, is a member of a small Calvinist congregation in Lantern Yard, a slum street in an unnamed city in Northern England. He is falsely accused of stealing the congregation&#39;s funds while watching over the very ill deacon of the group. Two clues are given against Silas: a pocket-knife and the discovery of the bag formerly containing the money in his own house. There is a strong suggestion that Silas&#39;s best friend, William Dane, has framed him, since Silas had lent the pocket-knife to William a short while before. Silas is proclaimed guilty. The woman he was to marry casts him off, and later marries William Dane. With his life shattered and his heart broken, he leaves Lantern Yard and the city.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=hc.silasmarner', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/LxUyKhpHu7xMRAvlIKnv8ZqV8--p0PoDJjJQdOOLotj4AYm-Ha1roCEwXwVy6UeddWc', 5.00, 'BOOKS_AND_REFERENCE', 'Free', '100+', ''),
(517, 'com.lunagames.flowsymbols', 'Flow Symbols Free', 'Lunagames', 'Flow Symbols - awesome fun - a simple and addictive puzzle game.<br>NEW: Free Unlimited Levels!<p>Connect the matching colored Symbols with pipe to create a flow. Pair all symbols, and cover the entire board to solve each puzzle. However you need to make sure no pipes overlap causing a them to break.<p>Flow Symbols features include:<br>- UNLIMITED levels of ENDLESS game-play (endless game mode)<br>- Time Attack game mode: solve as many puzzles before the buzzer<br>- Game Center support<br>- 5 different board sizes<br>- Excellent for color blind; each symbol has own color but also own sign<br>- Fun retro style graphics and sounds<p>Enjoy your endless zen of free levels!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.lunagames.flowsymbols', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/2AumbUATQOk02OPvitDdY2eLaFB8uob7d_12Hw9fk1hPD05QO8JQCPRRqlf_MSACbw', 4.18, 'BRAIN', 'Free', '50,000+', 'android.permission.WAKE_LOCK, android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE, android.permission.BATTERY_STATS, android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS, android.permission.SET_ORIENTATION, android.permission.DEVICE_POWER, android.permission.INTERNET, android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.VIBRATE'),
