(531, 'com.opera.browser.beta', 'Opera browser beta', 'Opera Software ASA', 'The free must-have app for your phone! Find friends – discover personalized news – download movies and music – search better. Do more online using less data, with the Opera browser. It’s our best all-in-one app for Android.<br>- Fast and easy to use: Our fastest browser for Android loads webpages almost instantly, in the right size and format for your phone.<br>- Keep your connection: Browse at high speed outside 3G coverage with Off-Road Mode.<br>- News for you: Find out what’s happening with the Discover feature, your personal news feed.<br>- Instant favorites: Set your top sites and bookmarks in the Speed Dial - open them with one click!<br>- Music, movies and more: Start, stop, resume, save and rename the media files you keep on your phone with our download manager.<p>If your device is not compatible with the Opera browser, download Opera Mini. <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://bit.ly/opera-mini-promo&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFnTgRw975_uPAK_B6ICoHKJ5hnrA" target="_blank">http://bit.ly/opera-mini-promo</a><p>Discover what Opera browser for Android can do for you. Download free.<p>Share the news with your friends! And +1 us on G+ too!<br>Discover more at <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://opera.com/mobile/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGV94egfGDG19qVJP6rwnKKVwFvjA" target="_blank">http://opera.com/mobile/</a><br>Keep in touch with Opera:<br>Twitter - <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://twitter.com/opera/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGTbtseWyNak28Z3aWVIdZu8Qk5Aw" target="_blank">http://twitter.com/opera/</a><br>Facebook - <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.facebook.com/opera/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFSdlFTcROg_TtysYiZeN5BQbz6vw" target="_blank">http://www.facebook.com/opera/</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.opera.browser.beta', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/Ft9CtYlydnio76EveAdr4ki6oUdQwgkMK3tKfIx-XqBYIqhEbRkC-925tcu8b7BFpD4', 4.13, 'COMMUNICATIO