(558, 'com.mfoundry.mb.android.mb_BMOH071025661', 'BMO Harris Mobile Banking', 'BMO Harris Bank N.A.', 'The BMO Harris Mobile Banking app offers a convenient, easy and secure way to bank on the go with your Android device. Please visit bmoharris.com/security for additional details.<p>BMO Harris Mobile is available to BMO Harris Online Banking customers. If you do not have a BMO Harris Online Banking account, visit bmoharris.com to enroll. <p>Make Deposits on the Go<br>Simply take a picture of your check with your Android device camera to securely deposit it into your account.  Eligibility requirements and transaction limits apply as described in the Mobile Banking Terms and Conditions.<p>Check Balances and Make Transfers<br>Stay up-to-date with your balances and account activity. Quickly transfer money between your eligible BMO Harris accounts with our simple transfer feature.<p>Pay Bills<br>Easily schedule payments to billers you&#39;ve set up in BMO Harris Online Banking, see and edit scheduled payments and view recent payment activity. The features of BMO Harris Bill Pay are now in the palm of your hand.<p>Find BMO Harris ATMs and Locations<br>Quickly find a BMO Harris Bank branch or ATM near you with our easy-to-use locator feature.<br>	<br>The BMO Harris Banking app is free to download and use. Message and data rates from your wireless carrier and other fees as noted in the BMO Harris Online Banking Services Agreement may apply.<p>Banking deposit and loan products and services are provided by BMO Harris Bank N.A. and are subject to bank and credit approval. BMO Harris and BMO Harris Bank are trade names used by BMO Harris Bank N.A. Member FDIC.<p>Copyright 2013, BMO Financial Corp., All Rights Reserved.<p>Android is a trademark of Google Inc.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mfoundry.mb.android.mb_BMOH071025661', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/xFq9LblqiKseRHYhiADmI2cqsINJN2vOHnoJK6frIeawWmbWpNbywI-EzGxsYJIv4g', 2.95, 'FINANCE', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.CAMERA'),
(559, 'com.pcfinancial.mobile', 'PC Financial Mobile Banking', 'CIBC', 'It’s easy to bank anywhere, with the President’s Choice Financial® Mobile Banking app for Android. Pay bills, transfer funds, check your balance and more with just a few steps. Simple, convenient and secure, it’s the ideal app for your everyday banking needs. <p>Register directly on your phone<br>•	No need to visit a pavilion, phone or go online to register.<p>Set recurring transactions<br>•	Whether you’re paying bills or transferring funds between accounts, you can easily set the start date, frequency and end date of recurring transactions and not worry about them again.<p>Update your info<br>•	You don’t have to jump through hoops to do tasks as simple as updating your address and phone number, resetting your password, or changing your personal verification questions.<p>Check account balances<br>•	Check account balances on all of your PC Financial® deposit, borrowing and investment accounts. <p>Pay bills<br>•	Pay bills you’ve already set up in PC Financial® Online Banking or set up new bills and future bill payments so you don’t miss a deadline. <p>Transfer money <br>•	Transfer money between your eligible PC Financial® banking accounts or other banks.<p>See past and upcoming transactions <br>•	View past and upcoming transactions, including bill payments and transfers. <p>Send and receive INTERAC® e-Transfers<br>•	Send and receive INTERAC® e-Transfers to anyone on your recipient list or add new recipients from your contact list*. You can also check the status of the e-Transfer. <p><br>Locate bank machines and pavilions<br>•	Use the GPS on your device to find nearby PC Financial® and CIBC bank machines and PC Financial® pavilions <p>View cheque images<br>•	View enlarged images of all your cleared cheques.<p>View statements<br>•	View statements for your accounts<p><br>Enrolment<br>If you&#39;re currently enroled in President’s Choice Financial® Online Banking, you can use the same card number, password and personal verification questions to sign on to PC Financial® Mobile Banking for Android. <p>Security while you bank<br>Ensuring the safety of your information online is vitally important. When you bank using the PC Financial® mobile banking app, your information is protected under the PC Financial® Personal Banking Online Security Guarantee. You can bank with confidence knowing your privacy is safe for more information just look under Security at pcfinancial.ca<p>LEGAL<p>Although PC Financial® will not charge any fees to access mobile banking, additional service fees may be charged by your internet or wireless service provider for access through your electronic device. Check with your service or hardware provider if you have questions about your specific electronic device.<p>*When sending e-Transfers, you can have the President’s Choice Financial® mobile banking app access information from your contact list to fill in the required recipient information. At no time is that contact list data transmitted to or shared with PC Financial®.<p>®PC, President&#39;s Choice, PC Financial and President&#39;s Choice Financial are trademarks of Loblaws Inc. <p>INTERAC® is a registered trademark of INTERAC Inc. CIBC a licensee of the marks.<p>President’s Choice Financial® personal banking services are provided by the direct banking division of CIBC.<p>Banking services not available in Quebec.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.pcfinancial.mobile', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/yJmxb1Ghdwn0MlgSofP56-w8L_zdE1_exBtZf_caG3S6f6n96j5LkyepyBMpa0YHPa9y', 3.77, 'FINANCE', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.WRITE_CONTACTS, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.READ_CONTACTS, android.permission.READ_CALL_LOG, android.permission.WRITE_CALL_LOG'),
(560, 'com.binarybricks.dexterapps.findbankifsccodes', 'Find Bank IFSC Code India', 'Pranay Airan', 'Now Find IFSC Code of Any bank across India. With IFSC Code Finder. <p>Find Bank IFSC Code helps you to find IFSC Codes for all Banks like ICICI, HDFC, SBI, PNB, HSBC, Citi etc. <p>With this simple app you can find all the information related to your bank like <br>=&gt; MICR Code<br>=&gt; IFSC Code<br>=&gt; Address<br>=&gt; Contact No<br>=&gt; Location on map<p>We have compiled a complete list of 90000 bank branches across India for more than 147 banks, lot of time we need to share our bank ifsc code and other information for multiple reasons Find Bank IFSC helps you to get all this information at the time of need.<p>Find Bank IFSC Comes with the following features<p>=&gt; Get IFSC as well as MICR Codes<br>=&gt; IFSC and MICR codes from 128 banks across India<br>=&gt; Comprehensive list of 90000 banks<br>=&gt; Save found IFSC for Offline references <br>=&gt; Share IFSC Results on SMS or email<p>Download now and get ifsc information from anywhere. <p>Note: If you are not able to find your bank please use BRANCH Name, you don&#39;t have to specify the complete name, partial names are acceptable.<p>A lot of banks have more than 100 branches in few cities the search without branch feature is limited to only 25 so that the app can work fast<p>Important Note: The data used in the app are taken from RBI website, please confirm any details shown in this app in case of doubt there can be mismatch possible<p>Report issue at <a href="mailto:pranay.airan@iiitb.net">pranay.airan@iiitb.net</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.binarybricks.dexterapps.findbankifsccodes', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/8uWT-bVyYPZN51Uv3CoIfQ5lRLQQ8tEmglffxTXPHoAnm4mW2ioG5bR4IuL7Bo6sz0yA', 4.33, 'FINANCE', 'Free', '50,000+', ''),
(561, 'com.sovereign.santander', 'Personal Banking', 'Santander Bank US', 'Santander Bank’s Personal Banking mobile app is a secure way for you to view your account balances and transactions, transfer funds, pay bills and locate branches and ATMs near you. <p>This app is available to all US customers enrolled in Santander Bank’s Online Banking with BillPay and is only offered in English. It’s fast, simple and convenient. And most importantly, secure.<p>What you can do:<br>•View account balances and transactions<br>•Transfer funds between eligible accounts<br>•View your Santander Credit Card transactions<br>•Pay your Credit Card bill <br>•Schedule and pay bills<br>•Transfer funds to other Santander Bank customers<br>•Locate your nearest Santander location and receive detailed directions<br>•Reach customer service with one-touch calling<p>Your security is our highest priority. Use your secure credentials to gain access to mobile banking. All of the information that flows between you and us is encrypted. What’s more, you’re fully protected against online fraud when you tell us right away. Please refer to our Online Banking Agreement for details.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sovereign.santander', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/6y0jFpmNoR7qLlbqat0tEdbPze5iRhudyrz6Fvi3mlmUiJWoiN52pCkd_jchI2odzdE', 3.96, 'FINANCE', 'Free', '50,000+', 'android.permission.CAMERA, android.permission.CALL_PHONE, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION'),
(562, 'ccom.ibebank.quiz', 'Bank Exams Preparation Kit', 'NixBiz', '-------------------------------------<br>Note: Please Comment below and Rate this app. Also please update which information or which new section you want. I will update new section and usefull information On Your Demand. <br>----------------------------------<br>This is official app from Indiabankingexam.com  which is powered by Achivers Bank Academy provided for Bank Po , Bank clerk , Bank exams Preparation .<br>It will help in Bank Job seekers, Bank Po , Bank clerk and other govt exams which required unique question collection.<br>Main Features <br>1.	Simple Interface.<br>2.	Latest questions updation from our server (Indiabankingexam) <br>3.	Feed back form to submit you query.<br>4.	Category wise questions (every week new categories will be added)<br>5.	weekly new question updation.<br>6.	definate answers to every question.<br>7.	bank exams prepration Tips and ideas<br>8.	Short learning Notes direct points<br>9.	Daily Updates quick news section<p><br>Categories<br>1.	Computer Knowledge<br>2.	English Language<br>3.	General Awarness<br>4.	Reasoning<br>5.	Quantitative Aptitude<br>6.	Many more new will be added soon.<br>NOTE: To give you more and more benefit in bank exams we have made app which uses Internet <br>++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++<br>THIS APPLICATION REQUIRED INTERNET FOR RECEIVING QUESTIONS FORM SERVER.<br>++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++<p><br>Q1) Who has been appointed the Director of the Institute of Banking Personnel Selection ?<p>a) M. Balachandran<br>b) M.D. Mallya  <br>c) Anup Sankar Bhattacharya<br>d) R. Gandhi<br>e)None of these<br>Answer: c<p>Q2) Who has been appointed the Chairman of Indian Banks Association?<br> <br>a) Pratap Choudhuri<br>b) Alok Mishra<br>c) J.P.Dua<br>d) K.R.Kamath<br>e)None of these<br>Answer: d<br>Q3) Head Office of which of  the following banks in Lucknow ?<p>a) RBI<br>b) SIDBI<br>c) NABARD<br>d) Corporation Bank<br>e)None of these<br>Answer: b<br>Q4) Who are the member of the RIC ?<p>a) Russia - Iran - China         <br>b) Russia- India- China                    <br>c) Romania-Iran-Canada                          <br>d) Romania-Israel-Chile         <br>e)None of these<p>Answer: b<br>Q5) Sushil Kumar Solanki is associated with the game of  ?<br> <br> a) Boxing <br> b) Swimming            <br> c) Wrestling              <br> d)Archery                    <br> e)None of these<p>Answer: c<p>This app having all latest bank questions and  practice tests.<br>This app is Powered by Indiabankingexams.com<br>Indiabankingexams is a comprehensive banking Portal for your preparation of the bank examination conducted by the IBPS in India. Our sole aim to be useful to banking aspirants and help them in their preparation by providing the best resources and information in a single place. All aspirants are requested to contribute towards the building of this resource and help generations of bank aspirants. Let this work as your study group even if you are preparing all alone!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=ccom.ibebank.quiz', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/zqyLf9WXwL-7M3a60FgHncR4lGNhysVcwtOIKQ4e-IH9CMa4l8Z9xvow9uUouLNtMQ', 4.36, 'EDUCATION', 'Free', '10,000+', ''),
(563, 'za.co.fnb.connect.itt', 'FNB Banking App', 'FNB', 'FNB is proud to bring you the FNB Banking App, South Africa’s first Banking Application for Smartphones. <br>The FNB Banking App for Smartphones is simple to use and provides a convenient, easy and secure way to do your banking anytime and anywhere. <p>With the FNB App you can: <p>- View account balances<br>- View detailed transaction, transfer and payment histories<br>- Make Payments<br>- Make once off payments<br>- Make and receive Geo Payments <br>- Make use of full eWallet functionality*<br>- Buy &amp; Sell Shares with Share Trading functionality<br>- Manage your eBucks Account<br>- Manage your FNB Cards<br>- Add payment recipients<br>- Update, view and delete recipient details <br>- Transfer funds between your accounts <br>- Buy Prepaid Airtime, Data and Electricity<br>- Make use of other value added services, such as:<br>	- Make and receive calls (powered by FNB Connect) with a new enhanced calling functionality (including free calls to FNB Call Centres)<br>	- Improved messaging functionality that allows you to send money and airtime while chatting, as well as share photos and videos <br>	- Send Money and Buy Prepaid while Messaging<br>	- Use Location Based Services to find FNB ATMs or Branches<br>	- View Forex rates<br>	- Apply for new FNB Accounts<br>	- Contact your Premier Banker<br>	- Make stop payments <br>	- Receive inContact messages<br>	- Top up your FNB Connect Surf prepaid accounts and purchase FNB Connect Surf ADSL Bundles<p><br>Anyone can download the FNB Banking App for Smartphones, but you need to be an FNB customer to make full use of the traditional banking services. <p>*Non FNB customers can now transact, make calls and send messages on the FNB Banking App for Smartphones, using eWallet. This includes the ability to make and receive Geo Payments.<p>If you are not an FNB customer, you can conveniently Switch to FNB from the App. Simply supply your details and an agent will get back to you. <p><p>*Terms &amp; Conditions Apply<p><br>Follow these easy steps to download and link the FNB Banking App for Smartphones to your device.<p>If you are registered for FNB Online Banking follow these steps:<br>1. Download the FNB Banking App for Smartphones from your devices&#39; App store. You can do this from your Smartphone, laptop or PC. If you download the App from your computer, the App will install on your Smart device the next time it is plugged into the computer.<br>2. Launch the FNB Banking App on your device, select &#39;Get Started&#39; and follow the prompts.<br>3. Log into FNB Online Banking, from your laptop or PC, and confirm that you wish to link your Smartphone to your Online Banking profile.<br>4. Launch the FNB Banking App again, select &#39;Login&#39; and enter your Online Banking password.<p>If you are not registered for Online Banking follow these steps:<br>1. Download the FNB Banking App for Smartphones from your devices&#39; App store. You can do this from your Smartphone, laptop or PC. If you download the App from your computer, the App will install on your Smart device the next time it is plugged into the computer.<br>2. Launch the FNB Banking App on your device, select &#39;Get Started&#39; and follow the prompts.<br>3. In order to fully transact you need to visit an FNB ATM or FNB Branch in order to verify yourself.<p>By downloading or using the FNB Banking App for Smartphones you agree to be bound by the license agreement located at <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://fnbtouch.fnbconnect.co.za/software_license.pdf&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFh9uRx0orLcGd95aDtYr27Pj3_2w" target="_blank">https://fnbtouch.fnbconnect.co.za/software_license.pdf</a>. This agreement is incorporated into this notice by reference. <br>If you do not agree to the licence agreement, do not download or use the application.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=za.co.fnb.connect.itt', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/gnIrn6SVfQyF4thzvrCWDo8gEw3abokMKWjJagWJNIXgBxo4r9l-euO5WS-URN-JfJA', 4.30, 'FINANCE', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.ACCESS_GPS, android.permission.READ_CONTACTS, android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO, android.permission.CALL_PHONE, android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, za.co.fnb.connect.itt.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, android.permission.RECEIVE_SMS, android.permission.READ_SMS, android.permission.USE_SIP, android.permission.READ_CALL_LOG'),
(564, 'com.sgarces.bank', 'You''re a Bank', 'Sergio Garces', 'Make millions in the only bank simulation game that&#39;s both accessible and fun.<p>Maximize your profit by adjusting interest rates, playing the Stock Market and borrowing from bigger banks.<p>Beautifully designed, this game gives you the experience of running an investment bank without risking a dime. You can learn to play in 2 minutes. Become a financial genius while having a blast.<p>Features:<br>- Loan money to clients and charge interest monthly<br>- Accept deposits to boost you cash reserves<br>- Control how much risk you&#39;re willing to take with your loans<br>- Entice your clients to deposit money with attractive interest rates<br>- Borrow money to leverage your investments<br>- Closely watch the prices while you buy and sell in the Stock Market<p>You have 36 months to make your fortune. After that, try again and beat your high score. The game is designed for you to experiment.<p>A personal note:<br>I was inspired to write this game after the financial crash of 2008. I wanted to understand how a bank operates and what the trade offs are. I believe this game accomplishes that while providing a fun experience through simple controls and a clean, attractive interface. I hope you enjoy it.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sgarces.bank', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/8Kmj4Qb2C--LaJUBvsc3p_ZRRxD5wZiVWWJA2jRwmJAoMvk8Mf8mcJEz25VFTPFNY0w', 3.94, 'CASUAL', '$1.99', '1,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.INTERNET'),
(565, 'ee.smkv.calc.loan', 'Simple Loan Calculator', 'Andrei Samkov', 'The Simple calculator for annuity, differentiated and fixed payments.<br>Calculation:the monthly payment, the amount of interest paid, the total cost of credit, amortization schedule and a comparison of all these indices between different loans.<p>About all issues please report to project home page or to my E-mail address.<p>Open source software, <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://code.google.com/p/android-simple-loan-calculator&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGk-Uin2IpasOPUZvccXmM0FNa92w" target="_blank">http://code.google.com/p/android-simple-loan-calculator</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=ee.smkv.calc.loan', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/b2zDDQdXLjdG-QqKXkQjFAfWw00b76_K4p4bbIyIONO7S567EEshPLny1gY0JRxnRrs', 4.65, 'FINANCE', 'Free', '100,000+', ''),
(566, 'com.dfckc.abmw', 'Academy Bank - MW', 'Dickinson Financial Corporation', 'Enjoy the convenience, security and ease of doing your banking right from your mobile device. You can check your account balances, transfer funds, view recent activity, receive alerts, find ATMs or banking centers - even make check deposits from your phone.<br> <br>To get started, download and launch the app. Then sign on with your Academy Bank Midwest Online Banking Access ID and Password. It’s that simple.<br> <br>Monitor Your Account <br>- See account balances and transaction history<p>Perform Transactions<br>- Pay bills<br>- Transfer money between Academy Bank Midwest accounts<br>- Place a stop payment<br> <br>Make Check Deposits<br>- Make check deposits with your phone <br> <br>Find Branch Locations and ATMs<br>- Find the nearest Academy Bank Midwest banking center locations &amp; ATMs<br>- Speak with a bank representative<br> <br>Alerts<br>- Balance level alerts:  let you know when you have gone above or dipped below your pre-selected amount. <br>- Transaction alerts:  let you know when specific transaction activity occurs on your account. <br>- Scheduled alerts:  send you the latest information on your available balance and recent account history.<br> <br>Safe and Secure<br>Academy Bank Midwest is committed to your security and protecting the privacy of your financial information. We use state of the art technology to protect unauthorized access to your account, your wireless communication is securely encrypted, and your personal information is not stored on your phone. <p>Have Questions?  Call 1-866-868-9141 <br> <br>Academy Bank a Division of Armed Forces Bank – Member FDIC', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dfckc.abmw', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/Vvs4kzdmIK2yL1ZgBzIaiXM2xOWmAl3T7Yi85gS1mNlJIT7G31AwDtDvduXcgFmHiO4', 4.21, 'FINANCE', 'Free', '10,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.ACCESS_LOCATION_EXTRA_COMMANDS, android.permission.CAMERA'),
(567, 'com.dfckc.afb', 'Armed Forces Bank', 'Dickinson Financial Corporation', 'Enjoy the convenience, security and ease of doing your banking right from your mobile device. You can check your account balances, transfer funds, view recent activity, receive alerts, find ATMs or banking centers - even make check deposits from your phone.<br> <br>To get started, download and launch the app. Then sign on with your Armed Forces Bank Online Banking Access ID and Password. It’s that simple.<br> <br>Monitor Your Account <br>- See account balances and transaction history<p>Perform Transactions<br>- Pay bills<br>- Transfer money between Armed Forces Bank accounts<br>- Place a stop payment<br> <br>Make Check Deposits<br>- Make check deposits with your phone <br> <br>Find Branch Locations and ATMs<br>- Find the nearest Armed Forces Bank banking center locations &amp; ATMs<br>- Speak with a bank representative<br> <br>Alerts<br>- Balance level alerts:  let you know when you have gone above or dipped below your pre-selected amount. <br>- Transaction alerts:  let you know when specific transaction activity occurs on your account. <br>- Scheduled alerts:  send you the latest information on your available balance and recent account history.<br> <br>Safe and Secure<br>Armed Forces Bank is committed to your security and protecting the privacy of your financial information. We use state of the art technology to protect unauthorized access to your account, your wireless communication is securely encrypted, and your personal information is not stored on your phone. <p>Have Questions?  Call 1-888-929-2265 <p>Armed Forces Bank – Member FDIC', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dfckc.afb', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/AZjxIZf8xEL_9M9fRE4mj2WLtC_uItqzXY4Bm_bJ1kjgPuDi-0h43kaZJjaTaPuD4D8', 4.22, 'FINANCE', 'Free', '10,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.ACCESS_LOCATION_EXTRA_COMMANDS, android.permission.CAMERA'),
(568, 'com.clairmail.greatwesternbank', 'Great Western Bank Mobile', 'Great Western Bank', 'Put your money where your mobile is! Great Western Bank’s FREE* mobile banking app** lets you bank on the go when it’s convenient for you.<br><b>To begin using this app, you will need to enroll in Mobile Banking by creating a new account on the app. You cannot log into Mobile Banking with your Online Banking credentials. You will need to create an account to use Mobile Banking.</b><br><br><br>LOCATE US! There are too many things to remember in life. We don’t expect you to memorize where all of our locations and ATMs are. With Great Western Bank mobile banking all you need to do is search by address to find us where you are or where you’re going.<p>CHECK YOUR BALANCE! Sometimes all you need – or want – to know is how much money is in your account. We can tell you that… and more if you want.<p>TRANSFER FUNDS! With just a few simple steps, you can transfer money between your accounts. So go ahead and make that big purchase… you got it covered with Great Western Bank mobile banking.<p>PAY BILLS!*** What’s worse than being on vacation and suddenly realizing you forgot to pay your water bill? No worries. With Great Western Bank mobile banking you can pay your bills from your lounge chair on the beach.<p>DEPOSIT CHECKS! Coming soon. And yes, it’s as good as it sounds.<p>Not only does Great Western Bank mobile banking have great features, it also has great security elements like real-time alerts, account nicknames instead of numbers, anti-tampering technology, and multiple encryption techniques.<p>For more information on Great Western Bank mobile banking, visit www.GreatWesternBank.com/mobile.<p>*The Great Western Bank mobile banking app is free to download. Your mobile carrier’s text messaging and web access charges may apply. Web access is needed to use app. Check with your carrier for specific fees and charges.<br>**By downloading the app, you agree to comply with Great Western Bank’s Terms and Conditions for Mobile Banking.<br>***Must have Online Bill Pay within Online Banking to utilize Bill Pay on mobile device.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.clairmail.greatwesternbank', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/0Y38bZlXnkarxooKgVBsdCvuxaw-6KeePNktK0lSeJXNaZgJSVbvrT_x7BsKAR-AiSQ', 2.61, 'FINANCE', 'Free', '10,000+', 'android.permission.CAMERA, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.ACCESS_LOCATION_EXTRA_COMMANDS'),
(569, 'com.onelearn.android.bpo', 'Bank Power: IBPS PO Exam Prep', 'GradeStack Education', '***FREE Daily GK Updates***<p>Get the Bank POwer advantage in your preparation for the Bank PO and clerk exam.<br>With a highly updated and relevant syllabus for SBI, IBPS and RRB recruitment exam. Get closer to your dream banking job with the Bank POwer course.<br>The online course covers in detail all the modules that are a part of the Bank PO exam. Along with each topic there is a large set of questions to practice online and on your mobile phone. Each of these test papers help you revise the concepts you study. The well-researched course material ensures comprehensive coverage of all basic concepts, with solved examples, short-cuts and strategies for improvement of performance.<br>This online cum mobile based course is designed for the SBI, IBPS and the RRB Exam. It covers the syllabus for recruitment into all major banks.<p><br>Course Modules<br>1. General Awareness<p>With special reference to the banking industry, General Awareness covers all major historical and current facts that are likely to come in the Bank PO Exam. The module also includes exhaustive questions and answers for important topics<br>2. Quantitative Aptitude<p>With 13 chapters covering the complete QA syllabus, this course is complete for you exam preparation and to test yourself on your skills in QA<br>3. English<p>Covers topics in Grammer, Reading comprehension and Word lIst. The English course is a quick reference guide to your Bank PO preparation. It also includes practice test papers and english vocabulary flashcards <br>4. Computers<p>The knowledge of computers is pivotal for a successful banking career and the exams also give it high importance. Get all the fundamentals and the set of important questions as a part of this course.<br>5. Reasoning<p><br>One of the more challenging subjects, the comprehensive and easy to understand course material helps you build your strength in Reasoning. Take the reasoning questions papers to further strengthen your grasp of the subject.<p>Like us on Facebook : <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.facebook.com/GradeStack&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNG_9b8M3dh1cYqvjy21woORWxkgvg" target="_blank">https://www.facebook.com/GradeStack</a><br>Follow us on Twitter : <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://twitter.com/grade_stack&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFdDd_hjDrDGtGEoD5xVjytIoKgoA" target="_blank">https://twitter.com/grade_stack</a><br>For more apps : https://play.google.com/store/apps/developer?id=GradeStack+Education', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.onelearn.android.bpo', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/65N7KSCXAMd-MehAH4rsClRk73wvC3x7ArZfLdtszkFAA08xUOW0cTsLWHWv2cw5tQ', 4.38, 'EDUCATION', 'Free', '10,000+', 'android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.READ_CONTACTS, com.android.vending.BILLING, com.onelearn.android.bpo.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE'),
(570, 'com.scbt.mobile', 'Bank Any Time', 'Fiserv Solutions, Inc.', 'Bank Any Time with the Mobile Banking app for South Carolina Bank and Trust (SCBT), North Carolina Bank and Trust (NCBT), Community Bank &amp; Trust (CBT), and The Savannah Bank customers.<p>You’ll have total freedom to access your accounts when and where you want. It’s simple and secure.<br>Account Balances – view balances for your checking, savings, and/or loans<br>Account Activity – view detailed information on recent transactions<br>Pay Bills – Make online bill payments* and change or cancel scheduled payments<br>Transfer Funds – transfer funds between your SCBT, NCBT, CBT, or Savannah Bank accounts<br>Locations – Search by zip, address or current locations for the nearest ATM or branch<p>To use this app you must be enrolled and active in Online Banking with South Carolina Bank and Trust (SCBT), North Carolina Bank and Trust (NCBT), Community Bank &amp; Trust (CBT), or The Savannah Bank.  <p>Our Mobile Banking app, like Online Banking, protects your account information using multiple layers of security.  Full account numbers are never displayed or transmitted.<p>Regardless of changes in technology and information we have always been-and will continue to be-committed to the principles of customer privacy.  View our Privacy Policy on our website.<p>If you need assistance at any time, please contact our Customer Care Center at <br>1-800-277-2175 for SCBT, 1-877-277-2185 for NCBT, 1-888-847-2265 for CBT, or 1-866-722-1035 for The Savannah Bank.<p>*For use with bill pay vendors previously set up in Online Banking.<p>© 2012  SCBT. Member FDIC<br>NCBT, a Division of SCBT<br>CBT, a Division of SCBT<br>The Savannah Bank, a Division of SCBT', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.scbt.mobile', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/R_O4Yua1k8oqv1WLp-Bz1nAPNJdIBBlGWN1iJDXRLpXwwnmsBVIu6MY0eyjEmfPZl4E', 4.27, 'FINANCE', 'Free', '10,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.ACCESS_LOCATION_EXTRA_COMMANDS, android.permission.CAMERA, android.permission.READ_CONTACTS, android.permission.READ_CALL_LOG'),
(571, 'com.jjinx.dropboxdownloader', 'Folder Downloader for Dropbox', 'Dario Solera', '<b>Folder Downloader for Dropbox lets you download entire folders from your Dropbox account to your Android device.</b><p>Problems? Drop me a line at <a href="mailto:solera.dario@gmail.com">solera.dario@gmail.com</a><p>HOW IT WORKS<br>1. Browse through your Dropbox folders<br>2. Long-press on the folder you want to download, select &quot;Download folder to...&quot; - or use the &quot;Download all to...&quot; button<br>3. Browse your Android&#39;s device local storage, and tap on the &quot;Select&quot; button to start the download<p>FEATURES<br>• Ability to create new folders on the local storage on the fly, so you don&#39;t need to use a separate file manager<br>• Supports both internal and SD card storage (defaults to device-defined external storage, navigate up to find other storage options)<br>• Downloads performed in background via an Android Service, so you don&#39;t have to keep the app running<br>• Ability to retry failed downloads from the report screen<br>• Support for MediaScanner, allowing other apps to immediately recognize downloaded files<br>• Authentication performed via OAuth and Dropbox&#39;s official API, so the app CANNOT read your Dropbox password<br>• No ads<p>NOTES<br>• Only one download job is performed at a time, subsequent jobs are queued and executed as soon as the previous are completed<br>• You&#39;ll need a Dropbox account to use this app, but the Dropbox app is optional', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jjinx.dropboxdownloader', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/XuFmp8zO-GjemqIvIDzQYaV8WF6z3-RhIeUd4B27ZaoYuQznKJzU2yKIoZXvEcwrQHWQ', 4.61, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '100,000+', ''),
(572, 'org.terukusu.dropboxdownloader', 'Downloader for Dropbox', 'teru_kusu', 'The Simple Downloader for the DropBox.<br>Not Sync! Just Download!<p>Step1. Browse DropBox<br>Step2. Select a file or a &quot;folder&quot; on the DropBox<br>Step3. start download<p>It&#39;s very simple!!<p>* Note that this app need the OI FileManager for selecting a local folder.<p>My Twitter: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://twitter.com/teru_kusu&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGdb_uBWbQIW_mABAwRAkBmQ1QvdQ" target="_blank">http://twitter.com/teru_kusu</a><p><br>Icon created by @mrshiromi (twitter)', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.terukusu.dropboxdownloader', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/XodtOnZ4pQJm1oS7wOPLLbkTG9I4g4QgNm31FWVBmK9fHxOPAF40nJgIWckb9dWXRpZ3', 3.59, 'TOOLS', 'Free', '100,000+', ''),
(573, 'com.doublecore.musicdropnplaylite', 'MusicDropNPlayLite for Dropbox', 'DoubleCore Mobile', 'Dropbox Music player Drop your music to Dropbox and play it anywhere! (mp3/m4a)<p>Do you have an android phone? And do you listen to the Music on your phone? And are you tired of copying songs from your computer to your phone via USB cable? If the answer is yes, then MusicDropNPlay can simplify your life.<p>For additional product information, follow us on Twitter <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://twitter.com/%23!/MusicDropNPlay&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNE5IOW_nR0bBLu30Z3Zrhxev6PMew" target="_blank">https://twitter.com/#!/MusicDropNPlay</a> and Facebook <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.facebook.com/pages/MusicDropNPlay/223220167792633&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGFr-PXvULgT-2z0lliNCwraKmMwA" target="_blank">http://www.facebook.com/pages/MusicDropNPlay/223220167792633</a>.<p>If you have not used Dropbox, Dropbox is a free cloud service which allows you to bring all your photos, docs and music anywhere. You can upload your music to your Dropbox account from your computer and MusicDropNPlay can stream and playback it on your android device. No need to copy songs via the cable anymore. To learn more about Dropbox, please check www.dropbox.com.<p>MusicDropNPlay allows you to stream mp3/m4a songs directly from your Dropbox account in real-time. It has extra features normal players don&#39;t have:<p>• Real time streaming - no need to download the song completely before playing it.<br>• Artist and album artwork downloads to give you extra visual enjoyment.<br>• Group songs by artist or album names to find your favour songs at your fingertips.<br>• One button press to add all the songs from a folder you select.<br>• Support different cache sizes up to 8G (2000 songs).<br>• A user-friendly Dropbox file explorer letting you select the songs you want to listen.<br>• Ability to seek to any position, which may not be even buffered.<br>• A sleek playlist widget making sorting and reordering so easy.<br>• Online and offline modes making sure you have music to listen wherever you go even there is no network coverage.<br>• Headset in-line remote control support keeping your phone in the pocket all the time.<br>• Quick download feature - a shortcut to download all the songs in one shot so you can go offline mode afterwards to save either bandwidth or survive network outage.<p>MusicDropNPlay: drop music anywhere and play music anytime! Your ultimate Dropbox music player on your Android phone!<br>Find it on Google Android Market:<br>Lite Version: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.doublecore.musicdropnplaylite <br>Full Version: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.doublecore.musicdropnplay', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.doublecore.musicdropnplaylite', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/J2snGe4rLLzbaD8OTeSIcfZrxNermKK_KtSDDZ4mpWey5TKRQLdS8OwwJOecClMsMVE', 3.77, 'MUSIC_AND_AUDIO', 'Free', '50,000+', ''),
(574, 'com.jb.gosms.brdropbox', 'GO SMS Pro Dropbox Backup', 'ZT.art', 'Dropbox Backup &amp; Restore plug-in is a GO SMS Pro paid feature that enables you to backup SMS, MMS as a compressed file and save to your Dropbox folder.<p>Main functions:<br>1. Backup SMS, MMS, Private SMS, Favorites, Filter folder SMSand the specific contacts SMS to Dropbox cloud server.<br>2. Restore SMS, MMS, Private SMS from Dropbox.<p>How to download and install the Find Phone plug-in?<br>- To install and use the plug-in, please purchase the Premium Pack Service in GO SMS Pro application center first.<br>- After purchasing, click the Dropbox backup icon in the GO SMS Application Center or the Premium Pack Service and follow the tips to download and install.<p>*Related website:<br>- Download the newest GO SMS Pro: Search “GO SMS Pro” in Google Market.<br>- Visit our Blog: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://gosms.goforandroid.com&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNE3HNhjpG6xR8-WtQE1GwowLiM3yA" target="_blank">http://gosms.goforandroid.com</a><br>- Email to us: <a href="mailto:gomessanger@gmail.com">gomessanger@gmail.com</a><br>- Visit our facebook: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.facebook.com/apps/application.php?id%3D178919808825035&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEljQ3MdcxTs7MB8Xxt9_Z81Xqm2w" target="_blank">http://www.facebook.com/apps/application.php?id=178919808825035</a><p>Thank you very much for your support.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jb.gosms.brdropbox', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/iDqk6h4mRbHL-ibH_lIaLqZWElvx68gmBzjToBT3hD-5EgeH9WKLvCKfPlTBswC_Bo45', 4.43, 'COMMUNICATION', 'Free', '100,000+', ''),
(575, 'com.maximussoft.cloudpipes', 'Cloudpipes for Dropbox', 'MaximusSoft', 'Cloudpipes is a versatile Dropbox automation tool.<p>Cloudpipes has a <br>- powerful Dropbox file manager<br>- powerful scheduler<p><b>What it can do</b><br>It can be used for file organisation, backup or automate file transfers. You can send or receive files from the cloud seamlessly whenever you want.<p>You can manage your media by scheduling an upload of your Camera folder, or downloading your mp3 playlist every morning.<p>Also, contains a powerful Dropbox browser that can upload/download whole folders at once!<p><b>How it works</b><br>You create pipes that link a remote dropbox folder to a folder on your device. From here you can upload or download files at a given time. You can schedule the transfers when you want.<p><b>Features</b><br> - Custom pipes! Direct your files to where you want to!<br> - Scheduler<br> - File filter (filter which files to transfer)<br> - Power aware (transfer on WiFi or on charge)<br> - Bandwidth aware (does revision checking on files)<br> - Runs in background without consuming extra processing<br> - Notifications<br> - Integration<br> - Dropbox browser with Folder upload/download capabilities<br> - Starts on boot<p><b>Usage suggestions</b><br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://cloudpipes.wordpress.com/usage-suggestions/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGWpzlWybFm1JUVPDnJ8CDIfD3PfA" target="_blank">http://cloudpipes.wordpress.com/usage-suggestions/</a><p><b>Limitations</b><br>The Dropbox API limits the maximum file upload size to 150 MB.<p>Support the developer by buying the eXTenDeD version of Cloudpipes.<p>Please report issues to <a href="mailto:cloudpipes@gmail.com">cloudpipes@gmail.com</a> so that the app can be improved.<p><b>Disclaimer</b><br>Please be aware that the developer takes no responsibility for loss of data or any other implications.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.maximussoft.cloudpipes', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/tsBoV6bKIDO8cb_qe311FDMmOuMNn1EUcJ09L7JCjGvT_cUmVHtl22rGJjPgY7um-A', 4.30, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '10,000+', 'android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, com.android.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, com.maximussoft.cloudpipes.permission.ACCESS_DATA'),
(576, 'jp.sblo.pandora.jota.plus.dropbox', 'Jota+ Dropbox Connector', 'Aquamarine Networks.', 'Jota+ Dropbox Connector is a plugin to connect Jota+ with Dropbox.<p>Install this plugin then you can activate the connectivity to Dropbox of Jota+.<p>This app only connect to Dropbox server.<p>Jota+ Dropbox Connector includes Dropbox SDK for Android.<br>----------------------------<br>This app needs Jota+ and Jota+?PRO-KEY.<p>----------------------------<br>How to use connector.<br>- Touch &#39;Open&#39; on the toolbar then file selector will open.<br>- On top of the selector screen, there is &quot;SD CARD&quot; label.<br>- Click it and select &quot;Settings&quot;.<br>- Select one which you want and install a connector.<br>- Login to the connector.<br>- Again on selector screen, touch &quot;SD CARD&quot;.<br>- Click the name of the connector.<br>- Browse directory on the file system.<br>- Open a file.<p>Don&#39;t use explorer apps.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.sblo.pandora.jota.plus.dropbox', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/r-en4531jVb0IWJEVpdLHHttaeQW-J__q7SZGXT4TJQrFoU5oUsoh1RS8yj1w9oIbTo', 4.36, 'TOOLS', 'Free', '10,000+', 'jp.sblo.pandora.jota.FILE_ACCESS'),
(577, 'com.snapwood.dropfolio', 'dFolio - Dropbox Photos HD', 'Snapwood Apps', 'dFolio is a fast and modern photo gallery and uploader for Dropbox that excels at offline viewing.  View and slideshow photos even when you do not have a network connection.  Instantly upload and backup your shots to Dropbox.<br> <br>.: Show Off :.<br>Present your photos in a fast and beautiful interface.  The photos are sized for your device, so enjoy extra high resolution photos on tablets.  View full screen slideshows for one folder across all of your folders.  If you have Android 4.2, enable Daydreams to run slideshows when you dock or charge your device.<br> <br>.: Easily Upload Your Pictures :.<br>Batch upload full resolution pictures in the background while you do other things.  Simply share photos or videos from your gallery with dFolio to upload them to Dropbox.  Turn auto uploads on to automatically upload photos and videos to your folders.<br> <br>.: Features :.<br>· Fast offline access to your photos<br>· Clean interface that looks great on phones and tablets<br>· Full screen slideshows by folder or across all folders<br>· Multiselect to copy, move, delete, and share multiple photos at a time<br>· Play videos<br>· Upload multiple photos and videos at at time<br>· Auto upload photos and videos<br>· Hide folders from the app<br>· Pinch to zoom<br>· Set pictures as wallpaper<br>· Share pictures using email, Facebook, and Twitter<br>· Control slideshow interval and randomization<br>· Automatically set full screen brightness when viewing photos<br>· Change storage location to external SD card (or any folder)', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.snapwood.dropfolio', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/twLHwicUL0vk2evH7cscP6D2Klh3CadrrcZU4rd0LM55XNQxBTrmIgmgB1P_xchyVfE', 4.38, 'PHOTOGRAPHY', '$2.99', '1,000+', 'android.permission.SET_WALLPAPER, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED'),
(578, 'com.doublecore.musicdropnplay', 'MusicDropNPlay for Dropbox', 'DoubleCore Mobile', 'Dropbox Music player Drop your music to Dropbox and play it anywhere! (mp3/m4a)<p>Do you have an android phone? And do you listen to the Music on your phone? And are you tired of copying songs from your computer to your phone via USB cable? If the answer is yes, then MusicDropNPlay can simplify your life.<p>For additional product information, follow us on Twitter <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://twitter.com/%23!/MusicDropNPlay&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNE5IOW_nR0bBLu30Z3Zrhxev6PMew" target="_blank">https://twitter.com/#!/MusicDropNPlay</a> and Facebook <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.facebook.com/pages/MusicDropNPlay/223220167792633&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGFr-PXvULgT-2z0lliNCwraKmMwA" target="_blank">http://www.facebook.com/pages/MusicDropNPlay/223220167792633</a>.<p>If you have not used Dropbox, Dropbox is a free cloud service which allows you to bring all your photos, docs and music anywhere. You can upload your music to your Dropbox account from your computer and MusicDropNPlay can stream and playback it on your android device. No need to copy songs via the cable anymore. To learn more about Dropbox, please check www.dropbox.com.<p>MusicDropNPlay allows you to stream mp3/m4a songs directly from your Dropbox account in real-time. It has extra features normal players don&#39;t have:<p>• Real time streaming - no need to download the song completely before playing it.<br>• Artist and album artwork downloads to give you extra visual enjoyment.<br>• Group songs by artist or album names to find your favour songs at your fingertips.<br>• One button press to add all the songs from a folder you select.<br>• Support different cache sizes up to 8G (2000 songs).<br>• A user-friendly Dropbox file explorer letting you select the songs you want to listen.<br>• Ability to seek to any position, which may not be even buffered.<br>• A sleek playlist widget making sorting and reordering so easy.<br>• Online and offline modes making sure you have music to listen wherever you go even there is no network coverage.<br>• Headset in-line remote control support keeping your phone in the pocket all the time.<br>• Quick download feature - a shortcut to download all the songs in one shot so you can go offline mode afterwards to save either bandwidth or survive network outage.<p>MusicDropNPlay: drop music anywhere and play music anytime! Your ultimate Dropbox music player on your Android phone!<br>Find it on Google Android Market:<br>Lite Version: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.doublecore.musicdropnplaylite <br>Full Version: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.doublecore.musicdropnplay', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.doublecore.musicdropnplay', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/OjcTfvmchRwhSCq6jUjapUIl2kpcPM84NjHs4NmSOBbeNxPS_5117n3L20rK4o6rgbE9', 3.64, 'MUSIC_AND_AUDIO', '$2.99', '1,000+', 'com.android.vending.CHECK_LICENSE, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS'),
(579, 'com.dolphin.addons.dropbox', 'Dolphin: Dropbox Add-on', 'Dolphin Add-ons', 'Upload your download files in Dolphin to your Dropbox and bring them anywhere on the go. With Dropbox for Dolphin, you can:<br>1.Connect Dolphin with your Dropbox<br>2.Upload your download files in Dolphin to your Dropbox automatically and easily<br>3.Access your Dolphin downloads anywhere in Dropbox<p>Dropbox for Dolphin is an exclusive Add-on for Dolphin Browser. Just search Dolphin Browser in Android Market or download here: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://bit.ly/D-Android&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGBWH-xDzc7tiBNJuDsBRK2bFvNRw" target="_blank">http://bit.ly/D-Android</a><p>What is an Add-on?<br>Beef up your Dolphin Browser by installing your favorite Add-ons. Similar to a desktop Plug-in, each  <br>Add-on will provides additional functionality on mobile device. <p>Forgot password? <br>Password Manager can help. <p>Want a new look for your Dolphin? <br>Download Shiny Shake to change colors. <p>Want to read a webpage in French? <br>Get Dolphin Translate. Click here to learn more: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://bit.ly/AndroidAdd-onList&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHgq5tOdbxfSRMFsew_Szmb0nmEEQ" target="_blank">http://bit.ly/AndroidAdd-onList</a><p>Other popular Dolphin Add-ons: <br>• Dolphin Webzine<br>• Box for Dolphin<br>• Dolphin.fm<br>• Dolphin QRCode Share<br>• Bookmark to SD<br>• Dolphin YouTube Search<br>• Dolphin eBay Search<br>• Dolphin Alexa Rank<br>• Web to PDF<br>• Dolphin Brightness<br>• Dolphin Password Manager Lite<br>• Password Manager Pro<br>• Lastpass for Dolphin Browser <br>• Xmarks for Dolphin <br>• Dolphin Reader<br>• Softpedia.com RSS<br>• Dolphin Screen Cut<br>• Bookmarks Widget<br>• Dolphin Desktop Toggle<p>We love hearing from you. Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@dolphin.com">support@dolphin.com</a> and rate us today!<br>Join Dolphin Facebook Fan page: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.facebook.com/DolphinFans&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNE4Fzogban6uL_jJ0XrYVakeRJMWQ" target="_blank">http://www.facebook.com/DolphinFans</a> <br>Follow Dolphin on Twitter: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://twitter.com/%23!/DolphinBrowser&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFgG2dMF-aP1ZyQNx_ItzuwiItxXA" target="_blank">https://twitter.com/#!/DolphinBrowser</a><br>Website: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.dolphin.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGCUFSV1BZL0B3udQPwPpIMfYoV1Q" target="_blank">http://www.dolphin.com/</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dolphin.addons.dropbox', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/u4RyXH_exkjQpAvbG-pF3mQ202SBnSlG2AvRthJkpPAXev-cz1ecPXjpTp-CLDgAfGU', 4.39, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '10,000+', 'com.android.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, com.dolphin.browser.permission.Addon');
