(580, 'com.anttek.remote.cloud', 'Dropbox / Box.net Client', 'AntTek', 'AntTek Dropbox /Box.net Client is a plugin for AntTek Explorer<p><b>Notice:</b><br>- Must install AntTek File Explorer to use this plugin. (Play store: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://bit.ly/anttekexplorer&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEUweFofZq6WNW5NXbpzcBrygn1TQ" target="_blank">http://bit.ly/anttekexplorer</a>)<br>- No icon on your launcher. <p><b>Features:</b><br>- Easy to configure<br>- Seamlessly browse Dropbox/Box.net storage<br>- Streaming music, video from server<br>- View image, document (pdf, doc) inline<br>- AntTek Explorer is a free Drag &amp; Drop anywhere file explorer with custom panel layouts', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.anttek.remote.cloud', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/kKST8bNhWrCbWMhyMkEaXGm5xiSZWZQdbLSmppz6K84rKR-1EVAr2LFG0p4Fb7MIxQ', 4.48, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '50,000+', ''),
(581, 'jp.co.kayo.android.localplayer.ds.dropbox', 'Dropbox Music Provider', 'yokmama', 'This is a plugin that allows you to use Dropbox from JustPlayer.<br>Please install the first JustPlayer.<p>ogg vorbis supported.<br>streaming video.<p>https://market.android.com/details?id=jp.co.kayo.android.localplayer', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.kayo.android.localplayer.ds.dropbox', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/YJYO6YSJ7e-gGOnWHsMfsh43xVn0xMh41bnbkTjm30Y3egFnIGQPgSS2Roa9_iCJuOs', 4.41, 'COMMUNICATION', 'Free', '10,000+', ''),
(582, 'com.rainy.syncboxlite', 'Wifi Dropbox Lite', 'Gábor Szántó', '!!!DOWNLOAD THE SERVER HERE: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://egeszsegtars.hu/syncbox&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEh9HrsGMx-xsEySVDvE8yaJeR42g" target="_blank">http://egeszsegtars.hu/syncbox</a> !!! If the app isn&#39;t working, try to turn off your firewall temporarily.<p>Wifi Dropbox (SyncBox) is a sync application, similar to Dropbox, but it uses WiFi to transfer data, so there&#39;s no unnecessary 3G data traffic, thus it&#39;s faster, and more reliable. The files ARE NOT copied to any cloud storage, so the data directly goes from the Phone to the PC or vice-versa. This is the easiest way to share your data between your PC and your Android device. It is designed to easily copy your music, pictures, videos, or any other file onto the phone, or VICE-VERSA. The transfer can run completely in the background if you want, and you can open your files immediately with the built-in file browser. The software comes with a nice widget. If you want to start the app, connect to the PC, and sync, you just click the widget and it all does the job at once.<p>For example: you sync your Phone&#39;s camera folder to your PC&#39;s Pictures folder. If you take a picture with the phone, that pictures is going to be automatically copied to your PC.<p>This is a lite (free) version of SyncBox, it is limited, you can manage only 1 folder, and ad-enabled. For full version, please visit https://market.android.com/details?id=com.rainy.syncbox', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.rainy.syncboxlite', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/XCoq63y--0XyL7n3a7vPaS5XoRTo2-A2HbCLoy5vFP6ZkbKTd6d1dTw8mHevwtFOW9nm', 4.17, 'TOOLS', 'Free', '10,000+', 'android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE'),
(583, 'com.rainy.syncbox', 'Wifi Dropbox Pro', 'Gábor Szántó', '!!!DOWNLOAD THE SERVER HERE: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://egeszsegtars.hu/syncbox&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEh9HrsGMx-xsEySVDvE8yaJeR42g" target="_blank">http://egeszsegtars.hu/syncbox</a> !!! If the app isn&#39;t working, try to turn off your firewall temporarily.<p>Wifi Dropbox (SyncBox) is a sync application, similar to Dropbox, but it uses WiFi to transfer data, so there&#39;s no unnecessary 3G data traffic, thus it&#39;s faster, and more reliable. The files ARE NOT copied to any cloud storage, so the data only goes from the Phone to the PC or vice-versa. This is the easiest way to share your data between your PC and your Android device. It is designed to easily copy your music, pictures, videos, or any other file onto the phone, or VICE-VERSA. The transfer can run completely in the background if you want, and you can open your files immediately with the built-in file browser. The software comes with a nice widget. If you want to start the app, connect to the PC, and sync, you just click the widget and it all does the job at once.<p>For example: you sync your Phone&#39;s camera folder to your PC&#39;s Pictures folder. If you take a picture with the phone, that picture is going to be automatically copied to your PC.<p>This app, SyncBox Pro, is ad-free, fast, and you can enjoy all options in the program. The client is free, but in order to make this app work, you have to download the server version for $1.99. You can download the server version here: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://egeszsegtars.hu/syncbox/ipn.php?buy&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNG4J8ide18zKNWMeaKa06JSibYedQ" target="_blank">http://egeszsegtars.hu/syncbox/ipn.php?buy</a><p>If you have any questions, please feel free to ask: <a href="mailto:szantogab@gmail.com">szantogab@gmail.com</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.rainy.syncbox', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/2dejQGxyMHR0txX9PN0av50hPEJ63Wuzsb-FQE5YmVfEgfbxiqPYoIxxzGYRur3EZA', 4.22, 'TOOLS', 'Free', '5,000+', 'android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE'),
(584, 'os.devwom.smanager.dropbox', 'SManager Dropbox addon', 'devwom', 'Script Manager - SManager Dropbox module<br>Allow browse Dropbox files using SManager Main Application<br>SManager 2.6 is needed', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=os.devwom.smanager.dropbox', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/jbcjFfWCW_mDbi3BP9G3eS5s7IeM6bLtig-yx4UzUt90At6S88S-h4ovsJwJP61Z31ke', 4.49, 'TOOLS', 'Free', '5,000+', ''),
(585, 'com.nobeid.androiddropboxnotifications', 'Android Dropbox Notifications', 'GooglyEyes', 'Android Dropbox Notifications (ADN) uses your Dropbox account to synchronize and maintain in an HTML file the last 10 notifications you receive on your Android device. You will never miss again important notifications because your phone was in silent mode, in your desk drawer or out of reach…<p><br>Features:<br>- Enable/Disable synchronization.<br>- Sanity check: reinitialize the HTML file on your Dropbox account in case of deletion, conflicted copies or any other malfunctioning.<br>- Filter notifications: choose the applications you want to be notified of on you Dropbox account.<br>- Volume restriction: choose if you want notifications to be synchronized only when your phone is in silent mode.<br>- Display restriction: choose if you want notifications to be synchronized only when your screen is off.<br>- Notification style: switch between three different notification styles.<br>      1- HTML + CSS: Default and recommended style.<br>      2- HTML only: For those who want to apply their own CSS or looking for a simpler look.<br>      3- TEXT: Plain text file for purists and bandwidth savers.<p><br>!! IMPORTANT !!<br>Android Dropbox Notifications (ADN) must be enabled in ACCESSIBILITY to be able to read notification content. ACCESSIBILITY can be accessed from your phone settings or directly from ADN.<p><br>Privacy Settings:<br>- We respect your privacy. We won’t use your Dropbox ID and E-mail address for other than in-app display purposes.<br>- We won’t use (read, store, share, publish, sell, etc.) your personal data e.g. Notification Content in any other way that is not stated in the application description.<br>- We might display some paid advertisement in the application, which may lead you to some external website. We are not responsible for the content of the external website.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nobeid.androiddropboxnotifications', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/H_p93QRfE59w5eRO9EqSrE3uIl18pUX_afbJT1D9BHzLeWs7v-EJ7OwYD5LTKK3Rfw', 4.58, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '1,000+', ''),
(586, 'com.andromo.dev16335.app34531', 'Dropbox Invitations', 'Blue King', 'Share your dropbox invitations with the world and get more dropbox space.<p>Join dropbox using the links in this app and start with a 2.25  GB free online storage.<p>Post your invites and expand your dropbox space up to 10 GB.<p>Check out our facebook page at <br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.facebook.com/DropboxShareInvitations?sk%3Dwall&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNF4K-_lXrEuT9b-7LFA4GXGFIxZiw" target="_blank">http://www.facebook.com/DropboxShareInvitations?sk=wall</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.andromo.dev16335.app34531', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/zQL0OU1K_NFS3a_6plzPVBhYPz8qvroQ1xtDzZJA4ZiJg6rga18Y-PbCWz3wFcQ38g', 4.29, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '1,000+', ''),
(587, 'com.lidroid.fileexplorer.dropbox', 'DropBox for Lidroid File', 'lidroid', 'Well, if you are a Dropbox user, of course you know how convenient it is, let alone the safety it offers to your files. But in the past you may be able to view and manage all your files stored there, but what if you want to take a look inside of a video or listen to a music file so you can put them into the right archive? No, you can not really do that. You will have to download them locally to know the content. And sometimes the slow internet speed just got you stuck and desperate.<p>Now with Lidroid file plugin for Dropbox installed, it will be a totally different story. Now You can watch videos, listen to audios and view pictures stored there directly without downloading them to the local. You can also enjoy those basic file management functions like visiting, uploading and downloading and managing your files. It enables you to enjoy unlimited convenience and it is very easy to install and operate. Now you do not need to waste your time on waiting for the files to be downloaded any more. It’s all because of this revolutionary change that Lidroid file brings to you. <p>This plugin can not be used independently. It is an attachment program of Lidroid File. If you are not a Lidroid File user yet, please search for it on Google Play and install and then enjoy the function this plugin offers. Lidroid file will load the plugins you installed automatically.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.lidroid.fileexplorer.dropbox', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/6E1RoolcXcE1NH7s3KQJgjCTFIRweFxz9qdUhRIsfXDS9C-gEQVKmsOjv93XIuSaioc', 4.65, 'TOOLS', 'Free', '1,000+', ''),
(588, 'com.ttxapps.dropsync.pro', 'Dropsync PRO Key', 'ttxapps', '<b>This is a license key to unlock PRO features in Dropsync app. Once the key app is downloaded and installed, PRO features will be unlocked. Please keep the free Dropsync app installed.</b><p>Keep your phone/tablet and your Dropbox in sync at all times. Rock-solid, battery efficient, full two-way(!) sync client for Dropbox.<p>&quot;Just like the desktop version of Dropbox, Dropsync supports true two-way data synchronization.&quot; --New York Times<p>&quot;Take a picture on your phone and watch as it’s already waiting for you on your laptop when you get home.&quot; --phandroid .com<p>&quot;I bought 5 other apps like this one, but this is the only one that didn&#39;t crash while synchronizing my large Photo &amp; Video folder&quot; --Dropsync user<p>&quot;Must have app. Now my phone - computer - tablet are one!&quot; --Dropsync user<p><b>FEATURES INCLUDE</b><p>? Full two-way sync. Just like Dropbox on desktop<br>? Instant upload: new files (for example photos) are uploaded to Dropbox immediately<br>? Very efficient, consumes almost no battery if there is no change detected and will not slow down your phone either<br>? Very easy to set up. Once set up files will be kept in sync without any effort from users<br>? Works reliably under ever changing network conditions on your phone<br>? Monitors battery level, WiFi/3G/4G/WiMax connectivity and adapts its behavior according to user preferences<br>? Configurable autosync interval: 15 minutes, 30 minutes, every hour,...<br>? Tasker/Locale plugin to allow power users to define sophisticated sync schedules and conditions<br>? Many sync modes. Not only two-way, you can also choose Upload only, Upload then delete, Download only, Download mirror,...<br>? Compact code size, memory efficient, no fancy graphics, no useless animation. We have enough bloatware. Do one thing and do it best<p>Beware that there are many apps out there on the Market which claim doing sync but in fact what they do is one-way dumb upload or download.<p>Dropsync provides the essential feature, two-way sync, which should be in the official Dropbox for Android since the beginning. For whatever reason it wasn&#39;t and still isn&#39;t. Now you have it.<p><b>PRO FEATURES INCLUDE</b><p>? Sync multiple folders<br>? Sync the whole Dropbox with a folder on your phone or tablet<br>? Upload large files, from 10 MB to several GB<br>? Smart Change Detection. Super fast method to determine file changes that need to be synced<br>? No ads<p>KW: Dropbox sync, Dropbox backup, media sync, music sync, photo sync, file sync, folder sync, full two-way sync, instant upload, Tasker plugin, Locale plugin, Locale plug-in', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ttxapps.dropsync.pro', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/5_ZedTNmIX3jlGq2SXYpbvQyxacX6mxWwlkCE2-loP2HMLuIDJgEpsR2Bbfd78lkVdM', 4.80, 'PRODUCTIVITY', '$4.99', '50,000+', 'com.android.vending.CHECK_LICENSE'),
(589, 'sts.pl', 'Pocket Legends', 'Spacetime Games', 'Play the world&#39;s FIRST and LARGEST mobile MMO Pocket Legends! In this groundbreaking, fantasy game you&#39;ll join millions of players from around the world on wild adventures in creepy dungeons, frigid mountain peaks, and steamy swamps. <p>Massively: Best Smartphone Game 2011<br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://massively.joystiq.com/2011/12/28/free-for-all-the-first-annual-frindie-awards/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGk2SFgu4sTBdOnaTXkZ86UcvYf8Q" target="_blank">http://massively.joystiq.com/2011/12/28/free-for-all-the-first-annual-frindie-awards/</a><p>&quot;A true Legend in its own time&quot; - Ten Ton Hammer<p>&quot;Must have game for Android&quot; - MSNBC<p>&quot;Highly recommended&quot; - Yahoo! Games<p>Pocket Legends is a FREE online, multiplayer, fantasy adventure and 3D Massively-Multiplayer Online Role Playing Game (MMORPG). This smash hit made it&#39;s debut on the iPad and continues to be a fan favorite where players take on the role of a bear, hawk, or an elf and strive to save the world of Alterra from zombies, crocs, aliens, and more! <p>Play online with friends in fast-paced Co-Op or PVP action. As you defeat enemies and bring justice to the land, you will unlock special abilities that you may customize to suit your play style. During your travels, you will also find rare treasures and gear. <p>Play with anyone, anywhere, anytime!<p>Features:<br>+ Free to play forever<br>+ Unlock and customize class abilities <br>+ Thousands of Weapons, Items, and Gear<br>+ Multiplayer &amp; Solo – Play in Co-Op, PVP, or Solo Mode<br>+ Worldwide MMORPG – Play with Millions Online<br>+ Supports Arm-v7a, OS 2.2 or greater, and OpenGL ES 2.0 <br>+ Plays Across Wi-Fi, Edge, 3G or 4G Networks <p>Check Us Out At:<br>www.PocketLegends.com<p>Want More Info? Visit our Forum!<br>www.spacetimestudios.com/forum.php<p>Developer’s website:<br>www.spacetimestudios.com', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=sts.pl', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/6wPENd-biBUaSgzr_i-slj2SYy0Q6x0AX3FYREsXbHlmg_UUk3b1uP3-ffp8fk4NmlA', 4.52, 'ARCADE', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE, android.permission.INTERNET, android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE, android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.VIBRATE, sts.pl.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE'),
(590, 'jp.r246.twicca', 'twicca', 'Tetsuya Aoyama', 'twicca is Twitter™ Client for Android™.<p>Features:<br>* Notification<br>* Auto pager<br>* Search<br>* Post with photo upload<br>* Shorten URL<br>* Geo tagging<br>* Saved searches<br>* Recent hashtags<br>* Reply history<br>* Lists<br>* Retweet<br>* Color label<br>* Managing twitter profile<br>* Trending topics<br>* Local trends<br>* Extending function by plug-in<br>* Widget<br>* Uploading profile icon<br>* Report for spam<br>* Block user<br>* Image Preview<br>* Geotagging with map preview<br>* Tweet filtering(Mute)<p>Experimental features:<br>* Multiple account support.<br>* Launch from status bar<br>* twitpic video preview<br>* New line<br>----<p>twicca is looking for supporters for the future development and maintenance. For more information, menu -&gt; more -&gt; twicca supporters.<p>----<p>* If you install to external storage, you might not be able to use some features.<p>* If widget is something wrong, please delete it and put new widget to home again.<p>* Please see <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://dev.twitter.com/terms/display-requirements&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEFkuQLTgixqNwLS1cUlsygFq97PQ" target="_blank">https://dev.twitter.com/terms/display-requirements</a><p>Twitter: @twicca_en', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.r246.twicca', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/xF3hmKNu0fduPKyJKSO1qgc8XgAOqgtJ8w9DEfaKMeF6eKiucrFCRXahI-7GSF-DcNI', 4.45, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, com.android.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.NFC'),
(591, 'com.bari_ikutsu.twiccaPlugin.multiImageUploader', 'twicca multi image plugin', 'Eiichi YOSHIKAWA', '***Please describe model of your phone and image service when you leave a comment about failure of upload. ***<p>***If you have trouble about uploading image, please try to re-authenticate. ***<p>***If you cannot solve problems about this plugin, please contact to Twitter @edo_bari_ikutsu. English or Japanese is welcome.***<p>***This plugin is only responsible for &quot;uploading&quot; image. Displaying image from your Twitter timeline is a function of twicca itself. If you have troubles about displaying image, please contact to twicca author. ***<p>This is a plugin of &quot;twicca&quot;, a Twitter client run on Android. By using this plugin, you can upload your image to Twitpic, yfrog, img.ly, Mobypicture or Twipple selectively.<p>* Current version supports landscape screen orientation.<p>* Due to limitation of twicca plugin specification, twitter authentication for this plugin is required besides for twicca itself.  It is not password sniffing.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bari_ikutsu.twiccaPlugin.multiImageUploader', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/koyaBNkiCPHBRAMQ9Jgl2aqfSYIuu38_TAwX4Ip03vBHTTZfSqQcbXuSAoaYTSZzBdc', 4.23, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '100,000+', ''),
(592, 'jp.mstssk.twiccaplugins.draft', 'Draft plug-in for twicca', 'mstssk', 'You can save draft tweets with this plugin on twicca!<p>* This plug-in author is @mstssk. Please do not make a inquiry concerning this plug-in the author of twicca.<p>How to use:<br>Touch ? button on Tweet view, then select &quot;List saved...&quot; or &quot;Save...&quot;.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.mstssk.twiccaplugins.draft', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/iowyiQinw4LWsQgvVRlwitEUJ0qyleWLtTNZZ42oSyO8ipI-XsEHI4DeeFy400jeDzg', 4.57, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '50,000+', ''),
(593, 'jp.r246.twiccaplugins.favotter', 'favotter plug-in for twicca', 'Tetsuya Aoyama', 'This is favotter plug-in for twicca.<p>favotter is popular twitter service in Japan. This plug-in open user page of favotter.net in your browser from twicca. You can see favorited tweets information.<p><br>This application needs &quot;twicca&quot; 0.7.31 or above.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.r246.twiccaplugins.favotter', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/pb8MGs7-awUJGmjlpUcQ3ARmarQ0QeFB_dpUT4bLoI-6eDmpZnzp1MtUtWOxoEcVPogf', 4.16, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '50,000+', ''),
(594, 'jp.r246.twiccaplugins.twitpic', 'twitpic plug-in for twicca', 'Tetsuya Aoyama', 'This application is twitpic upload plug-in for twicca.<p>This application needs &quot;twicca&quot;.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.r246.twiccaplugins.twitpic', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/zYMip47yBCpGitoEAuq4pafEZCTSi80m6sPXTurUxh92WQE7qb6mdYNJ9RlV9ry2VQ', 4.27, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '100,000+', ''),
(595, 'jp.r246.twiccaplugins.favstarfm', 'favstar.fm plug-in for twicca', 'Tetsuya Aoyama', 'This is favstar.fm plug-in for twicca.<p>This plug-in open favstar.fm in your browser from twicca. You can see favorited tweets information.<p>This application needs &quot;twicca&quot; 0.7.31 or above.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.r246.twiccaplugins.favstarfm', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/XKdU4LjJIaxzYXYdx2AdxcEo-C-ShEOnzG6GXO3na_DqB5A753Txi1wCnL1H74MlGuBM', 4.43, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '50,000+', ''),
