(617, 'chrome.icon.pack', 'Icon Pack - Chrome', 'Stealthychief', '<h2><b>Features</b></h2> <p>• 2,000+ HD Icons! (1,000+ icons of each style - background and no background)<br>• 2 Wallpapers<br>• Supports automatic apply and manual apply of icons<br>• Multiple launcher support (see below)<br>• Weekly updates every Friday<br>• Theme dashboard with several features (Including Request Icons and New Icons) <p><h2><b>Supported Launchers</b></h2> <p>• Nova Launcher<br>• Apex Launcher<br>• Action Launcher<br>• ADW Launcher<br>• GO Launcher<br>• Next Launcher 3D (Manual apply only. Jellybean users please email us for a fix.)<br>• TSF Shell<br>• Holo Launcher<br>• Unicorn (Icon Themer)<br>• Desktop Visualizer<br>• May work with other launchers and applications but this is not guaranteed.<p><h2><b>Theme Details</b></h2> <p>This is an icon pack with a dark style with a chrome effect. If you love dark icons or black icons then this is the icon pack for you!<p><h2><b>Support</b></h2><p>Please email us if you have any questions regarding this theme and we&#39;ll be happy to help! For icon requests, please use the Request Icons feature available within the Chrome application. Feel free to contact us on any of the social outlets listed below as well!<p>Google + : <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://plus.google.com/u/0/105194414710791941012/posts&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHJPtPoLA8N5-l_hN_363U20jxKEQ" target="_blank">http://plus.google.com/u/0/105194414710791941012/posts</a><br>Twitter : <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.twitter.com/Stealthychief&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEfrqpeohEbp-bzy2UQJCs5bJ2k_g" target="_blank">http://www.twitter.com/Stealthychief</a><br>Facebook : <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.facebook.com/Stealthychief&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHoL9br3Y2WknKOX2hjPeKSPC19VQ" target="_blank">http://www.facebook.com/Stealthychief</a><br>Website : <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.stealthychief.com&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNG1T1wN1iL