(618, 'com.gau.go.launcherex.theme.redchrome', 'Red Chrome Go Launcher Theme', 'Jaap Heijligers', 'This theme now has it&#39;s own GO Locker theme! Quick, take a look! <p>If you like the theme, please have a look at the premium blue version: &#39;Chromeberry Go Launcher Theme&#39;, thanks!<p>-&lt; Introduction &gt;-<br>Red Chrome, the red version of Chromeberry, is a dark red chrome Go Launcher EX Theme.<br>The theme covers: interface, app drawer, folders, dock icons and 4 wallpapers.<p>-&lt; How to install &gt;-<p>The GO Launcher EX launcher is required for this theme to work. It can be downloaded for free in the android market.<p>To apply this theme:<br>1. Download &amp; Install<br>2. Open theme through the Play Store<br>3. Enjoy<p>-&lt; Technical support &gt;-<br>You can always see your installed themes here: MENU -&gt; Themes -&gt; Installed<p>To apply additional wallpapers:<br>Menu -&gt; Wallpapers -&gt; GO Wallpapers -&gt; choose!<p>If something is not working, please send me a mail. Either I&#39;ll help you or you&#39;ll help me.<p>About permissions: I use a program of the GO dev Team to create themes, they choose which permissions are in it and how the theme apps work.<p><br>-&lt; Important &gt;-<br>Comments are appreciated<br>Thank you all for downloading!<p><p>Q&amp;A<p>Q: Is this a virus?<br>A: No.<p>Q: Why does this need the (...) permission?<br>A: GO Launcher needs all asked permissions.<p>Q: Are you an evil professor hiding in an underground lab collecting all my data to infringe my privacy?<br>A: No.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gau.go.launcherex.theme.redchrome', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/wPBgyy3t8UpT4QyZ6q6qw8QjgE-JF58tLdu9_l-1tXvNYpD84ox4cSyCMxdc0czTp98s', 4.53, 'PERSONALIZATION', 'Free', '50,000+', 'android.permission.CHANGE_COMPONENT_ENABLED_STATE, com.android.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT'),
(619, 'net.the4thdimension.chromecheatsheet', 'Chrome Developer Cheatsheet', 'The4D', 'This is NOT Chrome browser. Especially for Chrome extension,add-on or apps Developers.<p>A reference guide to passionate Google Chrome extensions/themes/Apps developers. This guide lists all the attributes of manifest.json file used in developing an extension for Google&#39;s Chrome platform.<p>Chrome Developer Cheatsheet serves as a powerful tool for offline access to the Chrome extension&#39;s manifest file&#39;s fields and their summary.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.the4thdimension.chromecheatsheet', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/eakdgXmvJZzXhxx66KJeXgFYcORfJFeMkvYos44OODrhXd0EHEQgytndffu3hw59YfY', 4.48, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '10,000+', '');
