(638, 'air.com.seedlabs.xgames', 'ESPN X Games', 'ESPN Inc', 'The ESPN X Games app for Android puts the world’s premier action sports events right at your fingertips, making it easier than ever to watch highlights, view schedules, track scores and keep up with the global expansion of the X Games to six events per year. Don’t forget to check out the HypeMeter, an interactive game that lets you contribute to the worldwide excitement around a trick, athlete or event. This FREE app is a must-have for X Games fans everywhere.<p>FEATURES<p>- Video Highlights: Watch the best runs, tricks, and clips from X Games, then share them quickly and easily with your friends<p>- Instant Results: Gold, silver, bronze and everything else – all right there on your device<p>- News: Get the inside scoop on X Games happenings while keeping up with breaking news from around the world of action sports<p>- Schedules: Calendars for every X Games event, whether you plan to attend in person or watch from home on your TV, tablet or mobile phone<p>- Real Series Bracket: Use the X Games app to watch and compare clips from the Real Series video contests throughout the year. Don’t forget to vote!<p>- Athlete Bios: Everything you’ve ever wanted to know about your favorite X Games athletes<p>- Guest Info: Navigate X Games venues, find parking info, take advantage of X Fest and learn about other X Games services', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.seedlabs.xgames', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/6A9GTdIfYs7EhqlOsTg4s0fsESj95empFeExAvkmcCGdGShJTpRtnRnJW6M4zqf-n_o', 4.46, 'SPORTS', 'Free', '10,000+', 'android.permission.BROADCAST_STICKY, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED'),
