(643, 'com.jacobsmedia.KIROAM', '710 ESPN Seattle', 'Bonneville International', 'A re-imagined listening experience for 710 ESPN Seattle fans. Listen to live talk shows, on-demand moments, and customized audio streams on your iPhone, iPad, or iPod touch. <p>710 ESPN Seattle is the radio home of the Seattle Seahawks and Seattle Mariners, in addition to a wide variety of local and syndicated sports talk programming. Local hosts include the dynamic team of Brock Huard and Mike Salk, Dave &quot;The Groz&quot; Grosby and Bob Stelton, Jim Moore and John Clayton. 710 ESPN Seattle also offers unique perspectives through a variety of &#39;Sports Insiders,&#39; local celebrity athletes and Sports reporters. <p>LISTEN <br>- The latest Seattle Sports news and opinion <br>- Your favorite 710 ESPN Seattle talk shows live and on-demand; Brock and Salk, Bob and Groz, Jim Moore, John Clayton, The Outdoor Line and more. <p>WATCH <br>- Watch all local 710 ESPN Seattle shows live in-studio <p>ON-DEMAND <br>- Podcast episodes of all 710 ESPN Seattle shows <br>- Create a playlist of your favorite 710 ESPN Seattle highlights, features and interviews <p>INTERACT <br>- Connect with the shows live on-air <br>- Leave an audio message for your favorite host or show', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jacobsmedia.KIROAM', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/mIQ1-2dPPFbtgz0DtJxkvwOMmSaDKyrEMqh72dS_yaddhf3e44TdiXGdsWyvCj3JMNI', 3.18, 'SPORTS', 'Free', '10,000+', 'android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO'),
(644, 'com.espn.espnfantasyhockey', 'ESPN Fantasy Hockey', 'ESPN Inc', 'With the ESPN Fantasy Hockey app, you can manage multiple teams and leagues, follow your matchups in real-time, add/drop/trade players, and make last second line up changes from wherever you are. You’ll be one tap away from your teams and leagues, and one step ahead of your friends. <br> <br>With the ESPN Fantasy Hockey app you can:<br> <br>* Follow your head-to-head matchup or rotisserie scoring live with FantasyCast<br>* Get exclusive news, analysis, videos and the latest Tweets from ESPN fantasy experts<br>* Follow live NHL scores<br>* Start, bench, add, drop, and claim players off waivers and propose trades<br>* View and post messages to your league message board<br> <br>Download now because there’s no better time to check on your fantasy hockey teams than anytime you please.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.espn.espnfantasyhockey', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/G8hZnhmGcojI0lsPNKdsvNt5QMz2wtkOVYBIdhaxkfULpgmiFJZqIlfFPmnTBsuBkqfU', 4.17, 'SPORTS', 'Free', '10,000+', 'com.espn.espnfantasyhockey.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.READ_LOGS, android.permission.GET_TASKS'),
(645, 'com.talismanlbs.espnhnl', 'ESPN 1420 AM Honolulu', 'Talisman LBS, LLC', 'NOTICE: The App previously was unable to find the updated streaming server locations. Update 1.1.7 Has this Issue fix now. It should work and no longer loose the server locations.<p>ESPN Honolulu&#39;s official Android application.<p>Now you can listen to all your favorite sports broadcasts from ESPN 1420 AM on your Android powered mobile handset!   <p>Features:<p>*Shows Guide for broadcast times and descriptions.<p>*Radio player with task bar access while stream is playing.<p>*Share Photos with ESPN&#39;s Fan Cam.<p>*Quick access to ESPN&#39;s Facebook and Twitter posts.<p>*Find the local hottest deals on the islands.<p>Update v1.0.3<p>*Fixed crashes reported from the Deals section.<p>*Upgrades to the Deals section.<p>*Fixes to the player task bar notifier.<p>Update v1.0.4<p>*Fix a bug with Notification icon not displaying and current track not displaying properly for Android 2.3+ users.<p>*Fixed problem causing force close on player occasionally.<p>*Modified media player to improve buffering.<p>***If the player stops playing by itself, you can open the player with the task bar item at the top. There you can press play again or pause to remove the task bar item.***<p>Update v1.0.5<p>*I have added programming to fix the stream when it fades.<p>Update v1.0.6<p>*Location provider fixes for disabled states.<p>*Implemented auto scrolling text for overflowing text on all headers.<p>Update v1.0.7<p>*Fixed Map Bug in Deals section causing other locations to show.<p>*Fixed Radius select to scroll better.<p>*Added Deals Indicator on the media player screen when in range of local deals.<p>*Added fail safe for stream connection errors on some Android Versions (2.3.4 &amp; 2.3.5). This Depends on Model and Network Provider. If all attempts to connect fail, it will kick it to other media players on the Device.<p>Update v1.0.8<p>*Urgent fix for Promo Coupons<p>Update v1.0.9<p>*Fix a bug with Radius select not properly setting the Radius.<p>*Fixed issue with Top 10 deals getting locked out when coupons refresh in background.<p>v1.1.0<p>Fixed mislabeled areas.<p>v1.1.2<p>*Fixed issues with force close on previous update.<br>*Made additional fixes to help stream work correctly. You will no longer get stuck with the buffering message when you stop the stream.<p>*System performance updates.<br>*User Interface Updates.<br>*Bug Fixes.<p>v1.1.3<p>*Startup Sequence fix, should not hang when location providers are disabled.<p>*Radius settings fixed for better search results.<p>v1.1.4<p>*Fixed boot up stall when locations services are deactivated.<p>v1.1.5<p>*Fix Top 10 offers issue with loading properly in some cases. <p>*Fixed issue with some offers not loading properly in some cases.<p>v1.1.6<p>*Player will now pause for phone calls made or received. <p>*updated to support Android 4.2 tablets and phones<p>v.1.1.7<p>*Station Streaming is now FIX. It will now maintain updated server streaming locations so it should not ever go down again.<p>*User Interface Updates.<p>*Offer images that are zoomed will now be centered and maximized to the width of screen.<p>*Fixed issue with coupon book crash under a specific condition that was not easily found before.<p>*Fixes for GCM Services.<p>v1.1.8<p>*Minor graphic and labeling updates.<br>*Few minor bug fixes.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.talismanlbs.espnhnl', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/-u-7AijkI9P47xkf1M4qm4oAFdztfZUgucRBJpmNAWoNyxSufvq9PBDWFIRLxPK24g', 3.04, 'SPORTS', 'Free', '5,000+', 'android.permission.CALL_PHONE, android.permission.CAMERA, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, com.talismanlbs.espnhnl.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE'),
(646, 'com.espn.android.radio', 'ESPN 700 Radio', 'GraySky Technologies', 'Listen to ESPN 700 Sports, home of ESPN Radio, University of Utah Athletics, and ReAL Salt Lake Soccer.<p>This is a simple application allowing you to listen to the radio stream from your mobile device.  There is also a link to visit www.ESPN700Sports.com website along with buttons to call the station to talk to the host or email Bill Riley.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.espn.android.radio', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/lZBrZ8WLoCN-wEJylgLsoFrHF0TDeGg4QXj_FgK8lrsgPTSLv1xJlMppfubF84mUQV4', 2.70, 'SPORTS', 'Free', '5,000+', 'android.permission.CALL_PHONE'),
(647, 'com.facebook.pages.app', 'Facebook Pages Manager', 'Facebook', 'Pages Manager helps admins connect with their audience and keep up with activity on multiple Pages, all in one place.<p>• Post updates and photos and respond to comments as your Pages<br>• View and reply to private messages sent to your Pages<br>• Option to get push notifications for new activity, tips and reminders<br>• View your latest Page Insights<br>• Turn push notifications on or off for each Page<br>• Upload a photo to a specific album<br>• Attach a photo to a status update<br>• Change profile and cover photos<br>• Save a shortcut to a Page on your phone&#39;s home screen<br>• Share links from other apps to Pages Manager<br>• Post and promote at the same time<br>• Turn an external link into a share post<br>• Share photos from other apps<br>• Create an album<br>• Save a draft of a post<br>• Write posts on an Event<br>• Use bookmark links to see full-page Messages, Insights, Photos, Events and Activity Log<br>• To delete a comment or ban someone from your Page, just tap the comment<br>• Go to Settings to edit basic info and invite friends to like your Page<br>• Upload multiple photos for a single post<br>• Edit Page admins: add new admins for the Pages you manage<br>• Tag people in comments to build a deeper connection with the people that matter to you<br>• Keep up with updates from other relevant pages in Pages Feed<br>• Tag other Pages in sharing tool<br>• Tap on a person/Page to easily access their Timeline<br>• Edit comments<br>• Tap on push notifications to go to messages and posts<p>Now you can get early access to the next version of Facebook Pages Manager by becoming a beta tester. Learn how to sign up, give feedback and leave the program in our Help Center: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://fb.me/pages_beta&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNF7WaCO1Jj8dHR45182ysgcnBHzBA" target="_blank">http://fb.me/pages_beta</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.facebook.pages.app', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/ZRk2UiizqjMp20WMTgy8iRsULF5sqOwAb4ynEJso031aRBLhR5oAsqMHV-ZjEM-0FRcu', 4.05, 'BUSINESS', 'Free', '10,000,000+', 'com.facebook.katana.provider.ACCESS, com.facebook.wakizashi.provider.ACCESS, com.facebook.permission.prod.FB_APP_COMMUNICATION, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.CAMERA, com.android.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, com.facebook.pages.app.permission.CROSS_PROCESS_BROADCAST_MANAGER, com.sec.android.provider.badge.permission.READ, com.sec.android.provider.badge.permission.WRITE, com.htc.launcher.permission.UPDATE_SHORTCUT, com.htc.launcher.permission.READ_SETTINGS, com.sonyericsson.home.permission.BROADCAST_BADGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, com.facebook.pages.app.permission.C2D_MESSAGE'),
(648, 'ro.weednet.contactssync', 'UberSync Facebook Contact Sync', 'Danut Chereches', 'Synchronize profile pictures for your Facebook friends on Android.<br> <br>To configure, add the account or check status, go to &quot;Settings =&gt; Accounts&quot;.<br>Depending on how many friends you have, the first import might take a while, so be patient.<br> <br>IMPORTANT:<br>* Facebook allows me to use only the profile pictures. Other info cannot be synced. (eg. emails, phone numbers)<br>* Facebook users have the option to block one or all apps. If they opt for that, they will be EXCLUDED from your friends list.<br> <br>Please send bug reports or any kind of feedback.<br>Consider submitting bugs directly on GitHub. (link below)<br> <br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.facebook.com/ContactSync&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNG15J5dBeQm7ZLpXqHKsM_xt2ai2w" target="_blank">https://www.facebook.com/ContactSync</a><br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://plus.google.com/u/0/100286050370302911737&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHufO2ELj_h95ntV63N1fxAuyuM2Q" target="_blank">https://plus.google.com/u/0/100286050370302911737</a><br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://github.com/loadrunner/Facebook-Contact-Sync&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNETPk_KEGc0cPG-4VbsRgybopIckQ" target="_blank">https://github.com/loadrunner/Facebook-Contact-Sync</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=ro.weednet.contactssync', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/lfAHBITF37oanJyk_PmqGVJ5IbsgrjNYFZKCUAJuQts_LV-CH_eOZTySUVRxJqwRSHZo', 4.27, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '500,000+', ''),
(649, 'com.giannz.photodownloader', 'MyPhotoDownloader for Facebook', 'giannz', 'Download all your favourites albums and pictures from Facebook with the most powerful tool available ever!<br>- View and download your albums, tags, timeline pictures and photos of your friends, groups and pages<br>- Pick which photos you want to save, or directly download the whole albums<br>- The only app that can download photos in full resolution! (Plus version)<p>*** This is the free version of PhotoDownloader for Facebook, if you&#39;re interested in the Plus version without ads and with full resolution photos download, click here: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://goo.gl/fLQbU&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEBlTtwb7t8AaVMeka7akc5mH2j5g" target="_blank">http://goo.gl/fLQbU</a> ***<p>LIMITATIONS: Sometimes not all the photos of an album are shown/downloaded, thanks to some FB bugs; I can&#39;t do anything about it. Due to other FB limitations, currently the app cannot display (and download) more than 400 photos in &quot;Photo tags&quot; sections and support to shared (timeline) photos changes depending of the total number of wall posts.<br>Check Settings -&gt; Advanced if you want to save photos into external SD card.<p>Send me an email if you have any problem, bad ratings here don&#39;t help to solve issues.<p><br>Instructions:<br>1) On first launch, click the &quot;login&quot; button and authorize the application when requested<br>2) Explore your photos directly from main menu, or friends&#39; photos by clicking &quot;Friends&quot;<br>3) Use checkboxes to choose which photos or albums you want to download, select all of them with the upper button or click on one of them to open the gallery<br>4) Click the upper download button. When finished, you can view your photos by accessing the image gallery, or by opening with a file explorer the &quot;sdcard/Pictures/FacebookPhotos&quot; folder<p><br>This app uses the Facebook(tm) API and is not endorsed or certified by Facebook. All Facebook(tm) logoes and trademarks displayed on this app are property of Facebook.<p>Keywords: picdownloader, photodownloader, facebook, photo, photos, pic, picture, pictures, likes, album, albums, groups, pages, download, downloader', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.giannz.photodownloader', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/UHWu_hwb-5J5dI-kuwWuSGorNhL421JIIM37KWmWx-0dveD34FcWmB49BOPc0fSPLPGg', 4.58, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '500,000+', ''),
(650, 'com.andrew.apollo.googlemusictheme', 'Apollo Google Music theme', 'Andrew Neal', 'A Google Music theme for Apollo.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.andrew.apollo.googlemusictheme', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/3F0dqBVEAZzo3ZqimH07blSAzW_oWRsoEB90q0T-qXsiLuDdcLfxXZvgoRMsRilcs4A', 3.69, 'PERSONALIZATION', 'Free', '100,000+', '');
