(690, 'net.rocketbird.TF2UberSoundboard', 'TF2 Uber Soundboard', 'Rocket Bird', 'Presenting the ultimate Team Fortress 2 soundboard! Over 300 sound clips from all 9 classes (Scout, Soldier, Sniper, Pyro, Spy, Engineer, Medic, Demoman, and Heavy), PLUS even more clips from The Administrator, Horseless Headless Horseman, Vagineer, and Saxton Hale himself! No mic spammer is complete without this TF2 collection - all 100% free!<p>Save any clip as a ringtone, or use them to make your own custom soundboards with the Soundboard Maker app!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.rocketbird.TF2UberSoundboard', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/3JfA78FlHjrF7kDn4cphsmXAkXREM5hjsZqd4JeNEuzNU1XVDW6VFsnsAQEmTgJiKhg', 4.62, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '50,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION'),
(691, 'com.pwnwithyourphone.talktomekbd.dictionary', 'Uber Keyboard - Alternate Dict', 'Pwn with your Phone', '* THIS APPLICATION DOES NOTHING ON ITS OWN, IT IS FOR USE WITH Uber Keyboard ONLY.  DO NOT INSTALL IF YOU WERE NOT TOLD TO BY THE APPLICATION *<p>This provides a dictionary for use with Uber Keyboard (formerly TalkToMe Keyboard) for spelling corrections if the application told you it was needed.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.pwnwithyourphone.talktomekbd.dictionary', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/FavX2gb-V7dk96a8Tt-IiDsOrNkm_qVte9-bENcP4PV9NVFWFmIL2S8cwVMP8NcZTQ', 3.76, 'TOOLS', 'Free', '10,000+', ''),
(692, 'com.google.android.youtube', 'YouTube', 'Google Inc.', 'YouTube your way. Get the official YouTube app for Android. Instantly become the DJ, learn Kung Fu and easily share with friends. Catch up on your favorite videos and playlists from around the world on the couch, in the kitchen or on the go.<p>Features:<br>* Enjoy “what to watch” recommendations<br>* Find videos and channels with voice search and instant search suggestions<br>* Subscribe to your favorite channels for easy access from the guide<br>* Sign-in to access your playlists and “watch later” list<br>* Share videos via Google+, E-mail, Facebook and Twitter', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.google.android.youtube', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/NrQdFAdPSI9-hreB4C7HNhj3yXRiW1jqOOi7eFyakIx_IA-Im0huIeYCs5jTidMT2qA', 4.00, 'MEDIA_AND_VIDEO', 'Free', '500,000,000+', 'android.permission.CHANGE_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.MANAGE_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS, com.google.android.providers.gsf.permission.READ_GSERVICES, com.google.android.googleapps.permission.GOOGLE_AUTH, com.google.android.googleapps.permission.GOOGLE_AUTH.youtube, com.google.android.googleapps.permission.GOOGLE_AUTH.YouTubeUser, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, android.permission.NFC, android.permission.CAMERA, com.google.android.youtube.permission.C2D_MESSAGE'),
(693, 'com.whatsapp', 'WhatsApp Messenger', 'WhatsApp Inc.', 'WhatsApp Messenger is a smartphone messenger available for Android and other smartphones. WhatsApp uses your 3G or WiFi (when available) to message with friends and family. Switch from SMS to WhatsApp to send and receive messages, pictures, audio notes, and video messages. First year FREE! ($0.99 USD/year after)<p>WHY USE WHATSAPP: <p>? NO HIDDEN COST: Once you and your friends download the application, you can use it to chat as much as you want. Send a million messages a day to your friends for free! WhatsApp uses your Internet connection: 3G/EDGE or Wi-Fi when available. <p>? MULTIMEDIA: Send Video, Images, and Voice notes to your friends and contacts. <p>? GROUP CHAT: Enjoy group conversations with your contacts. <p>? NO INTERNATIONAL CHARGES: Just like there is no added cost to send an international email, there is no cost to send WhatsApp messages internationally. Chat with your friends all over the world as long as they have WhatsApp Messenger installed and avoid those pesky international SMS costs. <p>? SAY NO TO PINS AND USERNAMES: Why even bother having to remember yet another PIN or username? WhatsApp works with your phone number, just like SMS would, and integrates flawlessly with your existing phone address book. <p>? NO NEED TO LOG IN/OUT: No more confusion about getting logged off from another computer or device. With push notifications WhatsApp is ALWAYS ON and ALWAYS CONNECTED. <p>? NO NEED TO ADD BUDDIES: Your Address Book is used to automatically connect you with your contacts. Your contacts who already have WhatsApp Messenger will be automatically displayed.<p>? OFFLINE MESSAGES: Even if you miss your push notifications or turn off your phone, WhatsApp will save your messages offline until you retrieve them during the next application use. <p>? AND MUCH MORE: Share location, Exchange contacts, Custom wallpaper, Custom notification sounds, Landscape mode, Precise message time stamps, Email chat history, Broadcast messages and MMS to many contacts at once and much much more! <p>--------------------------------------------------------- <br>We’re always excited to hear from you! If you have any feedback, questions, or concerns, please email us at: <p><a href="mailto:android-support@whatsapp.com">android-support@whatsapp.com</a> <p>or follow us on twitter: <p><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://twitter.com/WhatsApp&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGBaaHUeDzDvSx0kIT_i3yFZ-nz7A" target="_blank">http://twitter.com/WhatsApp</a><br>@WhatsApp<br>---------------------------------------------------------<p>When roaming, additional carrier data charges may apply.  Please contact your carrier for details.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.whatsapp', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/bwBj9B4fGmTN_of0JS8xdkwklCmqCzSne1tJ9RaUNRQIzU-FEyCuFWzlsLyyPoTbyJE', 4.54, 'COMMUNICATION', 'Free', '100,000,000+', 'com.whatsapp.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, android.permission.STORAGE, android.permission.READ_CONTACTS, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.WRITE_CONTACTS, android.permission.RECEIVE_SMS, android.permission.SEND_SMS, android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, android.permission.CALL_PHONE, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE, android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS, android.permission.MANAGE_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.AUTHENTICATE_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, android.permission.READ_SYNC_STATS, android.permission.READ_SYNC_SETTINGS, android.permission.WRITE_SYNC_SETTINGS, android.permission.GET_TASKS, com.android.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, com.android.launcher.permission.UNINSTALL_SHORTCUT, com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.READ_PROFILE, com.google.android.providers.gsf.permission.READ_GSERVICES, android.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, com.whatsapp.permission.MAPS_RECEIVE'),
(694, 'com.skype.raider', 'Skype - free IM & video calls', 'Skype', 'Say “hello” to friends and family with an instant message, voice or video call on Skype for free. Join the millions of people using Skype today to stay in touch with the people who matter most. There’s so much you can do, right from the palm of your hand. <br>Features:<br>• Find all your friends and family in an instant - With over 250 million people using Skype, you’re bound to bump into someone you know.<br>• Talk with your fingers - No matter where you are, your friends are always at your fingertips with free instant messaging.<br>• Call your world from Skype - Talk to your heart’s content with free voice and video calls to all your friends and family on Skype.<br>• Low cost calls to mobiles and landlines too - Keep in touch, even if they’re not on Skype, with low cost calls and SMS to mobiles and landlines on the other side of town or the world.<br>• Share your favourite snaps - Got a favourite photo to share? Send it over Skype to friends and family and you won’t have to worry about email size limits or expensive MMS charges.<br>• Chat with anyone, anywhere - Skype’s available on smartphones, tablets, PCs, Macs, and even TVs. Whatever device your friends or family use, Skype just works. Simple.<br>• Video messaging – Record life’s everyday moments and share them with the people who matter most, with free and unlimited video messaging over Skype.<p>* Operator data charges may apply. We recommend using an unlimited data plan or WiFi connection.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.skype.raider', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/1CxNUEdzrREikWZoaHIU5J63x2gOxTb7R-ZIbJd51uPBFt0jUj8AX2bMOhKiIBcuAqtH', 3.96, 'COMMUNICATION', 'Free', '100,000,000+', 'android.permission.DISABLE_KEYGUARD, android.permission.CAMERA, android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE, android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS, android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO, android.permission.BLUETOOTH, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.CALL_PHONE, android.permission.GET_TASKS, android.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS, android.permission.BROADCAST_STICKY, android.permission.AUTHENTICATE_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.MANAGE_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS, android.permission.READ_CONTACTS, android.permission.WRITE_CONTACTS, android.permission.READ_SYNC_SETTINGS, android.permission.WRITE_SYNC_SETTINGS, android.permission.READ_SYNC_STATS, com.skype.raider.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, com.skype.android.app.permission.RECEIVE_ADM_MESSAGE, com.amazon.device.messaging.permission.RECEIVE'),
(695, 'com.safer_taxi', 'SaferTaxi - safer, easy, fast', 'SaferTaxi', 'Available for FREE in Buenos Aires, Brasilia, Curitiba, Montevideo, Santiago de Chile, Sao Paulo (SP) and Rio de Janeiro. <p>Request a cab near you in 1 quick click. It is easy! Track your driver&#39;s arrival in real-time, and hold the driver accountable by rating him/her at the end of the ride. It IS FREE! You only pay the taxi meter fare. Taxi? SaferTaxi! <p>WHY USE SAFERTAXI?<p>- FREE: Safer Taxi is free to download and use. You only pay what is shown on the taxi meter. No hidden costs<p>- SUPER FAST AND EASY: We locate you automatically using your phone GPS and Wireless.  Your cab is merely 1 click away. Then, watch your driver approach in real-time on a map<p>- FREE WIFI: All our taxis are also WiFi hotspots. Enjoy our complimentary Internet, especially when you are stuck in traffic<p>- ELECTRONIC PAYMENT: Out of cash? Not a problem with Safer Taxi. In Sao Paulo (SP), Santiago de Chile, and Rio de Janeiro you can pay with your credit card <p>- NEED A CAB URGENTLY? During rainy days or rush hour, simply indicate a tip within your booking request to attract nearby drivers<p>- RIDE HISTORY: If you leave an item behind, do not worry, your ride history and driver detail are saved inside the application for your record<p>- LOYALTY POINTS: Accumulate taxi miles each trip you take and convert the miles to free rides<p>- TRAVEL: Are you a frequent traveler? No problem our app works in Brasil, Argentina, and Chile<p><br>Safer Taxi was praised by: CNN Chile, TVN, Veja Sao Paulo and Rio de Janeiro, La Nacion, Globo TV, Radio Cooperativa, Radio Metro, El Mercurio, Fohla, ...<p>----------------------------<br>????? &quot;That was amazing! In one click, my taxi was waiting outside for me when I walked out the door. I used Safer Taxi in both Rio de Janeiro and Sao Paulo and it works like a charm – way better than 99taxis.&quot; – Thyago (Sao Paulo, Brazil)<p>????? &quot;I love knowing what driver to expect when I book! The driver profiles and ratings are super cool. I tried Easy Taxi and they do not offer ratings.&quot; – Maria (Santiago, Chile)<br>----------------------------<p>We’re always excited to hear from you! If you have any feedback, questions, or concerns, please email us at: <a href="mailto:info@safertaxi.com">info@safertaxi.com</a><p><br>THE HISTORY OF SAFERTAXI<br>SaferTaxi was started in 2009 in Buenos Aires long before Uber, Hailo, myTaxi or GetTaxi gained popularity in Europe and the US. However, as it was a pure text message based taxi system, the founders decided to change the business model to be more similar to Uber or Hailo. Today you can use your cell phone to book a cab and pay electronically (in Santiago, Rio de Janeiro, and San Pablo only, and Buenos Aires will follow shortly). We believe our solution goes beyond what Uber and Hailo can offer with a pure focus to be the best app within Latin America.<p><br>ABOUT OUR COMPETITORS<br>In Argentina there are different applications to book taxis, for example, Easy Taxi, Dinero Taxi, and EcoTaxi. However, these applications do not target directly Buenos Aires like Safer Taxi does. In Chile, Safer Taxi is facing competition from Easy Taxi only (based in Santiago). There are nearly no radio taxi providers or remis companies. Cabbify offers a high-end service similar to Uber, but at a much higher price point than taxis. Finally, in Brazil, Safer Taxi faces competition from 99Taxis, Easy Taxi, ResolveAi, Taxija, Taxibeat, WayTaxi, moove Taxi, and icab2go. Of those, Taxibeat, Taxija, 99taxis and Easy Taxi are probably the more advanced once. However, none of the competitors in Argentina, Chile, and Brazil offer free wifi to customers, ride history, loyalty points, or electronic payment.<p><br>GPS AND MAPS DISCLAIMER<br>Please note that Safer Taxi is not responsible for the accuracy of your GPS. Your GPS position is influenced by the quality of your phone and whether you have WiFi assisted GPS turned on. Please note also, that unlike Waze or Foursquare, Safer Taxi is not building its own maps. All maps are provided by Google.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.safer_taxi', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/4Ak98BVJxKSGws_SL6KuUeNjiNCgSkZLYkYR0tVNeZGMTSuwO9vgHxlHN4JkpbOr8Q', 4.38, 'TRANSPORTATION', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, com.google.android.providers.gsf.permission.READ_GSERVICES, android.permission.RECEIVE_SMS, android.permission.READ_SMS, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, com.safer_taxi.permission.C2D_MESSAGE');
