(703, 'com.feelingtouch.racingcarcross', 'Death Racing 2: Desert', 'FT Games', 'Fast paced 3D racing game and easy to get started<br>Death Racing 2: Desert<br>Play With your facebook friends.<p>A new version of death racing.<br>Come on, let&#39;s pass through the desert together!<p>Unlock most fantastic cars by skillful plays, and challenge the extreme of speed and distance!<br>Complete bounty missions and earn honorable achievements;<br>Enjoy beautiful views along roads, bridges, seashore and more; <br>Explore the autumn and winter sceneries of the desert.<br>All glories come to you via a single finger!<p>Simple Controls:<br>#Tilt to turn <br>#Touch to accelerate<br>#Hit brake to slow down<p>Strategies:<br>#Keep accelerating to multiply scores. The number on top right is the KEY<br>#Beware of indicators. Other vehicles might turn left or right. Make your way through traffic<br>#Unlock more advanced cars to gain extra lives.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.feelingtouch.racingcarcross', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/f8wWmOa9dYaonnYgC24200datlP7cW855HrKmPsvgCrw4MvNA4vnUqfhok1JG6Lhcdk', 4.13, 'RACING', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.WAKE_LOCK, android.permission.INTERNET, android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE, android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE, android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE'),
(704, 'com.Company.desertStrike', 'Counter desert strike', 'PehuenSoft', 'Use your android phone for go Into a desert war and kill your enemies. <p>You are the elite sniper of the United States Army and fight against terrorists in the desert. This is a game of free throws and casual. Counter strike desert is a game for lovers of war.<p>This will be a deadly war against terrorism. You have tu be the best killer.<p>You Visualized the enemies and Then You Used the telescopic sight to shoot a real 3D scene. This shooter game has very good sound That will immerse you in battle.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Company.desertStrike', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/-nYif1BzW22W4HJZloZmf2OD3XjODAri6-h-F1p3GNw0ES0EQRe5x9BWNbxlgHS-cfs', 3.59, 'ARCADE', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'android.permission.INTERNET, android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION, android.permission.ACCESS_LOCATION_EXTRA_COMMANDS, android.permission.WAKE_LOCK, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE, android.permission.VIBRATE'),
(705, 'com.fingersoft.hillclimb', 'Hill Climb Racing', 'Fingersoft', 'One of the most addictive and entertaining physics based driving game ever made for Android! And it&#39;s free!<p><br>Meet Newton Bill, the young aspiring uphill racer. He is about to embark on a journey that takes him to where no ride has ever been before. With little respect to the laws of physics, Newton Bill will not rest until he has conquered the highest hills up on the moon!<p>Face the challenges of unique hill climbing environments with many different cars. Gain bonuses from daring tricks and collect coins to upgrade your car and reach even higher distances. Watch out though - Bill&#39;s stout neck is not what it used to be when he was a kid! And his good ol&#39; gasoline crematorium will easily run out of fuel.<p>Features:<br> - 14 different vehicles with unique upgrades (many different vehicles: bike, truck, jeep, tank etc)<br> - Upgradeable parts include engine, suspension, tires and 4WD<br> - 14 stages with levels to reach in each (Countryside, Desert, Arctic and the Moon! +++)<br> - Share your score with a screenshot with your friends!<br> - Cool graphics and smooth physics simulation<br> - Designed to look good on low resolution and high resolution devices (incl. tablets)<br> - Real turbo sound when you upgrade your engine!<p>Like us at Facebook and stay tuned with all new games and updates: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.facebook.com/Fingersoft&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGz4JeHd4p-qkCF8PEi_llXKtnwTQ" target="_blank">http://www.facebook.com/Fingersoft</a><p>We&#39;d appreciate if you&#39;d report any issues you&#39;re having with the game to <a href="mailto:support@fingersoft.net">support@fingersoft.net</a>, please include your device make and model.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fingersoft.hillclimb', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/EdHjP93VnEXgwvaKP0U6UtMj2h7PZmepmFQlk4eGiG_-L8YyekRm1IYoZ8fAqjpw3Wsj', 4.68, 'RACING', 'Free', '50,000,000+', 'android.permi