(760, 'com.ibeerfreelivewallpaper', 'iBeer Free Live Wallpaper', 'Live Wallpapers and Backgrounds', 'Are you craving for a pint of beer? Then &#39;iBeer Free Live Wallpaper&#39; is the right app for you! It will refresh you with five HD backgrounds! The fans of this alcoholic beverage will love this new live wallpaper! Now you can carry a “beer keg” wherever you go! Watch the rich foam sliding down the beer mug! Have a taste of good ale with the bubbles going up the glass! Your favorite drink is finally on your phone screen! Share a beer with your friends without going to a bar! Cheers!<p>Do you prefer a light ale or a pitcher of strong, dark beer? Well, now you can have both types of beer! This new app will make your mouth water each time you take a look at your desktop! Bubbles will float on your screen and give you the impression of a real draft beer in your hands! Thick foam on top will make your experience even better! Download this free live wallpaper now, and make your phone look like a frothing pitcher of this delicious lager!<p>?To use: Home -&gt; Menu -&gt; Wallpapers -&gt; Live Wallpapers<br>?Full support for both portrait and landscape mode!<p>Download &#39;iBeer Free Live Wallpaper&#39; and make your screen look like a glass of freshly brewed ale! Give yourself a break and have a nice glass of fresh, cold drink – on your phone! Be careful, though – these realistic wallpaper backgrounds will make you want to jump into the foaminess of your favorite “alcoholic drink”! Get this free app now and enjoy a pint of this refreshing malt liquor whenever you feel like it! Beer lovers, this is for you!<p>Your search for the perfect beer app is over! If you wanted to visit a brewery and never had a chance, don&#39;t worry – get this live wallpaper and feel like a skilled brewer! You can choose between a huge glass of dark beer or a pale ale and quench your thirst! Bring the pub atmosphere to your screen and relax! If you like your beer foamy and bubbly, you are in luck! Throw away all the bottles and drink this ice cold drink from a real beer mug! Raise your glass to everyone who enjoys a good lager as much as you do!<p>If you are thirsty, this beer wallpaper free is the solution! Don&#39;t go to a beer store – the best brewed ale is right here on your mobile phone! Stop longing for that bitter taste and get this cool app as soon as possible! Brew your own beer by just one click on the screen and share it with other beer lovers! Everyone who enjoys this type of liquor will enjoy these backgrounds and wallpapers because they are the best you can find on the market right now!<p>Don&#39;t know how to brew? Download &#39;iBeer Free Live Wallpaper&#39; and solve this problem! Organize your own beer festival without leaving the house! Fill your glass to the top with these beautiful pictures of the most popular alcoholic drink in the world! If you like beer drinking with you friends, this 2013 app is perfect for you! Turn your phone into a pint of beer with these phone backgrounds you have never seen before! Let the little bubbles go up your screen topped with thick foam! Get this free app for Android™ right now and find best live wallpapers dripping with ale! Bottoms up!<p>*Android is a trademark of Google Inc.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ibeerfreelivewallpaper', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/Pm66C5JxhxjpC59o7309GeN9hwlfrqG16Kr3IsIbCk19ULa9iw6EqGqrPzUDP3wC_BE', 3.92, 'PERSONALIZATION', 'Free', '50,000+', 'android.permission.SET_WALLPAPER, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, android.permission.GET_TASKS, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS'),
(761, 'app.onetouchdrawLite', 'One Touch Free', 'Migital Super Games', 'Do you like challenges? Then we challenge you to <b>draw these shapes without lifting your finger.</b><br>This game will baffle your mind, for it is not always so easy to draw a shape without lifting the finger and without retracing the same line.<p>Play this interesting game of drawing, and show if you really take challenges seriously.<br>All you need to do is <b>move your finger on the shape shown on your mobile screen.</b> But there are rules too!<p>?	6 amazing modes of gameplay!<br>?	600 levels to enjoy for hours in run!<br>?	Addictive &amp; mind baffling game!<br>?	No two shapes are same, each one comes with a unique level of difficulty!<p>Follow the rules, draw the shapes, have a time of your life!!<p>?	<b>Unlimited Fun</b> - <br>?	<b>Play six different modes with 600 difficult &amp; addictive levels in the game,</b> but remember each one is as much challenging as the last one.<p>?	<b>Interesting Rules</b> -<br>?	<b>Move your finger on the shape shown on your mobile screen</b>. You will learn why elders said that one must not drift away from his path :P<br>You must not lift your finger. <b>Lifting the finger will end your game.</b> Just keep moving it along the lines.<p>These are just the basic rules, you will have to follow different set of rules in each game mode.<p>?	<b>Warm Up</b> - Play 100 different levels in the <b>&#39;Warm up&#39;</b> mode. It will be easy just to get you into the groove!<p>?	<b>Warm Up Timer</b> – It will keep getting interesting with each mode. Rules are same as the pervious one, you just need to <b>beat the timer in the &#39;Warm Up Timer&#39;</b> mode. <p>?	<b>Dots to Dots</b> – In this mode you may think it is easier as the shape is already shown. But you&#39;d just be fooling yourself if you thought it was easier! ;)<p>?	<b>Connect the dots and make the shown shape in &#39;Dots to Dots&#39; mode.</b><p>?	<b>Deadly Dots</b> – Finish the shown shape before the time runs out!<br>So in a way <b>&#39;Deadly Dots&#39;</b> is just like <b>&#39;Dots to Dots&#39;</b> but DEADLY! <b>You need to finish in time.</b><p>?	<b>Double Trouble</b> – Lets get a twist in the game, now you won&#39;t be tracing the shape just once. <b>You will have to trace the Red line twice or your game will be over!</b><br>Be clever, some paths are worth walking twice. ;)<p>?	<b>Time Trouble</b> – We all know time is an enemy! Even in the games that we enjoy so much! Although you need to beat the time once again, but stay assured it&#39;s going to be even more fun than any of the modes above!<p>You will need to complete the shape while tracing the red line twice, just don&#39;t forget that the time is running out! Be fast or die!<p>Get down on drawing, but remember it is not so easy to draw in <b>&#39;One Touch&#39;</b>. It&#39;s addictive, challenging, &amp; very much fun to play this game. It will never get old!<p><p>“Please don&#39;t leave negative remarks on this page. If you are not satisfied with our app, mail your reviews &amp; suggestions to <a href="mailto:support@migital.com">support@migital.com</a><p>Tags – One Touch, Draw, Sketch, Draw shapes, puzzle, drawing, touch draw, challenge game, puzzle game, touch to draw, time based game, Migital', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=app.onetouchdrawLite', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/ToiQGTaiTv2g3kJUtIG4h4f1izx7zXfgQXhVNBXVfycz4gthiCoSrgQL0HVlWpdPEA', 4.52, 'BRAIN', 'Free', '10,000+', 'android.permission.INTERNET, com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE, android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, android.permission.VIBRATE, android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE'),
(762, 'com.kauf.games.stickmanbubbledeluxe', 'Stickman Bubble Deluxe', 'Kaufcom Games Apps Widgets', 'Stickman and his brothers have been trapped in some painted balls because their designer has decided to make them take part at a new exiting game. The only problem is that he did not explain them that the target of the game is to make them explode like soap bubbles to make space for other bros that keep falling down in the notebook frame. It is basically a match 3 game. <br>Tap on three or more adjacent doodle bubbles to make them disappear. <br>You will have to rush to find the matching color circles as you do not have just the time running against you, but also the other stickman bubbles that want fit into the drawn borders of the page. If more than 3 bubbles fall out of the borders, you lose.<p>Remove as many connected bubbles in one tap as you can to reach a higher score in less time.<p>???Features: ???<p>? Match 3 or more identical bubbles <br>? Colorful HD graphics and smooth animations<br>? 15 levels to play<br>? Maximum points reachable with one move: 300<p>If you like match-3 games, then you will definitely love this one.<p>Useful advice: You need to match at least 3 bubbles of the same color to get points, if you touch just 2 of them they will disappear and empty the space they occupied before, but you will not get any points.<p>Warning: if you touch in a place where no matching bubbles are, you will lose 50 points.<p>Try to burst as many bubbles as needed to pass each level! You will not find the usual bubbles or jewels you are used to see in these sorts of games, but some nice, a little bit scared doodle man trapped in some red, blue, yellow and green spheres.<br>While you are proceeding forward with the levels, you will find different office tools lying on the notebook’s page like bulldog clips, a compass, erasers, glues, markers, a scissor, a sharpener and many more that are going to restrict the available space.<p>Download the new addicting Stickman game and you will never be bored anymore. Pop the bubbles and blast them away to clean the paper sheet. You can play it everywhere you want at home, while having a break at work or at school, at the bus stop, in a park etc.<p><br>This application is for free! Play it every time you wish to kill some time!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kauf.games.stickmanbubbledeluxe', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/pgoj2oVeGqrr6b5yPzzoQjYMyOoHXCuW5f7jAxltTUneB5VopIf5t8ATjAWKajt9nw', 3.58, 'CASUAL', 'Free', '10,000+', 'android.permission.INTERNET, android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.WAKE_LOCK, android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE'),
