(799, 'com.mobisystems.fonts', 'OfficeSuite Font Package', 'Mobile Systems, Inc.', 'Get a genuine view of your Word documents with the Microsoft Windows font compatibility pack. The pack includes most used fonts. <p>Arial (Regular, Bold, Italic and Bold Italic) <br>Cambria (Regular, Bold, Italic and Bold Italic) <br>Calibri (Regular, Bold, Italic and Bold Italic) <br>Courier New (Regular, Bold, Italic and Bold Italic) <br>Times New Roman (Regular, Bold, Italic and Bold Italic) <br>Webdings (symbol character set) <br>Wingdings 1 (symbol character set) <br>Wingdings 2 (symbol character set) <br>Wingdings 3 (symbol character set) <br>Cambria Math (special character set)<br>Tahoma (Regular, Bold)<br>Verdana (Regular, Bold, Italic and Bold Italic<p>The font package is compatible with OfficeSuite Viewer and OfficeSuite Professional version 6.10 or higher.<p>Note that the Font Pack is an optional add-on product for OfficeSuite.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mobisystems.fonts', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/NqCheNdxL3NrSEqmmdBjGZZBMJC6Ln9Kh6xHWbKIejIM4TuwRRTxctEb60l6EFxaiQaF', 4.11, 'BUSINESS', '$6.99', '50,000+', ''),
(800, 'com.mins.tracker.activity', 'Package Tracker Pro', 'MinsTech Software', '***** 2012 5 stars Reviewers&#39; Choice Award Winner *****<p>Package Tracker Pro, the best selling package tracking application, is a solid, stable and handy business tool to help users to track over various shipping carriers’ packages (parcels), and provides All-In-One package / parcel tracking solution. <p>Mobile Package Tracker was 2010 top 4 paid Application in All Paid Applications in straight 5 months, and Package Tracker Pro is its successor. We do our best to make our application and server stable to serve our users&#39; daily package tracking. <p>As we provide long term support to our customers, if you have any question or suggestions, you can contact us @ <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.pdexpress.net&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNF6bNw6jxGsP2205hs4bYbRodwrnQ" target="_blank">http://www.pdexpress.net</a> or send us email.<p>Feature list:<p>1. Package tracking (Parcel tracking) of a variety of shipping carriers<br>2. Notification and alert via Ringtone / LED / vibration / email<br>3. Label/edit/delete package (hint: long touch the tracking #, and the options will pop up)<br>4. Sync tracking # list between PC (sync site) and phone without typing on phone. Using this extra value feature will save you and your team&#39;s time.<br>5. Push tracking # to the sync site<br>6. email tracking information<br>7. Display package route map if available<br>8. Customize your carrier list<br>9. option to sort package display by package add-on time<br>10. option to enable group package list by carrier<br>11. Support App2SD<p><br>The shipping carriers include:<br> - Aramex<br> - Australia Post<br> - Brazilian Post<br> - Canada Post<br> - City Link<br> - DHL USA<br> - DHL Global Mail<br> - DHL UK<br> - DHL DE / German<br> - DPD DE / German<br> - Ensenda<br> - Estafeta<br> - FedEx<br> - FedEx SmartPost<br> - FedEx UK<br> - Hermes DE / German<br> - Hongkong Post<br> - Japan Post EMS<br> - LaserShip<br> - Loomis Express<br> - New Zealand Post<br> - Norway Post<br> - OnTrac<br> - Parcelforce<br> - Prestige <br> - Pitt Ohio<br> - Purolator<br> - Royal Mail  <br> - Singapore Post (SingPost)<br> - Spanish Post / Correos Post<br> - Streamlite<br> - Swiss Post<br> - TNT<br> - UPS<br> - UPS Mail Innovations<br> - USPS<br> - Yamato Transport <p>If you have any question about the application and usage, please email us. We will get you back at the earliest time.<p>Parcels, Package Delivery, deliveries', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mins.tracker.activity', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/PpNv5CDMRr4lAMIF4IlPdAixM1qTwIhe3c0pAsm_BuXQ8tQtLyuFqIpylsnYa4LJ0g4', 4.59, 'BUSINESS', '$1.99', '10,000+', 'android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, com.android.vending.CHECK_LICENSE'),
(801, 'com.slice', 'Slice - Easy Package Tracker', 'Slice', 'Do you love online shopping? Just in time for the holiday shopping season, Black Friday and Cyber Monday. Discover what so many of our users say is &quot;a must-have app for online shoppers&quot;. <p>• The only Android phone or tablet app that tracks your shipments, price drops, &amp; product recalls AUTOMATICALLY<br>• TRACK PACKAGES from your favorite merchants, including Amazon, eBay, Walmart, Etsy, Nordstrom, Zappos, Groupon, iTunes and thousands more!<br>• SAVE MONEY when something you&#39;ve bought drops in price<br>• KEEP YOUR FAMILY SAFE when a product recall has been issued for one of your purchases<p>HOW IT WORKS:<p>1. Sign up with your Google, Yahoo, Facebook account. Or create a Slice account.<br>2. Link your email inbox from Gmail, Yahoo, Hotmail or Live.<br>3. Slice will automatically find your receipts and track your packages.<br>4. And the best part: get shipment notifications, price alerts, and product recall info automatically.<p>FEATURES:<p>TRACK YOUR PACKAGES<br>• Get push notifications when a package is shipped, out for delivery, or has been delivered.<br>• View the progress of shipments on a map.<br>• Track returns or other outgoing packages by scanning the shipping barcode.<br>• Integrated support for all the major US shipping carriers including USPS, UPS, UPS Mail Innovations (UPS-MI), FedEx DHL, OnTrac.<p>SAVE MONEY<br>• When the price drops for something AFTER you buy it, Slice will send you a price alert so you can recoup the difference!<br>• Get cash back from Nordstrom, Best Buy, Walmart, Crate &amp; Barrel, Buy.com, L.L. Bean, HSN.com and many more!<p>SAFETY FIRST<br>• Slice will alert you if your purchases match a product recall from the CPSC.<p>KEEP YOUR PURCHASES ORGANIZED<br>• Back up email receipts to facilitate returns, exchanges and warranty claims<br>• Keep track of your Groupon, LivingSocial, Bloomspot, Amazon Local and Gilt City vouchers. Don’t miss out on redeeming a daily deal because you forgot about it!<p>DISCOVER YOUR SHOPPING DNA<br>• What you buy says a lot about who you are! Are you a Gadget Geek or a Sharp Dresser? Discover your Thingerprint™.<br>• See how much you spend shopping online and on which categories and items.<p>IN THE PRESS:<p>• CNN: a simple way to organize your purchases and simultaneously track orders from multiple vendors.<br>• Android Central: an excellent way to keep track of your online purchases and keep up with orders that are on the way.<br>• CBS News: the service is incredibly secure…a must-have tool for online shopping…it was fun to see how I&#39;ve spent my money through the years.”<br>• Lifehacker Pack for Android: Our List of the Best Android Apps. “Slice is a brilliant companion to your online shopping … it&#39;s certainly going to be where I track my purchases for the foreseeable future.”<p>USER TESTIMONIALS:<br>• “Love it: I am an Amazon addict and this helps me keep track of everything”<br>• “It really works: No more typing in codes at FedEx or UPS. Great app.”<br>• “Awesome: Very useful app...Tracks Amazon, Ebay and Newegg flawlessly.”<br>• “It&#39;s made tracking everything so easy whether it&#39;s all from Amazon or orders from other various sites. I love Slice!!!”<br>• “Works like a charm: Great for tracking all of my Amazon, eBay and other orders.”<br>• “This is the best tracking system that I have ever used. Beats eBay and all the others that I have tried.”<br>• “Didn&#39;t realize how great this app was until an item I purchased went on sale $30 lower than what I had paid the same day I ordered it. Slice notified me of the price drop and even had options on how to resolve the matter. I clicked on the email link and it actually completed the email for me with order number, item description, and what the problem was. What an amazing app!!”<br>• “A Must have for the online shopper: Way cool, well laid out, useful and I imagine it will be a huge help this next holiday gift giving season!”<p>Slice is the ultimate companion for the online shopper. We’ve processed over 100 million purchases. We’ll save you time … and maybe even some money, too. Download today!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.slice', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/5KdA6P3cBnPhxlqLBa9hj5iQlQ2x0l4Hplw9dJ2Gt7GXBaRtiZMLUJkyM4aWDOe4BSn_', 4.50, 'SHOPPING', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.GET_TASKS, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, com.google.android.providers.gsf.permission.READ_GSERVICES, com.slice.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE'),
