(805, 'com.ztech.packagetracking2', 'Package Tracking 2.0', 'Zachary Cava', 'Note: You are not required to use sync at all, it is an opt-in feature for those that find it useful. You can use the program without that.<p>The original Package Tracking program returns to the market with its aptly named predecessor completely redesigned for your benefit.<p>The idea has remained the same, all information no fluff, and the user interface has been streamlined to allow for faster tracking of multiple packages. Simply select your previous packages right from the home screen or tap the plus button to add a new one. When you track a number your shipment information is displayed in an easy to read, unified format.<p>The smart update service has returned, running only at the intervals selected and shutting down after checks have been completed. No need to uselessly waste batter, your phone is an important device in your life.<p>It is not always easy to enter numbers on your phone, even in a streamlined interface like this and that is why I have built <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.package-tracking.info&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEBPRbWZBZhI6I0uGG0eHAD9vY_lg" target="_blank">http://www.package-tracking.info</a>. This web-extension of Package Tracking will allow you to manage the numbers on your Android powered devices from your computer, adding, editing, and deleting numbers as well. No need to make a QR code that you then scan on your phone, simply add the numbers from your desktop and leave your phone in your pocket. The only restriction of this feature is that it requires Android 2.2 or higher to be running on your device, but I am working on bringing it to 2.1 and lower sometime in the future.<p>The current supported carriers are:<br>-ABF<br>-DHL<br>-Fed-Ex<br>-Lasership<br>-OnTrac<br>-SDN<br>-SpeeDee Delivery<br>-TNT<br>-UPS<br>-US Postal Service<br>-YRC Regional<br>For each carrier supported, each and every type of shipment sent by that carrier is supported.<p>This is a pet project of mine that I use to apply new programming concepts I have learned, I am thrilled if you love it, but if you have any problems I would love to fix them because it benefits my learning experience. I cannot reply to market comments so if you have any problems or wish to request a carrier be added contact me at <a href="mailto:packagetrackingapp@gmail.com">packagetrackingapp@gmail.com</a><p>Some replies I believe are needed:<br>-Sure there is only 11 carriers, but even when I had 19 only 8 of them were used enough to warrant having them. I will happily more if you can supply shipment numbers to build scripts with.<br>-Notifications are only as fast as the carriers, what you see is exactly what you will see on the carriers website. I am working on a prediction algorithm but it will take some time.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ztech.packagetracking2', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/NU-TzAuF3w9LsYXuKBBM1ouOgZQspDl_ZSPL3191w-KgCp9My5rx3ZUifxKNSU3fXw', 3.99, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '100,000+', 'com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, com.ztech.packagetracking2.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED'),
(806, 'com.mins.tracker.express.activity', 'Package Tracker Express', 'MinsTech Software', 'Package Tracker Express is a free version of Package Tracker Pro (and Package Tracker for Tablet), the best selling package tracking application, which is a solid, stable and handy business tool to help users to track over various shipping carriers’ packages (parcels), and provides All-In-One package / parcel tracking solution. <p>Package Tracker Express includes all of the features of Package Tracker Pro except that package status change notification feature is not available in Package Tracker Express and Ad is enabled in the free version.<p>If you run into any issues, please contact us and we will provide free support.<p>Feature list:<p>1. Package tracking (parcel / parcels tracking) of a variety of shipping carriers<br>2. Label/edit/delete package (hint: long touch the tracking #, and the options will pop up)<br>3. Sync tracking # list between PC (sync site) and phone without typing on phone. Using this extra value feature will save you and your team&#39;s time.<br>4. Push tracking # to the sync site<br>5. Email tracking information<br>6. Display package route map if available<br>7. Customize your carrier list<br>8. Option to sort package display by package add-on time<br>9. Option to enable group package list by carrier<br>10. Support App2SD<p><br>The shipping carriers include:<br> - Aramex<br> - Australia Post<br> - Brazilian Post<br> - Canada Post<br> - City Link<br> - DHL USA<br> - DHL Global Mail<br> - DHL UK<br> - DHL DE / German<br> - DPD DE / German<br> - Ensenda<br> - Estafeta<br> - FedEx<br> - FedEx SmartPost<br> - FedEx UK<br> - Hermes DE / German<br> - Hongkong Post<br> - Japan Post EMS<br> - LaserShip<br> - Loomis Express<br> - New Zealand Post<br> - Norway Post<br> - OnTrac<br> - Parcelforce<br> - Prestige <br> - Pitt Ohio<br> - Purolator<br> - Royal Mail  <br> - Singapore Post (Sing Post) <br> - Spanish Post / Correos Post<br> - Streamlite<br> - Swiss Post<br> - TNT<br> - UPS<br> - UPS Mail Innovations<br> - USPS<br> - Yamato Transport <p>If you have any question about the application and usage, please email us. We will get you back at the earliest time.<p>Parcels, Package Delivery, deliveries', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mins.tracker.express.activity', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/oxBx3w85jTfWCVlRL2mQGGZQe1T9GPhsU3cJPYtTl1F1WbJLTeqYgXFIIW6hDlltXlE', 4.54, 'BUSINESS', 'Free', '10,000+', ''),
(807, 'com.jy.iconchanger.iconpkg', 'Icon Package for Icon Changer', 'Juyeong', 'This is Icons for <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jy.iconchanger.ad">ICON CHANGER</a><p>you should download <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jy.iconchanger.ad">ICON CHANGER</a> first', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jy.iconchanger.iconpkg', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/-74RfhsVaZBZsyYpDHZGfbtlJpvRiCi5LDRskxatSzuSkWovsbW2cP-nemABkWDBRQ', 4.36, 'PERSONALIZATION', 'Free', '100,000+', ''),
(808, 'com.jb.gosms.tr', 'GO SMS Pro Turkish package', 'GO Dev Team', 'This pack is for GO SMS Pro Turkish language support.<p>Install it and change the language in GO SMS Pro’s “Settings –Application Settings—Language selection”<p>Thanks cemx, Özgür Yalç?n, Saner Apayd?n, leventmann, Kan?t Kaplan,Ömer Emin DEDE, sheeper, hakk? kubilay kocabalkan, tuba_fb, Sam Islander, Korhanm, farukdgn, cemc, viski-pahali, zubeyirdsl,  Mehmet Selcuk Yayan, serkan-, KRALL for the translation.<p>Click the following link:<br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.googleandroid.gen.tr/Thread-go-sms-artik-turkce-language-of-application-is-turkish&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHDOMxtaTWA2bdAvlCT5Rp2uGEd7w" target="_blank">http://www.googleandroid.gen.tr/Thread-go-sms-artik-turkce-language-of-application-is-turkish</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jb.gosms.tr', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/cVBSNa5vm2qi8TqVVfDvUw3FZcYY64yUTc_8hPhYzCDJ0LA_Q6a3DN5U7_JRqiuG4g', 4.25, 'COMMUNICATION', 'Free', '100,000+', ''),
(809, 'com.ma.financial.activities', 'Accounting Package', 'Marlboro.Chu', 'Accounting Book for a convenient and simple operation of the accounting software. <br>Available anytime, anywhere through the phone easily record your daily life in the expenditure information.<p>*Electronic invoice receipt scanner<br>*Manual records of expenditure<br>*Monthly expenditure statements<br>*Invoice number on the Prize (the software is only available on the award information can not be used as basis for receiving awards)', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ma.financial.activities', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/J4pGM45oYq283j0mZW52MEIK_U5oJXKWfOVTQzxJYQ0YTWVuuPC3QNJmgo-Io0XLYWwT', 3.96, 'FINANCE', 'Free', '10,000+', 'android.permission.CAMERA');
