(810, 'com.ngc.fora.dict.lexdb', 'English Dictionary Package', 'NG-Computing', 'Self-extracting package for using in Fora Dictionary.<p>Fora Dictionary should be installed to use this dictionary.<p># Articles: 147306<br>Download size: ~ 12 MB<br>SD-card space used: ~ 40 MB<p>Manual:<br>Install, extract to SD-card and uninstall.<p>Uninstallation:<br>Dictionary Manager &gt; Dictionary &gt; &quot;Delete permanently&quot;.<p>Source:<br>WordNet 3.0, <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://wordnet.princeton.edu/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGCXidj5aatnZzAcTKfHfsTqSaNAQ" target="_blank">http://wordnet.princeton.edu/</a><p>Note:<br>May require relatively larger free phone memory during installation.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ngc.fora.dict.lexdb', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/wMcI8puFF7m4OwEgoevwgZi-uaZdO1VvaaUVNiDtRi8Wsei529CS5WeECKL5xjODRFY', 4.58, 'BOOKS_AND_REFERENCE', 'Free', '50,000+', ''),
(811, 'com.shiprack.client', 'Shiprack Package Tracker', 'Shiprack', 'Track packages and parcels with instant delivery notifications on Android with this fresh approach to package tracking.  Simply forward the ship-confirmation emails from your favorite online retailers to <a href="mailto:packages@ship-rack.com">packages@ship-rack.com</a>, and allow Shiprack to do the rest!  FedEx, UPS, USPS, DHL, and more, all in one single app.  Or if you send packages a lot, there&#39;s also a handy bar-code scanner to make your life easier.<p>Note: This is a free app that is supported by banner ads.  You can also click on the &quot;No-Ads&quot; button in the app to buy the add-free upgrade.<p>Full list of supported carriers:<p>Nation-wide and International: DHL, FedEx (including FedEx SmartPost), UPS (including UPS Mail Innovations)<p>Postal Carriers: Canada Post, Australia Post, US Postal Service.<p>Regional and specialized ones: A1 International, Ensenda, LaserShip, OnTrac, Prestige, and Purolator.<p><br>Keywords : package, parcels, tracking, tracker, fedex, ups, dhl, usps, amazon', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.shiprack.client', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/HVzztcrgZOLuRx547Qonn6V_0RUGOx-HgxCOcQD4oqmby4Ehkf0rUlYClCiVFS_2Gg', 4.58, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '10,000+', 'com.shiprack.client.permission.C2D_MESSAGE, com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEIVE, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, android.permission.USE_CREDENTIALS, android.permission.MANAGE_ACCOUNTS, com.android.vending.BILLING'),
(812, 'com.psyrus.packagebuddypro', 'Package Buddy Pro', 'Partial Software', 'Package Buddy is a package tracking app designed to allow you to track your packages, from many carriers (listed below), anywhere you go with your phone or tablet. <p>Sync with all of your Android devices (no extra cost if linked on same Google Account). Pro users can now forward shipping confirmation emails to <a href="mailto:packages@package-buddy.com">packages@package-buddy.com</a> to automatically add packages to their account (BETA).<p>Use the settings to customize your experience.  Set which lists to display, how much information to show, and when your device automatically updates/backs-up/syncs. Visit the FAQ on our site for more information.<p>Add packages easily by entering in the necessary information, or head to <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.package-buddy.com/code&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGPg2HnnNOqduTGAz_cLlrYQ37DHw" target="_blank">http://www.package-buddy.com/code</a> to create a QR code to scan in.<br>Send package information to others easily with the share screen. You can click on some carrier links to automatically fill out package information into Package Buddy.<p>With Package Buddy, you can see a detailed history and a map of the progress for your packages (amount of detail depends on carrier).<p>If you notice **ANY** problems with Package Buddy please send an **EMAIL**. Comments **DO NOT** allow us to communicate to you, which is vital. If you have a carrier or a feature you want added, just let us know and we&#39;ll see if it can be done.<p>There&#39;s also a new tablet upgrade which has all the features of the pro version and optimizes how information is shown for tablets (not necessary to run on tablets, just an extra feature).<p>Thanks everyone for your support!<p>Note: A package being visible on Amazon works slightly different. Check the carrier&#39;s site that they are using for actual tracking data.<p>The following carriers are supported:<br>- A-1 International<br>- Adrexo<br>- Aeronet<br>- Air21<br>- American Airlines Cargo<br>- AmeriJet<br>- An Post<br>- Aramex<br>- Argix Direct<br>- ATS Solutions<br>- Australia Post<br>- Australian Air Express<br>- Belgin Post<br>- Belpost<br>- Canada Post<br>- CEVA<br>- City Link<br>- Continental Cargo<br>- Chronopost<br>- Colissimo<br>- Collect Plus<br>- Correios Brazil<br>- Correos Chile<br>- Correos del Ecuador<br>- Correos Spain<br>- Courier Post (NZ)<br>- CTT Portugal<br>- Cyprus Post<br>- DB Schenker<br>- DB Schenker Privpak<br>- Delta Cargo<br>- DHL<br>- DHL ACG<br>- DHL Brazil<br>- DHL Canada<br>- DHL DE<br>- DHL GM<br>- DHL Poland<br>- DHL Same Day<br>- DHL Spain<br>- DHL Sweden<br>- DHL UK<br>- Direct Freight Express <br>- DPD<br>- DPD Ireland<br>- DPD Poland<br>- DPD UK<br>- Dynamax<br>- Empost<br>- Ensenda<br>- Expeditors<br>- FedEx<br>- FedEx UK<br>- Flyt Express<br>- Forward Air<br>- GLS<br>- GSO<br>- HDNL<br>- Hermes<br>- Hermes UK		<br>- Hong Kong Post<br>- i-parcel<br>- Interlink<br>- Irish Post<br>- Israel Post<br>- Itella<br>- Japan Post<br>- Korea Post<br>- Lasership<br>- LBC Express<br>- Luxembourg Post<br>- Magyar Post<br>- Mail Express<br>- Matkahuolto<br>- Metrowide Courier Express<br>- MRW ES<br>- Newgistics<br>- OCS<br>- Old Dominion<br>- OnTrac<br>- Parcel Force<br>- Poczta Polska<br>- PonyExpress Post<br>- Pos Indonesia<br>- Pos Daftar<br>- Pos Laju<br>- Pos Malaysia<br>- Post Austria<br>- Post Denmark<br>- Post NL<br>- Posten.no<br>- Posten.se<br>- PPL<br>- Prestige<br>- Purolator<br>- Quick International<br>- R &amp; L Carriers<br>- Royal Mail<br>- Saudi Post<br>- Servientrega<br>- Singapore Post<br>- Southeastern Freight <br>- Star Track Express<br>- Swiss Post<br>- Team Worldwide<br>- TNT<br>- TNT Express Australia<br>- TNT Post NL<br>- TNT UK<br>- Toll IPEC<br>- Tollpost<br>- Turkish Post<br>- UCS<br>- UKMail<br>- Ukrposhta<br>- UPS<br>- UPS Air Cargo<br>- UPS Mail Innovations<br>- UPS Supply Chain Solutions<br>- USPS<br>- Xend<br>- Yode