(813, 'com.jb.gosms.cs', 'GO SMS Pro Czech package', 'GO Dev Team', 'This pack is for GO SMS Pro Czech language support.<p>Install it and change the language in GO SMS Pro’s “Settings –Application Settings—Language selection”<p>The translation will be updated soon, please stay turned. Thanks<p>(Thanks Lukas Stary,Regi,Vít Pe?e?a,Mischell53,Mira Šiler,Lukáš Starý,Josef Nulí?ek,Keltek,Jakub Jáchym for the translation', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jb.gosms.cs', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/OuwBrzRkxmBB56UhCgfhH2g2slvhA4SOOv3YzSpcErDCWVruBKJM1sYA-KRmMJbYByU', 4.62, 'COMMUNICATION', 'Free', '50,000+', ''),
(814, 'com.pil.winslide', 'Sleep Maker Sound Package Lite', 'choi seung pil', 'Sleep Maker Sound Package Lite<p>White Noise. Rain Effect, Fire Effect, Windy Effect.<p>The best way to learn which sounds are most effective for you or your baby is to try as many as possible. These multi-sound package  are a great way to help you.<p>try it.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.pil.winslide', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/7Pu0V_jNiJBF9xQeSySJhb-5QdfNouILT8LGAavXOG7xu0fVLvDE9P9jwB5fzqfeNzQ', 3.96, 'HEALTH_AND_FITNESS', 'Free', '100,000+', ''),
(815, 'com.ngc.fora.dict.mobypron', 'English Pronunciations Package', 'NG-Computing', 'Self-extracting package for using in Fora Dictionary.<p>Fora Dictionary should be installed to use this dictionary.<p># Articles: 175630<br>Download size: ~ 5 MB<br>SD-card space used: ~ 14 MB<p>Manual: <br>Install, extract to SD-card and uninstall.<p>Uninstallation:<br>Dictionary Manager &gt; Dictionary &gt; &quot;Delete permanently&quot;.<p>Source:<br>Grady Ward&#39;s Moby, <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://icon.shef.ac.uk/Moby/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNH29vbGr4hnP1azhBY8OKVD8DtjZA" target="_blank">http://icon.shef.ac.uk/Moby/</a><p>Note: <br>Due to technical limitations, regular characters was used in place of phonetic symbols.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ngc.fora.dict.mobypron', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/B2uMZGDCqLaKvTNgjrehLc1aAy8KXZ1Skr2Wtjyse2zSV0pS_OXFvgpP72qsokGz71nE', 4.21, 'BOOKS_AND_REFERENCE', 'Free', '10,000+', ''),
(816, 'com.pack.navratri', 'Navratri Package', 'osCitas WebSolutions', 'Navratri Package is our sincere endeavor to bring in front of you all the information about Navratri. We have covered in it all the aspects, such as Navratri Improtance, Navratri History, The Puja Vidhi &amp; Vrat Kath.<p>We also have Aartis&#39;s &amp; Chalisa in the praise of Goddess Durga with Lyrics and Audio. Our Application is the exclusive one to bring the Navratri Recepies &amp; Wallpapers. And this app does not require internet connection for downloading files, once installed successfully.<p>Enjoy this Navratri Season with our Complete Navratri Package. May Maa Bring Happiness &amp; Luck to you.<br>Jai Mata Di!!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.pack.navratri', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/5lAI25lIS6qma81aPKU7op4LAi6F0NmjqwgbsspnB2IZBuwrTqMG1ilxFVc8NFsBr0Q', 4.79, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '5,000+', 'android.permission.SET_WALLPAPER'),
(817, 'skyktc.all', 'EngcaVoca Package', '???????', '“The Best Way to Study Vocabulary”<br>When working to improve your vocabulary it’s important to know your goals in order to best choose the way in which you want to learn. One of the most important things to do is to study vocabulary using topics that you like. This will help motivate you.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=skyktc.all', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/58825sy2TxUYVF3CQYglWGARGsvRuIXvvBC6lBoz3-XopN9-YZTx5rvPVEsfa9vIJss-', 3.81, 'EDUCATION', '$5.31', '1,000+', 'android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO, android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS'),
(818, 'com.appsorama.bday', 'Birthday Cards for Facebook', 'Apps-O-Rama', 'Never miss a friend&#39;s birthday again - Get Facebook&#39;s #1 Birthday Card App for your Android device!<br>- See all of your friends&#39; birthdays in chronological order (past, present and future) on our easy-to-use infinity loop display<br>- Get reminders via push notification on the actual day of your friends&#39; birthdays<br>- Browse our awesome selection of birthday cards which you can send and receive for free<br>- Add our widget to your home screen to see upcoming birthdays<p>****FAQ****<p>Q: Is it free?<br>A: Yes! You can post our beautiful cards to your friends&#39; Facebook walls absolutely free.<p>Q: It doesn&#39;t have all my friends&#39; birthdays listed. Why?<br>A: The application uses information provided by Facebook, so if your friend has not set his/her birthday or has chosen not to publicly display his/her birthday then it will not be shown in the Birthday Cards app.<p>Q: I was looking for a calendar but could not find it. Where is it?<br>A: Birthdays are shown in an endless chronological list. Scroll up to see past birthdays. Scroll down to see future birthdays.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.appsorama.bday', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/Dn5vglzC7qaYRhJwm8oJX7Ae-okrnuGGbrTY-gub5EkUQ6_vePuYFwqjuRQE3mVxOQ', 4.45, 'LIFESTYLE', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, com.android.vending.BILLING'),
(819, 'com.supreme.photosaver', 'Facebook Photo Downloader', 'Supreme apps', 'Save photo from Facebook with one click! The most powerful Facebook image downloader plugin!<p>Facebook on the android does not get the attention it deserves and android users cannot save their photos directly. Now Facebook photo downloader allows you to save the photo to your gallery in ONE click! Screen shots are no longer necessary thanks to this app. <p>There are other apps that allow you to save photos from Facebook, but they require you to leave the app. With this one you never leave Facebook! <br>Once saved, you can enjoy your pictures at any time, without relying on the internet. Saving the photo is as simple as sharing a photo with any other type of app. <p>---Features---<br>? Never leave Facebook while saving.<br>? Fastest Facebook photo download<br>? Save images in the highest possible quality.<br>? No login required.(No need to enter your facebook account or password)<br>? Enjoy your downloaded photos without relying on 3G or Internet connection.<br>? It is ultra lightweight. Uses very little storage space.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.supreme.photosaver', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/cbVV5hh2-NoeISfmlr7INtY5iKIMbwo0HF19pV15tB80LVMfCttJoVYeFcqsLlHv1P0', 4.35, 'MEDIA_AND_VIDEO', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, android.permission.DISABLE_KEYGUARD, com.android.launcher.permission.UNINSTALL_SHORTCUT, com.android.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT, android.permission.READ_CONTACTS, android.permission.BLUETOOTH, android.permission.READ_LOGS, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, com.android.browser.permission.READ_HISTORY_BOOKMARKS'),
(820, 'com.ne.facebookphoto', 'Facebook Video Downloader', 'New Essence', 'You can download videos and photo from Facebook to your own phone.<br>And the &#39;Fun TV&#39; feature on Facebook, one of the most Hot funny videos<br>So you can see and manage the files whenever and wherever.<br>View directly from the app, download on my phone and send it to a friends<br>It&#39;s Free!!<p># How to download Video<br>1. Click a video on Facebook<br>2. Choose [Facebook Downloader]<br>3. Done!<p># How to download Photo<br>1. See the picture on Facebook<br>2. Click &#39;Share&#39; on option menu<br>3. Choose [Facebook Downloader] and Done!<p># All files are downloaded at sdcard/Facebook Downloader<p># Please contact with developer if you have any problem about this application. Then I will solve the problem as soon as possible. (Most of problems could be solved by re-installation)', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ne.facebookphoto', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/0d0laJN7t-dQqcuTC8Ihb4wo4J2sB7qaGtrpmybjpFH-j0zkPJ8an8xX_0hd2DHLuzKq', 4.74, 'MEDIA_AND_VIDEO', 'Free', '500,000+', ''),
(821, 'androidPlatform.plugin.multiwindow.facebook', 'Facebook window', 'multi-window platform for android', 'Facebook. The multi-window platform is a new platform that enables you to enjoy the familiar windows feeling on your android device.<br>Open your favorite apps and sites in a new adjustable window and change the way you used to work.<br>You can put it on top of every app you want and do amazing things!<p>keywords: multi, window, float, floating, platform, android, window, windows, plugin, facebook, social, twitter', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=androidPlatform.plugin.multiwindow.facebook', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/X47ffhwpOUJzK3W7ZiNek9H5SITDsDyXHngDCVDiBoajXVEh3AAxLaWKwcrtysE3Nuc', 4.18, 'SOCIAL', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW, android.permission.GET_TASKS, com.android.vending.BILLING'),
