(838, 'com.phonegap.nzbunity', 'NZB Unity', 'Living Type', 'NZB Unity brings together the best applications and services used in the newsgroup community, into one easy to use, integrated interface. New services are being integrated on a regular basis.<p>The current release provides connectivity to SABnzbd, Sickbeard, NZBMatrix, CouchPotato (v2) and Headphones!.<p>Both NZB Unity and the various services it integrates with are in active development and may be prone to unexpected errors or results! Be warned.<p>For those using URL re-writes, or run their SABnzbd, Sickbeard, Couch Potato or Headphones instances in sub-directories, use the port field within settings to input these settings (i.e.: configure port = 8080/sickbeard). This will be directly addressed in a future release.<p>UI overhall development is underway. This will be a slow process, but progress is being made during each release. Stay tuned!<p>Release v5.3.4<br>!General<br>Removed all NZB Matrix Code - RIP NZB Matrix<br>Corrected LivingType News bug<br>Updated Authentication for SABnzbd, Sickbeard and CouchPotato<br>Donate page logo link error fix<br>!SABnzbd<br>Corrected Category selection bug<p>Release v5.3.3<br>SAB Config menu fix<p>Release v5.3.2<br>SAB Back button fix<br>SSL button fix<br>Minor updates<p>Release v5.3.1<br>!General<br>Menu Button fix<br>Backup / Restore Config Settings<br>Lots of UI cleanup<br>Cordova2 upgrade - Speed, Security, Stability<br>Tablet resolution tweaked views on Sickbeard, Couch Potato and Headphones - just testing the waters<br>!Couch Potato<br>Rewritten almost all, heaps of performance improvements<br>!Sickbeard<br>Changed &quot;Season Folders&quot; to &quot;Flatten Folders&quot;<br>!SABnzbd<br>Lots of code cleanup<p>Release v5.2.1<br>Thanks to Martin for such great detailed test result data - ICS fix wouldn&#39;t have come without his help!<br>!Headphones<br>Fix for ICS user&#39;s connection issues<br>Fix for Get Album bug<br>!NZBMatrix<br>Added &#39;Trusted Connection&#39; option - saves API calls<br>!General<br>Migrated most of &#39;General&#39; options / menus to new rendering function in prep for UI overhall<p>Release v5.1.0<br>!General<br>Hide unused services<br>!NZB Matrix<br>Browsing posts fixed<p>Release v5.0.1 <br>Headphones test changes<p>Release v5.0.0<br>! Headphones<br>INITIAL RELEASE!<br>Browse, Pause, Delete and Refresh Artists<br>Browse and Queue Albums<br>Recommend similar Artists<br>Optionally load Artist and Album covers<br>! General<br>Auto API retrieval (Only Android 2.x seems to work - give it a try)<br>Numerous Bug fixes<br>! NZB Matrix<br>Updated Search and Add code<p>Release v4.0.3<br>! General<br>App 2 SD enabled<br>! Sickbeard<br>Multi select / update episodes<br>! NZB Matrix<br>Re-written Browse Posts<p>Release v4.0.2<br>! General<br>Stability and speed improvements<br>Back button issues resolved<br>UI cleanups, bug fixes, the usual stuff<br>! Sickbeard<br>Windows add new show bugfix<br>! Couch Potato<br>Connection issue fix<br>Profile selection during add or modify<p>Release v4.0.x<br>! Couch Potato integration<p>Release v3.0.x<br>! Landscape mode<p>Release v2.1.x<br>! NZB Matrix integration<p>Release v2.0.x<br>! SABnzbd integration<br>! SSL Support!<p>Initial Release:<br>! Sickbeard integration', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.phonegap.nzbunity', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/XN1nk3SaxCTqPYRsiLCLFlmsWKPdZiDZVFd61b_pnylLMCriljaf_uDd5oYdMfROJic', 4.52, 'PRODUCTIVITY', 'Free', '50,000+', ''),
(839, 'com.kevinforeman.sabconnect', 'NZB 360', 'Kevin Foreman', 'Currently Added Services:<br>- SABnzbd, Sick Beard, CouchPotato(v2), Headphones, Unlimited Newznab Indexers<p><br>NZB 360 is a full-featured NZB manager that focuses on providing the best experience possible for controlling all of your NZB needs.<p>Main Features:<br>- Merges all of your NZB-related needs into one beautifully designed and executed experience.<br>- Switch between services simply and quickly, without needing to getting lost in the navigation.<br>- Nexus 7 support with layouts designed specifically to bring easy navigation to the Nexus 7.<br>- Extremely fluid and snappy interface.<br>- Submit Feedback feature allows you to quickly get in touch with developer for support and feature requests.<br>- Backup and restore all settings to/from sdcard.<br>- SSL/TLS support for all services.<br>- Supports HTTP Auth for all included services.  Great for users who run custom apache setups.<br>- Supports reverse proxies.<br>- Supports both local and remote IP/Host addresses and ports for each service.<p><br>SABnzbd Features:<br>- Elegant and informative UI, which brings out subtle information of your queue/history items.<br>- Pause/delete items within your queue.<br>- Pause for &quot;X&quot; time.<br>- Set categories for items in queue.<br>- Set priority for items in queue.<br>- Reorder items in queue.<br>- Rename items in queue.<br>- Full status of items in history.<br>- Delete items and files in history.<br>- Retry failed items.<br>- Innovative quick Speed Limit Threshold set menu.<br>- Pause/Resume entire queue.<br>- Add NZB by file or url.<br>- Associates with NZB files.<br>- Adjustable UI refresh rate.<br>- Wake On Lan (WOL) support.<br>- Restart SABnzbd support.<br>- Clear history.<p><br>Newznab Indexer Features:<br>- Unlimited support for Newznab indexers such as NZBs.org, NZB.su, DogNZB.cr, NZBGeek and many more!<br>- Beautiful &quot;Sexy Movie Layout&quot; that provides Cover art, parse titles/year info, IMDb ratings, and more for each movie while browsing.<br>- Private Newznab indexing support.<br>- Spotweb support.<br>- Browse all categories each indexer supports.<br>- Search content across all categories.<br>- View ratings, comments, grabs, and other indicators that each indexer supports.<br>- View in-depth details of items.<p><br>Sick Beard Features:<br>- Beautiful, XBMC-inspired interface for all TV Show content.<br>- Add new shows.<br>- Edit show qualities.<br>- &quot;Airing Soon&quot; view informs you know when all of your shows air next.<br>- &quot;Missed&quot; view allows you to see any shows that Sick Beard has not yet snatched, with the ability to quickly search for those episodes.<br>- &quot;History&quot; view.<br>- Multiple view layouts for shows.<br>- Elegant and easy to use episode manager, which utilizes batching functionality to quickly and easily manage all of your episode content.<br>- Quick searches for individual episodes.<br>- Restart Sick Beard support.<br>- Clear/trim history.<p><br>CouchPotato(v2) Features:<br>- Beautiful, XBMC-inspired interface for all Movie content.<br>- Add new movies.<br>- Edit movies.<br>- &quot;Wanted, Available, Manage, and History&quot; views.<br>- &quot;Available&quot; tab lets you quickly see which movies have releases available to download.<br>- Force release search.<br>- Restart CouchPotato support.<br>- View movie details (plot, runtime, Directors, Actors, etc).<br>- Force search for all wanted movies.<br>- Force renamer scan to run.<br>- Add from official IMDb app.<br>- View IMDb inline for each movie.<p><br>Headphones Features:<br>- Pretty much everything you&#39;d expect out of headphones.  I ran out of space in Google Play to list all of these features, heh.<p><p>NOTE: Minimum version of SABnzbd+ 0.6 required. Build 499+ of Sick Beard required. CouchPotato version 2 (2.2.1)+ required.  Newznab indexer required to search for content.<p><br>If you have any issues, ideas, questions, or comments, please use the built-in Submit Feedback feature within the application to quickly get in touch with the developer.<p>Thank you, and I really hope you enjoy NZB 360.<p><br>Tags: usenet, sab, sabnzbd, sabnzbd+, client, holo, newsgroup, nzb, 360, nzb360, sickbeard, couchpotato, headphones, couch potato, newznab, nzbs.org, nzb.su, dognzb.cr, spotweb, imdb', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kevinforeman.sabconnect', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/KHUrE41iT3y6i-JyrS2RTtxgV2x9kURHSh53JPDfIZWiP-GtOaBUJJNekWq5QCDcOA', 4.90, 'TOOLS', '$3.99', '5,000+', ''),
(840, 'com.beanian.hub', 'MediaDog', 'beanian', '*** New Widget &amp; History views for CouchPotato &amp; Sickbeard Added ******<br>MediaDog interfaces with SickBeard, CouchPotato, Headphones &amp; SABnzbd to give you a central point to access and control these applications from the comfort of your Android phone.<p>*First on Android with SickBeard<br>*First on Android with Couchpotato<br>*Now First on Android with HEADPHONES!!!<p>The features of each application are:<br>Sickbeard:<br>Search for and add new shows to your SickBeard instance.<br>Set episode &amp; season status to Wanted/Ignored/Archived or Skipped<br>Delete, Pause &amp; Un-Pause shows.<br>Displays your list of shows in a beautiful banner format<br>Displays a list of coming episodes with the date &amp; time of the show<p>CouchPotato:<br>Search for and add new movies to your Couchpotato queue.<br>Add movies to your queue using your custom quality formats.<br>Swipe between your wanted, Downloaded &amp; Snatched queues.<br>Remove movies from your queue.<br>Clear your snatched and downloaded queues in one go.<p>CouchPotato Server(v2) features only:<br>Upgrade the qualities of your wanted and downloaded movies.<br>Browse your entire movie library<br>When searching movies you already have or want are flagged.<br>IMDB Integration. Share a movie from IMDB to MediaDog to add it to your wanted queue<p>Headphones (Beta):<br>View Artist list<br>View Albums for artist <br>Set album status<br>Add artist<p>SABnzbd(requires 0.6.0+):<br>Queue:<br>View your current queue and speed.<br>Rearrange your queue by dragging and dropping queue items<br>Pause, Rename, Delete &amp; change category of individual jobs<br>Pause entire queue<br>History:<br>View history items<br>Failed items highlighted in red<br>View History Item Summary Information<br>Delete Individual history item<br>Delete all history items (Menu-&gt;Clear All History Items)<br>Retry failed job<br>Delete failed job &amp; all associated files<p>MediaDog also support multiple instances of each of these applications. <p>The central hub for Sickbeard, Couchpotato &amp; SABnzbd on Android!<br>Use #mediadog on Twitter to submit feature requests or questions!<br>**************Troubleshooting*****************<br>-Widget only works on Android 3.0+<br>-There is a known issue switching from a CouchPotato v2 server to a v1 server. MediaDog will crash however it will work once restarted.<br>-To refresh sickbeard banners/CouchPotato posters delete the Media Dog folder on your SD card.<br>-If you are having trouble connecting to any of the services verify you can open them in your phone&#39;s browser. If you can&#39;t MediaDog isn&#39;t the problem.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.beanian.hub', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/BsqZRlws2MorIUZn258agjCb2LP-j_NftBBKnF9Rbj96aBBCnAfbGWYJlsnK-3diPA', 4.43, 'PRODUCTIVITY', '$3.00', '1,000+', ''),
(841, 'com.nelissen.couchforwarder', 'Couch Forwarder Free', 'Boris Nelissen', 'Manage all your usenet services in one app, Couch Potato, Sickbeard, Sabnzbd, Headphones and Newznab.<p>This is the perfect usenet / newsgroup companion<p>- Add movies from IMDB directly to you Couch Potato queue with a simple share!<br>- Manage your shows and see upcoming episodes in Sickbeard over http &amp; https<br>- Manage your Sabnzbd downloads and see download history over http &amp; https<br>- Manage your Headphones artists and see detailed information about albums<br>- Search for content on Newznab servers of your choice and directly add nzb files to your Sabznbd queue<p>To remove the ads and support development please consider buying:<br>https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nelissen.payed.couchforwarder<p>This is the alternative to MediaDog and NZB Unity!<p>Join in a discussion here:<br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://forum.xbmc.org/showthread.php?tid%3D128565&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGgcH5F981TWbHezu63LEYhj8QhIw" target="_blank">http://forum.xbmc.org/showthread.php?tid=128565</a><p>Requirements:<br>CouchPotato V2 (Couch Potato Server)<br>IMDB app (Optional)<p>Any comments or suggestions are welcome, please send me an email!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nelissen.couchforwarder', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/UsZIAbO0epL-4869fZqNJNJNN5o7_M-BgRO8iMgyy3z8kOXVhG1JCsb4Ha7zmqClh1M', 4.18, 'MEDIA_AND_VIDEO', 'Free', '10,000+', ''),
(842, 'com.nelissen.payed.couchforwarder', 'Couch Forwarder', 'Boris Nelissen', 'Manage all your usenet services in one app, Couch Potato, Sickbeard, Sabnzbd, Headphones and Newznab.<p>This is the perfect usenet / newsgroup companion<p>- Add movies from IMDB directly to you Couch Potato queue with a simple share!<br>- Manage your shows and see upcoming episodes in Sickbeard over http &amp; https<br>- Manage your Sabnzbd downloads and see download history over http &amp; https<br>- Manage your Headphones artists and see detailed information about albums<br>- Search for content on Newznab servers of your choice and directly add nzb files to your Sabznbd queue<br>- No ads!<br>- You can now export your settings from the Free app!<p>This is the alternative to MediaDog and NZB Unity!<p>Join in a discussion here:<br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://forum.xbmc.org/showthread.php?tid%3D128565&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGgcH5F981TWbHezu63LEYhj8QhIw" target="_blank">http://forum.xbmc.org/showthread.php?tid=128565</a><p>Requirements:<br>CouchPotato V2 (Couch Potato Server)<br>IMDB app (Optional)<p>Any comments or suggestions are welcome, please send me an email!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nelissen.payed.couchforwarder', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/UcH4JW22Yyj4XyYCFo--Y49xB6ejKrRv9aB7jjCxFc1gg4VzM64UdAhOMubenW73HeM', 4.61, 'MEDIA_AND_VIDEO', '$1.88', '1,000+', ''),
(843, 'com.sabdroidex', 'SabdroidEx', 'hellhand', 'SABDroidEx is a frontend for sabnzbd+, Sickbeard and Couchpotato on Android. It is used to monitor your servers and to interact with them in the most complete and intuitive way.<p>General Functions<p>The servers can be contacted behind an Apache web server, separate authentication and access through SSL available, following Android 4.0+ UI Look &amp; Feel.<p>Sabnzbd+ Functions<p>See the list of downloads, see the history, the downloads can be separately paused or cancelled, the refresh rate can be changed, items can be removed from the History, downloads can be added with a direct link to an nzb, <br>downloads can be added by opening an nzb file, Sabnzbd+ server settings can be accessed and changed.<p>SickBeard Functions<p>See the list of Shows, see the seasons for each Show, see the status for each Episode of a Season, change the status for each Episode.<p>CouchPotato Functions<p>See the list of Movies, add movies, view information on available files, choose the release to download.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sabdroidex', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/AiLdM5mSLmsz1gjPX67HUZOypm9ZAeJ3iwbsNZaX7eVFSrlarga1tO5w3ED3d3YQDgg', 4.13, 'TOOLS', 'Free', '10,000+', ''),
(844, 'com.xinstaller', 'xApp Installer Free', 'Mario Coppola', 'xAppInstaller is an Android GUI version of the well known APP Installer PHP version written by TheHijacker (an active member of Xtreamer forum).<p>With xAppInstaller you will easily install additional application and extend the basic usage of your Xtreamer products (eTRAYz, Prodigy and/or Sidewinder3). Here some of most famous packages that will be possible to install on your Xtreamer device:<p>- Transmission, a cross-platform BitTorrent client.<br>- pyLoad, a fast, lightweight and full featured download manager.<br>- SABnzbd, an Open Source Binary Newsreader written in Python.<br>- Sick Beard, a PVR application that searches for and manages your TV shows.<br>- CouchPotato, an automatic NZB and torrent downloader.<br>- MiniDLNA, a server software with the aim of being fully compliant with DLNA/UPnP-AV clients.<br>- MediaTomb, an open source (GPL) UPnP MediaServer with a nice web user interface, it allows you to stream your digital media through your home network and listen to/watch it on a variety of UPnP compatible devices.<br>- .... and many many other interesting and useful packages, currently there are more than 130 packages and the list grow every day.<p>The xAppInstaller will permit you to install/remove/start/stop/backup/restore any packages on your Prodigy, eTRAYz and Sidewinder.<br>xAppInstaller features:<br>- Multilanguage: English, Italian, Slovenian, Russian, Ukranian, Dutch and Spanish<br>- Configure Device available on your network<br>- List all available packages for your device (feed managed by TheHijacker)<br>- List the latest packages added<br>- List packages by categories<br>- List packages by their status (installed/running/stopped/autostarted/using cron/...)<br>- Search a package<br>- Sort the list of packages by name, date added and category<br>- Show package details, comments, links and screenshots<br>- Install/Uninstall application on your devices<br>- Start/Stop application on your devices<br>- Set appliaction properties as autostart and backup/restore<br>- Shutdown/Restart your device<p>Next features:<br>- Autoinstall API App Installer on your device<br>- Modify device MySQL password<br>- Show device details and status (memory, hdd usage, cpu workload, ...)<br>- Tablet optimization<br>- Prodigy TV render optimization<p>Note: Ad Supported. (Ad free version is available! Please search &quot;xApp Installer AdFree&quot;.)<p>Requirements:<br>- Xtreamer device: Prodigy, Sidewinder3, eTRAYz<br>- APP Installer API: xAppInstaller is based on APP Installer API that must be installed on xtreamer product which you wish to manage. Here you can find istructions to install API Installer on your xtreamer device:<br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://forum.xtreamer.net/topic/30625-app-installer-php-api-v102/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHgxoGt_GoS9ts0Biu4gINsLNsUlQ" target="_blank">http://forum.xtreamer.net/topic/30625-app-installer-php-api-v102/</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.xinstaller', 'http://lh6.ggpht.com/SG4nf09GO9_cFfescVXIDCYMwS1vD1F2S2jFvBHw0Qln4PPRVVUdWNUMMdRHpY3pny3a', 3.35, 'TOOLS', 'Free', '5,000+', 'android.permission.DISABLE_KEYGUARD'),
(845, 'com.emtronics.powernzb', 'Power NZB - Android''s NZB App', 'Emile Belanger', 'Power NZB is the most powerful Usenet client for Android, enabling search, RSS, Download, Par2 repair, Unrar and Split file join of binary content. <p>Built in API to access NewNab servers such as: <br>nzb-matrix.eu<br>NZB.su<br>DOGnzb.cr<br>usenet-crawler.com<br>NZBS.org<br>NZBS.in<br>NewzTown<br>etc!<p>NOTICE:<br>nzbX.co has SHUTDOWN, the bottom search for nzbX.co will NOT WORK.<p>The built in file manager lets you manage and open your downloads without leaving the app.<p>Now includes an integrated SABNZBd client, download to your Android device OR send to to your PC!<p>&quot;A picture is worth a thousand words&quot; The Play store only allows 8 screen shots - not nearly enough to show all features!<br>Visit the website Gallery to see more images:<br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://powernzb.co.uk/gallery.html&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNF5T9XvC4RRfN_tthJJbG5JbUrIDg" target="_blank">http://powernzb.co.uk/gallery.html</a><p><br>BOUNS FEATURE:<br>PowerNZB includes the ability to run the Sickbeard Server directly on your Android device! See our other Apps for more details.<p><br>**** Note, the stock Android browser does not download some NZB files correctly, try using Opera or Firefox if there are errors loading NZB files. ****<p><br>Features:<br>*Queue multiple NZB files<br>*Open zip compressed NZBs<br>*Up to 16 simultaneous downloads<br>*Saves partial downloads<br>*Move items up and down queue<br>*Par2 verification and repair<br>*Unrar support<br>*Join files (*.001, *.002 ... etc)<br>*Auto Unrar<br>*Auto Par<br>*Download speed graph<br>*Skip &#39;samples&#39;<br>*NewzNab Search API. Browse and search categories<br>*nzbX.co API<br>*Web view for NZBIndex, MysterBin, NZBSearch, NZB.su, NZBClub, DOGnzb - download within app<br>*RSS support, browser + download<br>*Download throttle<br>*Organise your downloads into folder Categories<br>*Download over Wifi or Mobile<br>*File manager: Open, Delete with multi-select, Rename files or folders<br>*Quick select Alternative Usenet Server<br>*Play audio notification on complete download<br>*Save/Load settings to a file<p>SABNZBd Client features:<br>*Integrated with all NZB search/download above<br>*Multiple servers (2 at the moment)<br>*SSL<br>*Upload from file<br>*Move/Delete/Add/Pause queue items<br>*Change Category<br>*History tab<br>*Remove from History  <br>*Set Speed Limit<p>Future Features:<br>*Browse binary groups<br>*Watch folder<p>NOTE: If you have any issues PLEASE email us - we can not respond to comments below. Thank you.<p><br>Power NZB uses the standard licensing used by most paid apps and as recommended by Google. <br>If you are having any issues with the license on your particular device please contact <a href="mailto:support@powernzb.co.uk">support@powernzb.co.uk</a> for a solution! We can not get in contact from the comments below.<p><br>Note on Web View:<br>Please let me know your prefered nzb search site and we will see if we can add it to the list. It needs to be manual because we need to detect the download links.<br>Note, we can not currently get binsearch.info to work, but NZBIndex is very similar.<p>Note on notification Icon:<br>In order to prevent Android from killing the Download Service an icon needs to be present in the Notification area - this shows the service is active.<br>The Download Service will automatically shut down after 60 seconds when there are no items in the NZB Queue, no items in the Download Queue, and Power NZB is not in the foreground.<br>Therefore to save battery clear these queues when not in use.<p>Note on download speed:<br>Your maximum download speed may vary depending on device, these are roughly the speeds being seen:<p>Low end device: 400K/s to 800K/s<br>Mid range device: 800K/s to 1500K/s<br>High end device 1000K/s to 5500K/s<p>The bottle neck for downloading may be your SD Card, the cheaper ones have very poor random write speeds.<p><br>Refund Policy:<br>If you would like a refund just email <a href="mailto:support@powernzb.co.uk">support@powernzb.co.uk</a> with your Android Play recipt and we will issue a refund.<p>!Honeycombe 3.2 users! The app will currenty crash if you try and use the &#39;Compatiblity Zoom&#39; mode, this is being investigated. The app will work OK otherwise.<p><br>You need to download the free par library for par2 functionality.<p>Keywords:<br>Newsgroup usenet nzb leech download par par2 unrar quickpar newzbin rss sab sabnzb nzb.su', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.emtronics.powernzb', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/EU5yiI7d0xzc8gWRB8hC3IHjgMCzuQGegBlBPnzZns-TRdx5IcUyxVckHeV29TUnRzY', 4.67, 'TOOLS', '$3.76', '5,000+', 'com.android.vending.CHECK_LICENSE'),
(846, 'ch.berard.xbmcremotebeta', 'Music Pump XBMC Remote', 'Android Music Pump', 'Music Pump XBMC Remote is a remote control for xbmc. It&#39;s main purpose is to listen to your music collection and watch Movies/TV Shows<p>It supports many features and is fully compatible with XBMC Eden, Frodo and Gotham alpha builds:<p>* Music:<br>  - Browsing your xbmc library and playlists without having to turn on the tv<br>  - Music files on xbmc can be played through xbmc or can be streamed to your android device. <br>  - Caching of music database for super fast access<br>  - Filtering in every list<br>  - Music rating support (frodo or newer)<br>  - Start playlists in party mode on xbmc<p>* Video:<br>  - Browse your Movie collection and play/resume the movie and the trailer on xbmc<br>  - Browse your TV Shows and play/resume episodes on xbmc<br>  - Show/Hide watched videos<br>  - Mark movies and tv shows as watched/unwatched<br>  - Change subtitles and audio tracks<p>* Files:<br>  - Browse all files (music / video / files) and play/queue single files or directories. <br>  - Add any file or directory to the (local) favorites for faster access<p>* Addons:<br>  - Browse through your music and video addons and play items on xbmc<br>  - Add any addon to the favorites for faster access<p>* Other features<br>  - Select a video/music/picture from the file manager and play it on xbmc. <br>  - Rescan music and video library<br>  - Homescreen widget<br>  - Lockscreen widget<br>  - Headphone remote support (play/pause, next, previous). On headphone remotes with a single button, double click plays next song<br>  - Optimized for phone and tablets<br>  - Virtual keyboard<br>  - Works with Raspberry Pi<p>If you like this app and want to support further development please get the in-app unlocker. It will also enable many additional features:<br>  - Sync/download music files (single files, albums, playlists, playqueue..). <br>  - Music Pump can be used as simple music player to play music files stored on your android device or to stream music file to xbmc similar to airplay.<br>  - Optimized tablet layout for the music section with artist / album info<br>  - Themes<p>Do you want to help translate Music Pump XBMC Remote into your language? Create an account and translate it at <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.getlocalization.com/musicpumpxbmcremote&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNHsV7Ixkmg0CBonPCXs9HiVm6AjzQ" target="_blank">http://www.getlocalization.com/musicpumpxbmcremote</a><br>Setup instructions:<br>In XBMC go to System -&gt; Settings -&gt; Network <br>Enable the following settings:<br>  - Allow control of XBMC via HTTP<br>  - Allow programs of this system to control XBMC<br>  - Allow programs on other systems to control XBMC<p>In order to see your music and video files you need to enable the library function within xbmc and scan your music and video files to the library.<p><br>Common problems: <br>  - The app works with XBMC 11 Eden and Frodo =&gt; I have not tested older versions and they will not work properly since the json-rpc interface changed. <br>  - If you are using &quot;nightly builds&quot; things may not always work as expected since the json-rpc api is work in progress. =&gt; Report bugs in the xbmc forum at the link below <br>  - If you cannot connect check that your firewall does not block incoming connections on port 8080 (http port) and 9090 ( for notifications)<br>  - If music stops after playing a song tcp port 9090 is probably not reachable or used by another application. If it is still not working get the unlocked version and enable &quot;use xbmc queue&quot; in the settings<br>  - Playlists in xbmc must be in a special folder. See <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://wiki.xbmc.org/index.php?title%3DPlaylists&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFsJgPTK0aGinbr9S___YVAKY0sBQ" target="_blank">http://wiki.xbmc.org/index.php?title=Playlists</a><p>You can get the current xbmc version at <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://xbmc.org/download/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFMVygZhvXhazJe2F4lQqvTBSPnMw" target="_blank">http://xbmc.org/download/</a><p>IMPORTANT: For help and bug reports visit the xbmc forum at <br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://forum.xbmc.org/showthread.php?tid%3D131303&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNH6yujmxSuZLuN6zDoZnfO1AmbJjg" target="_blank">http://forum.xbmc.org/showthread.php?tid=131303</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=ch.berard.xbmcremotebeta', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/QYXDX3WiFhDYi8hG1Iz3q0iRUgRMbIIgUEznqxfm1YOcr0gmYo0PObY_6euLdveFJ9Kf', 4.52, 'MEDIA_AND_VIDEO', 'Free', '50,000+', 'android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_MULTICAST_STATE, com.android.vending.BILLING'),
(847, 'com.pandaeyes.tvapp', 'Foshow', 'PandaEyes', 'Foshow is a simple and stylish tool for managing many popular Usenet and Torrent services and applications.<br>It currently supports Sabnzb, Sickbeard, CouchPotato and Transmission. With many more on the way.<p>Foshow adds many useful features such as:<br>- Offline episode pinning. Take your shows with you when you&#39;re on the move.<br>- Search Newznab sites directly. <br>- Add movies via the integrated barcode scanner.<br>- Get movie and show suggestions based on what you watch.<br>- Settings webserver. Get up and running in seconds by configuring Foshow with a webbrowser. <br>- System notifications. Know exactly when your favourite shows are available. <p>Managing all things NZB has never been easier.<p>Update regularly. Please send any feature requests using the in-app option.<p>Keep up-to-date at <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://pandaeyesdev.wordpress.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFnBz8kEMBvthUFWdCL873rYGPjdg" target="_blank">http://pandaeyesdev.wordpress.com/</a><br>Note: A Sickbeard, Sabnzb or Couchpotato installation is required to use this app. <p>Disclaimer<br>Foshow is a manager for various usenet based tools, it is not a tool to download files illegally. The developer does not condone piracy and will take no responsibly for anyone using this software.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.pandaeyes.tvapp', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/NmZf3Zbs4Qozqf-wOwoIe2fbn_u2GZQPAYmUPsvU2og9Dipd6zKEf3FUihecfSDk2DI', 4.42, 'MEDIA_AND_VIDEO', 'Free', '1,000+', 'com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.CAMERA, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED'),
(848, 'com.halcyonsystems.nzbtrend', 'NZB Trend', 'Halcyon Systems', 'NZB Trend will keep you up to date on the hottest releases on Usenet. We are polling some of the top indexers to get you the most up to date and best information available. It will show you the top 20 Movies, and TV shows that are being downloaded right now. You can now also see the top 10 Games and Music releases. Please watch for updates as we are constantly upgrading. <br>NZB Trend will show you:<br>•	Release Name<br>•	Publish Date<br>•	IMDB Rating and Link (If applicable)<br>•	Cover Art (If available)<br>•	Genre (If available)<br>•	Size<br>•	Number of files<br>•	If the file is password protected<br>•	Platform (Xbox, PS3 or PC)<br>•	Plenty more to come with future upgrades<br>Tags: index, usenet, sab, sabnzbd, sabnzbd+, client, newsgroup, nzb, sickbeard, couch potato, newznab, nzbs.org, nzb.su, dognzb.cr, nzbx.co, imdb, smackdownonyou.com, nzbmatrix, binsearch.org, megasearch, couchpotato, headphones, head, phones, sick, beard, indexer, rottentomatoes.com, rottentomato', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.halcyonsystems.nzbtrend', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/RhxiDd74L0uVq8tpQiuq0Vr0KrcpgmDCW1QDOj1CMVWpvBAz0d1c7uXCWF_OjFh9aQ', 4.25, 'TOOLS', 'Free', '100+', ''),
(849, 'com.qonstrukt.qouchnzb', 'Qouch NZB', 'Qonstrukt', 'Qouch NZB is a trimmed down version of the highly acclaimed iOS app Qouch, which provides a portable frontend to SABnzbd with the following features: <p>- Support for multiple servers <br>- Support for SSL and reverse proxies <br>- Manage your download queue and history <br>- Search on several well-known index sites and add results directly to your queue <br>- Open NZB files directly with Qouch and add them to your SABnzbd queue<br>- Change the category, priority, post processing and script from within Qouch <br>- The required API key will be automatically detected <p>More functionality will be added soon. Starting with support for CouchPotato and Sick Beard. Get the app now for an extra low price before it might get pricier as features are added.<p>Follow us at <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://twitter.com/QonstruktQouch&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGPp6ZAEEdeniBiavsFZRntltdujg" target="_blank">http://twitter.com/QonstruktQouch</a> and leave your feedback so we can make our app even better. Or visit us on Facebook: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://facebook.com/Qouch&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFkaykg9fdGD9TVteADK3byINOYJA" target="_blank">http://facebook.com/Qouch</a><p>If you have any issues running the program, or connecting to your server, please contact us through the before mentioned Twitter account or through e-mail at <a href="mailto:qouch@qonstrukt.nl">qouch@qonstrukt.nl</a>, because we cannot respond to any of your feedback in the review section.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.qonstrukt.qouchnzb', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/hPIxf4HzAvmeNPdahPWhNHphyVgo-vmS1W8lhe5W02NCQkeGn7Oo_Nib71sKnPrQ_vY', 4.40, 'MEDIA_AND_VIDEO', '$1.02', '100+', ''),
(850, 'com.inxile.BardTale', 'The Bard''s Tale', 'inXile entertainment', '????? ALMOST FREE FOR CYBER WEEK! ?????<br>????? “The Bard’s Tale is easily the funniest game I’ve ever played” – IGN ?????<br>????? Google Play Editor&#39;s Choice ?????<br>?????     Best of 2012 - Games      ?????<p>They said it couldn’t be done… a full-scale massive 3D epic role-playing game on Android!  See why it’s the BIGGEST Android game ever made!<p>NOTE: Additional assets downloaded after install require at least 1.7GB of free space.<p>RECOMMENDED DEVICE SPECIFICATION: 1GHz or higher CPU; Adreno 205, Tegra 2, SGX 540 or Mali 400 or higher GPU.<p>“The Bard’s Tale is easily the funniest game I’ve ever played, and I’ve played all the funny games out there.” – IGN<p>You are the Bard, a selfish rogue weary of pointless sub-quests and rat-infested cellars.  Through magical song you summon characters to join you in battle, heal your party, and take damage on your behalf.  Ready your weapon as you embark on a quest for coin and cleavage!<p>“Ready your weapon and bladder as you embark on this ridiculously addicting quest and the funniest adventure of the year, The Bard’s Tale” – Game Chronicles<p>Play The Bard’s Tale today on your favorite compatible Android device*.  Prepare to immerse yourself in over 20-30 hours of adventure, featuring:<p>• 50 enemy types (not counting bosses!) <br>• A vast world to explore with towns, wild forests, rivers, castles, towers, secret dungeons, snowy mountains, caverns, haunted tombs and more <br>• A full cast of bizarre NPC’s <br>• Over a dozen special boss enemies to defeat <br>• 16 magical characters to discover and then summon at will to aid you <br>• Over 150 unique items of weaponry, armor, instruments, tokens, artifacts and loot! <br>• More Song &amp; Dance numbers than any other game, including a zombie dance-off! <br>• Over 14 hours of outstanding voice-acting from top Hollywood talent, including Cary Elwes (The Princess Bride) as the Bard, and the inimitable Tony Jay as the Narrator<p>But wait! That’s not all! Enjoy these great new additions in the Android version:<p>New Features:<br>• Autosave—option to save automatically when you near a save-book in game.<br>• Time-Savers—optional in-app purchases are available to pump up your Bard and save you time! (Note: All such items are attainable through normal game-play, with time and persistence, just as in the original console release.)  <br>• Includes the original classic The Bard’s Tale trilogy!<br>   + The Bard&#39;s Tale 1: Tales of the Unknown<br>   + The Bard&#39;s Tale 2: The Destiny Knight, and<br>   + The Bard&#39;s Tale 3: Thief of Fate<p>“This game is satire in its sharpest form” – Cheat Code Central<p>Play The Bard’s Tale today!<p>Support:<br>We hear you, and we are committed to improving The Bard’s Tale for Android.  Please send support questions/comments through The Bard’s Tale Support link below.  You are also welcome to join the discussion and get the latest news on our Facebook product page “The Bard’s Tale”.<p>IT IS HUGE!<br>Please note: Asset installation requires at least 1.7GB of free space on your device.  Thank you for your patience with the download time.<p>Android adaptation by Square One Games.<p>* Compatible with Android 2.3 and higher. XPeria Play Optimized.<p>Native Gamepad Support:<br>   o Wii Classic Controller (native or with free WiimoteController App)<br>   o Xbox 360 &amp; Logitech F310/510/710 in X mode.<br>   o PS3 SixAxis and Dualshock (native or with SixAxis Controller App). If using Sixaxis Controller app, use default key mappings set “Enable Gamepad” option to be “ON”.<br>   o NYKO PLAYPAD &amp; PLAYPAD PRO<br>   o MOGA Controller (with MOGA app or ObsidianX IME)<br>   o MOGA PRO (HID and Pivot App)<br>   o GameStop Red Samurai<br>   o Green Throttle (requires GT Arena app)<br>   o NVIDIA Project Shield<p>SixAxis, WiiController &amp; MOGA IMEs must be disabled to play original Bard’s Tale trilogy.<p>Supported languages: English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, Russia, Korean, Polish', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.inxile.BardTale', 'https://lh4.ggpht.com/uy9o3xnhIzWp8aoWC9gCSa3mr-nTLBfC6pyphKlH5CAuSjcFFCJvpsXYuOTmg5iu8A', 4.70, 'ARCADE', '$0.99', '100,000+', 'android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, android.permission.INTERNET, android.permission.WAKE_LOCK, android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE'),
(851, 'mominis.Generic_Android.Bouncy_Bill_Easter_Tales', 'Bouncy Bill Easter Tales', 'PlayScape', 'Guess what? Bill is back again! Especially for Easter DAY and he’s on a quest to find the magical Easter egg! Get in and get hooked in this joyful Easter atmosphere!<p>Once again, Zorik the Evil Wizard has cast a spell on poor Bill, captivating him in an endless spiral of Easter eggs hunting. Bill is now forced to jump and jump until he finds the magical Easter egg that will help him undo Zorik’s evil spell …<p>Want to break the spell? All you need to do is help Bill bounce on the magical platforms until he reaches the magical Easter egg. You’ll have to be extremely careful when you land on the magical platforms on your quest! If you play it wisely and get to the magical egg, a big surprise is waiting for you… so are you ready for it?  <p>How to play?<br>• Simply tap to jump<br>• A long tap will allow you to jump for longer period of time<p>Highlights:<br>• 24 new festive levels that will get you into the holiday spirit!<br>• Magical platforms and colorful Easter eggs in each level<p>A quick reminder of Bouncy Bill’s Story: <br>Bouncy Bill is a lovable but unlucky turtle that has been cursed by the evil wizard, Zorik, and lost his ability to move left and right. He can only jump upright! Now he is in a race against time to remove the evil spell.<br>Bouncy Bill needs your help to jump vertically onto the moving platforms in the sky and reach his destination as quickly as possible where he might win back his abilities to move around in any direction he wants! There are some tricky moves involved here and you need to land carefully on each platform or else Bouncy Bill might have to bounce forever!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=mominis.Generic_Android.Bouncy_Bill_Easter_Tales', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/om5eeu8VC-vz6QrflHAE43BT9wZtSXBMMa5k262Nis93lRa53KDKBRaTzIBgL5s5Onv_', 4.39, 'ARCADE', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'android.permission.INTERNET, android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE, com.mominis.permission.preferences.provider.READ_WRITE, com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.WAKE_LOCK, android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE'),
(852, 'mominis.Generic_Android.Puppy_Tales', 'Puppy Tales', 'PlayScape', 'It was one early morning when our puppy&#39;s nap was disturbed by an unusual green one eyed and quite rude visitor...<p>Driven by both boredom and curiosity, little puppy started following the intriguing intruder. But then, like so many other heroic stories, something unexpected happened; Puppy tripped over a rock into a mysterious unusual hole in ground. This very unusual hole was no normal hole, but a portal to another peculiar and very distant dimension – a home to strange looking monsters with unusual abilities… <br>And this is how the tales of a small but rather brave puppy begun.<p>Help our brave little puppy fight his way back home to his cozy doghouse and bowl full of delicious treats. Jump, dash and fly in order to save him from the strange looking monsters! If you fight right, you might get to see how the puppy tales end.<p>How to play: <br>- Tap the jump button to jump and the action button to use your special abilities<br>- Jump on the monsters to destroy them <br>- Collect tags, dog biscuits and coins to reach a better score<br>- Use different charms to enhance your performance<br>- Get upgrades, charms and costumes to diversify your gaming experience in the store<p>Highlights: <br>- Many challenging and engaging levels <br>- 3 different wonder worlds to explore<br>- Amazing abilities little puppy can learn and use<br>- Unique enemies to pop and squash<br>- Puppy costumes, power ups and upgrades in a cool store<br>- Interactive tutorials<p>Puppy Tales was developed by the talented team of Sticky Brainz <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://stickybrainz.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNH3xylvCvvpK9cps_t-aVzzLgRRJQ" target="_blank">http://stickybrainz.com/</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=mominis.Generic_Android.Puppy_Tales', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/LQdjMnh-OYEhVtbpCGWw7D-4rlWajHjlZwgZl6JKCZbAqIAt9mX_wKR6NWPM7biScA', 4.33, 'ARCADE', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.INTERNET, android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE, com.mominis.permission.preferences.provider.READ_WRITE, com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.WAKE_LOCK, android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE'),
(853, 'com.tabtale.fairytaleprincessdressup', 'Fairy Tale Princess Dress Up', 'TabTale', 'Calling all Princesses! Dress Up with Fabulous Fashion in this Creative Game! Play Dressup with 4 Beautiful Princesses from Classic Fairy Tales! Visit magical places with your Princess in this Gorgeous and Stylish Game!<p>Cinderella, the Princess and the Pea, Snow White and Sleeping Beauty - all of your favorite princesses together in a creative, magical and interactive dressup game! Show off your fashion skills and imagination by mixing and matching gowns, crowns, accessories and more. Hundreds of fashion combinations to choose from! Kids can even make Cinderella, Snow White, the Princess and the Pea or the Sleeping Beauty talk with our voice-recording microphone!  Make up your own dialogue and dress up your individual fairy tale princess in fantastic fashions in a wonderful make believe dressup game.  Visit the palace, the garden and the magical kingdom - tons to explore.  Kids can take their fashion sense and dress up their princesses in this creative game!<p>9 item categories in Fairy Tale Princess Dressup Game:<br>? Crowns, sparkly, festive and funky<br>? Hairstyles - up, down, cool hair styles!<br>? Necklaces - jewels, colorful, fancy and fun<br>? Dresses - gorgeous and fabulous!<br>? Shirts - different styles for different princesses<br>? Gloves - don’t forget that a princess likes her gloves!<br>? Pants - lots to choose from<br>? Skirts - short, long, lots of styles<br>? Shoes - high heels or casual - you can never have too many pairs!<p>You’ll find all you need to design and style the perfect princess! Put gloves on Cinderella, fancy shoes on Snow White, funky crowns on the Princess and the Pea and gorgeous dresses on the Sleeping Beauty, and get the princesses ready for a party!<p>This interactive princess dressup app provides endless hours of fashion fun with its animated scenes loaded with colorful effects and engaging interactions.  Cinderella and Snow White join Sleeping Beauty and the Princess and the Pea in a fashionable game kids will love!  With amazing high-quality illustrations, it’s just like dressing up a real princess!  Cinderella and Snow White have never looked so good!<p>Features in Fairy Tale Princess Dressup Game:<br>? 4 beautiful princesses including Sleeping Beauty and the Princess and the Pea from the most famous fairy tales.<br>? Hundreds of dress up combinations.<br>? Visit 4 fully-interactive scenes and discover fun activities.<br>? Record your own voice -  use your own voice and bring Cinderella and Snow White to life.<p>Parents and kids are our best reviewers and help us create and improve our apps.<br>We always welcome your suggestions, comments and thoughts. If you have a moment, feel free to rate and review our app.<br>Please note that we aren&#39;t able to respond to reviews in the Google Play store, but we&#39;d love to get your feedback to our email: support@TabTale.com<p>ABOUT TabTale:<br>Search “TabTale” on Google Play and discover more incredible apps for young kids.<br>TabTale’s smart games provide an exciting, interactive, and rich educational experience.<br>Filled with innovative and engaging activities, each application inspires creativity and<br>imagination in a way that is uniquely enjoyable and stimulating. Let the games begin! More<br>games are coming soon....<p>Join our Facebook Page: www.facebook.com/TabTale<br>Follow us on Twitter: @TabTale<p>If you&#39;re having problems with downloads, installs, refunds, payments, or Google Play access, please contact Google Play team through the Google Play Help Center at https://market.android.com/support/ and user forum at <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.google.com/support/forum/p/Android%2BMarket&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGMB57rqQxydb8LzijGwwV2fe05Rw" target="_blank">http://www.google.com/support/forum/p/Android+Market</a>.<p>By downloading this application you agree to the Terms of Use of TabTale Ltd. Which are available to your review on <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://tabtale.com/terms-of-use/&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNGtXS3NcU8z4oZKZHIjoUG0rTsf5Q" target="_blank">http://tabtale.com/terms-of-use/</a>.<p>NEED HELP?<br>Contact us 24/7 with any questions or comments:<br>support@TabTale.com', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tabtale.fairytaleprincessdressup', 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a2fq27kfaC4', 4.26, 'CASUAL', 'Free', '1,000,000+', 'android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO, android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, android.permission.INTERNET, android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED, android.permission.VIBRATE, android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE'),
(854, 'com.whisperarts.tales', 'Fairy tales and storybooks', 'Whisper Arts', 'Popular russian fairy tales for kids - all in one place! (All sounds and texts are in Russian only!)<p>Bright, cheerful, colorful pictures will cheer up you and your baby. Spend time with benefits. Read with pleasure!<p>Management is so simple that even cope with a 2-year-old kid.<p>In the catalog contains your favorite fairy tales:<br>- Turnip<br>- The Wolf and the Seven Little Kids<br>- The Three Little Pigs<br>- Gingerbread Man<br>- Tower-<br>- Speckled Hen<br>- Masha and the Bear<br>- Fox sister and the Wolf<br>- The Three Bears<br>- Two Greedy Bear<br>- The Tale of the Fisherman and the Fish<br>- Geese Swans<br>- The winged, hairy, oily yes<br>- Cockerel - golden comb<br>- Jack Frost<br>- The Fox and the Thrush<br>- The Princess and the Pea<br>- A man and a Bear<br>- Zayushkina hut<br>- Porridge from an ax<br>- Cock and zhernovtsy<br>- Cat Vorkot, Kotofey Kotofeich<br>- The Frog Princess<br>and many others.<p>Enjoy your reading!<p>Watch for updates. Catalog is constantly updated with new stories.<p>Want to receive the latest news about the application? Subscribe to the news group <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.facebook.com/WhisperArts&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNF5PCVquyeD7vLVfFHF3pND79eXhQ" target="_blank">https://www.facebook.com/WhisperArts</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.whisperarts.tales', 'http://lh3.ggpht.com/7yWxLPwaGlP46TBrb1a0hQNl6DzNhI75lNDBjnSai5E72nrV0zMyQUcswpPMJbbq7w', 4.36, 'BOOKS_AND_REFERENCE', 'Free', '500,000+', 'android.permission.CHANGE_COMPONENT_ENABLED_STATE'),
(855, 'com.centralbytes.forgottentales', 'Forgotten Tales RPG', 'DM Studio', 'The game offers many hours of classic RPG gameplay, exciting story, tons of diversified locations, monsters and quests. Get lost in arid deserts, endless forests, dark dungeons, explore snowy wastelands. Gather a party of adventurers and fight against knights, archers, trolls, orcs, barbarians,  dragons, skeletons and many other enemies. Explore a vast heroic fantasy world. Become a legend yourself. Travel the world of Forgotten Tales to meet new friends, find treasure, and encounter monsters! Use a variety of weapons to take out enemies in this real time RPG. Gain experience and levels. Solve quests, find hidden treasures and improve your equipment and skills. Use several types of weapons and magic spells. If you like role playing games (or books/movies like Conan or Lord of the Rings) you will enjoy this game. The graphics will remind you right away of the old PC games you used to play with it&#39;s top-down perspective. A medieval RPG that will bring back memories of games like Baldur&#39;s Gate or Diablo. Hack and slash, action and classic rpg fuse in one ultimate game: Forgotten Tales. This role playing game is completely free. Try the best open world RPG for Android!', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.centralbytes.forgottentales', 'https://lh3.ggpht.com/kNzAjfEXlY5k_QtyyxVZRu0zJrrKDZZwjekfquhZVkvznfvh064XgvGglid2bJ4_9g', 4.05, 'ARCADE', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.INTERNET, android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.VIBRATE, com.android.vending.BILLING, android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION, android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE, android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE, android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE');
