(856, 'com.thetisgames.zombiefree', 'Zombie Night: A Survival Tale', 'Thetis Games', 'Take back Los Angeles city after the invasion of zombies!<p>The story takes place in the Los Angeles metropolitan area. As a survivor, you need to search for a safe haven away from the shuffling hordes of walking zombies! They want to devour any living thing they catch! Your best friend: your M16 rifle and Shotgun.<p>????? &quot;Be aware! This game is quite scary!&quot;<p>Features:<br>• Great FPS (First Person Shooter) combat game.<br>• Attack realistic zombies.<br>• Get inside buildings to protect yourself from the hordes of zombies!<br>• Play with two different weapons. Explode the zombies heads!<br>• Play in four different missions, all in a real world environment:<br>      - Tutorial Mission: &quot;Warehouse&quot;<br>      - Mission 2: &quot;Take Back Los Angeles&quot;<br>      - Mission 3: &quot;Save Hollywood&quot;<br>      - Mission 4: &quot;Survive!!!&quot;<p>????? &quot;The most expected Zombie game for Android!&quot; - The Game Magazine 2013<br>????? Listen to the noises, and take advantage over the undead searching for you<br>????? Frequent updates, so the game is always getting better<p>Like us on Facebook: www.facebook.com/Thetis.Free.Fun.Games', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.thetisgames.zombiefree', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/9QDHyPDB7lAIYzYSqKXoE35Il_NIFkjGV05Rg1wYrOz-3kkpMdU8WfcPLEWl2jXDpVoo', 3.28, 'ARCADE', 'Free', '100,000+', 'com.android.vending.CHECK_LICENSE, android.permission.INTERNET, android.permission.WAKE_LOCK, android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE, android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE'),
(857, 'hu.info2k5.msd.CreepyTales', 'Creepy Tales', 'MSD', 'A collection of short stories, tales and urban legends designed to disturb and scare the reader. This application contains 100 stories organized in 7 categories.<p>If you are not scared enough, check out this app too: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://goo.gl/GnJb2&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNFabB0Ft081evh9xVGkpRZCdDX19Q" target="_blank">http://goo.gl/GnJb2</a>', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=hu.info2k5.msd.CreepyTales', 'http://lh4.ggpht.com/H_uVtxx6UQSp8Q3rRXOE1ezGMgKgGpYFmPVyQas9nqOvKZLeQaeorRxfiV5PrcKVjEw', 4.49, 'ENTERTAINMENT', 'Free', '100,000+', ''),
(858, 'com.tabtale.xmastale.google', 'Christmas Tale: kids Storybook', 'TabTale', 'A Christmas Tale Comes Alive in A Spectacular Interactive Storybook! Packed with coloring pages, puzzles and many more fantastic activities! A Revolutionary Reading Experience for Christmas &amp; the Holiday Season!<p>The Christmas Tale brings the joy of Christmas and the festivities of the holiday season together in a magnificent interactive story. Packed with gorgeous HD graphics and sound effects, young kids will experience Santa Claus, the elves, his sleigh and reindeer and the excitement of XMAS through a beautifully written story combined with engaging activities both children and their parents will love!<p>What’s Inside Christmas Tale kids Storybook:<br>? Make Music by tapping the Christmas Tree Ornament<br>? Create a XMAS “Wish List” and send it to Santa Claus or email it to a friend or relative<br>? Kids learn to spell the words “tree,” “reindeer,” “sky,” “snowman”&amp; more<br>? Take your time and try to find all the amazing interactions in each page yourself.<br>? Improved menu system makes navigation easier?<p>NEW exciting and educational games on each page of a Christmas Tale!<br>? Jigsaw puzzles - Awesome puzzles enhance the story and promote critical thinking skills<br>? Paint-a-Picture - Dozens of coloring pages and paints<br>? Get crafty with your kids and share their masterpieces with friends!<br>? Memory Match - Fire up your child’s memory skills with this smart activity!<br>? Placement Puzzle - Place a character in their puzzle piece<br>? Find the Item - Critical thinking skills and memory come together in this fun activity<br>? Memorize and Place - A great memory game that relates to the story and sharpens retention<p>This charming Christmas Tale story brings the power of the Christmas spirit and the joy of giving, together in a fantastic and interactive story. Come meet Santa Claus and his wife at home in the North Pole as they prepare for Christmas. The XMAS countdown is on - and a “Countdown” clock shows just how many days there are until XMAS. Listen to Santa Claus’s crackling fireplace that roars as a family of elves warms themselves in front of it. Play with the kids outside as they make snowballs and tap the snowman and see all of his cool outfits. Watch the kids dream about Santa Claus and Christmas morning. Join Santa Claus and his reindeer as he delivers presents to kids around the world.<p>Christmas Tale kids Storybook Features:<br>?Fantastic HD illustrations covering all book pages.<br>?“Read to Me” will automatically read the story to you<br>?“Read it Myself” will allow you to control the reading yourself.<br>?“Auto Play” automatically reads the entire story to you<br>?Recording Microphone that allows you to create your own dialogue for the characters<br>?Engage in numerous fun activities on every page and experience an interactive XMAS story!<p>WE VALUE YOUR FEEDBACK:<br>We always welcome your feedback, comments and suggestions- please take a minute to rate<br>and review this app :) You can also contact us at: support@TabTale.com<p>ABOUT TabTale:<br>Search “TabTale” on Google Play and discover more outstanding apps for young kids.<br>TabTale’s interactive storybooks provide an exciting and rich reading experience for many<br>of the most beloved children&#39;s stories. Filled with innovative and engaging activities, each<br>book inspires young children’s creativity and imagination in a stimulating, enjoyable and<br>interactive way. More fantastic stories and games by TabTale LTD are coming soon. . .<p>Join our Facebook Page: www.facebook.com/TabTale<br>Follow us on Twitter: @TabTale<p>We do not support our coloring game on devices using the Ardeno GPU by Qualcomm yet. We are currently working on this issue and hope to have it resolved soon!<p>By downloading this application you agree to the Terms of Use of TabTale Ltd. which are available to your review on <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://tabtale.com/terms-of-use&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNF-m9tdkqBW4NgK4ZoHyXj_O-N4fQ" target="_blank">http://tabtale.com/terms-of-use</a>.<p>NEED HELP?<br>Contact us 24/7 with any questions or comments:<br>support@TabTale.com', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tabtale.xmastale.google', 'https://lh5.ggpht.com/3-7DF6QRPRkC-xtbaiN5KY-tM5DbLzYUHSiZ4FGbTQPD-LduBVFpylwKYBeQ2NH6tUVp', 4.45, 'EDUCATION', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO, android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS, com.android.vending.BILLING'),
(859, 'com.g5e.strix.android', 'Tales from the Dragon Mountain', 'G5 Entertainment', 'Mina&#39;s dreams about her grandmother Kate have become unbearable nightmares. Haunted by one dream of the grandma’s house in flames, Mina takes a trip to her family&#39;s estate in Pozoj. And so began what turned into the greatest adventure of her life! Join Mina, searching Pozoj, solving dozens of puzzles, and meeting mythical creatures.  Defeat the evil spirit called Strix in Tales from the Dragon Mountain: The Strix, a fun Hidden Object Puzzle Adventure game! <p>TRY IT FREE, THEN UNLOCK THE FULL ADVENTURE FROM WITHIN THE GAME!<p>? 32 unique fantasy locations to explore <br>? 21 entertaining puzzles to solve <br>? Meet 10 mythical creatures in your search! <br>? 6 mysterious chapters <br>? Stunning graphics and a soothing soundtrack<br>____________________________ <p>***Sign up now for a weekly round-up of the best from G5 Games! www.g5e.com/e-mail***<br>____________________________ <p>***G5 Games - New game apps every week!***<p>Collect them all! Search for &quot;g5&quot; in Google Play! <p>Adventure: <p>? Games Navigator – By G5 Games <br>? The Secret Society®<br>? Special Enquiry Detail 2<br>? Nightmares from the Deep™<br>? Abyss: The Wraiths of Eden <br> <br>Strategy: <p>? Virtual City Playground®<br>? The Island: Castaway® <br>? Doomsday Preppers™ <br>? Youda Survivor <br>? Stand O’Food® 3 <br>____________________________ <p>VISIT US: www.g5e.com <br>WATCH US: www.youtube.com/g5enter <br>FIND US: www.facebook.com/g5games <br>FOLLOW US: www.twitter.com/g5games', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.g5e.strix.android', 'https://lh6.ggpht.com/b6tCqr4VH3569Qq8T1iYANi2OEqRghsZ5B42Q0OIDEw-rsMgObcYlEjz8XL_OmlBotQ', 4.30, 'BRAIN', 'Free', '100,000+', 'android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE, android.permission.WAKE_LOCK, android.permission.INTERNET, android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE, android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE, android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS, com.android.vending.BILLING, com.android.vending.CHECK_LICENSE, android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE'),
(860, 'com.whisperarts.tales.repka', 'Turnip Russian folk tale', 'WhisperArts Books', 'Fairy tale about how my grandfather planted a turnip. The turnip has grown so large that only through its close he was able to harvest.<p>Tale can not only read but also listen.<p>Viewing stories through the application, &quot;Fairy tales and storybooks for children&quot;', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.whisperarts.tales.repka', 'http://lh5.ggpht.com/qCix3D857Od-JrgEaDCbwmwIuncKJqNayTf6VZec9kr2pcqepnP-hyKmiFKq49upB1Wh', 4.49, 'BOOKS_AND_REFERENCE', 'Free', '100,000+', ''),
