(886, 'com.thesourcecod.nightcamads', 'Night vision spy cam free', 'thesourcecodemaker', 'Night vision spy cam free<br>Ability to see with very small quantities of light hyper silent spy camera with 3 vision modes night, infra-red, and thermal visions.<br>Take pictures when nobody see you in the Darkness.<br>Make in mind that, this Night vision spy camera doesn&#39;t work in complete darkness.<br>- Night vision spy cam support ARM and  ARM 7 optimized image processing to catch the smallest light  beam .<br>- Capture pictures with different effects - night vision thermal and infrared<br>- Shoot without the shutter sound<br>- Tactical mission timer <br>- Tactical clock<br>- Zoom in and Zoom out<p>If you like camera effects you can check Special Fx Camera Free on https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.cyberfreedom.seffectcamerafree<p>Permissions list:<br>Required to be able to access the camera device - required by the camera<br>Write to external storage - required in order to save the pictures to the SD card<br>Access the flashlight - required by the camera<br>Autofocus - required by the camera<br>Record audio - required by the camera<br>PowerManager WakeLocks - to keep processor from sleeping or screen from dimming<br>Internet -  required in order to display ads<br>Acces_network_state -  required in order to display ads<p>Support the free development<br>This application is for free so please don&#39;t write bad comments if  not work <br>if you find bug or you have questions related with the application  send us email on <a href="mailto:thesourcecodemaker@gmail.com">thesourcecodemaker@gmail.com</a><br>If you like Night Vision Spy Cam therese is paid version without ads on https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.thesourcecod.nightcam<p>In some countries taking picture without permission is a crime so use responsibility !!!<br>Thank you!<br>keywords:<br> Night Vision Spy Cam Camera picture image catch light<br>Night vision spy cam with 3 vision mode